context:
{
  "id": "line:0b5017f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "Noblewoman: How [i]dare[/i] you insinuate such a thing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7d41e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "CDress: I-[p/][s/]I wasn't [i]trying[/i] to insult you![p/][s/] I just—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f223f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "Noblewoman: Enough![p/] If you try to speak with me again,[p/] I'll have you arrested for harassment!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0672572",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "The noblewoman stormed off in a huff.[p/] Celeste just let out an exhausted sigh."
}

{
  "id": "line:09dd0f5",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "Every conversation she'd tried hadn't gone any differently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c90764",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "CDress: ...This isn't working."
}

{
  "id": "line:0241092",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "ADress: ...I don't think asking them like that will be very effective."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea286a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "CDress: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0915fa6",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "ADress: Did you expect anyone here to be truthful with you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09bd69a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "ADress: You're essentially asking them if they engaged in adultery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d65112",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "CDress: Oh...[p/] Hey, Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a62f9a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "ADress: I'm surprised to see you here."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e1afb",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "ADress: ...You're not \"party crashing\", are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06afabc",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "CDress: Of course not![p/][s/] I came here with Ruby and Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:005b3da",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "ADress: ...That honestly just raises more questions,[p/] but I'll take your word for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b09beb",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "CDress: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:039128c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "ADress: I don't know if it's any of my business,[p/] but you should think about whether this is what you truly want."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed216b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "CDress: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:080364e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "ADress: I understand wanting to find out more about yourself,[p/] but getting entangled in the aristocracy will only bring you misery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b197ba",
  "node": "CelesteInvest",
  "text": "ADress: ...I should know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0959fab",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: I just want to know more about where I came from.[p/] It might help me understand all this...[p/] weirdness inside me."
}

{
  "id": "line:025655a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "ADress: ...I don't think you're weird at all.[p/] I quite enjoy your company."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cd53a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: Aw...[p/] Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1e110",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "ADress: I'm sure Mr. Cuthbert feels the same way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a84b3b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: ...Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05415c8",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "ADress: ...Is something wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9528e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] It's just that—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0391356",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: ...Actually,[p/] what do [i]you[/i] think about Tyrion, Aria?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eba783",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "ADress: Well, he's a remarkable attorney.[p/] His deductive skills are incredible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa6ba7",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "ADress: Frankly,[p/] I'm a little envious of his talent.[p/] I'm loath to admit that Ruby Tymora has taught him well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c678dd",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: I meant as a [i]person[/i], Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abd14b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "ADress: ...I only know him in a professional capacity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0906928",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: But don't you notice how much he cares about people?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca940e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "ADress: I suppose he is quite dedicated to his job."
}

{
  "id": "line:0153164",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: But it's not just a job to him.[p/] He [i]really[/i] cares about his clients and helping them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0493c6b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: It doesn't matter how much danger he puts himself in.[p/] It doesn't matter who threatens him."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bff85",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: He just keeps going,[p/] and it's honestly kind of annoying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f860aa",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: He won't back down from [i]anyone[/i],[p/] even the Four Pillars."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b23eb",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: Ever since he indicted Pierce,[p/] [i]someone[/i] has been sending people into Tyrion's home."
}

{
  "id": "line:045524b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: I'm good at my job,[p/] but I'm worried I'm going to slip up one day and let him get seriously hurt."
}

{
  "id": "line:0193943",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "ADress: I am sorry about that.[p/] I wish I could do more to help you with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:073a13b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: It's fine.[p/] It's my responsibility to protect him."
}

{
  "id": "line:046dda8",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "ADress: Have you ever told him how worried you've been?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b92f7",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: ...I don't want to stop him from doing what he's doing,[p/] and I don't think he'd even listen if I did."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e11c8",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: That's what makes him who he is."
}

{
  "id": "line:02da466",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: He's helping a lot of people.[p/] He inspires them, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0067b6f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2",
  "text": "CDress: He's amazing,[p/] and courageous,[p/] and caring,[p/] and sweet,[p/] and—"
}

{
  "id": "line:079c7ec",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "ADress: ...Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d429b5",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "CDress: N-[p/][s/]No... I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0faf77b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "CDress: ...I don't know.[p/] Things have been really weird since Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:051afb6",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "ADress: I've been meaning to ask about that.[p/] Did something happen during Dracogen's trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:011ea85",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "CDress: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f61d4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "CDress: ...We kind of slept together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b26ec3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "ADress: Before marriage?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0824d05",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "CDress: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] Not like [i]that[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a54462",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "CDress: We just slept in the same bed...[p/] and held hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f585b9",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "ADress: Before [i]marriage[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:074f19c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "CDress: I—[p/][p/] ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04abe03",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "ADress: I-[p/][s/]I suppose everyone has different levels of...[p/] libido,[p/] but you shouldn't be so reckless."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b11514",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "CDress: ...Aria,[p/] I'm not going to get pregnant from holding Tyrion's hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5b823",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "ADress: Even so,[p/] I'm not sure what kind of woman you think I am."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a16af3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "ADress: I do not wish to indulge you in your lecherous tales of illicit hand-holding."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fd835",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "CDress: Oh, like [i]you've[/i] never wanted to hold Aster's hand or anything like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa5e4f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "ADress: I would [i]never[/i]![p/][s/] I only have the utmost respect for him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07db1d3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2a",
  "text": "CDress: Come on![p/][s/] I was [i]there[/i] at the Refinery![p/][s/] It's obvious you like him like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a066ad",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "ADress: Please.[p/] You're grossly exaggerating things."
}

{
  "id": "line:0675f80",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "CDress: ...And what if I told you he was standing right behind you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d1307",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "ADress: Do you honestly think I'd fall for such an obvious lie?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4c0c1",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "Aster: What are you falling for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0751263",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "ADress: A-[p/][s/]Ah?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c456f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "Aria's entire body whipped around to face her fiancé.[p/] She almost tripped as she stumbled backwards."
}

{
  "id": "line:033651e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "Her voice started to break into a soft, high-pitched whimper."
}

{
  "id": "line:021fe6f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "ADress: Y-[p/][s/]Y-[p/][s/]Y-[p/][s/]Your highness?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de87b1",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "Celeste noticed how Aria's eyes were frequently darting between the Crown Prince's face and his hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0614242",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "Alaric: Oh.[p/] Hello, Lady Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:063cf47",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "Knight: Your Highness![p/] Please don't run ahead like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:07aa6d4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "After my otherworldly encounter,[p/] I decided to head back to the ballroom and wait for Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d9a58",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "I was able to find a seat somewhere,[p/] and it gave me a chance to think over what had happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f8aa2",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "I'd solved some sort of riddle—[p/]it mentioned illumination and shadows."
}

{
  "id": "line:064e9a1",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "Horus was also the God of Light,[p/] and those earrings were of Luminian origin."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ae3cf",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2b",
  "text": "Did my Eye of Horus react to them?[p/] Lord Haroldson had probably owned those earrings for years,[p/] yet he didn't see anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff742b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "And then there was this—[p/] Actually,[p/] I had no idea [i]what[/i] this \"Divine Edict\" was."
}

{
  "id": "line:074c926",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "Was it a prayer?[p/] A riddle?[p/] An ability?"
}

{
  "id": "line:099e6c5",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "\"A divine invocation to manifest any covenant written in blood and spirit\"..."
}

{
  "id": "line:049730f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "What did that even mean?[p/] It just sounded like some flowery nonsense the Church of Bahamut would say."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab3239",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "If it was some kind of spell,[p/] it was nothing like the Arcane spells I'd seen in Compendiums."
}

{
  "id": "line:062c2a0",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "The descriptions of [i]those[/i] spells were far more straightforward."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6ef66",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "...Ugh.[p/] It just felt like the more I learned about myself,[p/] the more questions I found."
}

{
  "id": "line:076bb22",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "..."
}

{
  "id": "line:002daf0",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "...Scaled Lord,[p/] how long had I been staring at that girl?"
}

{
  "id": "line:096324e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "My eyes just locked onto the first thing across the room,[p/] but it was clear she noticed me looking at her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa9447",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "I quickly looked away,[p/] but as I glanced back,[p/] she tried to flash me a friendly smile."
}

{
  "id": "line:068242e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "She didn't look offended,[p/] which was a relief.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cde917",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "I'd imagine any other noblewoman would use this as an excuse to have me thrown out."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bbac2",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "...Actually,[p/] she seemed to be the only person in the room who wasn't disgusted by my presence."
}

{
  "id": "line:063b379",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "Maybe Celeste was right.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aff293",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "I needed to learn to approach new people,[p/] and fate was giving me an opportunity."
}

{
  "id": "line:06614c2",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "As I walked across the room,[p/] several nobles gave me the side-eye."
}

{
  "id": "line:0894576",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "She was surrounded by several attendants,[p/] who moved to stop me from approaching her."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cca35",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "However,[p/] she waved her hand to dismiss them.[p/] That was a good sign."
}

{
  "id": "line:043b0ac",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2c",
  "text": "Her attendants seemed to disapprove,[p/] but they didn't raise any objections and left quietly."
}

{
  "id": "line:00636ba",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "On a closer look,[p/] she seemed to be a noble of some renown,[p/] but she seemed to exhibit a modesty that most aristocrats lacked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc9d52",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "She was actually quite beautiful,[p/] not as beautiful as Celeste,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5a516",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "...Ugh,[p/] what was I thinking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01390fa",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "I shouldn't be objectifying them like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd6364",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "I needed to keep my thoughts clearer.[p/] I couldn't just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0210ac2",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "I realized I was just standing in front of her,[p/] silently having this conversation with myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:041751a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "She looked confused.[p/] I needed to say something.[p/] Uh...[p/] How [i]did[/i] normal people talk?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07adee4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Should I say a formal greeting,[p/] or would that just come off as pretentious?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0275743",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Maybe I should say something more casual,[p/] like Celeste would."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb3361",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "I could make some kind of observation to connect with her somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c2b73",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Agh![p/][s/] Come on, Tyrion![p/][s/] Just say something!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ad454",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hey, my fellow blonde.[p/][s/] What's—[p/] What's going on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b0f0e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "...This memory would haunt me for the rest of my life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0607789",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Laefe: Um...[p/] Hello."
}

{
  "id": "line:0343ec3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "I cleared my throat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f53473",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I-[p/][s/]I'm sorry if I was staring...[p/] I was just...[p/] daydreaming, I guess."
}

{
  "id": "line:08dbfd6",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Laefe: Oh,[p/] that's okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0701a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wasn't staring at you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a657e4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Tyrion: Er—[p/][s/] That's not to say,[p/][s/] that I [i]wouldn't[/i] intentionally stare at you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1e5d0",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Laefe: Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dee014",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Tyrion, what the hell are you saying?![p/][s/] She's going to think you're a psychopath!"
}

{
  "id": "line:071b127",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Recalibrate![p/][s/] Change the subject!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb40ef",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Social interactions occurred for the sake of engaging individuals in activities!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0541558",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "What activity would someone do at the Lords' Ball?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03914fd",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Would you like to dance?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0458780",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Tyrion![p/][s/] You don't know how to dance!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0001bcd",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_2d",
  "text": "Laefe: ...Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cab441",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "CDress: Hey, Aster.[p/] What do you think of Aria's dress?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e78596",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "Aster: It suits you quite well, Aria.[p/] You look lovely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6452b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "ADress: [i]*squeak*[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f81f6b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "Alaric: ...Gross."
}

{
  "id": "line:0473322",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "Aster: But I must say, Ms. McCoy.[p/] I'm surprised to see you here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f93d70",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "Aster: How did you get an invite to the Lords' Ball?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0982bd3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "CDress: I'm just tagging along for one of Ruby's jobs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f441ae",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "Aster: Ah,[p/] that explains why Mr. Cuthbert is here as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:035e214",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "CDress: Oh,[p/] Tyrion's back?[p/] Where is he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0adced5",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "Her eyes scanned the ballroom until she found Tyrion..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5e4a3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "CDress: ...Who the hell is that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0354608",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "Aster: Oh,[p/] I believe that's Lady Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:087fc0b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "Aster: That's strange.[p/] She usually rebukes most men who approach her."
}

{
  "id": "line:06edb0b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "CDress: Oh, she does, does she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f60e5",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "CDress: I guess Tyrion's special for some reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bf8bb",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "CDress: ...He never told me he could dance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b314c3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "They were stumbling along the dance floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0037bec",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "The Crown Prince watched as Tyrion stepped on Lady Frega's toes several times."
}

{
  "id": "line:080abb3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "Aster: ...I don't think he actually can."
}

{
  "id": "line:0033bf0",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "CDress: What would a Frega want with Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07bb3cf",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "CDress: She's up to something..."
}

{
  "id": "line:070e04e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "CDress: Aria,[p/] what do you know about her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb85a0",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "ADress: Hraaaaaaaaah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc5a1b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "Aria was still staring blankly at the Crown Prince."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d58c7",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "It looked like she was running through several calculations in her head,[p/] but failing to arrive at anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:01450e9",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3",
  "text": "CDress: Ugh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdbd3e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Another misstep caused me to step on her foot."
}

{
  "id": "line:033f3ef",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Tyrion: I am [i]so[/i] sorry.[p/] I don't do this a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:048500b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "...Or at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a94e0c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Laefe: I-[p/][s/]It's okay![p/][s/] At least,[p/] you're—"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ad215",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "She winced in pain as I accidentally kicked her foot again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db8342",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "It felt like I was slowly chipping away at that considerate smile on her face."
}

{
  "id": "line:041594c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Laefe: Perhaps you should follow [i]my[/i] lead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b02aa3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "I carefully looked downwards,[p/] watching to make sure I didn't accidentally parry her foot with mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fd1ad",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "It honestly made it easier.[p/] Looking at her face presented its own distraction."
}

{
  "id": "line:014ee36",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm Tyrion, by the way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0540c07",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Laefe: Yes,[p/] I'm aware.[p/] You've been in the paper a lot recently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3a131",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8b957",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm Laefe...[p/] of House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:002e33a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Oh!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c35da",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Of all the people I could have approached,[p/] I chose someone from one of the Four Pillars Families..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe5caf",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "...But she didn't seem too bothered.[p/] Why would she agree to dance with me if she knew who I was?"
}

{
  "id": "line:047659e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Laefe: ...I'm sorry for not bringing it up sooner."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fee448",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Laefe: I can imagine you wouldn't want to associate with someone like me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa8b76",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] It's just that—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07111dc",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Tyrion: I had a run-in with your sister a few months ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:069e9c4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't think she cares for me that much."
}

{
  "id": "line:0700509",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Laefe: ...Then it sounds like we have something in common."
}

{
  "id": "line:0625041",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3a",
  "text": "Laefe: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af4834",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "Before she could finish that thought,[p/] she suddenly froze."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a10094",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "I almost tripped as I avoided stepping on her foot again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0359910",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "She was staring wide-eyed at something behind me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4dbcc",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "Her breathing was quickening,[p/] and her hand began to squeeze my shoulder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcdfdd",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "I turned to look and saw Beatrice storming through the ballroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f0071",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "Laefe: Is that—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:076a548",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "Laefe: I-[p/][s/]I'm terribly sorry![p/][s/] I have to go!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dabf8b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "Without another word,[p/] she quickly left,[p/] hurrying after Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bc550",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "Did the two of them know each other?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9da5a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "CDress: ...Ah,[p/] did you get snubbed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4ec87",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, thank the Scaled Lord—[p/]someone I actually know."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a6e95",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "CDress: ...So?[p/][s/] Who was that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c04dbf",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "She wore her usual approachable smile,[p/] but I could've sworn something about her tone was louder than usual."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed9209",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was...[p/] trying to talk to people.[p/] Isn't that what you told me to do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00480c8",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "CDress: Yeah,[p/] but I didn't mean that you should shoot your shot with a Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f40978",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "CDress: You're going to tell me how you pulled [i]that[/i] off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca6161",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do I have to?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3ecbb",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "CDress: Yes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7d168",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "CDress: Sit down.[p/] I snuck you some bread rolls from the buffet."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f095e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh,[p/][s/] have you tried them?![p/][s/] They're amazing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa72af",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_3b",
  "text": "CDress: Yeah,[p/] yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7ecb4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Aster: It really [i]is[/i] you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df7392",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Aster: Where have you been all this time, Beatrice?![p/][s/] We've been so worried about you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05ac295",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07dc879",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "ADress: I-[p/][s/]It appears you two have much to talk about.[p/] I'll be taking my leave."
}

{
  "id": "line:0970615",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d5720",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: I've known for a while,[p/] but I still can't believe it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0297aaf",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: You're [i]actually[/i] marrying her, aren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fca158",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Aster: ...You didn't leave me much choice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1cea4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Aster: As the future king of Wyverngarde,[p/] I have responsibilities."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c46eb",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Aster: ...I doubt [i]you[/i] would know anything about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa6724",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: Hmph...[p/] When did [i]you[/i] suddenly start caring so much about \"responsibility\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08db834",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Aster: I've always done what I had to for the people of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1a3ad",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] ...I barely even recognize you anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:09907d6",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Aster: I'd certainly hope so,[p/] considering what I was like back then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0084d78",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: I've always done what was necessary to stay in control,[p/] but what you're doing to Aria...[p/] It's—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0653904",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Aster: I know,[p/] but she's willing to put aside her disdain of me for the sake of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:044796f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: Nine hells,[p/] do you seriously still not—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0612a31",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Never mind.[p/] It seems that you're just as much of an oaf as you were before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c92c64",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Aster: And your words still have such a unique way of cutting into me like a knife."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a2eab",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Aster: I oddly missed that."
}

{
  "id": "line:02846b6",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_4",
  "text": "Beatrice just scoffed at that."
}

{
  "id": "line:029c6d6",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "CDress: Oh my god,[p/] please say it again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3ccd0",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I really don't want to."
}

{
  "id": "line:06874a4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "CDress: Come on![p/][s/] The look on your face gets better each time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abe81b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]*sigh*[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:010caa6",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Hey, my fellow blonde.[p/] What's going on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:042e4d6",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "Celeste just started snickering to herself again."
}

{
  "id": "line:00adacf",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "She started slamming her fist on the table,[p/] drawing some looks from the aristocrats nearby."
}

{
  "id": "line:0302a15",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "CDress: I can't believe it."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d2520",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "CDress: I guess any line will work when it comes from you."
}

{
  "id": "line:092185c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm just glad it's over...[p/] I looked like an idiot out there."
}

{
  "id": "line:040fbaa",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "CDress: Hey,[p/] it's not over yet.[p/] You owe me a dance."
}

{
  "id": "line:067dd91",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e75b7f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "CDress: Don't be like that.[p/] How often do we get to go to a party like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c18d02",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dad67b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_5",
  "text": "Before I had a chance to object,[p/] she grabbed my hand and started dragging me to the middle of the dance floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0471353",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: C-[p/][s/]Celeste![p/][s/] People are staring at us..."
}

{
  "id": "line:065d9c8",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "CDress: Who cares?[p/] They're nobles."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1a951",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "CDress: They're going to hate us no matter what we do."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d2a98",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "She took hold of my other hand and pulled me into a waltz."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de1e32",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] I have no idea what I'm doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:059f6ac",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "CDress: It's easy.[p/] Just stop being so awkward about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d936f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "That was easy for her to say..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a8562",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Alright,[p/] can you at least tell me what to do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00cb661",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "CDress: Well, first..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eeaa11",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "CDress: You need to be closer to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0548a32",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "With one swift motion,[p/] she pulled my body closer to hers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc3350",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ed074",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I don't remember being this close when I was dancing with Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3b9ec",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "CDress: Yeah?[p/] Well,[p/] I'm not Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af734c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "CDress: Watch where I'm going and follow my lead."
}

{
  "id": "line:076a737",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Y-[p/][s/]You seem to know a lot about these things."
}

{
  "id": "line:065dcf9",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "CDress: I had to do a lot of networking when I was a mercenary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c04404",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "CDress: Do you know how many times I had to charm a merchant into hiring me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09fa5fd",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5acbb",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "I carefully watched the movements of her feet and tried to match them."
}

{
  "id": "line:096f5c5",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "After a while,[p/] we both fell into a gentle rhythm."
}

{
  "id": "line:01553d4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "I accidentally stepped on her foot,[p/] but she didn't seem to react at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb1df9",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "Was she being polite,[p/] or did she genuinely not feel any pain?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c8c79",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "CDress: ...You're getting it,[p/] but don't focus so much on where your feet are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e695d9",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "CDress: Just look at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1c689",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1a48f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "CDress: Come on, look up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af21cb",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "I finally looked up at her,[p/] and she smiled back at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0184ec8",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "It was embarrassing being this close,[p/] but every time I avoided her eyes,[p/] I found myself being drawn back into them."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cbc89",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "CDress: Ah, [i]there[/i] he is![p/] The [i]infamous[/i] Tyrion Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:069c61c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "CDress: He never turns away from challenging a noble,[p/] but he can't dance a step to save his life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1ac57",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "I was starting to become lightheaded for some reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:046c075",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "Was I sweating too much?[p/][s/] I really hoped it wasn't visible."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a6289",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "Every part of my body was tense,[p/] but I didn't want to break away from her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf9421",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_7",
  "text": "There was a comforting warmth behind all this.[p/] Things were always different with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de9fa6",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "I let myself relax a bit more and continued matching her movements."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f80df",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "CDress: See?[p/] There you go."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c01cc",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "CDress: But..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c1078",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce500a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "CDress: You know the man is supposed to lead, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac3367",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Maybe I don't subscribe to gender stereotypes."
}

{
  "id": "line:089476d",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "CDress: [i]Or[/i] maybe you just suck at this."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bbe43",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "...I'd forgotten what it was like to let go like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd3e09",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "It always felt like there was something to prepare for—[p/]a client that needed saving,[p/] a killer that needed catching."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc4074",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "I'd been so caught up in trying to learn more about the Eye of Horus that I was ignoring other thoughts I'd been having."
}

{
  "id": "line:046b186",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c0a5a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "I took a deep breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c7029",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can we talk about what happened in Aurinax...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdb1d4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "CDress: Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b7125",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "I felt her arm tense around my shoulder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db1eb1",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It was weird, wasn't it?[p/] Us sleeping together?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7998c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Or—[p/][s/]I mean—[p/][s/] I know we didn't \"sleep\" together,[p/][s/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:047b582",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "I was nailing this.[p/] I was absolutely nailing this."
}

{
  "id": "line:00be046",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] I get it...[p/] It wasn't exactly professional."
}

{
  "id": "line:043e0b5",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes![p/][s/] [i]Exactly[/i]![p/][s/] It was very unprofessional of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:031bf7f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if it was an accident,[p/] I'm worried that I overstepped my boundaries as your employer."
}

{
  "id": "line:07abbce",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: Well,[p/] [i]Ruby's[/i] my employer.[p/] You're different."
}

{
  "id": "line:0651cd8",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Different...?[p/] How?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06694be",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/][s/] Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec57a9",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "She seemed to think about it for a moment before she sighed to herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8521d",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: ...I guess you're the only person who doesn't treat me like a monster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce71a4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Because you're a mage?"
}

{
  "id": "line:022369a",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: Come on, Tyrion...[p/] You've seen me fight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bff9d7",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: I know you're just being polite about it,[p/] but it's off-putting, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:084e3f5",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "Tyrion: It really isn't.[p/] What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2dddb",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: Really?[p/] It doesn't freak you out whenever I beat up a crowd of thugs in an alleyway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b572da",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: Or how about last night when I ragdolled that thief trying to break into your house?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0046dea",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I was honestly more impressed by that than anything else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e425cb",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: Stop being nice about it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0d3a5",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: I [i]know[/i] it's not normal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e72657",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: ...Something inside me really enjoys fighting.[p/] I love it,[p/] but I also hate it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9db2d",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: Every time someone's seen me fight,[p/] they start looking at me like I'm some kind of bloodthirsty freak."
}

{
  "id": "line:064338c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8a",
  "text": "CDress: Even my parents used to look at me like that sometimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d155f3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm really sorry if [i]I've[/i] ever looked at you like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0097954",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "CDress: That's the worst part![p/] You haven't."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dae57",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "CDress: I never know what you're really thinking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b99590",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "CDress: You always charge headfirst into danger without a second thought."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ddfef",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "CDress: This whole kingdom is rotting with corruption.[p/] I don't get how you can be so hopeful and optimistic all the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b04c05",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "CDress: I really admire you for that,[p/] but sometimes it feels too good to be true."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fe453",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "CDress: It makes me wonder what's really going on inside your head."
}

{
  "id": "line:0253465",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're really passionate about protecting the people you care about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e16ff6",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: When you fight,[p/] I see someone who cares deeply."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcdda2",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: You love the people around you,[p/] so much so that you're driven to stop anyone who threatens them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0719dd8",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: You make it all look so effortless.[p/] I don't think I've ever met anyone as strong as you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c22c8f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: I thought you were always proud of that.[p/] It's one of the things I've always admired about you."
}

{
  "id": "line:069f6d4",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "I saw a smile curl on her lips as her face became flushed."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ae02e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: You know the truth about me.[p/] I'm not some idealistic hero."
}

{
  "id": "line:04681d3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm just a dumb traumatized kid who thinks he can save everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:09dd4a1",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "We both stayed silent for a while,[p/] simply moving to the beat of the music."
}

{
  "id": "line:063e3d7",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "CDress: ...Tyrion,[p/] I didn't mind being unprofessional with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a6407",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/][s/] That's good."
}

{
  "id": "line:0156d0d",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "CDress: But only if you were okay with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fb8ce",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "CDress: ...[i]Would[/i] you be okay with things like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:015fdec",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh...[p/] Uh—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddc1c3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "I still wasn't certain about what she meant,[p/][p/] or why she suddenly switched to the present tense."
}

{
  "id": "line:06710d3",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Was she trying to imply that she also wanted to—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09bc46c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "...No,[p/] I couldn't rush forward before I had more evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0385a14",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "I needed to be tactful...[p/] and vague."
}

{
  "id": "line:0196298",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well,[p/][s/] I appreciate some level of professionalism in my work,[p/][s/] but with you—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0913eab",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Er—[p/][s/] I mean—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0779c70",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Or that is to say,[p/][s/] that I'd like to attempt—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0984a5e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Agh![p/][s/] That's not to say that I don't not want to only be professional with you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcde2e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "CDress: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0344acd",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Scaled Lord,[p/][s/] I just needed to say what I wanted to say!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f14384",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I've never felt this way about someone before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0765f8f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't know how to navigate this,[p/] but I want to—[p/] If you're okay with it—"
}

{
  "id": "line:00266f2",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Um...[p/][s/] Could we try—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:036325e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "I suddenly heard the footfalls of several knights behind me."
}

{
  "id": "line:07829ef",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Celeste's eyes widened.[p/] Her lips pursed."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cdbdf",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Confused,[p/] I began to turn my head to see what the commotion was,[p/] but she just grabbed me by the chin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4d0d2",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "CDress: Hey,[p/] why don't you finish that thought first?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6b06b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Orym: Beatrice Frega!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0769b7b",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Did he just say \"Beatrice [i]Frega[/i]\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0931db7",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[s/][p/]Oh...[p/][s/] Um...[p/][s/] I think something's happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed01ad",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "CDress: Nope![p/][s/] It's just Orym!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02558f7",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "CDress: Turns out he's just an absolute monster on the dance floor!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e5bfe",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Well,[p/] [i]that[/i] just made me want to look more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2b766",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Orym: By the authority of the Wyverngarde crown,[p/][s/] you’re under arrest!"
}

{
  "id": "line:038e706",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "CDress: Seriously?![p/][s/] Now?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a92ab",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...W-[p/][s/]We should go see what's happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdec17",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_8c",
  "text": "CDress: Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0465129",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Aster: You are [i]completely[/i] out of line, Commander!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cefce",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Aster: I thought I told you to stand down!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcc250",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Alaric: Do you not recognize who you're speaking to?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d46e1f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Alaric: Let go of Lady Frega!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f47abd",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Orym: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] I can't really do that, Your Highnesses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb5806",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "As we approached Beatrice,[p/] we saw the two princes standing between the Inquisition and Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bb791",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Highness,[p/] what's going on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a69d84",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "The Crown Prince scanned the room.[p/] Everyone's eyes were on him."
}

{
  "id": "line:01dd124",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "He leaned towards me and spoke in a hushed whisper."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f585db",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Aster: It's William Frega.[p/] He was found murdered in his study."
}

{
  "id": "line:096e96c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Aster: And these cretins think that [i]Beatrice[/i] is behind it somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ea5a7",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Orym: S-[p/][s/]Sorry, Your Highness,[p/] but my orders come straight from Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe1fbe",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Alaric: Lady Steelwind sent you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e491c8",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Beatrice cursed under her breath and clapped her hands together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c892d5",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Beatrice: I should go with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0805a54",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Alaric: What?![p/][s/] No!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ec68e",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_9",
  "text": "Aster: My brother is right![p/] They have no right to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f39744",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Beatrice: We're causing a scene,[p/] and I don't want to cause friction between you and Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:038793c",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Beatrice: She's always been meticulous.[p/] I'm sure she's just being careful..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0104f75",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Beatrice: I'm sure I'll be exonerated once they've thoroughly investigated what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:025aab2",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Aster: ...Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:01707f8",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Alaric: What?![p/][s/] You can't just let them take her away!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0759334",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Aster: ...Brother.[p/] She's correct.[p/] It is not our place to interfere with the laws of our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ebca1",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Alaric: B-[p/][s/]But—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f91d53",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Aster: ...[i]However[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:082e035",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Orym: ...Y-[p/][s/]Yes, Your Highness?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0c016",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Aster: Ms. Beatrice is blind.[p/] One of your knights will need to escort her."
}

{
  "id": "line:041b7db",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Orym: ...She's what?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d686d",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Orym: Uh...[p/] Anyways,[p/] we're going to need to take you to a holding cell, lady."
}

{
  "id": "line:075a2ae",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Orym: One of you should stay with her and guide her through—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e07b92",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Beatrice: Please.[p/] I'm not a child."
}

{
  "id": "line:016ac00",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Beatrice walked past the knights and toward the foyer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9b058",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "It appeared that she already knew her way out."
}

{
  "id": "line:051f934",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Orym: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fee5f",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Shouldn't you all be following her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:077887d",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "Orym: R-[p/][s/]Right![p/][s/] Inquisition,[p/][s/] move out!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01cd565",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "It seemed to be just my luck that a night like this would end in a murder..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04eeb42",
  "node": "CelesteInvest_10",
  "text": "What the hell was going on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb0789",
  "node": "Examine_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Chandalier"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6af61",
  "node": "Examine_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: These chandeliers look fancy enough to be worth a small fortune."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f94d9",
  "node": "Examine_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: The Banking Houses are loaded, aren't they?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a58cb",
  "node": "Examine_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Flowers"
}

{
  "id": "line:0575603",
  "node": "Examine_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Each of these tables has a centerpiece of flowers on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01de765",
  "node": "Examine_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: To be honest,[p/] it kind of looks tacky."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b80ac4",
  "node": "Examine_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure their notion of aesthetics must fly over the heads of peasants like us..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0787bbc",
  "node": "Examine_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Back"
}

{
  "id": "line:00633af",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: The Investigation"
}

{
  "id": "line:0086fe4",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cc622",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you worried about your missing sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce01aa",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: N-[p/][s/]No!"
}

{
  "id": "line:043f0d7",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, yes.[p/] I [i]am[/i] worried."
}

{
  "id": "line:0454fc1",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: But I'm sure it'll turn up eventually."
}

{
  "id": "line:042196f",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "She was trying her best to hide how worried she was.[p/] I knew how important her sword was to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad9ca1",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Hopefully,[p/] it would turn up somewhere in the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:020a677",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: A murder in a locked room.[p/] It's like something out of a mystery novel."
}

{
  "id": "line:055e7d6",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The murderer must have used something to break into the Duke's study,[p/] but what?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0472f1b",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: It should be obvious, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:085b17d",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: They [i]had[/i] to have used the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb5d69",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That [i]is[/i] the most obvious answer."
}

{
  "id": "line:03877d0",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Something about that seemed off, though..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03af77b",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Laefe and Jan's testimonies don't give us much to go on."
}

{
  "id": "line:064e5a8",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: We still have no idea who murdered the Duke [i]or[/i] who stole the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d068b6",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] But I can't help but feel like all of these facts fit together somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fe32d",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, at least we were able to find Crimson Lotus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b66dda",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "But honestly,[p/] that just raised even more questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7f9a7",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: William Frega was loaded.[p/] It sounds like a [i]bunch[/i] of people had a reason to murder him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0446f65",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah,[p/] and we still don't have any evidence that incriminates [i]any[/i] of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:03af0d3",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "But this thread [i]had[/i] to lead somewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:054a368",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Duke was planning to disinherit a lot of people that night..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0510a57",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: But he died [i]before[/i] his revised will was submitted."
}

{
  "id": "line:06384ef",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Does that mean they'll just use his old will?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02fdb4c",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It depends on the last instructions he gave to his attorney,[p/] but it's very likely that's what will happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0388fbb",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "That would've been a really strong motive for anyone to murder him."
}

{
  "id": "line:061c9da",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Next Lead"
}

{
  "id": "line:080ba9c",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Where should we go next?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb51e7",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The body was supposedly found in the Duke's study on the top floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfb1f4",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should probably start our investigation there."
}

{
  "id": "line:057abcf",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We have a lot of leads to follow up on."
}

{
  "id": "line:096b1dd",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Jan Hughes was apparently here last night,[p/] and he supposedly heard an altercation between William and the murderer."
}

{
  "id": "line:080a197",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And Laefe Frega was the last person to see the Duke alive before the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cac85",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: They both might have information we can use."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e85031",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have a feeling that Laefe is hiding something,[p/] but I don't have the evidence to confront her yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4f1b9",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Supposedly,[p/] Lord von Sanctus had a decent motive to murder the Duke."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f66c3",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I doubt he [i]actually[/i] did it.[p/] But he might be able to point us in the right direction."
}

{
  "id": "line:031b1d7",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "If you can even get him to cooperate, that is..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b2bd0",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Von Sanctus was surprisingly helpful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d49290",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should talk to Laefe again."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c13b7",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We can use the new information we've gained to probe her."
}

{
  "id": "line:03152bd",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And there's also Haroldson..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a0689",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if he's not involved in this,[p/] I'd like to ask him a few more questions about the gallery's security."
}

{
  "id": "line:0305962",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That might help us figure out how the Sword of Spell Eating was stolen."
}

{
  "id": "line:09723e7",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's still one last person we should speak with:[p/] Harold Haroldson."
}

{
  "id": "line:0538dd9",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I still refuse to believe [i]that's[/i] his actual name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0828fb8",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: He would have the most details about the Sword of Spell Eating.[p/] And we would know about the abjuration wards that [i]should[/i] have protected it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bb7e6",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: There's also his inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:02aaf30",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Right.[p/] You don't want to suspect him,[p/] but you need to consider every possibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:089f014",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We've found a lot of information.[p/] I'm sure Ms. Tymora will appreciate knowing about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d772d6",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's probably at the Barracks with Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:067798b",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'll probably find her there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0111d",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: BACK"
}

{
  "id": "line:0340c57",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Runestone"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb42dc",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Ah,[p/] there it is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3cc7c",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thanks for fixing my Runestone.[p/] I was worried I'd have to buy a replacement."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bbbcb",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Honestly,[p/] artificery is kind of fun.[p/] I kind of want to make something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a7cbb",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you want to learn how to make small machines?"
}

{
  "id": "line:014158b",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I was thinking more of a weapon."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cc006",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Be careful.[p/] Making magic weapons can be iffy with the Kingdom's Laws."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e04f94",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, it's a good thing I have a pretty [i]good[/i] lawyer."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ce205",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion"
}

{
  "id": "line:055548f",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't believe Tyrion Cuthbert doesn't know how to do a simple waltz."
}

{
  "id": "line:09635e1",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...There was never any need for me to learn how to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef834b",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: How about it?[p/] Do you want to try dancing again?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eeff9f",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We're technically on a job right now.[p/] What will Aster say if he sees us goofing off?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07abbd2",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Celeste"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbcb4a",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've never danced before.[p/] It was embarrassing to do that in front of so many people."
}

{
  "id": "line:052a749",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Sorry...[p/] I kind of pulled you into that, didn't I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ff3ee",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I didn't mind it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05101f3",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "There was also something peaceful about it.[p/] It made everything else disappear from the world."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e3156",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Swaying with her at such a gentle rhythm—[p/]the feeling of her hand clasped within mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b420a",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": ":...And [i]that[/i] just reminded me of that night in Aurinax:[p/] something that would've been VERY distracting if I started thinking about it again!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0236716",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I think I wouldn't mind doing something like that regularly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0385bae",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are probably some books I could read about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0099e16",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste chuckled to herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a9cde",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Or I could just teach you, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:020b0f4",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I-[p/][s/]I suppose that could work too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc6107",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Aria"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc4d72",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I actually saw Aria during the ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b60002",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, I must've just missed her.[p/] I guess every noble in the kingdom was here last night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c611f4",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Does that mean her father was here too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0560b6b",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Hopefully,[p/] we don't run into him."
}

{
  "id": "line:04161d2",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Aster"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e83f1d",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I never would have imagined that we'd be on good terms with the Crown Prince of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f03244",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm surprised you even considered trusting him.[p/] I'd thought you would hate anyone from the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6a0c0",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I have an insight when it comes to gauging people's sincerity."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c9540",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Jan"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b169a9",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm glad Jan and the twins were able to find jobs after the Nightgrave case."
}

{
  "id": "line:03483b5",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I still feel a little bit guilty about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d935ee",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on.[p/] You [i]had[/i] to indict Redmond to save Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:014ea07",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know...[p/] I just wish I'd done more."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d9c4b",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Wallace"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e6bca",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I never expected to see Wallace with Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f442fb",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wonder why she'd choose him of all people as her aide?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df31b1",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Maybe she's trying to copy us.[p/] An attorney and a mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbfe2d",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But she can already cast [b]Detect Magic[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3d0a8",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on![p/] That's not the [i]only[/i] thing I do!"
}

{
  "id": "line:040d616",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice|Beatrice's Inheritance 0|Beatrice's Blindness"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a82447",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Beatrice has been through a lot, hasn't she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8d206",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...From what we've heard about her father's cold behavior,[p/] I don't blame her for leaving."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6c46e",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: She probably wanted to leave her old life behind."
}

{
  "id": "line:049109c",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "The two of us were similar in that regard..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aabb42",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: William|Autopsy Report: William Frega"
}

{
  "id": "line:038ee21",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: William Frega doesn't sound like the best person, does he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0894180",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Many people in Wyverngarde live in poverty...[p/] Yet [i]he's[/i] able to afford this extravagant house."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c3780",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You don't live a life like this without hoarding wealth for yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:09caa06",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbb0a8",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But like anyone else,[p/] even [i]he[/i] deserves justice for his death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1a4c5",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Lucio"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb0ad6",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you still mad at Lord Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e1bb4",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...How could I not?[p/] He could have seriously hurt you."
}

{
  "id": "line:037c818",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: With his reputation,[p/] we might want to stay away from him."
}

{
  "id": "line:056c003",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Laefe"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a3da0",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: \"...Hey, my fellow blonde.[p/][s/] What's—[p/] What's going on?\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6d69a",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You're never going to let me live that down, are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:013f2bd",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: You sounded like an Arcane Construct trying to pose as a human."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adf6c3",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was nervous, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff5107",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Oh, you were nervous?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0185edf",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Look,[p/] I was just as nervous when I first met you."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e2692",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait,[p/] you were nervous when you met me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a61a0",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e2394",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "...Why would I say that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6be00",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Miriam"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c17eb",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Miriam seems different now.[p/] She's a lot less...[p/] arrogant."
}

{
  "id": "line:030950a",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: She must be going through a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cd640",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: She unexpectedly lost her father [i]and[/i] her long-lost sister is being charged with murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f241a",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Harold"
}

{
  "id": "line:05929fc",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: \"Harold Haroldson\" [i]has[/i] to be some kind of stage name, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d9fe9",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Who would actually name their child that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:076cc36",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think you're getting way too hung up on his name..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfdadd",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Like...[p/] Does [i]he[/i] have children?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0243cbf",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Are they [i]also[/i] named Harold?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0037b6b",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...He has a pet monkey."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef3b94",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: You're just making things up now."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d0158",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Sword of Spell Eating|Sword of Spell Eating 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab5028",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: A sword forged by a demon.[p/] Do you think the legends are true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05efd9d",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3fac3",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh,[p/] sorry.[p/] I just got a little distracted."
}

{
  "id": "line:039f6b9",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Missing Sword"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5d433",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Celeste's Sword"
}

{
  "id": "line:037abc7",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm glad we found Crimson Lotus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da055b",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is that the name of your sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0085b17",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Yep!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c80b6f",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "I was glad she was in better spirits,[p/] but how did her sword end up under Beatrice's bed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5d9e4",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Liafal's Engagement"
}

{
  "id": "line:041850e",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I could never imagine marrying someone for diplomatic reasons..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fc568",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: It just sounds so sad."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaab74",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] Although,[p/] I suppose Prosecutor Steelwind lucked out in that regard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc62cd",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't believe Aster [i]still[/i] thinks she hates him."
}

{
  "id": "line:02aed07",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know...[p/] I don't understand how anyone could be [i]that[/i] oblivious to someone else's feelings."
}

{
  "id": "line:003fd42",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] Sounds [i]pretty[/i] annoying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcd635",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Tracker"
}

{
  "id": "line:058ac76",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I've never really liked dogs..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf6140",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?![p/][s/] How could you [i]say[/i] that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d85eb",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you telling me that you prefer Violetta over Tracker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a286ac",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, yeah.[p/] Cats are [i]so[/i] much better than dogs."
}

{
  "id": "line:09404dc",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's like I don't even know who you are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0226367",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Cats are fickle and will lash out at you for the [i]smallest[/i] things!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b2ff8",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: You have to [s/][i]work[/i] for a cat's affection.[p/] Dogs will worship anyone and everyone who's friendly to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:079def4",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Dogs are loyal companions![p/][s/] No matter what happens,[p/][s/] they'll always stand by your side to protect you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0344cac",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I guess we'll just have to agree to disagree."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d3c47",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Player: Default"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b8671",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about [i]this[/i], Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b7f0c",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Sorry, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ef926",
  "node": "Present_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't think I can help you with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b5644",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't believe they kept us here until noon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de6825",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "The Lords' Ball had already run well into the night,[p/] even [i]before[/i] the murder occurred."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd41fb",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "I wanted nothing more than to catch up on my lost sleep,[p/] but I'd made a promise to the Crown Prince."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a9cbc",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Aster: After her meeting with William,[p/] she was with my brother and me the entire night."
}

{
  "id": "line:082cf7d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Aster: She couldn't have stolen the Sword of Spell Eating [i]and[/i] have murdered her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b892e7",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Of all the people that could have done those two crimes,[p/] why would Steelwind suspect a blind woman?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c54998",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Steelwind was never one to abuse her authority.[p/] There had to be a reason behind the arrest."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ac0d6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Not to mention that the Sword of Spell Eating had been stolen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0552a79",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "After what Harold had said about it,[p/] I was uneasy about it going missing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0551ebe",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Aster: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:050cee5",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Aster: Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] could you defend Beatrice against these awful charges?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0659479",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I doubt that will be necessary."
}

{
  "id": "line:080f251",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Aster: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e55ce",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "CDress: Beatrice is Ruby's client.[p/] I'm sure that she'll be one defending her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0947757",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Aster: Well,[p/] that certainly puts my mind at ease."
}

{
  "id": "line:032d8c7",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0521450",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Aster: I'd like for you to investigate the crime scene for me, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a752e6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?[p/] But we just told you that Ms. Tymora will—"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b9d7b",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Aster: I know,[p/] but Beatrice is a dear friend of mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0065126",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Aster: I'd like every chance for her to be found innocent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e49982",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "She was a \"dear friend\"...?[p/] They must've known each other since she was a Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc70cd",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "But why would Ms. Tymora,[p/] of all people,[p/] represent a member of a Pillar Family?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae5deb",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Laefe also seemed like she hadn't seen Beatrice in a long time.[p/] It was as if she'd spotted a ghost."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bc007",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't believe this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:078f0b0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste returned to the ballroom.[p/] She'd changed back into her normal clothes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcef5f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: The people in the coat room said that they couldn't find my sword!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d02758",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "She'd once told me that it was forged in the Eastern Kingdoms and crafted from the bones of a Purple Worm."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cc914",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "It was potentially very valuable.[p/] Did someone steal it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcd4a5",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let's keep an eye out for it while we look around the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc8c63",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: This might all just be some kind of mix-up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6e0be",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I hope so..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15d42",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Uh...[p/] So..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd6979",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Can we continue what we were talking about before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1c610",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh,[p/] uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a81d8a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Why was I so nervous about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b6a5a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "I just needed to tell her how I felt."
}

{
  "id": "line:00deb9f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "...How [i]did[/i] I feel?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a36c7",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]It might be for the best that we focus on the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:018672d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: His Highness [i]is[/i] counting on us, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:051b7c6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "I was being a coward,[p/] but there was a kernel of truth to what I was saying."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e7062",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...O-[p/][s/]Okay. [h=\"But we [i]will[/i] be|talking about this later.\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a17115",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Let's head to the crime scene.[p/] His Highness said that's where the body was found."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffe190",
  "node": "Examine_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Their notion of aesthetics must fly over the heads of peasants like us."
}

{
  "id": "line:011f757",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Celeste: I just can't wrap my head around it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ee40f",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Celeste: I know he wasn't the best dad,[p/] but I can't believe she actually killed him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bedcb5",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Celeste: And for what?[p/] Wealth and power?"
}

{
  "id": "line:009decc",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's just how the aristocracy works."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d597c8",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even the weakest noble has a large amount of political power."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c85a39",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Celeste: Sometimes I feel lucky that I grew up in Kornhaven."
}

{
  "id": "line:0850320",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "She'd been in a bad mood since we met Lucio Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:01855aa",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Hopefully,[p/] the investigation might help take her mind off of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:073fa40",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "...But I also felt a bit happy that she'd get that angry for my sake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a90815",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Celeste: Why didn't you tell me that you could [i]talk[/i] to animals?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da1192",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: U-[p/][s/]Uh...[p/] Well, you never asked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e31a15",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "I thought about telling her about the Eye of Horus.[p/] She's more than earned my trust."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b667d",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "But I could do that later.[p/] For now,[p/] we needed to focus on the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:05be88c",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: William retreated into his study to draft a new will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d410df",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if it's not valid,[p/] we should try to look for it there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f86586",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It might give us some insight into the headspace he was in that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a62bb",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: We sent the Inquisition to investigate the theft of the Sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b409a0",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe we should check Beatrice's Bedroom to see if they've found anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ca624",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tracker supposedly found the Sword of Spell Eating lying in a hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d4fa4",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: There has to be a reason why it was there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d77f9b",
  "node": "Talk_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we go there,[p/] we might finally find some evidence of how it got there."
}

{
  "id": "line:01787c3",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "We all returned to the ballroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d60ad2",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Celeste: You okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b7bb2",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] I just needed a moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1a11c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "I closed my eyes and took a deep breath.[p/] I still had a job to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:058a11a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: The will reading bought us a few more hours to investigate the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcaad3",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should take advantage of the new information we just learned."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e38bf",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Orym: So...[p/] Where should we start first?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e8569",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Right...[p/] [i]I[/i] was the prosecutor now.[p/] That technically made me his boss for the time being."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e3ebd",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Orym: ...This is weird, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:075d291",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Celeste: Yep."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f3263",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Awkwardness aside,[p/] I've never really led a task force before..."
}

{
  "id": "line:074b250",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What would Steelwind normally do in this situation?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e533a7",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Orym: Well,[p/] she'd normally have us investigate areas of interest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0001182",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] The context of the investigation tends to change after each round of court proceedings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddbd86",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What we're lacking right now is physical evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:085684d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you and the Inquisition search the gallery and Beatrice's room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c75f82",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe you can find evidence of how the Sword of Spell Eating was stolen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4b325",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Orym: Whatever you say, [i]Boss[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0024d86",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Celeste: That covers the Inquisition,[p/] but what are [i]we[/i] going to do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0501637",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Duke's inheritance plays a large role in this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a398ef",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if it's not valid,[p/] we should take a look at the modified will that he was drafting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a13130",
  "node": "Check_Events_Ballroom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It might give us some insight about what he was [i]really[/i] planning to do with his inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bd0b0",
  "node": "Examine_BallroomIntro",
  "text": "Several gold-tinted chandeliers hung from the ceiling of the ballroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0504278",
  "node": "Examine_BallroomIntro",
  "text": "They looked fancy enough to be worth a small fortune."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc5a06",
  "node": "Examine_BallroomIntro",
  "text": "It irked me knowing how much wealth the Duke must have been hoarding to afford all of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d23deb",
  "node": "Examine_BallroomIntro",
  "text": "Each table had a centerpiece of flowers on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0918d10",
  "node": "Examine_BallroomIntro",
  "text": "Most of the seats at the tables were filled.[p/] It didn't look like I'd be able to play here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0d276",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1",
  "text": "I arrived at the dungeon to search for Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c32e7d",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1",
  "text": "She wasn't at Frega Manor.[p/] So she must have been here to discuss the case with Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9876e",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1",
  "text": "...Or at least that's what I thought.[p/] I didn't see her anywhere here, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:026b48d",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1",
  "text": "Eris: I didn't expect to see you here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b5925",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1",
  "text": "Celeste: A-[p/][s/]Ah!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec5d42",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1",
  "text": "Celeste let out a shriek as Eris approached the two of us from behind."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bd8d3",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1",
  "text": "She really had a habit of doing that.[p/] I was starting to wonder if she was doing that on purpose."
}

{
  "id": "line:048b4fc",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Eris?[p/][s/] What are you doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:043b42b",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1",
  "text": "Eris: Ah...[p/] Beatrice is actually an acquaintance of my father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ece114",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1",
  "text": "Eris: He sent me here to help her through this ordeal."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bb808",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "That brought up [i]so[/i] many questions,[p/] but I didn't really have the time to pull on that thread."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e615fa",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "There was less than an hour before the trial began.[p/] I needed to find Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:064de7b",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have you seen Ms. Tymora anywhere?[p/] I need to talk to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:083b336",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Eris: She was just here,[p/] but she left to retrieve some documents from her office."
}

{
  "id": "line:0952f14",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you have any idea when she'll be back?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3f81e",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Eris: She didn't say,[p/] but I can pass a message on to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ee89d",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sorry.[p/] It's related to Beatrice's case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7e757",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Eris: In that case,[p/] why don't you leave a message with Beatrice herself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0102018",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Eris: She [i]is[/i] the defendant in this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c16dcf",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "I felt a little hesitant,[p/] but it [i]was[/i] Beatrice's life on the line."
}

{
  "id": "line:0153a3c",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "If anyone should know about what I'd found,[p/] it's her."
}

{
  "id": "line:085f49a",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay,[p/] let's go find her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7e2c3",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "I followed Eris's lead as she led us to Beatrice's cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0506fec",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Once we found her,[p/] she left the dungeons to give us some privacy."
}

{
  "id": "line:030561c",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "I spent some time going through my findings with Beatrice—[p/]from the list of suspects,[p/] to the possible motives behind the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:090da22",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "I noticed that with each revelation,[p/] she became more uneasy."
}

{
  "id": "line:00df646",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "The idea of someone framing her must have been stressing her out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0731801",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Beatrice: I...[p/] see.[p/] You've certainly been very thorough."
}

{
  "id": "line:0417833",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes,[p/] but I still have no concrete evidence that points to anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc477e",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Hm... [h=\"If he reveals these findings to Prince Aster,|he might suspect something.\" e=\"fa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bdf8c",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Sorry,[p/] I was just thinking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0165bbd",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "And [i]I[/i] was able to catch one of those thoughts."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be5fed",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Beatrice.[p/] I'm sure you're aware that Prince Aster has your best interests at heart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b183d2",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "Beatrice: I know.[p/] Even though we haven't spoken for the last five years,[p/] I still consider him a close friend."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbac38",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then I suppose you have no issue with me sharing these findings with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d95cf5",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Of course not. [h=\"This is bad.|Even [i]he[/i] wouldn't support us if he knew that I was involved.\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c26461",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "What?![p/][s/] She was actually involved in this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0990b0a",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Is something wrong, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b86ae",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "Beatrice was actually behind this?![p/][s/] But how?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bfe29",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "She's completely blind![p/][s/] She couldn't have navigated through the manor [i]and[/i] avoided the guards."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be995b",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "Aria [i]did[/i] say that she was intelligent,[p/] but doing all of this while blind was ludicrous."
}

{
  "id": "line:0633523",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "No...[p/] I must've been taking her thoughts out of context."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f56f92",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Perhaps you should get some rest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0423503",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "I thought very carefully about what to say next."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6f235",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "There was [i]one[/i] way to get a certain answer through the Eye,[p/] but if I was wrong..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc8f42",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Beatrice...[p/] You weren't [i]actually[/i] involved in this, were you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0672af2",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9f598",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Her gaze narrowed in response to my question."
}

{
  "id": "line:053554d",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Once again,[p/] she clapped her hands together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9a5b8",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Do [i]you[/i] suspect me now, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0223f18",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You didn't answer my question, Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e0904",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: As if I'd even need to justify it with a response."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b9839",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: But no, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] I was not responsible for my father's murder. [h=\"I might as well have been...|Legally, I was more of an accomplice.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d39e2",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "\"An accomplice\"...[p/][s/] Someone else was involved in this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1a4ab",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d644a1",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: M-[p/][s/]Ms. Tymora?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb0309",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Ruby: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b831f",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "My mentor seemed to have sensed the mood in the air.[p/] She raised her brow at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:06de28d",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora...[p/] Can I speak with you alone for a second?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d59cfa",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0023bf7",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Ruby: What's wrong?[p/] Is everything okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0209996",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora![p/] Beatrice,[p/] she..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ccd11",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: She actually [i]did[/i] murder William Frega!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09fd87c",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Ms. Tymora's lips pursed.[p/] Her eyes darted around the room to make sure the guards didn't overhear us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfba3c",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Ruby: What are you talking about?[p/] How could you [i]possibly[/i] know that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a67e8e",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I saw it with the Eye of Horus.[p/] She conspired with someone else to orchestrate William Frega's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:09982db",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Ruby: Have you told anyone else about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da9b29",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] It's not as if they'd believe me, anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc843c",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're the only other person who knows about my abilities."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4996a",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Ruby: Okay...[p/] We'll talk about this later."
}

{
  "id": "line:0556fa5",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Ruby: I need to get ready.[p/] The trial starts in half an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:056a0e0",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:022bf77",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're not seriously going to defend her, are you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0027330",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Ruby: Of course I am![p/] I'm her attorney!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0baf6c4",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: But she's guilty![p/][s/] I [i]saw[/i] it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee2118",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Ruby: Look.[p/] At this point,[p/] I don't know [i]what[/i] you saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9e7ed",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Ruby: Do you think I can just abandon a client minutes before a trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0416704",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:00bed0e",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Ruby: It's not for either of us to decide who's guilty and who's not.[p/] [i]Everyone[/i] has a right to an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:078f230",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_5",
  "text": "Ruby: More importantly,[p/] you had no right to use the Eye of Horus on [i]my[/i] client."
}

{
  "id": "line:067b692",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:049a073",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Ruby: I don't have time to argue about this.[p/] We [i]will[/i] be talking about this later."
}

{
  "id": "line:07852b9",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Before I had a chance to respond,[p/] Ms. Tymora walked away."
}

{
  "id": "line:022c7b3",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Celeste had given us some privacy,[p/] but she'd definitely inferred the tone of our conversation."
}

{
  "id": "line:07449f0",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is everything okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0031853",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste...[p/] I think...[p/] Beatrice was actually behind this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d76157",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Celeste: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d87eb",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "I couldn't blame her for not believing me...[p/] It's not as if I could tell her about the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dda421",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Although,[p/] why [i]hadn't[/i] I told her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:096612f",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright,[p/] so what do you want to do now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0429b8d",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Celeste: You wouldn't say something like that if you weren't sure, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:098a281",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "I thought long and hard for a moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5a0aa",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Maybe we don't need to do anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0727ac6",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Celeste: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02073a7",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind is handling the prosecution,[p/] and she's far from being a pushover."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa5fde",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: If Beatrice is truly guilty,[p/] I'll just have to trust her to get the job done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cda817",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Either way,[p/] I don't think we're in any position to get involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf5a6f",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright,[p/] if you say so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dac96c",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_6",
  "text": "It was really none of my business."
}

{
  "id": "line:05da5ae",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_7",
  "text": "I had no stake in this.[p/] I wasn't obligated to do anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:048995f",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_7",
  "text": "I'd done everything I could.[p/] I would just have to leave it in Steelwind's hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:044f758",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_7",
  "text": "It was none of my business."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a7a6b",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "William Frega was a tyrant anyway.[p/] He was a noble who did nothing but steal wealth from the commonfolk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef317b",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "The world was better off without him,[p/] and it's not as if any of this was my responsibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b4ddc",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "Ms. Tymora must have been doing this for a reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fce1f0",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "All I had to do was wait for the trial to run its course so we could put this all behind us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0919b31",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "TyrionP: Your Honor![p/][s/] I'm afraid you can't pass a verdict just yet!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c7b89",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "Judge: M-[p/][s/]Mr. Cuthbert?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9afeb",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "RubyD: ...Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ab95c",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "RubyD: What the hell are you doing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7a765",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "TyrionP: I...[p/] don't know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5167f",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "TyrionP: But what I [i]do[/i] know is that there was a massive contradiction in Miriam Frega's testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0563809",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "...Who was I kidding?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0576783",
  "node": "BeforeTrial1_8",
  "text": "As if I'd ever stand by and do nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:083b6da",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f7b4d",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: The entire room is covered in traces of [b]abjuration[/b] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d782d5",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]Everything[/i] is glowing white."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e522e5",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] That makes sense.[p/] There were several [i]Anti-Magic Fields[/i] covering the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d15460",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Those fields probably left traces of [b]abjuration[/b] everywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6f548",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I won't bother showing you the traces of [b]abjuration[/b] I find while we're here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf0e76",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Bed"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a437c",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a highly extravagant bed.[p/] It looks similar to the one in Miriam's dorm at the Imperial Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e023ea",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Dresser"
}

{
  "id": "line:069d0ae",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a dresser covered in a layer of dust.[p/] It doesn't look like it's been touched in years."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5561a",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ba651",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Table"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a97446",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a table for guests,[p/] but like everything else,[p/] it's extremely dusty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0470725",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Detect Sword"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e44f7",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: There's a trace of [b]transmutation[/b] magic under the bed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8282a",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't see it clearly...[p/] Let me take a closer look."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2211f",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: It's Crimson Lotus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebfac4",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: It's my sword!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02fb959",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddd05b",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "I never knew her sword had a name..."
}

{
  "id": "line:059cf84",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: So [i]this[/i] is where it's been!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ad612",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "But why was it in Beatrice's room...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7ca77",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "She reached out to take it,[p/] but I blocked her hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da7f66",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: This was the room where they found the Sword of Spell Eating..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abecb9",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's likely that the two thefts are related."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b12898",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: But why?[p/] The only thing similar about them is that they're both swords."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccb143",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know,[p/] but this could still be a part of the crime scene.[p/] We shouldn't disturb it."
}

{
  "id": "line:051a407",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: But—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09af427",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll talk to Steelwind.[p/] She can send some knights to guard it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a38c02",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Okay, fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f68a1",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "There was definitely more to this,[p/] but what?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09cbccc",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: What was William doing? (ARGUMENT)"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c7a6b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: What was William doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e2cc9",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I wasn't trying to be difficult,[p/] but I didn't know who I could trust."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7d79a",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Considering the circumstances,[p/] that's perfectly understandable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1ae2b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm not sure why,[p/] but my father was extremely upset that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:009750b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: According to him,[p/] Beatrice had returned,[p/] and in his words,[p/] \"she was even more impudent than before.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:076b065",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did he tell you what their meeting was about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0898ae9",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: He didn't,[p/] and I honestly didn't really care."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aab3db",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I was just so happy that my sister had finally returned."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a5681",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ...My father clearly felt otherwise."
}

{
  "id": "line:08560cc",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Before he entered his study,[p/] he told me that he would be pruning the family tree."
}

{
  "id": "line:055f7c2",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: He said he was going to draft a will to disinherit my sister and several other members of our family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0813b9e",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Has anyone found the draft of this will?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e826eb",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: No.[p/] It was one of the first things I looked for after the investigation began."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e57463",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "The modified will was missing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b6af3",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "I doubted that it would be enforced.[p/] He never got a chance to submit it for probate before he died."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a29132",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "But I couldn't discount the possibility that the murderer destroyed it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c58645",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Does anyone else know about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0682959",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: No one.[p/] I didn't even tell Lady Steelwind when she was questioning me."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a3d45",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Because it would've established a motive for Beatrice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5e67e",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] thank you, Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:00415ee",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ...Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:074a53b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0efb85d",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: My sister isn't a bad person."
}

{
  "id": "line:00aa37e",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: She would never do something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:02567a7",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I know,[p/] but she's in good hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:035ccb0",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ruby Tymora is the one defending her in the trial, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f25d32",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Okay... [h=\"I'm not sure if|that's a good thing or not...\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0452fc2",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: What did you see?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c644ac",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind told us that you were the last person to see William Frega that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:025ed78",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you notice anything unusual about your father's behavior?"
}

{
  "id": "line:060930f",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Well,[p/] he [i]was[/i] extremely upset.[p/] I think Beatrice may have offended him during their meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cb779",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: The servants said that he demanded to be left alone.[p/] He retreated into his study immediately after Beatrice left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa8cba",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I tried to speak with him when the theft was reported,[p/] but he didn't much care about the missing artifact."
}

{
  "id": "line:000182e",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: He told me to leave him alone and let the Kingsguard investigate the Sword. [h=\"He was probably busy|making the changes to his will.\" e=\"s\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d05090",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Now [i]that[/i] was an interesting thought..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03072f4",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...When did you speak with him last?"
}

{
  "id": "line:083781a",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: It was before they activated the lockdown.[p/] It was a little after 1:00 AM that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0754a5e",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And do you have any idea what he was doing in his study?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a62e70",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0331c7f",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] I have no idea."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f7903",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Laefe,[p/] is there something you're not telling us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0957545",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's important for us to know about your father's actions that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:091d2b5",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ...I'm sorry.[p/] I don't know anything else."
}

{
  "id": "line:05943c8",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: My father didn't share much with anyone,[p/] even his own family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3c5ce",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I wish I could be of more help,[p/] but I really don't know anything else. [h=\"I refuse to believe|<i>that's</i> why he was killed.\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbb434",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "She was clearly holding something back."
}

{
  "id": "line:041464f",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "If I could reveal what she's hiding through an ARGUMENT,[p/] she might be more willing to cooperate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af12d4",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "But I would need more information about William and his will first."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d56de2",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice's Room"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b62a9",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: This room is really dusty.[p/] Why hasn't anyone cleaned it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0352b5b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ...I've forbidden the servants from cleaning this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f36518",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Beatrice was—[p/][s/] [i]is[/i] very dear to me,[p/] and I couldn't bear to have her room disturbed after she left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6d64e",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: This room was the only memory I had of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:098647c",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "She must have been holding onto the hope that her sister would return."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9878d",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "That must have been five really long years."
}

{
  "id": "line:0081f3c",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And what about the Sword of Spell Eating?[p/] Do you know how it ended up in this room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a70aad",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I-[p/][s/]I'm not sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e40d64",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Perhaps they knew that the servants were ordered never to enter this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:040e3b5",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: It's even possible someone planted it here to frame Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0972db6",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: William Frega"
}

{
  "id": "line:0621465",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about your father?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf1c20",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: My father was a...[p/] complicated man."
}

{
  "id": "line:0300a49",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: He was a brilliant aristocrat and businessman,[p/] but he was a cold and distant father."
}

{
  "id": "line:020a88f",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I see.[p/] Did he have any enemies?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db6f71",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: As the head of House Frega,[p/] he controlled every banking house in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ae7a8",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: There were many people who resented his wealth and power."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b52c5",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you remember anyone specific?[p/] Perhaps someone that he'd slighted recently?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d240a1",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: There [i]was[/i] Lloyd von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0951351",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...The ruling Lord of Aurinax?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4b13e",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Yes.[p/] I'm sure you remember him.[p/] His reputation plummeted after Dracogen's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4f2e6",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: My father took that as an opportunity to slowly take control of Von Sanctus Industries."
}

{
  "id": "line:0817fb9",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: From what I've heard,[p/] he's been extremely bitter about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:072c9ff",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "With things as tense as they were,[p/] I doubted that he'd get himself involved in [i]another[/i] murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e49ceb",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "But I could never be too sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df2ff5",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...No one spotted a cat walking around during the Lords' Ball, did they?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05de5a8",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: No,[p/] I am certain there weren't any cats present."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15fb6",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "She was oddly confident about that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:061a1d8",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] it sounded like I would have to speak with him and get more details."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a187b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "...But I really doubted that he'd even consider cooperating with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b116e2",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice Frega"
}

{
  "id": "line:0998ca0",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about Beatrice Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06fc1e0",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I heard that she fled the Frega estate five years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0c21d",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Before she left,[p/] Beatrice was one of the most powerful mages I'd ever seen."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d2df6",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: She was...[p/] She [i]is[/i] incredible."
}

{
  "id": "line:015e12b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: At the age of thirteen,[p/] her talent for magic had even eclipsed my father's."
}

{
  "id": "line:012283d",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ...But it was never enough for him."
}

{
  "id": "line:03690a1",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c83153",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Before my mother died,[p/] he desperately wanted a son,[p/] but he only ever had daughters."
}

{
  "id": "line:0896847",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: But Beatrice was just as sharp as he was."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f6ab6",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: She knew which threads to pull to get the results that she wanted,[p/] just like my father."
}

{
  "id": "line:03466a9",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Everyone thought that Beatrice would inevitably become the head of House Frega,[p/] but our family knew the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f00b9",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: No matter how hard Beatrice tried,[p/] my father would never acknowledge her accomplishments."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d10819",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: He was extremely cruel to her.[p/] He constantly belittled her achievements and dismissed anything she said to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a5244",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: And after the accident,[p/] he used her disability as an excuse to take away everything she had built for herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d65925",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: The Accident"
}

{
  "id": "line:061c86b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: If it's not too painful for you,[p/] could you tell me more about Beatrice's accident?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0389b38",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ...Is this even relevant to the investigation?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8565c",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Any small detail could make a difference.[p/] I need to learn everything I can."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5f38a",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm not sure about exactly what happened,[p/] but it was a magical experiment gone wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcd232",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Beatrice was working on a project at the Imperial Academy.[p/] She was trying to create a new spell formula."
}

{
  "id": "line:0405a91",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: We're still not sure what happened,[p/] but there was an adverse magical reaction."
}

{
  "id": "line:056b16a",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ...The resulting explosion seriously injured her and left her completely blind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0403875",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't imagine how she must have taken that."
}

{
  "id": "line:071e55f",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Actually,[p/] she was probably the most unfazed by what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0840c4f",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Even on that hospital bed,[p/] she was still thinking of how to move forward.[p/] She was always calculating like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3c791",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ...But that didn't matter,[p/] my father saw his opportunity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea5797",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: He told me that he was relieving her of her duties so that she could recover."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa3993",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: But I knew the truth.[p/] He was going to take away her political power and social standing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5aaf6",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: He wanted to reduce her to a mere decoration for our home,[p/] just like he'd done to every other woman in our family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0826b8b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And [i]that[/i] must have been why she left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6cb39",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did she contact you during the time that she was missing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e616d3",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: No.[p/] No one had heard from her during that time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c887c5",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: But as much as I was worried for her,[p/] I was also a little happy."
}

{
  "id": "line:08564de",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Unlike Miriam and I,[p/] she had finally broken free from my father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b37a99",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: It's a Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c58e46",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's an [i]Attorney's[/i] Runestone.[p/] It proves that I'm a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:028bf6b",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Yes,[p/] I'm quite familiar with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:054c223",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: They're truly a feat of artificery."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a0f4e",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ...Miriam has one for her studies."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bab09",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: She's always so engrossed in it whenever she visits... [h=\"She never talks to me\" e=\"s\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c08c3c",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I've heard of you.[p/] You're that defense attorney that everyone is talking about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0727f00",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Wow...[p/] I didn't expect you to know who I was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1c1e5",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Yes.[p/] Many nobles are uneasy due to your recent actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba4aa6",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: It's very clear that no one is safe from you."
}

{
  "id": "line:008d6d0",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc1d3d",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice|Beatrice's Inheritance 0"
}

{
  "id": "line:078c47d",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure Beatrice's return must have been surprising for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0794b7c",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: It is.[p/] To be honest,[p/] I've been hoping for years that she'd finally return."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d94bef",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: But now that she has,[p/] she's just gotten pulled into another one of our family's messes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcba6d",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What is your relationship like with Miriam?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f674f",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: My youngest sister?[p/] I actually don't see her that much."
}

{
  "id": "line:0343098",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Really?[p/] Even though you're sisters?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b089a7",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Our lives as nobles keep us very busy.[p/] We rarely have the chance to speak with each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb4897",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: And ever since Beatrice fled the estate,[p/] she's been throwing herself into her schoolwork."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e60ac",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: That man...[p/] he was my father,[p/] but I can't say I have fond memories of him."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c3909",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: He must have been difficult to deal with."
}

{
  "id": "line:01df7bf",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: You have no idea.[p/] He was cruel,[p/] tyrannical,[p/] and only ever cared about his own legacy."
}

{
  "id": "line:093bd50",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: He was willing to sacrifice anything and anyone to maintain his power and status,[p/] including his own daughters."
}

{
  "id": "line:01cff2b",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It sounds like his treatment of Beatrice was particularly harsh."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d9b70",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: It was.[p/] He never saw her as a worthy successor to our family's legacy, simply because she was a woman."
}

{
  "id": "line:028e9e5",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Even after her accident,[p/] he used her disability as an excuse to strip her of any power she had left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0088054",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can only imagine how difficult that must have been for all of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4ed65",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: It's been a constant struggle,[p/] but we managed to survive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a21f07",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: As bad as it sounds,[p/] now that he's gone,[p/] we might have a chance to rebuild our family."
}

{
  "id": "line:022803f",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice's Blindness"
}

{
  "id": "line:085209e",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Even after being blinded,[p/] Beatrice continued to fight for her freedom."
}

{
  "id": "line:022c815",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Despite everything that's happened to her,[p/] she's always remained determined to live her life on her own terms."
}

{
  "id": "line:0680d21",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I remember when she first came back to the estate after her accident,[p/] my father was convinced that she'd be completely helpless without her sight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0613166",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: But she refused to let her blindness define her.[p/] She learned how to navigate the estate using her other senses and continued to study magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2c2e4",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: It's ironic,[p/] really.[p/] My father tried to use her disability as a way to control her,[p/] but in the end,[p/] it was the very thing that allowed her to break free."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fac38",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Lady Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff665f",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: My apologies.[p/] I don't think I'll be of much help with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e24a69",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Come on, Tracker...[p/] Where are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f97ceb",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aaaaaa[p/][p/][s/]choo!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e180c7",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "As I entered Beatrice's Room,[p/] I was assaulted by a large cloud of dust."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae1c56",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] Some of it got in my eyes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ce678",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Oh?"
}

{
  "id": "line:009200f",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "As my vision cleared up,[p/] I realized that there was someone else in the room with us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd7f49",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/][s/] Laefe!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eaf37b",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sorry...[p/] I didn't mean to barge in."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bcd57",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: No,[p/] there's no need to apologize."
}

{
  "id": "line:055fd8f",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: ...Hello, fellow blond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0000985",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "I really didn't need to be reminded about that right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ebe84",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: U-[p/][s/]Uh...[p/] Hi."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b83202",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm really sorry for leaving so abruptly like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:033b96a",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No,[p/] I understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca5ebf",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "My eyes wandered around the room.[p/] I felt really awkward for some reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:008891a",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was probably for the best, anyway.[p/] I had no idea what I was doing out there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec178e",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] You were fine... [h=\"My feet still hurt...\" e=\"s\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:077edb8",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm sure with enough practice,[p/] you'll get the hang of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:028475c",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: I'd love to dance with you again."
}

{
  "id": "line:062f0cc",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: Most of the men who approach me during the Ball seem to think too highly of themselves.[p/] I much prefer your company."
}

{
  "id": "line:049951a",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, [i]that[/i] will have to wait."
}

{
  "id": "line:0994190",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: We're here on behalf of the Crown Prince to investigate what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0155d40",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right...[p/] We were wondering if we could ask you some questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:066b7c8",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Her posture became tense,[p/] which was to be expected considering the circumstances."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d99cfd",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe: O-[p/][s/]Of course.[p/] I'd be happy to help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3a3de",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "I'd learned everything I could for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0568366",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "It was time to MOVE elsewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0713ece",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": "I think I'd learned everything I could from Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:099f1f1",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom1",
  "text": ":There was only one last person to speak with:[p/] Harold Haroldson."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9f789",
  "node": "LialfalArgument_Fail",
  "text": "Laefe: You can ask me as many times as you like."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fab7c7",
  "node": "LialfalArgument_Fail",
  "text": "Laefe: The answer will always be the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:022c5b4",
  "node": "LialfalArgument_Fail",
  "text": "Damn it...[p/] I needed to change my approach."
}

{
  "id": "line:030dd6f",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "Laefe was hiding what her father was doing in his study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbe238",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "I doubted that she was doing this for any nefarious reasons.[p/] She might not even think that it's relevant to the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af8a72",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "But William Frega had many enemies,[p/] and he retreated into his study to do [i]something[/i] that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:064e3c0",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "And that \"something\" could be related to why he was murdered."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ab841",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "Yes"
}

{
  "id": "line:06fdb69",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "No"
}

{
  "id": "line:016d6d7",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is there something you're not telling us, Laefe?"
}

{
  "id": "line:013df1c",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because I have a feeling that you know more than you're letting on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0601c27",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "Laefe: W-[p/][s/]What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03df66a",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "Tyrion: What was your father doing in his study?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcb2fd",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "Laefe: I already told you.[p/] I don't know."
}

{
  "id": "line:04eefd6",
  "node": "LiafalArgument",
  "text": "Laefe: My father was a private man.[p/] He wouldn't share something like that with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a21582",
  "node": "LiafalArgument2",
  "text": "Liafal's Testimony 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:093c1ba",
  "node": "LiafalArgument2",
  "text": "Default"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccee9c",
  "node": "LiafalArgument2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...What is this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef0eab",
  "node": "LiafalArgument2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's proof that you had [i]some[/i] idea of what your father was doing in his study!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09dae61",
  "node": "LiafalArgument2",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] I don't think [i]that[/i] really proves anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:058a84c",
  "node": "LiafalArgument2",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/]Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6ab55",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "Tyrion: He was making some sort of change to his will,[p/] wasn't he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcc1ce",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "Laefe: W-[p/][s/]What?! [h=\"Did someone else tell him?\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e92387",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why did you find the need to hide this from us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01cbb6b",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "Laefe: I-[p/][s/]I didn't!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5d144",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "The thoughts I saw earlier seemed to disagree with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:04908d9",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "Tyrion: We've only just met.[p/] So I understand if you don't trust us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e41faa",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "Tyrion: But the Inquisition thinks that [i]Beatrice[/i] murdered your father,[p/] and they're claiming she did so for his inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ac8fe",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "Laefe: That's absolutely absurd!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d47f58",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Regardless,[p/] your father's inheritance was probably the motive behind his murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:089429a",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "Celeste: Which means that a lot of people would have a lot to gain from his death,[p/] including you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b29ca8",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "What?![p/][s/] What was she doing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c407a",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "Laefe: [i]Excuse[/i] me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0510189",
  "node": "LiafalArgument3",
  "text": "Laefe: How could you even [i]think[/i] that I'd be capable of something like this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:021d5cd",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Rationalize [c=\"I didn't mean to imply that you were involved in this. But it's clear that the murderer's motive was to take control of House Frega.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b45c7",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Threaten [c=\"The prosecution clearly won't shy away from prosecuting members of your family. If your sister is truly innocent, where do you think they'll turn their attention next?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd43d0",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It doesn't matter what I think."
}

{
  "id": "line:05de114",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Tyrion: The prosecution clearly won't shy away from prosecuting members of your family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc4fca",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were the last person to see your father alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0842ef7",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So if your sister is truly innocent,[p/] where do you think they'll turn their attention next?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0657afe",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Laefe: Please.[p/] Do you think I'll respond to such empty threats?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09dd0d8",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Laefe: I have cooperated with the Inquisition.[p/] I have nothing to hide."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c3c25",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Doubt [c=\"I'm not so sure... You were the last person to see your father alive. It's possible that you've been lying to us.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06116e1",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not so sure..."
}

{
  "id": "line:002d4a4",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's possible that you've been lying to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b9eaf",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Laefe: And what could I have [i]possibly[/i] gained by doing that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c8e93",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Laefe: I gave my testimony to the Inquisition of my own volition!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c66d6a",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Laefe: If I had truly been involved,[p/] I would have simply stayed silent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4a246",
  "node": "LiafalArgument4",
  "text": "Right...[p/] She had a point there."
}

{
  "id": "line:045db43",
  "node": "LiafalArgument5",
  "text": "TYRION: W-[p/][s/]We didn't mean to imply that you were involved in this."
}

{
  "id": "line:026b542",
  "node": "LiafalArgument5",
  "text": "Tyrion: But it's clear that the murderer's motive was to take control of House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:06774ba",
  "node": "LiafalArgument5",
  "text": "Tyrion: This means that their plan heavily relied on who William Frega was leaving his assets to."
}

{
  "id": "line:04149a5",
  "node": "LiafalArgument5",
  "text": "Tyrion: So I need to know, Ms. Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0034c33",
  "node": "LiafalArgument5",
  "text": "Tyrion: How was your father planning to change his will?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03df5f9",
  "node": "LiafalArgument5",
  "text": "Laefe: I-[p/][s/]I don't know...[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:039a22d",
  "node": "LiafalArgument5",
  "text": "Laefe: I've already told you.[p/] My father was a secretive man."
}

{
  "id": "line:0142203",
  "node": "LiafalArgument5",
  "text": "Laefe: He didn't share the details of his estate with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:04610f3",
  "node": "LiafalArgument6",
  "text": "Liafal's Engagement"
}

{
  "id": "line:0efef43",
  "node": "LiafalArgument6",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's proof that you had [i]some[/i] idea of what your father was doing to his will!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0614273",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is that really true, though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecf4e0",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I already know about your arranged marriage to Jaiden von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dadd2f",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: And I also know that as a part of this deal,[p/] Jaiden would inherit House Frega instead of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4d1b1",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: You definitely knew about this,[p/] and you heavily resisted the marriage in an attempt to stall it."
}

{
  "id": "line:035e0a5",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which means that you had [i]some[/i] idea of how your father's will was arranged."
}

{
  "id": "line:0109ed2",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: So what aren't you telling me, Laefe?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06adfb3",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "Laefe: I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0383363",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "Laefe: I can't trust you."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a6f30",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "Laefe: You are here on behalf of Crown Prince Aster,[p/] and you're a known dissident."
}

{
  "id": "line:05baaed",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "Laefe: You,[p/] the other Pillar families,[p/] [i]and[/i] the Crown have much to gain from my father's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4bb47",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "Laefe: How can you assure me that this information won't be used against my family?"
}

{
  "id": "line:019e6c6",
  "node": "LiafalArgument7",
  "text": "So [i]that's[/i] why she was being so secretive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa3294",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Appeal [c=\"There's nothing I could possibly say to make you trust me. But please understand, I'm only trying to find out who murdered your father.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac7a45",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Rationalize [c=\"I may have been hired by Prince Aster. But I'm an independent agent. I have no stake in this conflict. I was only hired to arrive at the truth.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01db23f",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I may have been hired by Prince Aster,[p/] but I'm an independent agent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b626b8",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have no stake in this conflict.[p/] I was only hired to arrive at the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ea415",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: You've read about me in the paper.[p/] You at least have some idea of what I stand for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0628d57",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Laefe: ...How can you expect me to trust you when you're so obviously close to Prince Aster and Lady Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b27ee",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm sorry,[p/] but I just can't trust you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8b00d",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Trust was a matter of emotion,[p/] not logic."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fb7e4",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "I needed to try another approach."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e899a",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Threaten [c=\"I'll arrive at the truth. One way or another. If you refuse to cooperate with me, I'll have no choice but to treat you as another suspect.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d4fce",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll arrive at the truth.[p/] One way or another."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3a1a2",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you refuse to cooperate with me,[p/] I'll have no choice but to treat you as another suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:049bf11",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "Laefe: And if you find this truth,[p/] you'll know that I have done nothing worthy of an indictment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0763ed6",
  "node": "LiafalArgument8",
  "text": "...That bluff didn't work"
}

{
  "id": "line:01dad5e",
  "node": "LiafalArgument9",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's nothing I could possibly say to make you trust me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4b6e7",
  "node": "LiafalArgument9",
  "text": "Tyrion: But please understand,[p/] I'm only trying to find out who murdered your father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ade195",
  "node": "LiafalArgument9",
  "text": "Tyrion: To do that,[p/] I need to know what kind of changes he was making to his will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0e015",
  "node": "LiafalArgument9",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's likely that whoever did this wanted to prevent those changes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b325cc",
  "node": "LiafalArgument9",
  "text": "Laefe: I have no reason to trust you."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ef8f7",
  "node": "LiafalArgument9",
  "text": "Laefe: But somehow,[p/] I can tell that you're being sincere."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ea9cf",
  "node": "LiafalArgument9",
  "text": "Laefe: ...Will you really protect Beatrice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1b163",
  "node": "LiafalArgument9",
  "text": "Reassuring her would be the best course of action,[p/] but something in the back of my mind stopped me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2c35b",
  "node": "LiafalArgument9",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'll get to the truth of what really happened.[p/] No matter what it is."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ffa9d",
  "node": "LiafalArgument9",
  "text": "Laefe: Okay.[p/] If that's truly what you're planning to do,[p/] I'll tell you what I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc9507",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a highly extravagant bed.[p/] It looks similar to the one in Miriam's dorm."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b5d09",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: This Tracker's bed.[p/] It's like resting on cloud."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa3b3c",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a table for guests.[p/] But it's extremely dusty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba0753",
  "node": "Examine_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "You should never see this dialogue."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cb7fa",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Tracker\"...[p/] Is that your name?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b06e5",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: How did you—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0161a85",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Yes.[p/] \"Tracker\" is Tracker.[p/] That's the name queen gib to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b2b9f",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker gestured towards Laefe when he mentioned his \"queen\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd3cfb",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He called you his \"queen\".[p/] Do you know him, Laefe?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc5395",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...[p/] But how—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d65a40",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: How are you talking to it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:021300e",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/][s/]Ah...[p/] That's—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec2194",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "I was so distracted by Tracker that I didn't realize how strange this scene must look to everyone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a5ffb",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I'm...[p/] a dog whisperer."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d3255",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: You've never mentioned that before..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0537c7c",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Orym: Do you honestly expect us to believe something like that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00cf5de",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: But Tracker says he can understand him.[p/] He told me himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0898f1b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/][s/] How do [i]you[/i] know that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0882849",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: U-[p/][s/]Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:021957a",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Player: Laefe and Tracker"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eaedcf",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So Laefe,[p/] how are [i]you[/i] able to communicate with Tracker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eac8e2",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Tracker is my familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:04aeee3",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Familiar...[p/] So you have the same magical bond Harold has with his monkey."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b65624",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "[b]Familial Bond[/b] allowed the caster to telepathically speak with their familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ea978",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "That must be how she could understand him."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c76e8",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Orym: ...You never mentioned him during questioning."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e92e6",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: It wasn't relevant to the investigation..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d5304",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: And I've...[p/] been keeping him a secret from my family."
}

{
  "id": "line:08945b2",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose that makes sense...[p/] I doubt William Frega would've allowed you to keep an animal in his home."
}

{
  "id": "line:085ac97",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Orym: Well, I don't appreciate you keeping this info from us."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b04c2",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Orym: I'm just glad no one got hurt 'cause of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ebabc",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Orym: Aside from this dog,[p/] we haven't really found anything new."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f83d4",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] They couldn't find any more physical evidence of the theft."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da6078",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "It looked like we'd run into another dead end."
}

{
  "id": "line:081a510",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Unless..."
}

{
  "id": "line:074190b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Player: The Night of the Murder"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4281a",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tracker.[p/] I saw you on the night of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a87bbd",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d0b47",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: Tracker!"
}

{
  "id": "line:013cd57",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Ruh Roh."
}

{
  "id": "line:0416cd3",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: He's [i]supposed[/i] to stay in this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0055dce",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Is [i]that[/i] why you won't allow the servants to enter it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc691b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: I didn't [i]want[/i] to keep him in Beatrice's room,[p/] but he was very insistent that he stay here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dea085",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker like the ambiance."
}

{
  "id": "line:023d908",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Right."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bb673",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] If you live in this room,[p/][s/] did [i]you[/i] see who brought the Sword of Spell Eating here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af62b1",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: I already asked him about that,[p/] but he didn't see anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:047e08c",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: He must have been taking a nap..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0797c53",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: Either that or he was roaming outside even though I [i]told[/i] him to stay here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f4de8",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a22c2",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:043516b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker see a lot of other things, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f4d6d",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker see many new people that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0105599",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Right.[p/] He was roaming the manor during the Lords' Ball.[p/] He must have seen a lot of new people..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf3e71",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Wait...[p/] If he was walking around,[p/][s/] did he see something that the other witnesses didn't?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01822f3",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Player: What did Tracker see?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0837265",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you tell us what you saw on the night of the murder, Tracker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e0e82",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker see rat people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7879e",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "This might've been more difficult than I expected..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdd89b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I need you to be more specific."
}

{
  "id": "line:053f749",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you go in order...?[p/] Tell me about everyone that you saw that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:036a6fd",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Mmmmm...[p/] Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b557e",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker was taking nap in room,[p/] but Tracker woke up from loud sounds outside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e27552",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker hear small things running in the walls."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c9dc0",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Running in the walls\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfff83",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker called queen,[p/] but she didn't answer.[p/] So Tracker decided to check sound alone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e98c4a",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker follow sound outside.[p/] That's when Tracker smell the bad smell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1d76c",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Bad smell\"...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:098dcd3",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: That's when Tracker smell flying rat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b56700",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]smelled[/i] a \"flying rat\"?[p/] Did you mean like a pigeon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfac8b",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker could smell where rat was,[p/] so Tracker bork at him and bite.[p/] He taste bad."
}

{
  "id": "line:0848a33",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker must have scared rat,[p/] because he fell onto the floor and dropped his stick."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d72077",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...The rat had a stick?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a1bf1",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker could see them now.[p/] So Tracker did one final bork to scare them off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e56b13",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: The rats were scared and went back into the walls."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e85c8",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It went into the [i]walls[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7b59f",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: That's when Tracker picked up the stick rat dropped."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ad06f",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Queen finally answered Tracker.[p/] She told him to go back to his room and hide."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0c074",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: After message,[p/] Tracker bring stick back to room for inspection."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f3035",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you remember what time this encounter happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d57277",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: What is \"time\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00fc95e",
  "node": "Talk_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh my god..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb6950",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Look, Tracker![p/][s/] It's my Attorney's Runestone!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0403666",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Rock."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca0adf",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s fitted with artificery![p/][s/] I can use it to take pictures of evidence and crime scenes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0a6a5",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker like you, friend.[p/] You smell nice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0461997",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Um...[p/] Thank you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9ebc0",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: What did he say?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d583a9",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...He told me that I smell nice."
}

{
  "id": "line:015f4bc",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, yeah.[p/] I kind of see what he means."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc2b32",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: My queen is a good friend.[p/] Saved Tracker when Tracker was pup."
}

{
  "id": "line:0873b47",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is that how you ended up becoming her pet?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbb6f0",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Yeah.[p/] I always hear about other animals joining humans,[p/] but Tracker didn't understand until he met queen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5d667",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Now I gib queen protection.[p/] Queen gib me honey bacon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0760920",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Player: William"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e09f80",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker don't like blue man."
}

{
  "id": "line:059e6e7",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Blue man\".[p/] Do you mean William Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a7636",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Blue man always yells at queen.[p/] Makes her cry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0382cf6",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've spoken to a lot of animals,[p/] but I think dogs have always been my favorites."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c639a7",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: You friend.[p/] You very fluent in Dog."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abbcc6",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Tracker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0333e12",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker don't—"
}

{
  "id": "line:00dcf89",
  "node": "Present_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "He got distracted by a squirrel outside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0285769",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "We entered Beatrice's bedroom and saw the Inquisition combing through it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0286624",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "It looked like their search was focused under her bed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0442dea",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Orym: Oh.[p/] Hey, kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0484e",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Commander."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba737e",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Orym: We're still doing a deep search of the room,[p/] but we're not done yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e70c01",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Orym: You should probably come back later."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c6759",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Orym: Keep it in that corner![p/][s/] Don't let it get away!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5f4a4",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...Get away from him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05524b1",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "As we entered Beatrice's room,[p/] we saw the Inquisition cornering something near the bed."
}

{
  "id": "line:068554e",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "It was some sort of animal—[p/]a wolf,[p/] to be exact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8362d",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Is that—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f4d69",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "I remember spotting that same wolf on the night of the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:015c0cb",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Has it been in the house since the murder?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af0689",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: ... [h=\"Intruders!|Must protect queen!\" e=\"fa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c12bbb",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: ... [h=\"I'm surrounded!|I must protect territory from enemies!\" e=\"fa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05ca667",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "He must've seen the Inquisition as intruders in his territory..."
}

{
  "id": "line:016b442",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "But did that mean he saw this room as his home?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed722b",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "I slowly started to walk towards him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db8a6c",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]Wait...[p/][s/] Tyrion?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d39527",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Orym: Stay back, kid![p/][s/] There's no telling [i]what[/i] it'll do!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0150984",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "I ignored them and continued to approach him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d959cd",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Don't worry.[p/] I'm not here to hurt you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f6957",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Tracker: Huh?[p/] This human...[p/] He can speak language of dog?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f29dd",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "It was the same thing that happened with Violetta.[p/] I could communicate with any animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c77c7",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Why are you talking to it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0666bc8",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "There was a good opportunity before me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ca218",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "I had access to a witness that no one else could talk to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0080970",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "...And one that couldn't lie to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:003d137",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: What did he say, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa943b",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: Did he see anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:044e9de",
  "node": "Check_Events_BeatriceRoom2",
  "text": "Well, he definitely saw [i]something[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:012db85",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce",
  "text": "Okay...[p/] Let's try to take a moment to work through this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc1c37",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce",
  "text": "Tracker is an animal.[p/] And despite being able to speak with him,[p/] his use of words is very primitive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad2c40",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce",
  "text": "So you should carefully examine each of his statements."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed8e98",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce",
  "text": "The first thing he heard was \"small things running in the walls.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9479f",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce",
  "text": "You recall that someone else observed something similar that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e6e82",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce2",
  "text": "0000"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6a01e",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce2",
  "text": "Player: Fail"
}

{
  "id": "line:0151f31",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce2",
  "text": "No...[p/] Tracker heard \"small things running in the walls.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:02ad3ee",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce2",
  "text": "In the context of everything that happened that night,[p/] he must've been talking about something specific."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5c24b",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce2",
  "text": "Didn't someone else mention hearing the same thing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:070b1b6",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce3",
  "text": "Jan: The servants were complaining about rats running through the air vents.[p/] So they sent me to take care of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00db3d1",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce3",
  "text": "Jan: I heard one of them running in the vents upstairs.[p/] And I followed it here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0386952",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce3",
  "text": "Jan: I figured it had nowhere else to go.[p/] So I opened it up and put a trap down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea997d",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce3",
  "text": "He must have heard the rats that Jan mentioned."
}

{
  "id": "line:064b56a",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce3",
  "text": "They weren't [i]actually[/i] running in the walls.[p/] They were running in the vents."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fc0af",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce3",
  "text": "The next thing he did was \"call the queen\",[p/] but she didn't answer."
}

{
  "id": "line:077013a",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce3",
  "text": "He was referring to Laefe,[p/] but she wasn't with him at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0699340",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce3",
  "text": "He must have called out to her telepathically."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d31f1a",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce4",
  "text": "000"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0325a",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce4",
  "text": "No...[p/] Laefe clearly didn't want Tracker to leave the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fa8ea",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce4",
  "text": "If he contacted her,[p/] she would have said [i]something[/i] in response."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8c604",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce4",
  "text": "So something else must have happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:04efd9b",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "Laefe didn't respond because she never got Tracker's message."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8fccc",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "The telepathic capabilities granted by [b]Familial Bond[/b] were disabled by the [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:015040c",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "...Which meant that this encounter happened [i]during[/i] the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3d086",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "So that covered his first two statements,[p/] but I wasn't really sure what to make of the \"flying rat\" he saw..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05407b5",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tracker,[p/] why did you refer to the rat as \"flying\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa69e9",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "Tracker: Because rats don't usually jump and fly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0545de9",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes.[p/] I got that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2236c",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is it possible that what you saw wasn't really a rat?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa9075",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "Tracker: Rats are rats.[p/] They're small things that run and hide."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8705c",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] So \"rat\" is a general term for him.[p/] He uses it to refer to small animals that are acting suspiciously."
}

{
  "id": "line:0634c4f",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "Anyways,[p/] with everything I knew,[p/] his last statement didn't make any sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c71e4",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "He said that the \"queen finally answered\" him,[p/] and this happened after he picked up the \"stick\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:059a494",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce5",
  "text": "But that shouldn't have been possible due to the [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:001da49",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce6",
  "text": "0000|0020"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b35ec7",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce6",
  "text": "No...[p/] Laefe told Tracker to go back to his room."
}

{
  "id": "line:00845c0",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce6",
  "text": "His attempts to contact her failed previously because of the lockdown system."
}

{
  "id": "line:046d20c",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce6",
  "text": "But something changed that allowed him to hear her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c66b3a",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce6",
  "text": "I recall that he picked up a \"stick\" before receiving her message."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8c139",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Tracker.[p/] About that \"stick\" you found..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f4738",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Where did you put it after you came back to this room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:068a817",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker hide stick in safe space.[p/] Under the bed."
}

{
  "id": "line:051b585",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And this \"stick\".[p/] Did it look like the sword that my friend is carrying?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6c08a",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:031de49",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tracker: Hey![p/][s/] Your friend stole my other stick!"
}

{
  "id": "line:001b65e",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Your \"[i]other[/i]\" stick?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ce169",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tracker: Yeah![p/][s/] Tracker found it while he was hiding from the metal men."
}

{
  "id": "line:0910835",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "\"Metal men\"...?[p/] Is he referring to the Kingsguard?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a3df6",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "He must have left the bedroom when they were searching for the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d77521",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Are [i]you[/i] the one who stole Celeste's sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:074b783",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tracker: Did Tracker do a bad...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3329a",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's as I suspected..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c35632",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Tracker[/i] was the one who brought the Sword of Spell Eating here."
}

{
  "id": "line:02491cb",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have no idea how or why,[p/] but the Sword of Spell Eating was lying in a hallway somewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0944392",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tracker found it and brought it back to Beatrice's room,[p/] [i]his[/i] room."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a9dfb",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce7",
  "text": "Laefe: That can't be...[p/] So the person who framed Beatrice for the theft was..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ab548",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "If it weren't for Tracker,[p/] the Inquisition would've never honed in on Beatrice at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d67604",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "But why would the Sword of Spell Eating be lying in a random hallway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d39ede",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Laefe.[p/] Do you mind if I borrow Tracker for a little bit?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0454374",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "Tracker: It's okay, queen.[p/] He smell good.[p/] Tracker trust him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d51d03",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thanks...[p/] I guess?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e2799",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "Laefe: ...Okay,[p/] but only if I can come with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:00de665",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "I knew Miriam's position,[p/] but how did Laefe feel about me prosecuting her sister?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a36417",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "I nodded to Laefe,[p/] but I also sent a subtle gesture to Celeste to keep an eye on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b63478",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "She silently nodded and slowly followed behind her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cad959",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Alright,[p/] Tracker.[p/] Can you take us to the hallway where you found these rats?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09558f3",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "Tracker: Sure thing, King."
}

{
  "id": "line:009c71f",
  "node": "TrackerDeduce8",
  "text": "...It sounded like I'd received a promotion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a286d7",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "JUDGE: Court is now in session for the trial of Beatrice Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c7211",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "AriaC: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:021a387",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "Judge: Ms. Steelwind?[p/] Is the prosecution ready?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3b6b0",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "AriaC: O-[p/][s/]Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6a588",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "AriaC: The prosecution is ready, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:01efb03",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "RubyD: ...The defense is also ready, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eda41e",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "She definitely looked less self-assured than usual."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4097e",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "Her history with Beatrice might be throwing her off."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c9bc7",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "JUDGE: ...Very well.[p/] Let’s begin the proceedings."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e60fe",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "JUDGE: Prosecutor Steelwind,[p/] could you please list the charges?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06af064",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "AriaC: Your Honor.[p/] The defendant is charged with first-degree murder and grand theft."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc4ae9",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "AriaC: As many of you know,[p/] Beatrice Frega is the formerly missing daughter of the now-late William Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:019d766",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "AriaC: And the [i]victim[/i] of the murder is William Frega himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:077d922",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "Judge: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...[p/] I'm well aware of that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad4a84",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "Judge: The people of Wyverngarde will certainly mourn the loss of House Frega's head."
}

{
  "id": "line:0760010",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "Please.[p/] The only people who \"mourned\" him were the banking houses' shareholders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8abbe",
  "node": "CourtroomC41",
  "text": "Judge: On that matter,[p/] did you also say that the defendant is accused of grand theft?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0004710",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_1",
  "text": "AriaC: Yes, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed2cc7",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_1",
  "text": "AriaC: The crimes took place during the Lords' Ball,[p/] an event that was hosted in Frega Manor yesterday evening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0132051",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_1",
  "text": "AriaC: The Haroldson Hall of History was hosting an exhibit within the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bb968",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_1",
  "text": "AriaC: They were showcasing several magical artifacts donated to the Wyverngarde Historical Society."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f305ec",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_1",
  "text": "AriaC: One of these items was the \"Sword of Spell Eating\":[p/] a magical artifact that allows its wielder to nullify magical effects."
}

{
  "id": "line:0408d09",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_1",
  "text": "AriaC: The prosecution believes that the defendant stole this item to break into the victim's study, which was secured with a magical lock."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e68837",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_1",
  "text": "AriaC: After breaking into the study,[p/] she attacked the victim and slashed his throat open using a letter opener."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4e850",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_1",
  "text": "AriaC: He died of blood loss shortly after."
}

{
  "id": "line:074c273",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_1",
  "text": "Judge: I-[p/][s/]I see...[p/] Does the prosecution have a motive?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a3ac2",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_1",
  "text": "AriaC: ...William Frega and his daughter were not close.[p/] Saying that they had a strained relationship would be an understatement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f458bf",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_1",
  "text": "AriaC: In fact,[p/] five years prior to the murder,[p/] Beatrice abandoned and fled her home."
}

{
  "id": "line:0971943",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "AriaC: She went into hiding and cut contact with all of her friends or family."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d3194",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Her whereabouts were unknown until she contacted her father a week ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a11f4e",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "RubyD: My client left the Frega household because of her toxic relationship with her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae112d",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "RubyD: She wanted to create a life for herself that was free from his influence and abuse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e49c7c",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...I won't disagree with your claims."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dd672",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "AriaC: But that simply highlights how desperate the defendant must have been."
}

{
  "id": "line:043ceab",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "AriaC: She had clearly fallen on hard times and begrudgingly contacted her father for financial aid."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ad536",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "AriaC: I have no idea why they would schedule this meeting [i]during[/i] the yearly Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc9ffa",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "AriaC: But nevertheless,[p/] several witnesses [i]did[/i] see her that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce3b8c",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "AriaC: And these same witnesses saw her storming out of her father's study in anger."
}

{
  "id": "line:05babcf",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Her father must have refused her request for aid.[p/] So she decided to murder him to claim his inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e8d7d",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "BeatriceA: It's a good thing we prepared for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5b194",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "RubyD: ...What you're saying is all conjecture, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:073dbf8",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "RubyD: You don't have [i]any[/i] evidence to confirm why my client contacted her late father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c67f8c",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Yes.[p/] I'm well aware that the defendant has refused to tell us what they discussed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6556c",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_3",
  "text": "RubyD: ...And be honest, Steelwind.[p/] Do you seriously think that my client committed these crimes in [i]spite[/i] of her condition?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0acf460",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_3",
  "text": "Judge: ...\"Condition\"?[p/] What do you mean by that, Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c76fc",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_3",
  "text": "RubyD: Why don't [i]you[/i] tell him, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02bd281",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_3",
  "text": "RubyD: Tell the court about my client's disability."
}

{
  "id": "line:001c0d4",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Your Honor.[p/] Beatrice Frega [i]is[/i] legally disabled.[p/] However—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a91b24",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_3",
  "text": "RubyD: \"Legally disabled\"?[p/] That's a [i]convenient[/i] way of putting it, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4fc06",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_3",
  "text": "RubyD: My client is completely blind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3f294",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_3",
  "text": "Judge: Completely blind...?[p/] Is this true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e892a",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_3",
  "text": "RubyD: We have several medical documents [i]and[/i] testimony from several chirurgeons attesting to that fact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf2ae3",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_3",
  "text": "RubyD: My client is unable to see [i]anything[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffeef0",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_3",
  "text": "Judge: What is the meaning of this, Ms. Steelwind?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af80ea",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "Judge: Do you expect me to believe that a [i]blind[/i] woman performed any of the acts you're accusing her of?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbe507",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "RubyD: I'm glad you [i]also[/i] see how ridiculous these claims are, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b1b50",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "AriaC: I-[p/][s/]If the court would just let me elaborate—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bece60",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "RubyD: Your Honor.[p/] The prosecution's first charge is grand theft."
}

{
  "id": "line:081e314",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "RubyD: My client would have needed to break into a display case that was [i]magically[/i] secured."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4c041",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "RubyD: Performing such an act would be a difficult task for [i]anyone[/i],[p/] much less my client."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f94b5f",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "AriaC: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:04cf03a",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "RubyD: And the [i]second[/i] charge is first-degree murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df6a32",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "RubyD: My client would have needed to use the Sword of Spell Eating on the lock leading to the victim's study."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d41b0",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "RubyD: [i]Then[/i] she would have needed to grab a letter opener,[p/] overpower the victim,[p/] [i]and[/i] deliver a precise and fatal blow to the victim's neck."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcdf37",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "RubyD: Does [i]any[/i] of that sound like a reasonable theory, Your Honor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:017ae6d",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "Judge: I'm compelled to agree with you, Ms. Tymora..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec00f3",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "Judge: It all sounds quite ludicrous,[p/] to be perfectly honest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0340a76",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "Gallery: This is just awful."
}

{
  "id": "line:042754d",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "Gallery: The Steelwinds have always been at odds with the Fregas."
}

{
  "id": "line:0796016",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_4",
  "text": "Gallery: They're just taking advantage of the Duke's death!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a7032",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Enough!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a49b40",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Your Honor.[p/] The court has [i]not[/i] seen the evidence that supports this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e9f4a",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Nor have you listened to the Inquisition's testimony regarding their investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d6ebc",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Until you have done so,[p/] you are in no position to pass judgment."
}

{
  "id": "line:007dd70",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "Judge: ...Very well, Ms. Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c8660",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "Hmph.[p/] I guess the little lady had some claws after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a379d",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "But it didn't matter,[p/] their case against Beatrice was questionable at best."
}

{
  "id": "line:062e3cf",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "Frankly,[p/] it was surprising that Steelwind even went through with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:037f3ef",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "It was only a matter of time before the judge saw things my way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f84b77",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "AriaC: To begin,[p/] the prosecution would like to call Commander Orym White to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e6840",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Commander White,[p/] please testify to the court about the Inquisition’s findings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f297eb",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_5",
  "text": "ORYM: Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edfe1f",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_6",
  "text": "Orym: We didn't want to cause panic after the Sword was stolen.[p/] So we activated the manor's silent security system.[p/] It put an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b] over the entire manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:088358e",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_6",
  "text": "Orym: We did a search of the house,[p/] and we found the stolen sword in the defendant's bedroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad2cba",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_6",
  "text": "Orym: It didn't look like she was going to run,[p/] and Crown Prince Aster told us to stand down.[p/] So we just kept a close eye on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f8802",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_6",
  "text": "Orym: William Frega was in a bad mood that night.[p/] He'd already locked himself inside his study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0257198",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_6",
  "text": "Orym: But an hour later,[p/] we entered the Study and found him lying dead in a pool of his own blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:02de782",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_6",
  "text": "Orym: The lock was still engaged,[p/] and no one teleported in.[p/] The perp must've temporarily disabled the lock using the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0944dc1",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_6",
  "text": "Orym: We have testimonies that say the defendant was seriously in debt.[p/] I guess she murdered the victim to get a part of his inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ef02e",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_6",
  "text": "Hmph...[p/] Their case against Beatrice was just as I'd predicted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c184aa",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_6",
  "text": "I already had a countermeasure to disprove the existence of any motive."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f6d2c",
  "node": "CourtroomC41_6",
  "text": "All I had to do was PRESENT that to the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9cd3c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: ...Wait,[p/] doesn't the Sword make the wielder immune to magical effects?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc6635",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: An [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b] would've only disempowered everyone [i]except[/i] the thief."
}

{
  "id": "line:026ebbd",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah, well...[p/] We didn't know what the Sword could do until [i]after[/i] the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e71559",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: Up until then,[p/] we thought it was just a dusty old artifact."
}

{
  "id": "line:04913bb",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: That seems pretty negligent.[p/] Are you sure you're qualified for your position, Orym?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09545f2",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: The situation was unprecedented for everyone involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:0907609",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: One could hardly expect an ancient artifact to have magical capabilities."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf4b86",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: Anyways,[p/] what did you do after the theft, Commander?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a8bd3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: That seems like a strange conclusion to jump to."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f5753",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: My client hadn't set foot into the Frega Manor in years."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfe9e0",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: After being gone for so long,[p/] her bedroom [i]had[/i] to have been repurposed for something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:081bc26",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: I'm not sure about the details,[p/] but one of the defendant's sisters refused to let the servants disturb that room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8117f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: I guess she was hoping that her sister would come back one day."
}

{
  "id": "line:082fa89",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "BeatriceA: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Laefe..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d83780",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: And why would the prince tell you to stand down, Orym?"
}

{
  "id": "line:086da70",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: W-[p/][s/]Well..."
}

{
  "id": "line:089979c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: Crown Prince Aster knew the defendant well.[p/] He was confident that she wasn't going to flee the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0765800",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: Are you sure he just \"knew her well\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:006b374",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: If I recall correctly,[p/] the prince is still very adamant about her innocence."
}

{
  "id": "line:05734a3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Judge: The Crown Prince is vouching for the defendant?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e014f5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Judge: Is this true, Ms. Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d5734",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: ...It is.[p/] However,[p/] I believe that the evidence found throughout the investigation proves the contrary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f23cd4",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: Are you sure your judgment isn't simply being clouded by your jealousy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0be1970",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: Your fiancé [i]was[/i] previously engaged to my client, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7db6c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "BeatriceA: You're enjoying this a bit too much..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cad285",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: Did anyone see him enter the study?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4d20e",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: A few people.[p/] One of them was Laefe Frega:[p/] the victim's second daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0610887",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: She said that he was extremely irritated.[p/] So he went into his study for some peace and quiet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0f1b3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: I guess his meeting with the defendant put him in a bad mood."
}

{
  "id": "line:0457106",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: But if the manor was covered in an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b],[p/] how did he lock the door magically?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02123e1",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: I'm not sure how.[p/] But the locks in the manor aren't affected by [b]Anti-Magic Fields[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c1e9f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: Um...[p/] How?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2adfd",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: The magical locks generate a smaller [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b] around themselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:067d56e",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: The two fields cancel each other out.[p/] It's akin to multiplying two negative numbers together."
}

{
  "id": "line:046a035",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: I'm going to be honest.[p/] I don't know a lot about artificery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0334c65",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: Is what she's saying true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0be4311",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "BeatriceA: Yes.[p/] Overlapping [b]Anti-Magic Fields[/b] are a well-studied phenomenon."
}

{
  "id": "line:00da9bb",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "BeatriceA: It's a frequently used fail-safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:05dd567",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "I would just have to take her word for it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3b572",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: Who discovered the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:035d602",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: The same person who saw him last—[p/]his daughter:[p/] Laefe Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0115337",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "BeatriceA: ...I really wish it could've been anyone other than her."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d42c5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: ...Was anyone else there with Laefe when she happened upon the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e94d29",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah.[p/] Supposedly,[p/] one of the servants got himself locked in a nearby storage closet."
}

{
  "id": "line:08892bb",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: And he heard the violent attack through one of the air vents."
}

{
  "id": "line:050311e",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: When he finally got out,[p/] he told Laefe and they went into the study,[p/] accompanied by some knights."
}

{
  "id": "line:033753b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: The lock was still engaged,[p/] and no one teleported in.[p/] The perp must've temporarily disabled the lock using something like the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5b2c1",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: This sword is integral to the case against my client.[p/] So why is the description of its capabilities so vague?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7f9a3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: To be honest,[p/] the Sword [i]is[/i] magical,[p/] but it doesn't seem to behave like any spells we know about."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fe0b6",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: And we can't identify its magic like we usually do with most artificery devices."
}

{
  "id": "line:068fec6",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: ...According to Lord Haroldson,[p/] its powers are \"demonic\" in nature."
}

{
  "id": "line:0496dfb",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: But if you ask me,[p/] [i]that's[/i] all a bunch of hooey."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3091d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "BeatriceA: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d25c98",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Orym: Either way,[p/] it's obvious that it doesn't follow the normal rules of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0580b56",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01bc666",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Judge: What is it, Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:077dfa1",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: I-[p/][s/]It's nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f88cd",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Cuthbert was watching from the gallery.[p/] So he must have heard that too."
}

{
  "id": "line:08484ce",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "...Ugh.[p/] I needed to focus on getting the client an acquittal, first."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb17d1",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "I could worry about Cuthbert later."
}

{
  "id": "line:020b39f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: Either way,[p/] we've tested the Sword's magic on similar locks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0171fcc",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: When used correctly,[p/] it [i]is[/i] capable of disabling the lock on the Duke's study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0408987",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: You have \"testimonies\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c18e0",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: Wouldn't an official record be more valid evidence?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e42c72",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Tymora.[p/] You and I [i]both[/i] know that your client's creditors are not the type to keep such records."
}

{
  "id": "line:021c22d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: So you're admitting that you're relying on hearsay."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fb7ca",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: One [i]could[/i] conclude that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3670e",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: But it doesn't matter if we can prove that this debt exists.[p/] The Frega estate is unimaginably vast."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0af08",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: Debt or no debt,[p/] that amount of wealth would be a tempting boon to any individual."
}

{
  "id": "line:0498ae8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "She had a point.[p/] House Frega owned every banking house in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0823f8e",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "People could only dream of having that much wealth and power."
}

{
  "id": "line:01db912",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Player: Overflow"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e8762",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "The prosecution's case against Beatrice was already really weak."
}

{
  "id": "line:088436d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "I was surprised she even brought this to trial in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e697c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "I already had testimony from someone else that directly contradicted the commander's testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0664259",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Once I PRESENTed that to the court,[p/] this case was as good as mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce8e42",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Player: Objection"
}

{
  "id": "line:092704a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: Your Honor.[p/] The witness's testimony contradicts [i]this[/i] piece of evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:07aa166",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Judge: My apologies, Ms. Tymora..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15cd2",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "Judge: But I fail to see [i]any[/i] contradiction there."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b55c5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: Perhaps you should look harder, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:018f80f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "AriaC: Or perhaps [i]you[/i] should stop making such careless claims."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b59050",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "RubyD: R-[p/][s/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8251b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "I needed to stop playing around."
}

{
  "id": "line:052b0a3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_OrymR",
  "text": "I had the evidence I needed.[p/] I just needed to PRESENT it to the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffa4df",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj",
  "text": "RubyD: Your Honor.[p/] The prosecution's case against my client is riddled with holes."
}

{
  "id": "line:09578d6",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj",
  "text": "RubyD: And the prosecution's proposed \"motive\" is the largest among them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee94df",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj",
  "text": "Judge: What do you mean, Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01785fe",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj",
  "text": "Judge: Of all the elements in this case,[p/] the motive is the most believable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0466370",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj",
  "text": "Judge: Your client would have had much to gain through her father's inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae20ed",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj",
  "text": "RubyD: That may be."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d95099",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj",
  "text": "RubyD: ...But that's assuming my client had [i]anything[/i] to inherit at all!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0648650",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj",
  "text": "AriaC: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08301d2",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj",
  "text": "RubyD: Your Honor,[p/] my client fled from her psychologically abusive father five years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:01eb636",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj",
  "text": "RubyD: William Frega was a petty and vindictive man."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3c9b4",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj",
  "text": "RubyD: Do you honestly think that he'd leave his inheritance to someone who disobeyed him so egregiously?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcb93d",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "RubyD: ...No.[p/][s/] He'd do everything in his power to make sure she didn't see a [i]shred[/i] of his wealth!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad3449",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Yes.[p/] We're already well aware of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a46649",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "The moment she slammed her cane down,[p/] I noticed her wince a little."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e6ef1",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "She was getting more and more heated.[p/] I didn't realize her rivalry with Beatrice was that personal."
}

{
  "id": "line:003bd70",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...On the night of the murder,[p/] the victim made the decision to disinherit the defendant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0024bb2",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: However,[p/] his murder deprived him of the opportunity to submit his will to his attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0274a9a",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: This only further proves the defendant's motive."
}

{
  "id": "line:04655cd",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: She would have needed to act quickly.[p/] Lest her father submit the changes to his will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6bf37",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "RubyD: I'm afraid [i]you're[/i] mistaken, Steelwind.[p/] William Frega didn't disinherit my client that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bb4e9",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "RubyD: He disinherited my client five years ago when she left!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05481bb",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "RubyD: I have witness testimony from Miriam Frega:[p/] William's youngest daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a192a",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "RubyD: By her own admission,[p/][s/] her father disinherited my client before she fled the household![p/][s/] That's [i]why[/i] she left!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9a1d9",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5840d",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...She never brought that up during questioning..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9515e",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "RubyD: Why would she release that information to one of her family's enemies?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd1883",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "RubyD: If you don't believe me,[p/][s/] why don't we call her to the stand and ask her ourselves?"
}

{
  "id": "line:049bafe",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...What have you done, Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0955dd9",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "RubyD: I have [i]no[/i] idea what you're talking about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe27bc",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Well,[p/] it's clear we won't get anywhere until we hear from Miriam directly."
}

{
  "id": "line:087f933",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: Bailiff,[p/] please escort Miriam Frega to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:088646c",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Miriam.[p/] Is the defense correct?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9683d",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: Did your father disinherit Beatrice five years ago?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e48793",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "Miriam: Y-[p/][s/]Yes..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c4957",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...And you didn't think it was [i]necessary[/i] to share this information with me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04122eb",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "Miriam: W-[p/][s/]Well...[p/] You never asked."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a4b98",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: If I recall correctly,[p/] you were also tight-lipped during questioning this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b69fb",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "Miriam: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8eef5",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "RubyD: The witness had just lost her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b932c2",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "RubyD: You can hardly expect her to recall [i]every[/i] detail that's relevant to his murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb858f",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Which raises a more concerning question:[p/] how did [i]you[/i] extract this information?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0698d37",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "RubyD: Who knows?[p/] I [i]have[/i] always had a way with people."
}

{
  "id": "line:069891c",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: Miriam,[p/] please testify to the court about [i]how[/i] you found out about Beatrice's disinheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:02159f9",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_3",
  "text": "Miriam: Y-[p/][s/]Yes.[p/] Of course..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee0a01",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "Miriam: After my sister's...[p/] accident,[p/] my father said that she was unfit to inherit our noble house."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c3275",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "Miriam: He declared to our family that he would be removing her from his will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad9f61",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "Miriam: It was five years ago,[p/] but I remember it well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0890a12",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "Miriam: One day,[p/] we all woke up and discovered that Beatrice had fled from our home."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1ad75",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "Miriam: She left a note for us,[p/] and in it,[p/] she renounced her name and denounced my father."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f3a83",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: ...And are you sure this all happened five years ago?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d165e3",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "Miriam: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...[p/] Even now,[p/] I can remember everything clearly..."
}

{
  "id": "line:026fbba",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: I...[p/] see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab2324",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "Her speech was getting slower,[p/] and I could have sworn that her words were slurring."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b5fab",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "Nightgrave seemed extremely concerned for some reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:024f305",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: And Laefe was there with you at this meeting?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06201f0",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "Miriam: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...[p/] She was."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d1211",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1086a",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: However,[p/] Laefe couldn't have possibly been there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf6d31",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "She was starting to sway as if she couldn't keep her balance."
}

{
  "id": "line:01acb51",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "Was this trial getting to her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eda3f9",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "RubyD: Hey...[p/] Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0208e79",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: Of course, I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07454d1",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "RubyD: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfdeb5",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "Judge: ...By the Scaled Lord![p/][s/] Is that [i]blood[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a22599",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "Judge: B-[p/][s/]Bailiff![p/][s/] Find [i]anyone[/i] capable of casting healing magic!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c29a85",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "Judge: Escort them to the courtroom immediately!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0466aa1",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "After some scrambling,[p/] a couple of healers were able to help Nightgrave stabilize the prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccff02",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "In all the chaos,[p/] I caught a glimpse of her.[p/] There were deep wounds and lacerations on several parts of her body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaebd1",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "She must have used some kind of illusion to hide them,[p/] but the mages dispelled it to identify her wounds."
}

{
  "id": "line:03dd042",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "They took Steelwind out of the courtroom on a stretcher,[p/] but as they were doing that,[p/] she grabbed Nightgrave and rasped something into his ear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0728226",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "He looked confused,[p/] but he simply nodded and made his way to the witness stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:088fc2b",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "...But not before passing a message onto the bailiff,[p/] who seemed equally confused."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e08bf3",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Nightgrave![p/][s/] Explain yourself!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f0211",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "Judge: What is going on?![p/][s/] Why would Ms. Steelwind prosecute if she was so gravely injured?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04bfaf0",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_5",
  "text": "Wallace: I'm sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:087f765",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "Wallace: But I wasn't actually here as Ms. Steelwind's aide.[p/] I was here as her doctor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df0e81",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "RubyD: ...Her doctor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdb0f2",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "Wallace: The truth is that Ms. Steelwind was violently attacked at noon today."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c1b9d",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "Wallace: She was in critical condition,[p/] but she insisted on prosecuting the case anyways."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c53c7",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "Wallace: She suddenly showed up at my house and asked me to channel my [b]necromancy[/b] to keep her wounds closed during the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c7a47",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "Judge: Scaled Lord![p/][s/] Why didn't she just recuse herself?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:018beaf",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "She must have known..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6fe88",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "If anyone else tried to prosecute Beatrice,[p/] I would have handily won the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c26c82",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "Nevertheless,[p/] she showed up when no one else would,[p/] and she did it all despite the risk to her life..."
}

{
  "id": "line:039646e",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "It almost made me respect her a little."
}

{
  "id": "line:040e9ac",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "RubyD: Anyways,[p/] is there any need to prolong this trial, Your Honor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c2fe6",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "Judge: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:059df1f",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "RubyD: Even [i]you[/i] must acknowledge how weak the case against my client is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd3986",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "RubyD: In addition to that,[p/] Miriam's testimony shows that my client had nothing to gain from her father's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba6190",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "Judge: M-[p/][s/]Ms. Tymora![p/][s/] Ms. Steelwind has been gravely injured!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d981c4",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "Judge: And you're still only concerned about—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e6770",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "RubyD: The only thing I'm \"concerned\" about is seeking justice for my client."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dde196",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "Judge: E-[p/][s/]Even so...[p/] We cannot move forward until we find another prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:048febd",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_6",
  "text": "RubyD: And how long do you think that will take, Your Honor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ecf46",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_7",
  "text": "RubyD: It's been nearly twelve hours since the murder took place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5344b",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_7",
  "text": "RubyD: That gives us what?[p/] Thirty-six hours?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d8ded",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_7",
  "text": "RubyD: After that,[p/] every magical trace at the crime scene will fully disappear."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e2b4b",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_7",
  "text": "Wallace: B-[p/][s/]But there [i]might[/i] be someone—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa0cdb",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_7",
  "text": "RubyD: If Steelwind had simply allowed [i]another[/i] prosecutor to work this case,[p/] we wouldn't be in this situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb04dc",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_7",
  "text": "RubyD: She took a risk,[p/] and now she has to take responsibility for that.[p/] Wouldn't you agree, Your Honor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0429f70",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_7",
  "text": "Judge: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:024ae73",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_7",
  "text": "I wasn't completely proud of winning this way,[p/] but I wouldn't let an opportunity like this pass me by."
}

{
  "id": "line:09395a1",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_7",
  "text": "The judge was clearly unhappy with this turn of events,[p/] but Steelwind didn't leave him any choice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b47993",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_7",
  "text": "Judge: ...It seems that there aren't any prosecutors available to immediately take Ms. Steelwind's place."
}

{
  "id": "line:02226f8",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_7",
  "text": "Judge: We will take a brief recess.[p/] After that,[p/] I'll deliver my verdict."
}

{
  "id": "line:0160700",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_8",
  "text": "RubyD: Cuthbert![p/][s/] What the hell are you doing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:001f9e8",
  "node": "OrymC4Obj_8",
  "text": "TyrionP: But what I [i]do[/i] know is that there was a massive contradiction in Miriam Frega's testimony!"
}

{
  "id": "line:011bc3e",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1",
  "text": "TyrionP: Your Honor![p/][s/] The defense—[p/][s/] I mean the prosecution—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07eafb4",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1",
  "text": "TyrionP: [i]I[/i] would like the right to cross-examine this witness!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0141432",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1",
  "text": "Judge: Bailiff.[p/] Arrest Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] I am holding him in contempt."
}

{
  "id": "line:03311d1",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1",
  "text": "TyrionP: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/][s/] W-[p/][s/]Wait!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd5648",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1",
  "text": "I really didn't think this through, did I...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0015f89",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1",
  "text": "Instead of following his order,[p/] the bailiff walked over to the judge's podium and whispered something into his ear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0867a46",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1",
  "text": "Judge: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a66a9e",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1",
  "text": "Judge: I see.[p/] Very well, then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec8b81",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1",
  "text": "...What were they saying?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00fc57b",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1",
  "text": "Judge: It appears that Ms. Steelwind has [i]somehow[/i] predicted that this would happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f08a41",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1",
  "text": "Judge: In accordance with her wishes,[p/] Mr. Cuthbert may act as the prosecutor in her stead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0644e7e",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "RubyD: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d41ab5",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Judge: The paperwork was submitted shortly before the trial.[p/] Mr. Cuthbert is designated as her stand-in."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab1a95",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Judge: It's unorthodox,[p/] but it's not without precedent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0978d35",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "I remembered when Steelwind asked me something strange earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a032ca",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Aria: What would you do if you discovered that one of your clients was guilty?"
}

{
  "id": "line:056c6a5",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Aria: And what would you do if they were guilty?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a6978",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose...[p/] I'd withdraw and tell them to find another lawyer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0e336",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Aria: And if no one else would represent them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:013a416",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don't know.[p/] It would definitely be a difficult choice for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b116c0",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But,[p/] I would never be able to represent them if I knew the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9b456",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't think I could stand by and let a murderer escape justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7cbd4",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Steelwind...[p/] Did she somehow [i]know[/i] this would happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0546ffe",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Celeste: Well...[p/] [i]this[/i] isn't how I expected the trial to go..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02368e6",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Shortly after I barged onto the prosecutor's table,[p/] Celeste awkwardly followed behind me."
}

{
  "id": "line:00df2ef",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "...Curiously,[p/] she only did so [i]after[/i] the bailiff didn't arrest me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0173d76",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I guess we're really doing this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0063ef2",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "TyrionP: What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:043d81f",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Celeste: This feels weird.[p/] We're on the other side of the courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a81eda",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "TyrionP: I mean...[p/] This [i]is[/i] where the prosecutor is [i]supposed[/i] to stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b867a7",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...No.[p/] I don't like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7c585",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Celeste: Ruby![p/] Can we switch tables?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc9164",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "TyrionP: Your Honor, please ignore her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:034ea8b",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Celeste: No![p/][s/] This is way too weird!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03bbd75",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion![p/][s/] File a motion![p/][s/] Get her to switch with us!"
}

{
  "id": "line:037de02",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c2e64",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "RubyD: For the love of—...[p/] I [i]genuinely[/i] don't care."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7b104",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_2",
  "text": "RubyD: Cuthbert can have this side if he wants it so badly."
}

{
  "id": "line:048d0ee",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "TyrionP: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0449a3d",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Judge: With [i]that[/i] out of the way.[p/] Let's resume proceedings."
}

{
  "id": "line:05613ee",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Judge: ...Assuming that we're all at our preferred spots."
}

{
  "id": "line:014e8f7",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: We are, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3c470",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "As much as I hated to admit it,[p/] I [i]was[/i] more comfortable here."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f4723",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Not that I wanted to encourage her to do this again..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e05ede",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Judge: With all of these interruptions,[p/] I think it best to review the proceedings up until now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0770c63",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Judge: The prosecution proposed that Beatrice Frega's motive for the murder was to claim the victim's inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d34682",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Judge: However,[p/] the defense brought forth a witness who testified that Beatrice was disinherited by her father five years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:075be29",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Judge: Am I correct, Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf405a",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "RubyC: You are, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eab134",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Judge: Very well.[p/] Considering the circumstances,[p/] I think it's best to have Lady Frega repeat her testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:05116b2",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Judge: Bailiff.[p/] Please escort Lady Frega to the stand once more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe1827",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Frega,[p/] could you please give your testimony to the court once more?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd98f3",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_3",
  "text": "Miriam: Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f3cd0",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So your father disinherited Beatrice shortly after her departure."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b25f9",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_4",
  "text": "Miriam: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...[p/] He did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a02bac",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_4",
  "text": "RubyC: As such,[p/] Beatrice would have no motive to murder her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8b362",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_4",
  "text": "RubyC: Any inheritance she could have received would be long gone by the night of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:067a6a1",
  "node": "CourtroomC4T1_4",
  "text": "Was that really true, though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0382299",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Miriam: After my sister's...[p/] accident,[p/] my father said that she was unfit to inherit his assets."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c88f8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: That seems awfully cruel of him.[p/] It was just an accident, wasn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b462f9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Miriam: My father was always thinking about the broader picture. [h=\"He just wanted an excuse|to punish her...\" e=\"as\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae8930",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Miriam: He must have thought that this was for my sister's own good."
}

{
  "id": "line:062a2aa",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "She probably didn't want to speak ill of her father in the courts,[p/] but it seemed that she understood the type of person he was."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ee8a2",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So he was making a show of it and sending a message to the rest of your family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0093231",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "I felt a little guilty for doing this to her,[p/] but I would need to establish Beatrice's motive whenever I could."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cad328",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "RubyC: Your Honor.[p/] I find Cuthbert's comments to be extremely insensitive to the witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c7c82",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "RubyC: I see no reason for him to speak ill of the deceased."
}

{
  "id": "line:073a067",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Judge: I-[p/][s/]I am compelled to agree."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2e2dc",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] She was using the judge's fear of House Frega against me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f421c3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You must have been less than thirteen years old at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d9411",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't imagine how that must have been."
}

{
  "id": "line:002cf71",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But can we really trust your testimony if you were only a child at the time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09080c8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Miriam: ...I remember it vividly.[p/] My father's words,[p/] the look of absolute fury on my sister's face."
}

{
  "id": "line:08497c4",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Miriam: I even remember the way the sun was shining through the window that morning... [h=\"It was all my fault...\" e=\"s\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd6da6",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Miriam: I remember everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:06750f5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "It sounded like a painful memory for her,[p/] and she seemed to blame herself for what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9ad5e",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "It'd be best not to press her more than necessary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4f588",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: That must have been a surprise for all of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:008a22d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did she tell anyone else about her plan?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d1ba2",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Miriam: No...[p/] She didn't."
}

{
  "id": "line:09df0a0",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Miriam: She left without a word to anyone. [h=\"She should have|spoken with us first...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:068c1ca",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "She seemed to be sincere about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0387434",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Miriam: She left a note for us.[p/] And in it,[p/] she renounced her name and denounced my father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdaaf5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: From what I've heard about your father,[p/] I don't find that surprising."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a46e90",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Miriam: T-[p/][s/]That's—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad608c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "RubyC: It's clear to everyone involved that my client was not treated well by her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad4256",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "RubyC: That's what drove her to leave the Frega estate."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ba1d6",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Miriam: ....My father had many responsibilities.[p/] He had much to consider."
}

{
  "id": "line:092be2b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "RubyC: And that justified his treatment of your sister?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c88332",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Despite being [i]her[/i] witness,[p/] Ms. Tymora really wasn't holding back against Miriam."
}

{
  "id": "line:01148d5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "I'd felt it while I was watching from the gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a057b8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "A part of her testimony didn't match with what I'd learned from my investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c7620",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "It must have been something that Laefe told me."
}

{
  "id": "line:03344ff",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] It's clear that the witness's testimony is contradictory!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0611c70",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: And [i]this[/i] piece of evidence proves it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3fb74",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Judge: I fail to see how [i]that[/i] proves anything, Mr. Cuthbert..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0596581",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_MiriamC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/]Oh...[p/] I guess you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:05df644",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Frega,[p/] it's clear that you're regretful about how your eldest sister was treated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5cb9e",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: That guilt must have eaten at you after all these years."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf0bbd",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "RubyC: Cuthbert.[p/] I know you don't have a good history with the witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0885687",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "RubyC: But you shouldn't rub salt in her wounds."
}

{
  "id": "line:00faae4",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was just pointing out the witness's personal connection to the defendant, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0241b9d",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: She clearly regrets not standing up for her sister all those years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa38fa",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So perhaps she's trying to make up for that—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0d1a4",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: —By lying to protect her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2db9a",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "Miriam: Excuse me?![p/][s/] I did nothing of the sort!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0624430",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Frega.[p/] You testified that your father disinherited Beatrice five years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c993a8",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: However,[p/] I have testimony from another witness who [i]spoke[/i] with the victim on the night of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a007d",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: After Beatrice's meeting with William Frega,[p/] he openly declared that he would be removing her from his will."
}

{
  "id": "line:00759b2",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: He even entered his study to draft a new will to reflect that decision."
}

{
  "id": "line:080f802",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So that raises the following question.[p/] Why would the victim need to declare that he was disinheriting the defendant?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0657948",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It doesn't make sense if he had already disinherited her five years ago!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0bdfd",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Miriam: I-[p/][s/]Is that so?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d2832",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Miriam: W-[p/][s/]Well, who did you hear this from?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c80df2",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Miriam: It's clear that they had [i]no[/i] understanding of my father's estate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c63fda",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: They had no \"understanding\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:025a086",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Miriam,[p/] this testimony came [i]directly[/i] from your sister:[p/] Laefe Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e509b7",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Miriam grimaced.[p/] She probably didn't talk to Laefe about this beforehand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0616398",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And [i]she[/i] should have also been present during this alleged meeting five years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:001982c",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Miriam: W-[p/][s/]Well,[p/] she must be mistaken then!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7ade1",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "RubyC: Your Honor.[p/] How can we trust second-hand testimony from a witness who isn't here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0922b99",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "RubyC: Wouldn't it make more sense to have Laefe give her testimony directly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f37f2",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Judge: Hm...[p/] I must agree with you, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4400c",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Judge: Laefe Frega should be allowed to clear up this misunderstanding."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0f785",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "...She looked way too confident.[p/] What was she planning?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f6c73",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "I'm not sure if it was intentional,[p/] but Miriam's testimony [i]was[/i] clearly contradictory."
}

{
  "id": "line:096685e",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_2",
  "text": "Could she be lying to protect Beatrice?[p/] Ms. Tymora might be betting that Laefe would do the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f10258",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "Judge: Bailiff.[p/] Please escort Laefe Frega to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:040fa14",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Laefe.[p/] When we spoke earlier,[p/] you mentioned that your father decided to disinherit Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af3cab",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: And he decided this [i]after[/i] their meeting on the night of the murder.[p/] Is that correct?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff255e",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "Laefe: U-[p/][s/]Um, yes.[p/] I [i]did[/i] say that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f82501",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: You see, Laefe,[p/] Cuthbert doubts the testimony given by your younger sister."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2e941",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: He seems to think that she's committed perjury."
}

{
  "id": "line:035546d",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wouldn't go so far as to say—"
}

{
  "id": "line:094c3ab",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: Witness.[p/] Lying under oath is a serious crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:08944ee",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: It would have harsh consequences,[p/] even for someone of your status."
}

{
  "id": "line:003095b",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "Laefe: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] She couldn't have—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cad032",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: Wonderful.[p/] Are you saying that you can corroborate your sister's testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfe290",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora.[p/] You can't just intimidate the witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9b7b4",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: I have no idea what you're talking about, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0feef8a",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: I'm just informing the witness of the law.[p/] What she does is ultimately her choice."
}

{
  "id": "line:016a35a",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "She really [i]was[/i] as ruthless as people said she was.[p/] I just never expected to have to deal with this myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:009ef22",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: So, Laefe.[p/] Assuming Miriam [i]wasn't[/i] lying under oath,[p/] could you please testify to the court to confirm what your sister said?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f5fb5",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_3",
  "text": "Laefe: Y-[p/]Yes...[p/] Of course..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6fcd7",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_4",
  "text": "Laefe: You see,[p/] Miriam was quite young when my father called us into his study five years ago.[p/] She didn't understand what he was [i]really[/i] doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0772684",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_4",
  "text": "Laefe: My father would often lie to us.[p/] It was one of the many ways that he kept us in line."
}

{
  "id": "line:0261ccc",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_4",
  "text": "Laefe: The encounter that Miriam described was just another one of his lies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0990e7e",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_4",
  "text": "Laefe: Despite their disagreements,[p/] my father would never disinherit Beatrice without a good reason.[p/] Even when she left,[p/] he always assumed that she would eventually return home."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddbb99",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_4",
  "text": "Laefe: The truth is that none of us knew what my father was planning for House Frega's future."
}

{
  "id": "line:033c4fb",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_4",
  "text": "RubyC: See, Cuthbert?[p/] The truth is much more complicated."
}

{
  "id": "line:078ec8c",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_4",
  "text": "RubyC: No one could have really known what William Frega was planning for his estate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0446806",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_4",
  "text": "Laefe was definitely trying to cover for Miriam,[p/] and Ms. Tymora was playing her like a fiddle."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4405c",
  "node": "MiriamObjC4_4",
  "text": "...Luckily for me,[p/] she wasn't the only person who gave a statement to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f62aee",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you're saying that Miriam's testimony was based on a misunderstanding?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09072f2",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: Yes.[p/] My father was never direct with his actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fdb91",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: He's always known just what to say to keep people under control."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c733b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm aware of how it sounds,[p/] but he had much to consider outside of his family."
}

{
  "id": "line:07141d8",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: The Fregas are one of the pillars of Wyverngarde, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0889993",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: Keeping the family aligned with our House's goals was one of his responsibilities. [h=\"But we were his daughters...|How could he be so cruel?\" e=\"sa\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aac3d1",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "It's clear that she didn't agree with what she's saying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0083454",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "She must also be trying to keep her family's name clean."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c29007",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you really think that your father would lie about something so important?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0675585",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: It [i]was[/i] of great importance.[p/] That's why he had to lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7d3c5",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: He wanted to make us understand the consequences of disobeying him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0334a46",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What kind of father does that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03cfaec",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But if he truly wanted to scare all of you,[p/] why [i]wouldn't[/i] he disinherit Beatrice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a3985",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: My father was always more pragmatic than vengeful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a18107",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: I imagine that he [i]expected[/i] her to fail on her own,[p/] and if she ever came back,[p/] she would be forced to admit that she needed him."
}

{
  "id": "line:037e077",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: If he could make someone like Beatrice feel powerless,[p/] the rest of us would no doubt have fallen into line."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8be57",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: Looking back,[p/] I suppose that's all we ever were to him:[p/] assets to be appraised and traded."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b883e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "I heard a bit of resentment in her voice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4e056",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: If that were true,[p/] why would he tell you that he was disinheriting Beatrice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9faae",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: Perhaps it was a warning.[p/] I had my own share of disagreements with him, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a845ef",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm still not sure if he was telling me the truth last night, either."
}

{
  "id": "line:0704b92",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "That would depend on what Ms. Tymora and Beatrice discussed with the Duke."
}

{
  "id": "line:057f3d9",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "And right now,[p/] I still had no idea [i]what[/i] they even talked about."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b77b0",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Celeste: Did William Frega really lie to them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08638d1",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: From what we know,[p/] I honestly wouldn't put it past him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3bcfa",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: He clearly had very little respect for his daughters."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dea8e4",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Celeste: But there were other people that he [i]did[/i] respect."
}

{
  "id": "line:0720a9b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_LiafalC4",
  "text": "Right...[p/] Was there anyone else that he would have told the truth to?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0836f55",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Frega,[p/] did you really have [i]no[/i] idea about House Frega's future?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05875dc",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Laefe: No,[p/] I didn't.[p/] My father made sure of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:07655f6",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Laefe: As I told you,[p/] he kept many secrets and wasn't above lying to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bdf88",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But with Beatrice gone,[p/] [i]you[/i] would have been the one to inherit your father's estate."
}

{
  "id": "line:001bace",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Would you really be ignorant of your father's plans for House Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f46cd0",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Unfortunately for you,[p/] I don't think you'd be that careless."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fd0fe",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: In fact,[p/] I have it on good authority that you knew [i]exactly[/i] how William's inheritance would be divided before that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:065c437",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Laefe.[p/] According to Lloyd von Sanctus,[p/] you were arranged into a diplomatic marriage with his son."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0c0ad",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You expressed resistance to this arrangement.[p/] Am I correct?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0112dd0",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Laefe: ...I-[p/][s/]I have no reason to comment on that matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:05eb307",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "RubyC: Cuthbert.[p/] The witness's personal matters are hardly any of our business."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2e6ff",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Judge: Yes.[p/] I must ask that you keep this discussion relevant to the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c5fe5",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor.[p/] Laefe's resistance to this marriage is exactly how I know that her testimony is false."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e9f84",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: She would make sure to know every detail about how it would affect her [i]and[/i] her House."
}

{
  "id": "line:07aa2af",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: And that [i]includes[/i] how House Frega would be inherited by her future husband!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b2a22",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Laefe: I-[p/][s/]I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07afb3b",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So that raises the question, Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f46c6",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you already knew the intricate details of this marriage,[p/] why would your father tell you that he was disinheriting your sister?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0091f40",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: That statement would [i]only[/i] make sense if Beatrice [i]was[/i] already in his will beforehand!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc27a8",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4",
  "text": "Tyrion: That would render Miriam's testimony false,[p/][s/] [i]and[/i] constitute a motive for the defendant!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0194dfe",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "RubyC: It's a decent argument, Cuthbert,[p/] but it relies on one assumption."
}

{
  "id": "line:0255b19",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And what assumption would that be, Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f4c21",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if he [i]was[/i] lying,[p/] the victim declared that he was revoking Beatrice's inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:081fb83",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: She [i]must[/i] have already been named in the will previously.[p/] Otherwise,[p/] there would have been no need for him to say that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d51605",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It wouldn't make any sense, otherwise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3e722",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "RubyC: And that's where your assumption is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f54aea",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "RubyC: You're assuming that William Frega was acting logically."
}

{
  "id": "line:098aa45",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ef98d",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "RubyC: It's clear that William Frega was extremely controlling of his daughters."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3918f",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "RubyC: By your own admission,[p/] Laefe Frega was resistant to the marriage arranged by her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:028cf43",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "RubyC: In addition to that,[p/] Miriam Frega found herself wrapped in controversy regarding the Nightgrave trial a few months ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:000ce82",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "RubyC: And finally,[p/] Beatrice Frega:[p/] the prodigal child,[p/] finally returned and made a public spectacle of it during the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e11b2",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...What are you trying to insinuate?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df6a9a",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_2",
  "text": "RubyC: In his eyes,[p/] William Frega's ability to keep his daughters in line was clearly weakening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0626860",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: He must have gotten desperate and made a grand declaration in a feeble attempt to scare you, Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fa8b6",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: Even [i]if[/i] that declaration was clearly inconsistent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0738e01",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "Laefe: ...But he wouldn't—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e53a1",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: Your ability to remember must be muddled by the shock of your father's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f58ddd",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: His statement couldn't have possibly been true."
}

{
  "id": "line:09874f0",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: If by some chance it [i]were[/i] true,[p/] that would make [i]you[/i] guilty of perjury."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f22fa2",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: Or perhaps it was [i]Miriam[/i] that was lying in her testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c27dcc",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: If your father's statement [i]were[/i] true,[p/] the court might be inclined to investigate [i]her[/i] for lying on the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:02785c9",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: M-[p/][s/]Ms. Tymora,[p/][s/] are you threatening her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:010d5fb",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: As I said before,[p/] I am merely stating the law."
}

{
  "id": "line:05248ff",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "RubyC: ...I'm just asking her to consider the potential consequences of what she says next."
}

{
  "id": "line:0536b16",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "Laefe: ... [h=\"What do I do?\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c486d0",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_3",
  "text": "Damn it...[p/] She was really pressuring Laefe to side with her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e92697",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "She was clearly conflicted though...[p/] Wasn't there anything I could do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce6e21",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "I could feel a sense of clarity when I looked at her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da8120",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "Was the Eye of Horus reacting to her stress?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b747ac",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm sorry.[p/] I need time to think."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f27de",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "Laefe: Please don't stare at me like that, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:050fadd",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] don't stare at her like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c9367",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "Tyrion, focus."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fbf4b",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "RubyC: Wait a minute..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c176af",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "RubyC: Y-[p/][s/]Your Honor![p/][s/] I would like to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:01085ae",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "It was too late."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a8614",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "I activated the Empowered Eye once again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b59ec1",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "There [i]had[/i] to be something in her mind that I could use."
}

{
  "id": "line:036caaa",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "The state of her father's inheritance was the backbone of my case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad2f1e",
  "node": "LiafalObjC4_4",
  "text": "Was there anything in her mind that could definitively prove what was on his will?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e85e8d",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Miriam"
}

{
  "id": "line:05de484",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: Why would Miriam say those things?[p/] Am I misremembering what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:084d54d",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: No.[p/] I would have remembered something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acf54a",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: She must be trying to protect Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc3724",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "So Miriam's testimony [i]was[/i] a conscious lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:06af9f8",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Beatrice's inheritance wasn't revoked until the night of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a79c21",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": ":William|Autopsy Report: William Frega"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ca79a",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: Father...[p/] I know we had our differences,[p/] but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:029b8e8",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: I did love you,[p/] and I never wanted you to die."
}

{
  "id": "line:070aa4f",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] She seemed genuinely surprised and regretful about his death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa251d",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "From our encounter earlier,[p/] I knew that Beatrice had an accomplice.[p/] But I doubted that it was Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0271e5b",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Ruby"
}

{
  "id": "line:062dd4c",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: Ruby Tymora...[p/] I've heard stories about her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c50241",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: I never expected Beatrice to hire someone like her."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a75b9",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: I wonder if she'll be at the will-reading tomorrow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4400a",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "A will reading?[p/] Was it for William Frega's will?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0919e23",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Lloyd|Liafal's Engagement|Beatrice's Inheritance 1"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1dfd3",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: As much as I hate to admit it,[p/] this trial is a perfect opportunity to back out of my marriage to Jaiden."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d42375",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: Von Sanctus' holdings are weakening by the day.[p/] I doubt he'll be able to put up much resistance."
}

{
  "id": "line:045d2f6",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: And once Beatrice inherits the estate,[p/] we might be able to rebuild our family."
}

{
  "id": "line:025236d",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "She was assuming that Beatrice would inherit House Frega..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e4e22",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "That confidence must've meant that she was certain of what was in William's will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f082c1",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "But how could I prove that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:066ca05",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Tyrion"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a042bc",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: This man...[p/] I thought Aster hired him to [i]protect[/i] Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0116d83",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: Is someone paying him to betray us...?[p/] Or is Beatrice actually—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3154f",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: No.[p/] She can't be."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3ceb5",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: I refuse to believe that she'd do something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cdcf1",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "I didn't get any leads from that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5082f",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Beatrice|Beatrice's Blindness"
}

{
  "id": "line:07deedc",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: Beatrice...[p/] After all these years,[p/] she's finally returned..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c63ca",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: I can't believe that [i]this[/i] is how things have ended up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb64f7",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: If only I were as strong as her.[p/] I'd be able to endure this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:081eb52",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Sword of Spell Eating|Sword of Spell Eating 2|Sword of Spell Eating 3|Missing Sword|Celeste's Sword"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9a144",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: How did both of the swords find their way into Beatrice's room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c00ae",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: Could Tracker have...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a553b4",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: No...[p/] Ms. McCoy's sword is one thing,[p/] but he couldn't have possibly broken into the Haroldson gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:09733f2",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: Although...[p/] He was extremely fixated on it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0598cd7",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "...What?[p/] Did she know [i]how[/i] Celeste's sword was taken?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0418a76",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] As much as I wanted to follow that lead,[p/] it would be all for nothing if the trial ended now."
}

{
  "id": "line:081c687",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "I needed to try something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0c837",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Liafal's Testimony|Liafal's Testimony 2|Liafal Frega"
}

{
  "id": "line:09fa171",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: I need to make sure that I tell the truth [i]without[/i] harming Miriam or Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d228e",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: Beatrice couldn't have possibly done this,[p/] and I'm sure Miriam also has her reasons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0180982",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: They couldn't rely on me back then,[p/] but they can now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd36a5",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "Laefe: Why am I thinking about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ee78b",
  "node": "LiafalEye",
  "text": "That didn’t evoke any useful thoughts from her."
}

{
  "id": "line:078a641",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "Judge: I believe you've had enough time for deliberation, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e17b4c",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "Judge: Are you able to prove the defendant's motive or not?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0f7b4",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm not, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0880bb0",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "Tyrion: At least, not [i]yet[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a106a",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's clear we won't get anywhere until we can confirm the state of William Frega's will."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d61c3",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "Tyrion: And we can easily confirm that tomorrow morning..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e0b47",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "Tyrion: When William Frega's will is read to his family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aac9a1",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "RubyC: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:097e4a9",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "Judge: I see...[p/] Once his will is read,[p/] it will become public record."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3cd6b",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "Judge: I see no harm in waiting until tomorrow morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfcaa8",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "Judge: I have no choice but to suspend this trial until William Frega's will can be read."
}

{
  "id": "line:044b0b9",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "RubyC: This is ludicrous![p/][s/] The case against my client is completely outrageous!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2bb73",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "RubyC: We've spent the entire court proceedings arguing if her motive even [i]exists[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03dc153",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye",
  "text": "RubyC: The prosecution has very little evidence that [i]physically[/i] implicates my client!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d8e9d",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora.[p/] You [i]clearly[/i] don't believe that the defendant had anything to do with the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:04316ef",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "RubyC: Of course, I don't.[p/] She's completely innocent."
}

{
  "id": "line:090d475",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, if [i]your[/i] client didn't murder the victim, who did?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec4a6e",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "RubyC: You little—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00aabe0",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor.[p/] With no other suspects,[p/] are you in a position to pass a verdict?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a969d",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Judge: No...[p/] I am not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0044880",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "I felt a bit guilty for using this trick against Ms. Tymora,[p/] but I knew Beatrice was guilty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a35ce6",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "She'd always taught me to use any ploy I could to win anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:050e14f",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert is correct.[p/] The court does not have enough information to pass a verdict."
}

{
  "id": "line:059a776",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Judge: Until the Inquisition has time to investigate these new developments,[p/] I will be suspending today's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0883939",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Judge: We will resume the trial tomorrow afternoon.[p/] Court is adjourned."
}

{
  "id": "line:0234ff1",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, [i]that[/i] happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b842a",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry,[p/] I kind of acted without thinking..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce8523",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Celeste: But the weirdest part is that Steelwind somehow [i]knew[/i] you would do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fa64c",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] That [i]is[/i] strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:06620a4",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Did she seriously predict what I'd do off of that [i]one[/i] conversation?"
}

{
  "id": "line:005489b",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_3",
  "text": "Considering how things turned out,[p/] she was right on the mark."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ae87d",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_3",
  "text": "But that was still a gigantic gamble on her part."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca6d43",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] we have some time to ourselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d42fe",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'd really like to catch up on some sleep."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7dae7",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah.[p/] Today's been exhausting for a [i]lot[/i] of reasons."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c3f81",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_3",
  "text": "And my work had only started...[p/] I still had no idea who Beatrice's accomplice was."
}

{
  "id": "line:06df566",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_3",
  "text": "The will reading was just an opportunity to buy us some time..."
}

{
  "id": "line:098a125",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_3",
  "text": "So the question remained...[p/] Who [i]really[/i] murdered William Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec6a51",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: What the [i]hell[/i] was that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1a82d",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: Why is your [i]son[/i] filling in for Aria?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08dbd0a",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: You told me he was harmless!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1fbde",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Ruby: Listen![p/] I [i]have[/i] the situation under control."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c177e",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Eris: ...Hmph,[p/] if that's true,[p/] I'd hate to see a situation you consider \"out of control\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ace5fe",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Ruby: Eris..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf613b",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Eris: My father is not pleased with today's developments."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac501e",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Eris: You promised that the verdict would be passed [i]before[/i] William Frega's will became public record."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a08ef4",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Eris: This has thrown quite a wrench into the plan."
}

{
  "id": "line:0347a35",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Ruby: I-[p/][s/]I understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:094751c",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert is just confused,[p/] but he's not a threat to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4f748",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Eris: We'd better hope you're right, Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0929d1c",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Eris: ...Or else your poor ward might suffer the same fate as Prosecutor Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:06dfa60",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Ruby: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:066e4ae",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Eris: House Frega is too important a prize for us to let go."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecaf34",
  "node": "LiafalAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Eris: Bring us results, Tymora,[p/] or else we might [i]continue[/i] to take more drastic measures."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc8a7f",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Laefe: Miriam![p/][s/] There you are![p/] Where have you been?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c8073",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Miriam: I've been speaking to father's attorneys.[p/] His estate is in absolute chaos."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c463d0",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Laefe: Do you really need to do that?[p/] I'm sure they have it under control."
}

{
  "id": "line:0847955",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Miriam: These vultures are practically salivating over Father's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:08779af",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Miriam: The will hasn't even been read,[p/] yet I can barely keep these cretins from robbing us blind."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c607f",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Laefe: O-[p/][s/]Oh,[p/] I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:070245c",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...You were quiet at the funeral this morning.[p/] Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de9014",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Miriam: Of course I am."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2d8d5",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Laefe: Miriam, I know things are chaotic now,[p/] but we'll get through this together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a14c20",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Laefe: Beatrice has finally returned.[p/] Maybe now we can—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c04b9f",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Miriam: ...And why do you think she returned?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03494f3",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Miriam: She was clearly doing quite well for herself.[p/] She could have come back at any time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca49f5",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Miriam: ...And the very night she returns,[p/] Father ends up with a knife in his throat."
}

{
  "id": "line:053a949",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Laefe: How can you say that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e418e",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Laefe: Weren't you trying to protect her at the trial yesterday?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8ee6f",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2",
  "text": "Laefe: Don't tell me you actually believe she did this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0768b75",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: Her attorney is Ruby Tymora, Laefe.[p/] Even [i]you[/i] can put together what that means."
}

{
  "id": "line:0016107",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Laefe: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] I know her![p/][s/] She would never do this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0316e6c",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: You [i]know[/i] her?![p/][s/] Laefe, she's a completely different person!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3fb51",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: She might as well be a stranger to us!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a463b",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Laefe: How can you say that?![p/][s/] You adored her so much!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbe91b",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: I [i]did[/i], Laefe![p/][s/] But things have obviously changed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:082c0fd",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: [i]Everything[/i] changed after she abandoned us!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02709f4",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: The only difference is that [i]I'm[/i] not going to fall apart over it like some sad, mournful child!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a1006",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Laefe: M-[p/][s/]Miriam,[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d38388",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Laefe: ...I just wanted us to be a family again..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0974e3a",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: Well, you're going to be sorely disappointed,[p/][s/] just like you always are!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02403ce",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: You always live in a land of fairy tales!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddbe0f",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: Then you act like the victim when reality fails to live up to that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a89433",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Laefe: I-[p/][s/]I don't do that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb5067",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: Wake up, Laefe![p/][s/] She's not here for us![p/][s/] She's here for Father's money!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03fbf0d",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: Now, if you're done weeping over the absolute disaster that is our family,[p/] [i]I[/i] need to think about what all of this means for my future!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a99195",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Miriam: I suggest you do the same!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01427d0",
  "node": "MiriamAndLaefe2b",
  "text": "Laefe: ...What do I do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:064f0a2",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Judge: Court is now resumed for the trial of Beatrice Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:08547ae",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Judge: Let us review yesterday's proceedings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a874c2",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Judge: There was much debate over William Frega's inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:031d782",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Judge: More specifically,[p/] it was unknown whether the defendant had any claim to her father's inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d8769",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Judge: This detail was crucial in determining whether the defendant even [i]had[/i] a motive to commit the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf7326",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Judge: Luckily,[p/] the victim's will was supposedly read earlier today,[p/] and it is now a part of the public record."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c8865",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Judge: What were the results of the will reading, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b03fe",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Tyrion: William Frega was planning to leave all of his assets to Jaiden von Sanctus:[p/] his hopeful son-in-law."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e04354",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Tyrion: However,[p/] this was predicated on the condition that Jaiden marry the victim's daughter:[p/] Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d93e2c",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was clear to anyone present that Ms. Laefe would never follow through on this engagement."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fe029",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Tyrion: If the engagement is not made in six months,[p/] William Frega's assets would be divided among his three daughters."
}

{
  "id": "line:0faad53",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Judge: I see.[p/] So there was no mention of the defendant's disinheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ef3d3",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Tyrion: Correct, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fb8d1",
  "node": "CourtroomC42",
  "text": "Tyrion: This means that the defendant [i]did[/i] have something to gain from the victim's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adf63f",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "RubyC: Your Honor.[p/] Despite the confusion around the victim's inheritance,[p/] there is still very little physical evidence that implicates my client."
}

{
  "id": "line:07623be",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: May I remind you that Miriam Frega was [i]not[/i] telling the truth in yesterday's proceedings?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e34dc2",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]That[/i] itself,[p/] is extremely suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb1c12",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "RubyC: ...And?[p/] William Frega was clearly not above manipulation and lying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0788521",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "RubyC: You can't prove that she [i]knowingly[/i] gave false testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a1d95",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'll admit that I can't prove that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8903a",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll also admit that there's a lack of [i]apparent[/i] physical evidence to substantiate our case."
}

{
  "id": "line:004b8b1",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Which is why the prosecution would like to call Harold Haroldson to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:015568a",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Judge: ...Lord Haroldson?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab3841",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Sword of Spell Eating clearly plays a large role in the murder,[p/] and its theft is one of the few pieces of physical evidence in this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c57558",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: As the gallery's curator,[p/] I believe he can further elaborate on how the Sword was stolen that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b0c8c",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "More specifically,[p/] I could find out more about what [i]he[/i] did on the night of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:056249c",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Judge: I see..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ed506",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Judge: Bailiff.[p/] Please escort Lord Haroldson to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c38e10",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Witness.[p/] Please state your name and occupation for the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:017b76b",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Harold: Of course.[p/] My name is Harold Haroldson."
}

{
  "id": "line:06feba1",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Harold: I am the owner and curator of the Haroldson Hall of History,[p/] located in Homherith."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4d5e6",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Judge: That's quite the...[p/] alliterative occupation."
}

{
  "id": "line:020b85f",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Harold.[p/] Could you please testify to the court about how you discovered that the Sword of Spell Eating was stolen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f8178",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Harold: If it will help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b950ec",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Harold: I was keeping an eye on my gallery's exhibits when I realized that my familiar hadn't returned."
}

{
  "id": "line:033a6c1",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Harold: I called to him telepathically,[p/] but he didn't respond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce16b2",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Harold: I became worried,[p/] so I went around the manor to search for him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf8984",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Harold: About an hour later,[p/] I returned to the gallery and discovered that the exhibit holding the Sword of Spell Eating was completely destroyed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3e703",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Harold: The artifact was missing.[p/] So I reported the crime to the knights at the Ball,[p/] and they activated a discreet lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4882b",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Harold: Luckily,[p/] we found the Sword [i]and[/i] my familiar later that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:06dbdd5",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you went to search for your monkey.[p/] And [i]that's[/i] why you didn't witness the theft?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0e51c",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Harold: Yes.[p/] The thief was probably waiting for me to leave."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a27da8",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "Harold: They must have wanted to commit the crime without anyone seeing them."
}

{
  "id": "line:04dcbc8",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "...[i]Or[/i] his testimony is completely full of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da2fdd",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "His \"search\" for Eugene must have been a cover that he's using to hide his actions that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b001b0",
  "node": "CourtroomC42_2",
  "text": "So how do you prove that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0479569",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you referring to Eugene?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0760d8f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Judge: \"Eugene\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0679a51",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eugene Haroldson, Your Honor.[p/] It's the name of the witness's familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c54671",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: Yes.[p/] Eugene is a spry orangutan monkey.[p/] He helps me with my day-to-day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0203454",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Judge: ...I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c739eb",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] you said that he hadn't returned.[p/] Does this mean he left you earlier in the night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f7400",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: Yes.[p/] He always likes to explore large buildings like Frega Manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b9796",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: But he usually doesn't leave for that long."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ff123",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: Does he typically ignore you like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd3c81",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: Sometimes.[p/] He's a young boy.[p/] So he likes to have his privacy."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c6229",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: I try not to pry,[p/] but I was wary of what would happen if a noble or a knight came across him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0827adc",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: He usually knows not to bother people,[p/] but you never know what might happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:08db35e",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: You left the gallery room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04775ed",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: Yes.[p/] As I said,[p/] I was worried that something had happened to Eugene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c88be9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: Where did you go during your search?"
}

{
  "id": "line:069528a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: Eugene usually knows to stay out of people's bedrooms.[p/] So I went downstairs and searched for him there."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b0a42",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: I checked the Bathroom,[p/] Sitting Room,[p/] and Coat Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9f4f3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: Then I finally checked the Kitchen and Pantry.[p/] He might have gone there to steal some snacks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff725a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you didn't find him in any of those places."
}

{
  "id": "line:09667e5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: No, I didn't."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a80d0b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: If I recall correctly,[p/] the glass was completely shattered."
}

{
  "id": "line:013c43d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: This is despite the presence of several abjuration spells that protected it."
}

{
  "id": "line:027350f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: Yes.[p/] It would have taken an extremely powerful spell to break it like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:093fcf6",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: As you saw,[p/] the glass display was shattered into pieces."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc5fbf",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] Harold told me that the thief shattered the glass while the protective wards were active."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7ab1d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "But if he was involved,[p/] could he just have been lying?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0623b09",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: The artifact was missing.[p/] So I reported the crime to the knights at the Ball, and they activated a discreet lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c78ac2",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Sword of Spell Eating makes its wielder immune to magical effects.[p/] What use would the lockdown have been?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d10863",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: Honestly,[p/] not much."
}

{
  "id": "line:01573a8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: The wielder would have been immune to the [b]Anti-Magic Fields[/b] [i]and[/i] the spells that prevented people from leaving."
}

{
  "id": "line:0767cd7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: But at that point,[p/] the Kingsguard just wanted to activate it for good measure."
}

{
  "id": "line:018c777",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: As you probably know,[p/] the Kingsguard found the Sword of Spell Eating in the defendant's room."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bf3bf",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Harold: Eugene finally responded to my telepathic messages.[p/] I met up with him in the gallery room before they finally found the artifact."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fb74c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "CELESTE: He says that he went around the manor to look for Eugene."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d9bfa",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you think he's telling the truth?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1445f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe,[p/] but his so-called \"search\" for Eugene gave him a good excuse to be unaccounted for."
}

{
  "id": "line:05918fc",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a decent alibi,[p/] but it's not without its flaws."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3b59d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Harold",
  "text": "I just needed to poke some holes in it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0896f2e",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "His statement just now was missing some details."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9f1bf",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "I needed to ask for something I could use against him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4793d",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "How did you find the Sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f259a",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did you eventually find the Sword of Spell Eating?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d60cbd",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Harold: The Kingsguard and I slowly and carefully checked each room in the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0951d5a",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Harold: After about an hour,[p/] we finally found the artifact under the bed in the defendant's room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b12d84",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "That must be where Tracker hides the \"sticks\" that he finds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbbe10",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Now that I thought about it,[p/] [i]he[/i] probably stole Celeste's sword too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf8d45",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "How did you find Eugene?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b18233",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did you eventually find Eugene that night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8ff44",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Harold: After an hour of silence,[p/] he finally responded to my telepathic messages."
}

{
  "id": "line:0333cf4",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Harold: He met up with me in the gallery before we went to search for the Sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a31441",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Tyrion: So this would have been [i]after[/i] the theft was reported."
}

{
  "id": "line:093ec78",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Harold: Yes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdfce7",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "He would have had to pick up Eugene after he murdered the Duke."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a86661",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "This must be the alibi they're using to account for the time that no one could see Eugene."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c341d",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] this detail could be extremely important.[p/] Please add it to your testimony, witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:056ee81",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Harold: Harold."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bfe05",
  "node": "HaroldPressState",
  "text": "Tyrion: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...[p/] Of course, Harold."
}

{
  "id": "line:05abf56",
  "node": "HaroldObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Harold.[p/] You found Eugene [i]before[/i] you went to search for the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:074ebe7",
  "node": "HaroldObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: This would mean that this all happened while the lockdown was still active.[p/] Am I correct?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb822e",
  "node": "HaroldObj",
  "text": "Harold: Yes.[p/] As much as I was worried about the artifact,[p/] Eugene's safety was far more important."
}

{
  "id": "line:0761aef",
  "node": "HaroldObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's the thing, Harold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0199b3d",
  "node": "HaroldObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: You said that after an hour of silence,[p/] you finally received a telepathic message back from Eugene."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d6e48",
  "node": "HaroldObj",
  "text": "RubyC: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:028b093",
  "node": "HaroldObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: So that leaves one question."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b8877",
  "node": "HaroldObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did you communicate with Eugene telepathically..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d4ee8",
  "node": "HaroldObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...if you were [i]both[/i] within an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b699e0",
  "node": "HaroldObj",
  "text": "Harold: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d732d9",
  "node": "HaroldObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Harold.[p/] In response to the theft,[p/] the Kingsguard activated the lockdown system to prevent anyone from leaving."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b09ce2",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That same lockdown system would have placed an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b] over every [i]inch[/i] of that manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:005c8e9",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That [b]Field[/b] [i]should[/i] have suppressed the telepathic abilities given to you by [b]Familial Bond[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:018c355",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You wouldn't have been able to speak with Eugene at all!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec5548",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "RubyC: Please.[p/] Cuthbert is blowing this entire thing out of proportion."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e3bee",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "RubyC: [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b] is a resource-intensive spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:088494a",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "RubyC: We can't assume that they managed to cover [i]every[/i] inch of the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e31184",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "RubyC: Especially,[p/] the areas that would only be accessible to a small animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:061e2c8",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora.[p/] Let's assume that Eugene managed to reach some sort of blind spot in the lockdown system."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f66ea",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: The magical telepathy granted by [b]Familial Bond[/b] connects [i]two[/i] people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e15f7d",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even [i]if[/i] Eugene wasn't affected by the [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b],[p/][s/] Harold would be!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d61af",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "Harold: That's very true...[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d0966",
  "node": "HaroldObj2",
  "text": "Harold: So how did I hear him that night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c6679",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's only one answer that makes sense, Harold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0eec7",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]did[/i] hear Eugene telepathically!"
}

{
  "id": "line:056b808",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Because [i]Eugene[/i] was wielding the Sword of Spell Eating!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa5f05",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "RubyC: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e301d",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "Harold: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ffd6a",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "Judge: I'm sorry,[p/] Mr. Cuthbert..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b1c15",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "Judge: But are you saying that the Sword of Spell Eating was stolen by the witness's pet [i]monkey[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b4f3c",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I am, Your Honor![p/][s/] It's the only way the witness's testimony makes sense!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4a614",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "RubyC: ... [h=\"He wouldn't say something so ridiculous|if it weren't true...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c38d9",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "She didn't have a rebuttal.[p/] I could push this while I still had the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0156e20",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Harold Haroldson.[p/][s/] [i]You[/i] were the one who \"stole\" the Sword of Spell Eating, weren't you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0207a4b",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "Harold: And what reason would I have to steal something that already belonged to me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b1e8f",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was to take suspicion off of you,[p/][s/] because [i]you[/i] were the one who had William Frega killed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ded00",
  "node": "HaroldObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You staged a robbery and used the Sword of Spell Eating to make Eugene invisible!"
}

{
  "id": "line:063d6d0",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then you sent him through the manor's ventilation system—[p/]all so you could have him [i]murder[/i] William Frega in his study!"
}

{
  "id": "line:031b752",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "RubyC: Well done, Cuthbert.[p/] I suppose you just can't stop yourself from pursuing a lying witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad5c29",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's what I do best, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:06994e2",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "RubyC: ...Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:073de9b",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "RubyC: Witness.[p/] Do you have anything to say in your defense?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0452430",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "Harold: It's quite obvious,[p/] but I completely refute the prosecution's allegations. [h=\"He's misguided,|but he's just doing his job.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e85a6b",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] I was expecting his thoughts to be hostile like before."
}

{
  "id": "line:000e550",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "RubyC: Then,[p/] do you also refute your statement about Eugene telepathically speaking with you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3365b",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "Harold: ...I know better than to lie on the stand to try to save myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a799f",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "Harold: I can't explain [i]how[/i] it happened,[p/] but I stand behind my testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6bef8",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "Harold: Eugene [i]did[/i] telepathically contact me during the lockdown. [h=\"But how did he do it?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:045b089",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "Wait.[p/] So he [i]didn't[/i] know how that telepathic communication happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:075b39c",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "Maybe he wasn't thinking about it when he planned the murder with Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca5154",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "RubyC: And that's your position, Cuthbert?[p/] That the witness sent a [i]monkey[/i] to murder William Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0178796",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It may sound ridiculous,[p/] but it's the only thing that makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a9e88",
  "node": "HaroldObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Or do you have any evidence to refute that, Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd5da6",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: No.[p/] I fully and wholeheartedly agree with you, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f1bb4",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2e335",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "Judge: ...Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Did you forget that you were [i]prosecuting[/i] Beatrice Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0430f42",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: Your Honor.[p/] Even as a prosecutor,[p/] it's clear that Cuthbert just can't [i]stop[/i] himself from finding the true culprit."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a8076",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Wait![p/][s/] I [i]also[/i] meant to say that the defendant conspired with the witness to [i]commit[/i] the crime!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb8b0d",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: Oh, really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e232d3",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: And do you have any proof of this conspiracy to commit?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b4aa4",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0328cc5",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: Of course, you don't."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a46409",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]But, even so—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f05ac8",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: But let's assume that you [i]did[/i] have evidence to prove your statement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8490a",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: If this was [i]really[/i] a plot formed by my client and the witness,[p/] what would my client even contribute to this plan?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08136b9",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: From what you said,[p/] this plot was completely carried out by Lord Haroldson and his familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b04eee",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Well..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0247279",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...The glass![p/][s/] He would have needed a powerful mage like the defendant to break the Sword's display case and stage the robbery!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0183385",
  "node": "HaroldObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: ...So her contribution to the murder was breaking some glass."
}

{
  "id": "line:0302b75",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: Can you [i]prove[/i] that my client shattered the display case?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0920ac1",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: And can you prove that she did so [i]knowing[/i] that it would somehow lead to her father's death?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e98314",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "I [i]might[/i] have been a little too eager to prove Harold's guilt..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7e536",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: The physical evidence against my client was almost non-existent in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b40c0e",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: Meanwhile,[p/] it seems the [i]prosecution[/i] has just brought forward physical evidence that implicates Lord Haroldson."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a00977",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: Physical evidence that is supported by his own testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:06381ac",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "Harold: ... [h=\"There <i>has</i> to be some|explanation for this.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfe566",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: Cuthbert.[p/] Didn't you ask me something yesterday?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0577125",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: If [i]my[/i] client didn't kill the victim,[p/] then who did?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa4ce0",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: I suppose I should thank you for finding the answer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e56878",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "Damn it...[p/] All I did was make it [i]more[/i] difficult to prove my case."
}

{
  "id": "line:055fa5f",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "But Harold [i]had[/i] to be involved in this...[p/] I wasn't wrong about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da54bf",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "Only Eugene would be small enough to traverse the air vents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4b142",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "Wasn't there anything else I could use?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0231ca4",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "...With the threat of indictment,[p/] Harold [i]must've[/i] been stressed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0133c0e",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "It had gotten me out of tight spots before.[p/] Maybe I could [i]find[/i] the evidence in his mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ed14b",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: ...Hmph.[p/] You can use every trick you have, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:08eaaa8",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: It won't help you."
}

{
  "id": "line:007fac9",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "I calmed my mind and focused the Eye of Horus on him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eea810",
  "node": "HaroldObj6",
  "text": "I needed to find something,[p/] [i]anything[/i],[p/] that might tie the murder to Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e09d4",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: Hm...[p/] It appears the boy thinks that I was involved in this."
}

{
  "id": "line:091abc7",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: Although,[p/] given what he said,[p/] I can't blame him for thinking that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9d98b",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: I truly wonder about what really happened, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5cda5",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "What...?[p/] He was talking as if he didn't have any hand in this."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c8146",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "But that can't be true, can it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:002db93",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Eugene|Familial Bond"
}

{
  "id": "line:0223094",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: Eugene...[p/] Just what [i]were[/i] you doing that night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:035883f",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: Did you really wield the Sword,[p/] if only for a brief moment?"
}

{
  "id": "line:095619a",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Wait...[p/] He should have known [i]exactly[/i] where Eugene was that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0514123",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Why would his thoughts say that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad2157",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Beatrice|Beatrice's Inheritance 0|Beatrice's Inheritance 1|Beatrice's Inheritance|Beatrice's Blindness"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a25de",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: It's truly a shame that Beatrice was driven to flee from her own family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0857cd5",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: If only I'd introduced myself to her.[p/] Perhaps we could have found a solution together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2d3ed",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "He...[p/] doesn't know Beatrice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:013da92",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "But, how?![p/][s/] She planned the murder with him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b0fa6",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Sword of Spell Eating|Sword of Spell Eating 2|Sword of Spell Eating 3"
}

{
  "id": "line:03522b0",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: I can't believe that one of my artifacts was used to commit a [i]murder[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f6189",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: It's completely disrespectful to the culture and history behind it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f13e2d",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Haroldson's Security|Haroldson's Security 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcca5b",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: Not one but [i]two[/i] artifacts were stolen during the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0455044",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: I never expected anyone to completely bypass my security like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0058b2f",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d52c65",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I've gotten myself wrapped in quite the predicament, haven't I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06dfaab",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: Oh, well.[p/] I've gotten out of far worse situations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0617da3",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: I'm sure it will be fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:01038bb",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] William.[p/] It's a shame that things ended up this way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0418364",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: I truly hoped I could show you the value of Wyverngarde's history."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff2f0e",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Earrings of Vitality"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9c0c6",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: At least the Earrings of Vitality were left untouched."
}

{
  "id": "line:057d74c",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: It's one of the few Luminite artifacts I've been able to find."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e0baa",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Armbands of Intellect|Armbands of Intellect 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe3e68",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: The Armbands of Intellect are still missing..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0438830",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: But I inspected it closely before the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:060a619",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: They were still there when I moved them to Frega Manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdb4d2",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: Someone must have stolen it [i]during[/i] the Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:021e8e5",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Right...[p/] I never [i]did[/i] find what happened to the Armbands..."
}

{
  "id": "line:064eb45",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Could there seriously have been a second thief that night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0942755",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Lockdown System|Anti-Magic Field"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8d908",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: Young Tyrion's argument makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0402ee0",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: I couldn't have heard Eugene when the lockdown was active."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f346d",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: What is going on here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f4211",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: ...What?[p/] Why am I thinking about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0933ec3",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Harold: My mind can't be going already, can it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3c1a4",
  "node": "HaroldEye",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] That piece of evidence didn’t evoke any useful thoughts from him."
}

{
  "id": "line:05987f7",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "What...?[p/][s/] What's going on?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a89940",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "He's speaking as if he had no idea what was going on!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b7e35",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "You could guard yourself from the Eye of Horus,[p/] but you couldn't lie to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfcc62",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "And if that was true,[p/][s/] was I wrong about Harold's involvement?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ccba6",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "Is he really innocent?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:094e16c",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "RubyC: ...See anything, Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d959f",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "RubyC: Your Honor.[p/] It's clear that the prosecution has [i]nothing[/i] left to argue."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acce7f",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "RubyC: There's very little evidence implicating my client,[p/] and there's a [i]far[/i] more likely suspect in front of us right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd5063",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "Judge: ...Yes.[p/] I must agree, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d042e",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "Judge: At the very least,[p/] I see no reason to prolong this trial any longer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c78d94",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Wait!"
}

{
  "id": "line:033e3f7",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "Beatrice couldn't have personally done this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb7951",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye",
  "text": "Discounting the fact that she's completely blind,[p/] she was with the two princes for most of the night."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ce89b",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye2",
  "text": "So who actually killed William Frega in his study?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:058a279",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye2",
  "text": "I needed to think about this...[p/] The reason why I suspected Harold in the first place was because of what Tracker said."
}

{
  "id": "line:0864dc6",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tracker's vocabulary is primitive and limited.[p/] He uses the word \"rat\" to describe small creatures that hide and act suspiciously."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b91327",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye2",
  "text": "Celeste: But even if it wasn't an [i]actual[/i] rat,[p/][s/] it still couldn't have been a human, right?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc0346",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're right...[p/] It would have been a small animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:051f1a0",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...A small animal with the strength and dexterity to traverse a small air vent while holding a sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cd13e",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye2",
  "text": "Tracker definitely saw [i]some[/i] kind of animal.[p/] Was it someone [i]else's[/i] familiar?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f19a80",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye3",
  "text": "0"
}

{
  "id": "line:0febb6f",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye3",
  "text": "Right.[p/] It [i]had[/i] to have been Eugene.[p/] Tracker found the Sword in that hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1266b",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye3",
  "text": "No...[p/] It [i]had[/i] to have been Eugene.[p/] Tracker found the Sword in that hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c52e8",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye4",
  "text": "And Eugene couldn't have communicated with Harold unless the Sword protected [i]both[/i] of them from the [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:068a306",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye4",
  "text": "But...[p/][s/] why?[p/] Did Eugene just [i]happen[/i] to be in that hallway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c773b",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye4",
  "text": "That also doesn't explain why the Sword of Spell Eating was even there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0180925",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye4",
  "text": "No...[p/] Tracker said that Eugene came out of the air vent on one side of the hallway.[p/] Then he fled into the air vent on the other side."
}

{
  "id": "line:0407e59",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye4",
  "text": "Even for a small monkey,[p/] those vents would be extremely cramped."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd8f84",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye4",
  "text": "He wouldn't have entered those vents out of mere curiosity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5ea53",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye4",
  "text": "I now knew that [i]Harold[/i] didn't participate in the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dabbe7",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye4",
  "text": "But did he know about what Eugene was doing that night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0adbbfe",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye5",
  "text": "000|020"
}

{
  "id": "line:0679f7b",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye5",
  "text": "No...[p/] I couldn't say for sure [i]why[/i] Eugene was there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6052f",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye5",
  "text": "But it's unlikely that Harold even knew about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f62ab",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "Eugene was acting of his own free will..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cf51f",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "That's...[p/] the explanation that makes the most sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2f5df",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "But how...?[p/][s/] And why?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c98262",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "Harold is the only person who is magically connected to Eugene..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0a8c8",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "And even if Beatrice somehow got Eugene to follow her orders,[p/] she wouldn't have been able to direct his actions telepathically."
}

{
  "id": "line:096b9b0",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "Beatrice couldn't use any other [b]conjuration[/b] spell to contact him, either."
}

{
  "id": "line:06355b5",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "[i]She[/i] was also in the [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b] when she was with Aster."
}

{
  "id": "line:070b0a3",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "So if Eugene was the one who murdered William Frega,[p/] was he acting independently...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a5b51",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "No...[p/] That couldn't be possible..."
}

{
  "id": "line:031074d",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "This plan required knowledge of Frega Manor's ventilation system."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8ae03",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "It also involved murdering William [i]during[/i] the lockdown [i]and[/i] destroying his will."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bf06d",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "Eugene might be smart for a monkey,[p/] but a normal monkey wouldn't have known how to identify and destroy William's will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e78c66",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye6",
  "text": "Even [i]if[/i] Beatrice had somehow trained him to do all this beforehand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0533ecb",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye7",
  "text": "No...[p/] Eugene must have been acting independently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0414d23",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye7",
  "text": "But a normal monkey wouldn't have the intellect to identify and destroy the will."
}

{
  "id": "line:016f066",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye7",
  "text": "So how did he come up with a plan like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9ddd0",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "No...[p/] It couldn't be..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6092c",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "Harold: After the Sword of Spell Eating was reported missing,[p/] I checked the other exhibits."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ea5f7",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "Harold: That's when I discovered that the Armbands of Intellect had been stolen as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:00078be",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "Harold: And unlike the Sword of Spell Eating,[p/] we still haven't found the Armbands."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c3e66",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "I looked at the glass case where the Armbands used to be."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8120b",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "They'd been removed,[p/] but the glass case was completely intact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0458c7a",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "Tyrion: The thief didn't shatter the glass..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c5026",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "Harold: Moreover,[p/] the Armbands were actually replaced with a very well-made replica."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fc0de",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How are they normally disabled?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08719da",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "Harold: They can be turned on and off using a spoken password."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecd1ad",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "Tyrion: And how many people know this password?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08627f8",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "Harold: Only myself.[p/] I personally oversee the transport of these items when they're moved."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f3977",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "Only Harold knew the password,[p/] but someone could have overheard him saying it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0354920",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye8",
  "text": "...Someone that's constantly hanging off of his shoulder."
}

{
  "id": "line:056eb1b",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "...If I didn't play this right,[p/] this ridiculous accusation could end my legal career."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c1e07",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "I would have to be smart about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f90d66",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] I think there's one more witness that can clear up this discrepancy once and for all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0886f3d",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "Tyrion: I believe [i]he[/i] can prove the prosecution's case to the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc2875",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "Judge: Really...?[p/] I frankly find [i]that[/i] hard to believe."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ae0cf",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Please trust me, Your Honor.[p/] There's an element to this that we [i]all[/i] aren't seeing."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b65ba",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "And it's one that no one would believe..."
}

{
  "id": "line:034c465",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "RubyC: Hmph...[p/] What do you have planned now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b4b9a",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "Judge: Very well.[p/] I'll give you one last chance, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ff502",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "Judge: But know that if your next witness fails to unveil any new information,[p/] I won't hesitate to end this trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:09086ce",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "Tyrion: I understand, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0307cbf",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...So, I'm going to need you to bear with me for a moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:05797b2",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye10",
  "text": "Judge: ...Why?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ea700",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] The prosecution calls Eugene the monkey to the stand!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d45262",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Tyrion: U-[p/][s/]Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdc1aa",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Judge: [i]*sigh*[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cffc02",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Judge: Never mind.[p/] I retract my earlier statement.[p/] I'll be passing my verdict—"
}

{
  "id": "line:000bcb4",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Wait![p/][s/] Just [i]bear[/i] with me for a moment!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c7c60",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert![p/][s/] I should find you in contempt for even [i]suggesting[/i] this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:096b779",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Judge: Do you honestly think I'll allow a [i]monkey[/i] to give testimony in [i]my[/i] courtroom?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0017057",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] It sounds pretty out there,[p/] even for us..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b1c4e",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'd like to remind the court of the [i]nature[/i] of Harold's bond with Eugene."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a698a",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eugene is a familiar.[p/] This means that Harold Haroldson [i]can[/i] speak with him telepathically."
}

{
  "id": "line:03394d7",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Tyrion: He can relay Eugene's testimony to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e996c8",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Judge: B-[p/][s/]But this is absolutely—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d89a4",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Show me the law that says an animal can't give testimony, Your Honor!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aadf54",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye11",
  "text": "Tyrion: It may be unprecedented,[p/] but it's [i]not[/i] against the law!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6a74c",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye12",
  "text": "Judge: ...Very well."
}

{
  "id": "line:044ef1b",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye12",
  "text": "RubyC: ...Your Honor,[p/] are you serious?"
}

{
  "id": "line:091fb8b",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye12",
  "text": "Judge: Oh, Ms. Tymora.[p/] I am looking for [i]any[/i] possible reason not to entertain this."
}

{
  "id": "line:032ca7b",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye12",
  "text": "Judge: But Mr. Cuthbert has a point.[p/] There are no laws against his proposal."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a3165",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye12",
  "text": "Judge: So I have no choice but to oblige his frankly [i]insane[/i] request for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ac7f0",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye12",
  "text": "RubyC: Well, I guess it doesn't matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d0ca8",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye12",
  "text": "RubyC: It's not as if [i]this[/i] will reveal anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e7816",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye12",
  "text": "Judge: I can't believe I'm saying this, but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b144c6",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye12",
  "text": "Judge: Bailiff.[p/] Please escort Lord Haroldson's monkey to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7dadd",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "RubyC: ...Witness.[p/] Please state your name and occupation to the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a52d24",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "Tyrion: I could do without the sarcasm, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c4963",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "Eugene: Eugene is Eugene![p/][s/] Eugene monke!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0378b3d",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "RubyC: Bailiff.[p/] Make sure the stenographer gets Haroldson's translations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0150fba",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ugh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:014b873",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "I didn't see the armbands.[p/] He must've been at his normal intelligence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e119de",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "Although,[p/] how [i]would[/i] he even wear them...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0146e52",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "Perhaps he held them in his hands on that night.[p/] They only required physical contact, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:05362e9",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eugene.[p/][s/] Did you steal from the gallery on the night of the murder?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef5c60",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "Eugene: Ook![p/][s/] Ook![p/][s/] Agh![p/][s/] Agh!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aae715",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "Eugene: Eugene never steal from Harold![p/][s/] Eugene respec Harold!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0778775",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Then you'll have no problem testifying about where you went during the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2a147",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye13",
  "text": "Judge: I can't believe I let you convince me to permit this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0562e66",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye14",
  "text": "Eugene: Ook![p/][s/] Ook! [h=\"Eugene explore house!|Eugene look for new place to play!\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfa1a7",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye14",
  "text": "Eugene: Agh![p/][s/] Agh! [h=\"Eugene also look for spiders!|Spiders yum yum!\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06255ec",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye14",
  "text": "Eugene: Ook? [h=\"You think Eugene steal|Armbands of Intellect?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:086fee6",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye14",
  "text": "Eugene: Ook![p/][s/] Agh! [h=\"Eugene never steal from Harold!|Harold friend!\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a10c27",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye14",
  "text": "Eugene: Ook![p/][s/] Ook![p/][s/] Agh![p/][s/] Agh! [h=\"Eugene always Harold's friend!|Apes strong together!\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0307744",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye14",
  "text": "RubyC: Wow.[p/] You did it, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:067d0e3",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye14",
  "text": "RubyC: You blew this case wide open..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d94175",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye14",
  "text": "Celeste: Is this [i]really[/i] going to help us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b06c45",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Look...[p/] You'll just have to trust me on this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0368076",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye14",
  "text": "Celeste: I trust you...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9df81",
  "node": "HaroldAfterEye14",
  "text": "...That sentence sounded like it turned into a question at the end."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb8da3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Eugene explore house! Eugene look for new place to play!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c59c27",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: But Harold is an associate of House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bdc84",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Surely you've visited Frega Manor before that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0187a23",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Manor constantly changes.[p/][s/] William always doing renovations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e090dc",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: There's always a new discovery to be made!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c03a7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "I suppose that made sense.[p/] William certainly had the gold for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c745ba",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] what else did you do that night, Eugene?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af4994",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Eugene also look for spiders! Spiders yum yum!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01eb73c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you enjoy eating spiders?"
}

{
  "id": "line:018e1d7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Spiders good![p/][s/] Rich in nutrients!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c74f3b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa6e15",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Celeste: Some cultures in the Eastern Kingdoms eat roasted crickets."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9e519",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Celeste: I've tried them.[p/] They're actually not bad if they're prepared correctly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0460c93",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't think I could ever be that adventurous..."
}

{
  "id": "line:015b116",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Judge: ...Can we [i]please[/i] stay on topic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0527af8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: You think Eugene steal Armbands of Intellect?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d52875",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wasn't accusing you of anything, Eugene."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a26ba",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Perhaps you accidentally unlocked the case and took them thinking they were some sort of toy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb82f4",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: This could all be an honest mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae8d76",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Eugene not dum dum."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f1fd7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Eugene know how important artifacts are to Harold.[p/] Eugene never take from him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0724dd4",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Eugene never steal from Harold! Harold friend!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03bcd25",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: You might not have [i]knowingly[/i] done it,[p/] but perhaps you took one of the artifacts by accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:05328d4",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: E-[p/][s/]Eugene never do that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7db78",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then how do you explain your brief contact with the Sword of Spell Eating?"
}

{
  "id": "line:031df00",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Harold couldn't have telepathically contacted you unless one of you was wielding it."
}

{
  "id": "line:079bbc9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc9563",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Eugene don't understand question."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6a733",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Right...[p/] He probably wouldn't understand how the Sword worked without his heightened intelligence."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e9968",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Eugene always Harold's friend! Apes strong together!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4c0df",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you consider yourself close to Harold?"
}

{
  "id": "line:065c8ed",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "RubyC: I would guess so.[p/] They [i]literally[/i] have a magical connection with each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:07dabbb",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right.[p/] I suppose the bond between a mage and his familiar [i]would[/i] require a lot of trust."
}

{
  "id": "line:0298217",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Harold save Eugene from bad man years ago.[p/][s/] Eugene would never betray..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f1c4c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you're a rescue."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c53d59",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Bad man lock Eugene in cage.[p/][s/] He tell people to throw peanuts at Eugene..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbf42f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Eugene: Harold take Eugene away from that prison.[p/][s/] Lock up bad man."
}

{
  "id": "line:072d20d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "He seemed to genuinely care for Harold.[p/] Could [i]that[/i] be why he did this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07358b9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "He clearly feels indebted to him.[p/] That might have been his motive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3ea0b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know it looks bad,[p/][s/] but I [i]swear[/i] there's more to this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d4c8f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Celeste: If you say so..."
}

{
  "id": "line:018526b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "There had to be [i]something[/i] in his statements."
}

{
  "id": "line:067e7d7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "He had to have been wearing the Armbands on the night of the murder.[p/] Which thought revealed that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd19cc",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Think about how Tracker spoke.[p/] Was there anything different about the way Eugene was speaking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ac62e",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] The witness's thoughts contradict the evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:01555ea",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Judge: ...Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] The \"witness's\" statement was many things.[p/] But it was not contradictory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0760527",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right...[p/] I suppose I see what you mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf1aba",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "...Wait a minute."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4e951",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eugene.[p/] I asked you before if you stole anything from Harold's gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:087f2ff",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "Eugene: Eugene know![p/][s/] Eugene would never steal from Harold!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05abfaa",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "RubyC: Cuthbert.[p/] Don't waste our time by having him repeat that statement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0793fcf",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's the thing, Ms. Tymora.[p/] That's [i]not[/i] the same statement he made in his testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:089cf01",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I asked the witness if he stole an [i]artifact[/i] from the gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8b3b0",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I never mentioned the Armbands of Intellect!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0209eab",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "Eugene: O-[p/][s/]Ook?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aeb1dc",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "RubyC: What are you talking about now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00247dd",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "RubyC: The witness lacks the understanding to differentiate between the artifacts."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eab056",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: If that's true,[p/] why did he use its [i]actual[/i] name?"
}

{
  "id": "line:008a261",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "Judge: ...I'm afraid I don't understand what you mean, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8a012",
  "node": "EugeneObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor.[p/] Animals can't speak the same way that humans do."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a486f",
  "node": "EugeneObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even when a telepathic link is established,[p/] their vocabulary is extremely limited."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d28e5c",
  "node": "EugeneObj2",
  "text": "Celeste: Right.[p/] Tracker called the Sword of Spell Eating a \"stick\" before."
}

{
  "id": "line:094a527",
  "node": "EugeneObj2",
  "text": "Celeste: It was hard to understand what he [i]really[/i] meant."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c395d",
  "node": "EugeneObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Exactly.[p/] So that raises the question:[p/][s/] [i]how[/i] did Eugene know they were [i]called[/i] the \"Armbands of Intellect\"?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c8a7c",
  "node": "EugeneObj2",
  "text": "Wait...[p/] How [i]did[/i] he know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c694c9",
  "node": "EugeneObj2",
  "text": "The Armbands were stolen during the Lords' Ball and replaced with a well-made replica."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d3d9f",
  "node": "EugeneObj2",
  "text": "If he [i]had[/i] worn the Armbands when he was sneaking through the vents,[p/] he would have never had the opportunity to put them back..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d93446",
  "node": "EugeneObj2",
  "text": "And the Armbands were [i]still[/i] missing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0caec1b",
  "node": "EugeneObj3",
  "text": "No...[p/] Eugene must have worn the Armbands when Tracker caught him sneaking through the vents."
}

{
  "id": "line:096e1f6",
  "node": "EugeneObj3",
  "text": "The Armbands were still missing,[p/] and the investigation would have prevented him from discreetly putting them back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be63c8",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "It couldn't be...[p/] Was he really—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe8096",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "The Armbands were designed to be worn by humans.[p/] So Eugene couldn't wear them on his arms..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ad668",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "So where [i]would[/i] he wear them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ff3a0",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "I initially thought that just he carried them,[p/] but there's a far simpler explanation."
}

{
  "id": "line:074c534",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eugene.[p/] Do you still maintain that you didn't steal the Armbands of Intellect?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ebc35",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "Eugene: Eugene told you already![p/][s/] Eugene never steal from Harold!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1cf35",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then I suppose you wouldn't mind—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0915149",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: —taking off your hat!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f7ead",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "RubyC: ...You can't be serious, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffd78e",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "RubyC: Do you seriously think he's wearing them right [i]now[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddd5ed",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's the only thing that makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:022ec11",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Armbands were taken on the night of the murder,[p/] and they are [i]still[/i] missing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b04248",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: If Eugene [i]did[/i] indeed steal the Armbands that night,[p/] he would have never had the opportunity to return them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c54d4a",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: He had no choice but to continue wearing them until the investigation was over!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc89a8",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "RubyC: This is absolutely ridiculous![p/][s/] You're spinning a fairy tale!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db5584",
  "node": "EugeneObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: If I'm wrong,[p/] the witness can easily refute my theory by removing his hat!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07110db",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well?[p/][s/] What's it going to be, Eugene?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8f104",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "He finally broke character,[p/] his posture straightening into something far less primitive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf9b7f",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "His back straightened.[p/] His breathing became controlled.[p/] His arms became more deliberate in their movements."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb49f8",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "He slowly but silently lifted his hat,[p/] revealing what had been right under all of our noses."
}

{
  "id": "line:033041f",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: No...[p/] You can't be serious..."
}

{
  "id": "line:045c40f",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "Everyone could see it plainly.[p/] He was wearing the Armbands like a crown around his tiny head."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d342af",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "From out of his hat,[p/] I saw him pull out something else..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e7517",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "Eugene: Well done, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] I shouldn't have underestimated you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0543164",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: Are—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:088184a",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "Judge: You—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09cd0e0",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "Celeste: Serious?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:017c60c",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "Eugene: This is probably a blessing in disguise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acbf16",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "Eugene: Acting like a common chimp was humiliating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd06e4",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: Objection, Your Honor!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3ddb3",
  "node": "EugeneObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...On what grounds, Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0badc06",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: On what [i]grounds[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b4e6b",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: [i]Everything[/i] about this situation is objectionable!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ddd48",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: It's downright absurd! [h=\"Is <i>he</i> seriously|Beatrice's accomplice?!\" e=\"fa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:090ab0a",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "Judge: B-[p/][s/]But, Ms. Tymora..."
}

{
  "id": "line:039eca7",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "Judge: We can't deny what's clearly in front of us."
}

{
  "id": "line:028e121",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I was not ready for today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0775118",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "Celeste: How is he even talking right now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c88e10",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Scholars believe that humans and apes evolved from a common ancestor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bac9c1",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Perhaps [i]all[/i] apes can speak the Common language under the right circumstances."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2b6cd",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "Eugene: \"Evolved\"?[p/] Please,[p/] I've observed your society."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6cf3a",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "Eugene: I think calling yourselves \"evolved\" is being quite generous."
}

{
  "id": "line:0294d4b",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: This can't be happening..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c4833",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "Eugene: Well?[p/] Are you all done gawking at me?[p/] Bloody philistines..."
}

{
  "id": "line:001477e",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "\"Philistines\"...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:090b3f7",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait a minute..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fddec2",
  "node": "EugeneObj6",
  "text": "Harold: The Duke of Finance invites my museum to set up some displays here every year. [h=\"He must think it adds|a semblance of culture, the philistine.\" e=\"as\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3347c",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Every insulting thought that I'd been seeing from Harold.[p/][s/] They weren't Harold's thoughts at all!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7195e",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "They were [i]Eugene's[/i] thoughts![p/][s/] He'd been wearing the Armbands since we first met!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1fb16",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I still don't understand..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d74677",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why would you even take the Armbands in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c319cf",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Eugene: ...I'll admit that the Lords' Ball was one of many occasions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb7c76",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Eugene: The [i]first[/i] time I touched them was due to sheer chance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f51259",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: You put them on by accident?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcb0f1",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Eugene: My unawakened self was enamored by its glittering sheen."
}

{
  "id": "line:003e4c5",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Eugene: I merely wanted to touch them,[p/] but when I first held them in my hands,[p/] I experienced a sense of clarity that was intoxicating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0471d",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Eugene: I was afraid of what I'd experienced.[p/] So I placed them back where they belonged."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d9dd0",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Eugene: ...But as I returned to my primitive lifestyle,[p/] I couldn't stop thinking about what I felt."
}

{
  "id": "line:00938fe",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were hooked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0534121",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Eugene: I wouldn't [i]quite[/i] phrase it like that,[p/] but I suppose you're not wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:037b8a1",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Eugene: I'd heard the password to Harold's vault more times than I could count,[p/] so I'd come in from time to time and indulge in the Armbands' power."
}

{
  "id": "line:0531877",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Eugene: But the more time I spent with my awakened intellect,[p/] the more I craved its power when I had to put them back."
}

{
  "id": "line:020cf09",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And that's when you made the replica."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f0e5e",
  "node": "EugeneObj7",
  "text": "Eugene: While no one was watching,[p/] I devised a plan to discreetly take the Armbands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f56641",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: Harold would have eventually discovered that they were stolen,[p/] but he would have concluded that a noble from the Lords' Ball took them."
}

{
  "id": "line:039fedf",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because of the pressure that he was receiving from the Crown."
}

{
  "id": "line:06eac60",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: I'm not proud of what I've done,[p/] but I never expected things to reach this point."
}

{
  "id": "line:04aaa79",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: I didn't expect someone to steal the Sword of Spell Eating as well,[p/] and I certainly didn't expect a murder to happen that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a3389",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you still maintain that you're innocent."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d8533",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: Of course, I do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d00fe3",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: I stole the Armbands,[p/] but I did [i]not[/i] murder William Frega.[p/] Nor did I take the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0484a66",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: ...Allow me to elaborate."
}

{
  "id": "line:032bbe7",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: I'll admit that I took the Armbands and replaced them with a replica,[p/] but I was [i]not[/i] the crook who stole the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0783a5e",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: The thefts were completely different from one another.[p/] The display case for the Sword was completely shattered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0730d41",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: I spotted the Sword when I was exploring the manor.[p/] It was lying in the middle of a hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c7375",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: I wondered why such an important artifact would be lying there.[p/] So I took a closer look to inspect it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0479323",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: That's when I heard Harold call out to me telepathically.[p/] The Sword must have protected me,[p/] and by extension Harold,[p/] from the [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d22ce3",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Eugene: I wanted to take the Sword and return it,[p/] but a wild dog chased me away from the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:052e9e5",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Celeste: He has a point...[p/] He didn't need to shatter the display case of the Sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f76453",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah,[p/] he already knew the passwords."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ef21e",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "But Tracker said that [i]Eugene[/i] was the one who dropped the Sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0349190",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "Furthermore,[p/] he escaped into the air vent that led into William's Study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5a5b8",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "His actions that night were definitely not as innocent as his testimony implied."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb0bcd",
  "node": "EugeneObj8",
  "text": "He must have lied [i]somewhere[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7c237",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You stole the Armbands by using Harold's spoken password?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfd1f5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: Yes.[p/] I sit on his shoulder most of the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:098caee",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: He obviously never suspected what I'd do.[p/] So it was a simple matter of listening to him when he transported the artifacts to Frega Manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3fa19",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And can I assume that you knew the passwords for the other displays as well?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03607e2",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: I do,[p/] and I could easily demonstrate that if needed."
}

{
  "id": "line:003448a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "I doubted that he'd lie about that when we could easily check him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb4350",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even so,[p/] you already lied about not stealing the Armbands."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e1819",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why should we believe you now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0754cef",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: The answer to that lies in the physical evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f9e56",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: How do we know that you didn't shatter the glass to cover your tracks?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0960030",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: Harold's password would have disengaged the locks,[p/] but they wouldn't disable the magic that protects the glass."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca3eed",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: The spells weren't even disabled anyways."
}

{
  "id": "line:076e1f2",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: Harold told you himself, didn't he?[p/] Only a powerful mage could have shattered the reinforced glass."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7489f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But as a familiar,[p/] magic [i]can[/i] be cast through you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0220796",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: Only Harold can cast magic through me.[p/] I can't cast any spells by myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b33448",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: And even if I could,[p/] Harold's [b]Spell Compendium[/b] doesn't have a spell that's powerful enough for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05900f3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "His logic was sound..."
}

{
  "id": "line:049942a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "But if what he was saying was true,[p/] [i]who[/i] shattered the glass?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001eb33",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: Anyways..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0905de7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But [i]that[/i] location was near the Fregas' bedrooms..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0534217",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't tell me that you—..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0820517",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: What do you take me for—[p/][s/]some primitive lecher?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a03d7b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: I [i]know[/i] what a bedroom looks like,[p/] and I'd never enter one uninvited—[p/]especially a young woman's!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc51a2",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then why were you there in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e1a3a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: ...I was coming back from the Rooftop Garden,[p/] but I suddenly felt something interfering with the Armbands' magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ab3eb",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: The [b]Anti-Magic Fields[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:011d4ab",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: Yes.[p/] I was worried that something had happened,[p/] so I made my way back to the Gallery to meet up with Harold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b44f03",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I see...[p/] Could you add this to your testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0032710",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: ...Very well."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d72be",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: I spotted the Sword when I was heading back from the Rooftop Garden to the Gallery.[p/] It was lying in the middle of a hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:035c33b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you were heading directly from the Rooftop Garden to the Gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0727722",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But do you honestly expect us to believe that someone just [i]left[/i] the Sword of Spell Eating in that hallway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fda409",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: Think what you will,[p/] but it's the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a2ce9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: Perhaps the murderer left it there after they'd been done using it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5e171",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: If the Kingsguard found it there,[p/] they would have had no idea who stole it."
}

{
  "id": "line:076b060",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "That [i]did[/i] sound possible,[p/] but I still had my doubts."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a40a9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And [i]that's[/i] when you made contact with it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:014cc93",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: Yes.[p/] I was quite surprised too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da324c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: At the time,[p/] the magic of the Armbands was being nullified."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd6ef8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: But when I picked up the Sword,[p/] my intelligence temporarily returned."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5293e",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: That's how I knew that I was holding the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0867344",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I understand how it would've protected you,[p/] but how would it have protected Harold?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d5435",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: [b]Familial Bond[/b] connects the magic of both targets."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b4af1",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: When one spell affects one target,[p/] it can also affect the other creature in the bond."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ba146",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: The protection from the Sword of Spell Eating extended to both of us once I held it in my hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d55cbc",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "That made sense.[p/] That also explained how Tracker heard Laefe when [i]he[/i] held the Sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebbdd5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: I wanted to take the Sword and return it.[p/] But a wild dog chased me away from the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db909d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Didn't you have enough time to grab the sword?[p/] You [i]were[/i] holding it after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c118d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: I'm not proud to admit it,[p/] but my survival instincts took over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9209a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Eugene: At that point,[p/] I was more concerned about escaping that wild animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d9b2a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tracker [i]was[/i] several times larger than him.[p/] He had every reason to be afraid."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c8fde",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Celeste: His story makes sense...[p/] There's no way [i]he[/i] could have shattered the glass."
}

{
  "id": "line:016c5d7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose so..."
}

{
  "id": "line:033bc9d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But Tracker saw him that night.[p/] He was definitely traversing the vents in that hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:079b640",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which means he lied [i]somewhere[/i] in his testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0022b97",
  "node": "Eug2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eugene.[p/] I'm sure you're well aware of this,[p/] but the best way to lie is to hide a false detail within many truths."
}

{
  "id": "line:0603cf4",
  "node": "Eug2Obj",
  "text": "Eugene: ...And what are you trying to insinuate, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:057c7ca",
  "node": "Eug2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: You said that you were heading from the Terrace to the Gallery.[p/] Did you take [i]any[/i] detours?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0793de8",
  "node": "Eug2Obj",
  "text": "Eugene: ...Of course not.[p/] With the Armbands nullified,[p/] my intelligence was slowly fading."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d1bb6",
  "node": "Eug2Obj",
  "text": "Eugene: I wanted to return to Harold as soon as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c2625",
  "node": "Eug2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Witness.[p/] I'd like for you to take a look at this floor map of Frega Manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c83e8",
  "node": "Eug2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]This[/i] is the location where that \"wild dog\" found the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf5381",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So tell me, Eugene...[p/] How did you \"spot\" the Sword of Spell Eating?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed1e9f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...When it was hidden in the hallway [i]north[/i] of Beatrice's room!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4c9c3",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Eugene: T-[p/][s/]That's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2eeef",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "RubyC: Why are you nitpicking such an insignificant statement?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e18d8",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "RubyC: He probably just got distracted and went down the wrong hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e962b",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora.[p/] Eugene came from the Rooftop Garden."
}

{
  "id": "line:019ca36",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And he was adamant that he went [i]directly[/i] to the Gallery to reunite with Harold."
}

{
  "id": "line:03efd6c",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if his intellect was muddled,[p/] he was intent on reuniting with his worried companion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2cf49",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He definitely took the direct route,[p/] but if he did,[p/] he would never have been able to see into that hallway!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f12a5",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Judge: I see your point, Mr. Cuthbert...[p/] But what does this mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c77ef",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It means that the witness lied about where he was [i]before[/i] he discovered the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8912d",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He wasn't coming from the Rooftop Garden!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0279673",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He came from the air vents in that [i]specific[/i] hallway!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f16131",
  "node": "Eug2Obj2",
  "text": "Eugene: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ca2a1",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: So why were you in that hallway, Eugene?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:014dbf7",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]lied[/i] in your testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0963fba",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was it because you wanted to hide what you were [i]really[/i] doing that night?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d9d0a",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Eugene: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf1b99",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eugene,[p/] you snuck through the air vents to avoid detection!"
}

{
  "id": "line:042f3c2",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then you used the air vent in that hallway to break into William's Study!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da7565",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: After that,[p/] you murdered him using his letter opener, didn't you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0951659",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Eugene: That's not what I went there to do!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07deede",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Eugene: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] I didn't mean—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc710b",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Judge: Order![p/][s/] Order in the court!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0753f2f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Judge: Witness...[p/] Is this true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f14354",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Judge: Did you break into William Frega's Study during the lockdown?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0258c6b",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Eugene: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...[p/][s/] I [i]did[/i] enter his study,[p/][s/] but not for the reason you think!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e20d08",
  "node": "Eug2Obj3",
  "text": "Eugene: William Frega was already dead when I got there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e858f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj4",
  "text": "RubyC: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0893697",
  "node": "Eug2Obj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did you just say?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af39ed",
  "node": "Eug2Obj4",
  "text": "Eugene: It's true!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6bb50",
  "node": "Eug2Obj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you honestly expect us to believe a story like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccbe0c",
  "node": "Eug2Obj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: How could [i]someone else[/i] have killed the victim before you got there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc01fa",
  "node": "Eug2Obj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tracker took the Sword of Spell Eating,[p/][s/] and [i]you[/i] were the only intelligent creature that could walk through the air vents!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8d166",
  "node": "Eug2Obj4",
  "text": "Eugene: I understand how unbelievable and suspicious it sounds!  [h=\"Why do you think I lied|in the first place?!\" e=\"af\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0947560",
  "node": "Eug2Obj4",
  "text": "Eugene: But it's the truth, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] You have to believe me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e7706",
  "node": "Eug2Obj4",
  "text": "I didn't see any contradicting thoughts through the Eye,[p/] but that [i]hardly[/i] absolved him of any guilt."
}

{
  "id": "line:0882fab",
  "node": "Eug2Obj4",
  "text": "But could he really be telling the truth...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:019f267",
  "node": "Eug2Obj4",
  "text": "If that was true,[p/] that only brought me back to the one question I'd been asking since this all began."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ab8d4",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Who [i]really[/i] did this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0117cc0",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay, Eugene.[p/] Let's assume you're telling the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fcb7e",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: ...Do you [i]actually[/i] believe me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f86cbf",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let's not get ahead of ourselves.[p/] You're still my only suspect for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:058539c",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I'll give you the benefit of the doubt for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:010ca66",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: ...I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0139a53",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: However,[p/] if you want to absolve yourself,[p/] I [i]need[/i] you to tell me about what you really saw that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:042ebd2",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: There might be something—[p/][i]anything[/i]—[p/]that might point to who really did this."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f7eab",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: Very well...[p/] I'll tell you what I saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d0a8b",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: Although,[p/] I doubt you'll believe me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f99025",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: I discreetly made my way to that hallway through another air vent.[p/] I exited the air vent in that hallway and tried to leap to the other side."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a5fe6",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: I'm not sure if it was my waning intelligence or my carelessness,[p/] but I collided with something that I couldn't see."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a3d28",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: I fell to the ground and found the Sword of Spell Eating laying next to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:078e171",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: I wanted to retrieve the Sword,[p/] but that wild dog forced me to retreat.[p/] After that,[p/] I continued to make my way to the study."
}

{
  "id": "line:036dae5",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: ...And that's when I found William Frega.[p/] He was dead on the floor and lying in a pool of blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d67de4",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: And as if I were blessed by the Scaled Lord himself,[p/] I found the will that he'd been drafting.[p/] So I destroyed it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d52d7",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Judge: Frankly,[p/] Mr. Haroldson.[p/] I find that story very difficult to believe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f393e6",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: I assumed as much.[p/] But you know what they say."
}

{
  "id": "line:0197100",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Eugene: Truth is stranger than fiction."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0c240",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "RubyC: Isn't it more likely that [i]you[/i] murdered the victim?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0508d15",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "RubyC: You're clearly trying to cover up what you did by saying that he was already dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:019573f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Celeste: Honestly,[p/] I really don't know [i]what[/i] to think..."
}

{
  "id": "line:050db22",
  "node": "Eug2Obj5",
  "text": "Was he really telling the truth?"
}

{
  "id": "line:050a0a6",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: But why were you there in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c0a91",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: It all began when William Frega got into that argument with Harold."
}

{
  "id": "line:001ca5a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: That cur wanted to [i]defund[/i] the prestigious Haroldson Hall of History!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff2604",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I knew a man like William probably had many secrets."
}

{
  "id": "line:036ebed",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: So I devised a plan to break into his Study and find [i]something[/i] that I could use to blackmail him."
}

{
  "id": "line:029015b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: As you know,[p/] there's a small air vent in that hallway.[p/] It connects to William's Study on the ground floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fbc91",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I thought I could look through his documents while he was preoccupied with the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:052bb52",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I wasn't aware that William was planning to stay in his Study all night."
}

{
  "id": "line:062c06d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "I suppose that [i]did[/i] make sense,[p/] but was he really telling the truth?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e235f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "RubyC: What happened when you tried to leap to the other air vent, Eugene?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ceb92",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I thought monkeys were extremely dexterous."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e078ee",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you just clumsy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0129bfc",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I have [i]impeccable[/i] dexterity!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2a099",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "...It sounded like I struck a nerve there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff0ed9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I-[p/][s/]I must have been muddled from losing the Armbands' magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff06e3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I fell to the ground and found the Sword of Spell Eating lying next to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc2c0b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did you know it was the Sword of Spell Eating?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5a9c8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: When I held it in my hands,[p/] I felt my intelligence return..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac5b6a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: But I also heard Harold calling out to me telepathically."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a280e4",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: He was clearly growing worried.[p/] So I knew I needed to move quickly."
}

{
  "id": "line:071f681",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did this \"wild dog\" have a white coat of fur?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdf77c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: He did.[p/] Are you acquainted with him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0259d5c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eadcd4",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: Well, next time you meet him,[p/] tell him that I don't appreciate being called a \"rat\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0265e81",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I am a proud orangutan."
}

{
  "id": "line:02147d3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can understand him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07198c6",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I've picked up a little of the Canine language throughout my life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0efaa",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I'm also fluent in Squirrel and Pigeon."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c8a26",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I can also speak Owl,[p/] but I admit it's barely conversational."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df157f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0077879",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "As much as I wanted to test the validity of those claims,[p/] they weren't relevant to the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec2741",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "RubyC: What happened when you entered the study?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6e141",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "RubyC: It seems awfully convenient that he was murdered [i]before[/i] you arrived."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e133d4",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I know how it may seem,[p/] but I'm telling you the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:04058a7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: And do you have any explanation for [i]how[/i] the assailant broke into the study without the Sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0561e9d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I, unfortunately, do not..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d08ec9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "RubyC: Please.[p/] It's obvious your testimony doesn't match up with the evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:08aa355",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "RubyC: Whoever did this either entered through the vents [i]or[/i] they used the Sword to nullify the lock."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d781d6",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "RubyC: And your [i]own[/i] testimony states that the Sword was abandoned in that hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0162104",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "It didn't match up with what I'd [i]thought[/i] happened,[p/] but did it really contradict the evidence I had?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8b785",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] what did you do when you discovered the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d27997",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I knew it was only a matter of time before someone discovered the body.[p/] So I quickly searched the room for something I could use."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcd9e9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: So [i]you[/i] were the one who took the will.[p/] I've been trying to find it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0f7e9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did it say?"
}

{
  "id": "line:036d067",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I was pressed for time.[p/] So I didn't read the entire document."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1b367",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: I only skimmed it and found an order to defund the Haroldson Hall of History."
}

{
  "id": "line:0518632",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: Since he went out of his way to specify that on the current copy,[p/] I concluded that his former will didn't have this addendum."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7154c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you tried to save Harold's museum by ensuring that the new will would never be submitted for probate."
}

{
  "id": "line:063ad77",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] do you have the will with you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a47fb8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Eugene: My apologies.[p/] I crumpled up the will into a ball and ate it.[p/] I then left the room before my intelligence was completely gone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd801d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "I was really hoping to see if William followed through on his threat to disinherit Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:043d2dd",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Celeste: He seems to be telling the truth this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d988a7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I agree,[p/] but we still need to be sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c0f19",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Eugene3",
  "text": "I needed to carefully inspect and PRESS each of his statements."
}

{
  "id": "line:024eecc",
  "node": "Eug2Obj7",
  "text": "It was hard to believe,[p/] but I couldn't see any [i]direct[/i] contradictions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0157318",
  "node": "Eug2Obj7",
  "text": "I didn't think PRESSING him anymore would get me anywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f451ac",
  "node": "Eug2Obj7",
  "text": "If Eugene [i]did[/i] indeed do this,[p/] my next course of action was clear."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fa24f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj7",
  "text": "Although,[p/] that [i]still[/i] didn't explain how Beatrice fit into all of this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bbf57",
  "node": "Eug2Obj7",
  "text": "...I remembered something that Tracker had said to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ddb05",
  "node": "Eug2Obj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tracker.[p/] You said you had to [i]smell[/i] to \"see\" where the rat was?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0beae3c",
  "node": "Eug2Obj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: And when he dropped his \"stick\" you were finally able to see him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a60d6e",
  "node": "Eug2Obj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Does this mean you couldn't [i]visually[/i] see him [i]before[/i] he fell down?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e51afe",
  "node": "Eug2Obj8",
  "text": "Tracker: Yeah.[p/] Tracker couldn't see the rat with his eyes.[p/] So Tracker used his nose to see it."
}

{
  "id": "line:021b815",
  "node": "Eug2Obj8",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Eugene was invisible!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0caff0d",
  "node": "Eug2Obj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eugene.[p/] When you were carrying out your plan,[p/] did you turn yourself invisible somehow?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cff85",
  "node": "Eug2Obj8",
  "text": "Eugene: ...No?[p/] I hardly had the means to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0993efc",
  "node": "Eug2Obj8",
  "text": "Eugene: And even if I [i]had[/i] somehow convinced Harold to cast a spell on me,[p/] he doesn't know how to cast [b]Invisibility[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb7de4",
  "node": "Eug2Obj8",
  "text": "Eugene: Very few mages do."
}

{
  "id": "line:059af45",
  "node": "Eug2Obj9",
  "text": "Right.[p/] I remember Eris saying the same thing during Wallace's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e02eb",
  "node": "Eug2Obj9",
  "text": "Only a master of [b]illusion[/b] magic could do that.[p/] That's how I first thought Beatrice was involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:0456697",
  "node": "Eug2Obj9",
  "text": "But if Eugene was truly innocent,[p/] did she turn someone [i]else[/i] invisible?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea776c",
  "node": "Eug2Obj9",
  "text": "But,[p/] once again,[p/] that just put me right back where I started!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09fe55e",
  "node": "Eug2Obj9",
  "text": "No...[p/] I needed to think through this."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f6978",
  "node": "Eug2Obj9",
  "text": "Eugene's testimony filled in a blank that had been missing."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d60f6",
  "node": "Eug2Obj9",
  "text": "I then cross-referenced that with Tracker's testimony..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a0f84",
  "node": "Eug2Obj10",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker could smell where rat was,[p/] so Tracker bork at him."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c2e97",
  "node": "Eug2Obj10",
  "text": "So where does that lead us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e71e4c",
  "node": "Eug2Obj11",
  "text": "No...[p/] In Eugene's testimony,[p/] he fell onto the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad8acb",
  "node": "Eug2Obj11",
  "text": "And when he got his bearings,[p/] he realized that Sword was lying next to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b67afd",
  "node": "Eug2Obj11",
  "text": "But Tracker said that the \"rat\" dropped the Sword when he fell onto the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8883c",
  "node": "Eug2Obj11",
  "text": "These testimonies appear to conflict with each other,[p/] but what's the commonality between them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0915599",
  "node": "Eug2Obj12",
  "text": "The thief dropped the Sword in that hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b110f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj12",
  "text": "...But how did [i]that[/i] make sense?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3d861",
  "node": "Eug2Obj12",
  "text": "Did they hide the Sword there as I'd originally thought?"
}

{
  "id": "line:092d7f6",
  "node": "Eug2Obj12",
  "text": "No...[p/] That hallway was close to the Gallery.[p/] There were plenty of better places to hide the Sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:01107de",
  "node": "Eug2Obj12",
  "text": "If it weren't for Tracker taking it,[p/] it would've been found even sooner."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e9279",
  "node": "Eug2Obj12",
  "text": "The thief must have accidentally dropped the sword there...[p/] That could only mean one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0608098",
  "node": "Eug2Obj13",
  "text": "No...[p/] That hallway leads toward the Bath."
}

{
  "id": "line:060d513",
  "node": "Eug2Obj13",
  "text": "I could think of very little reason why the thief would be [i]walking[/i] there."
}

{
  "id": "line:05854f9",
  "node": "Eug2Obj13",
  "text": "But there was another explanation for why they were at that specific location."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fd961",
  "node": "Eug2Obj14",
  "text": "The thief was also sneaking through the air vents..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e0c2d",
  "node": "Eug2Obj14",
  "text": "That's the only reason why they would be there,[p/] but that would imply that the thief was as small as Eugene..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd3c42",
  "node": "Eug2Obj14",
  "text": "Could it have been [i]another[/i] familiar?[p/] And if so,[p/] why didn't Eugene notice them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093fd50",
  "node": "Eug2Obj14",
  "text": "Wait..."
}

{
  "id": "line:032674a",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "He collided with something he \"couldn't\" see...[p/] In other words,[p/] it was something that wasn't visible to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c245f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "And as a master of [b]illusion[/b] magic,[p/] Beatrice was one of the few people at the Ball that [i]could[/i] cast [b]Invisibility[/b]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a986c5",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "Laefe: Beatrice would never trust anyone enough to work together like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b27a57",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's completely blind.[p/] She wouldn't have much of a choice."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a4cab",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "Laefe: She's not the type of person to trust her accomplice to stay quiet."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a28c0",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "Laefe: She wouldn't leave a loose end open like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ef225",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "Had I been approaching this situation incorrectly the entire time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0807a0f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "Through the Eye,[p/] I knew that Beatrice was involved somehow,[p/] but I'd just assumed that she had plotted this with someone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:057de3c",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "The breaking of the glass and the casting of [b]Invisibility[/b]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bfdea",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "These were the elements that I [i]knew[/i] that she was involved with,[p/] but it never really fit together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0172f0e",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "...Not unless [i]she[/i] was the one pulling the strings the entire time."
}

{
  "id": "line:015897d",
  "node": "Eug2Obj15",
  "text": "And there was only one way she could be in control the entire time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d49fc3",
  "node": "Eug2Obj16",
  "text": "Familial Bond"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b220af",
  "node": "Eug2Obj16",
  "text": "No...[p/] I'd been underestimating Beatrice's role in what happened that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:03df319",
  "node": "Eug2Obj16",
  "text": "Everyone assumed that Beatrice couldn't perform certain actions due to her blindness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a33448",
  "node": "Eug2Obj16",
  "text": "But there was one \"tool\" that she could have used to do all of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0657aaf",
  "node": "Eug2Obj17",
  "text": "A couple of memories came back to me in that moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b410fe",
  "node": "Eug2Obj17",
  "text": "Harold: Yes.[p/] This is my familiar:[p/] Eugene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf665d",
  "node": "Eug2Obj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh,[p/] you cast [b]Familial Bond[/b] on him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec0cfd",
  "node": "Eug2Obj17",
  "text": "Harold: I'm surprised you know about it.[p/] It's quite rare."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc9182",
  "node": "Eug2Obj17",
  "text": "Harold: Very few mages take the time to learn how to cast it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a46cfb",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: H-[p/][s/]Hi, I'm Tyrion.[p/] I'm Ms. Tymora's...[p/] ward."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcd58e",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "Instead of taking my hand,[p/] she clapped her hands together and took a deep breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0311e",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2e1ce",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "Beatrice: Ah![p/][s/] S-[p/][s/]Sorry.[p/] I didn't mean to do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:094f8f7",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "Beatrice: It's a bit of a habit of mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0450bfc",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "Beatrice: I'm Beatrice.[p/] I've heard much about you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6f69d",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "She shook my hand before looking to Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec0356",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "I didn't know that she was blind back then,[p/] so I barely even noticed it."
}

{
  "id": "line:010afad",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "But how did she know that I was holding out my hand?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0783146",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "Eugene: Well?[p/] Do you have any other questions for me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:041e8f6",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "If I were wrong about this,[p/] Beatrice would surely be acquitted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaf9ed",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "And after that,[p/] the Inquisition would turn its attention to Harold and Eugene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0040405",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "But there was only one way to know for sure..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00400a6",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor.[p/] The prosecution has no further questions for the current witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e3b91",
  "node": "Eug2Obj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: He is dismissed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc1ee9",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Eugene: I...[p/] see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0335e52",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You have something else planned, don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03af9b9",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah,[p/] and I actually need your help."
}

{
  "id": "line:07509f3",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:067636a",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "I whispered it into her ear."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d3e25",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Celeste: Really?[p/] You're making some big assumptions there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2836f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Celeste: Wouldn't the Inquisition check for something like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:067d154",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know,[p/] but it's the best play we have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aeb463",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you remember what Steelwind said yesterday?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a61e0",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Aria: But the moment the guards saw the body,[p/] one of them cast [b]Detect Magic[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dca519",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Aria: With that spell,[p/] they would have seen any invisible people hiding in this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8917e",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait, you can use [b]Detect Magic[/b] like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0092b44",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Aria: Of course.[p/] It's standard procedure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d496f3",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Aria: Like all spells,[p/] [b]Invisibility[/b] leaves traces of magic on the person it's cast on."
}

{
  "id": "line:055302f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj19",
  "text": "Aria: So mages can use [b]Detect Magic[/b] as a way to see them."
}

{
  "id": "line:055d5c7",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "Tyrion: If everything goes the way I think it will,[p/] I'll be able to prove its existence in front of everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:097b763",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright...[p/] I'll follow your lead then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acb136",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "Judge: So, Mr. Cuthbert?[p/] How do we proceed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d24938",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "Judge: Your [i]previous[/i] witness brought about more revelations than I could have ever guessed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d76adc",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "Judge: However,[p/] you still haven't given a substantial explanation about [i]how[/i] the murder occurred or [i]who[/i] actually did it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c52fc9",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "Tyrion: I understand that, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2fa07",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "Tyrion: But it will all make sense after I call my next witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b6e12",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "Judge: ...[i]Another[/i] witness?"
}

{
  "id": "line:070e79f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "Tyrion: I understand your hesitance, Your Honor,[p/] but everything that we've learned throughout these trials is finally coming together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0affa94",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "Tyrion: And this final witness will tie it all together in a perfect knot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0067f61",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor.[p/] The prosecution calls Beatrice Frega to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d5837",
  "node": "Eug2Obj20",
  "text": "RubyC: Seriously, Cuthbert?[p/] You went to [i]all[/i] that trouble just to end up calling my client to the stand?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f7da6",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "Tyrion: You and your client have the right to refuse, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6c64d",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I wonder how that will reflect on your client's character."
}

{
  "id": "line:00726c2",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "It didn't really matter.[p/] She was already standing next to Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:039ef13",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "We could carry out our plan regardless of what she decided to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f33a1",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "...But it would have much more impact if I could bait her into lying on the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ce425",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "RubyC: My client says that she's willing to testify."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c34774",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "RubyC: However,[p/] we would like to propose a short recess."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8aeaa",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "RubyC: With these new developments,[p/] I'm sure you can understand that we have much to discuss."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a197c8",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "Judge: Hm...[p/] I see no reason not to grant the defense's request."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f6308",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "Celeste: Is this really okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0957223",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "Celeste: If we give them time to prep,[p/] they might realize what we're doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:072f2f8",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know,[p/] but I don't think we have anything to worry about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d05e5f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj21",
  "text": "I'd been learning a lot about Beatrice since this case began."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d27a2",
  "node": "Eug2Obj22",
  "text": "It was hard to read her expression and emotions,[p/] even [i]with[/i] the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd43ba",
  "node": "Eug2Obj22",
  "text": "She kept herself guarded and kept her true intentions unknown."
}

{
  "id": "line:02aaa1c",
  "node": "Eug2Obj22",
  "text": "She's powerful—[p/]more powerful than her father ever cared to admit."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a5183",
  "node": "Eug2Obj22",
  "text": "Despite this,[p/] he tried to control her and put her inside a cage."
}

{
  "id": "line:03371d7",
  "node": "Eug2Obj22",
  "text": "...But Beatrice Frega would never live in a cage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0078469",
  "node": "Eug2Obj22",
  "text": "She wanted freedom and control,[p/] and she would do whatever it took to get it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a39a52",
  "node": "Eug2Obj22",
  "text": "I'm sure the accident that blinded her didn't help things,[p/] but it also worked in her favor."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ff1ed",
  "node": "Eug2Obj22",
  "text": "Her blindness made people underestimate her,[p/] and she found a way to use even [i]that[/i] to her advantage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec132e",
  "node": "Eug2Obj23",
  "text": "When everything was said and done,[p/] she abandoned everything—[p/]her wealth,[p/] her status,[p/] even her family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0134289",
  "node": "Eug2Obj23",
  "text": "She could have waited.[p/] She could have gritted her teeth until it was her turn to lead House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:05752ce",
  "node": "Eug2Obj23",
  "text": "If she was willing,[p/] she could have even secretly pushed her father past the gates of death herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:031b76d",
  "node": "Eug2Obj23",
  "text": "But she couldn't bear to live like that,[p/] even temporarily."
}

{
  "id": "line:066d0b4",
  "node": "Eug2Obj23",
  "text": "I had no idea why [i]this[/i] was how she chose to do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:071fd0f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj23",
  "text": "Perhaps it had something to do with their meeting..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04924e1",
  "node": "Eug2Obj23",
  "text": "But I did know one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7f040",
  "node": "Eug2Obj23",
  "text": "Beatrice Frega would never put herself in a position of vulnerability."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca121a",
  "node": "Eug2Obj23",
  "text": "If I faced her head-on,[p/] she would respond in kind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c50f5f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj24",
  "text": "Judge: In the interest of giving the defense time to deliberate,[p/] we will be taking an extended recess."
}

{
  "id": "line:060e409",
  "node": "Eug2Obj24",
  "text": "Judge: Court is adjourned."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfe5ee",
  "node": "Eug2Obj24",
  "text": "As I was exiting the courtroom,[p/] I sent Celeste to do some reconnaissance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c305c9",
  "node": "Eug2Obj24",
  "text": "It should be similar to when she scanned Valentina during Wallace's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b10b06",
  "node": "Eug2Obj24",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a78da1",
  "node": "Eug2Obj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste.[p/] Were you able to see it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e072cd",
  "node": "Eug2Obj24",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah.[p/] It's definitely there,[p/] and it sits on her shoulder most of the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d7178",
  "node": "Eug2Obj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: So she keeps it close to her...[p/] That's good to know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0915260",
  "node": "Eug2Obj25",
  "text": "Celeste: It looks kind of weird, though...[p/] I've never used [b]Detect Magic[/b] like this before."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c471e",
  "node": "Eug2Obj25",
  "text": "Well, I doubted that someone like her would choose a conventional animal,[p/] especially for something as important as this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0114f7f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj25",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c8185",
  "node": "Eug2Obj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: M-[p/][s/]Ms. Tymora..."
}

{
  "id": "line:068545b",
  "node": "Eug2Obj25",
  "text": "Ruby: There's...[p/] something I need to show you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0173f13",
  "node": "Eug2Obj25",
  "text": "Ruby: ... Preferably, alone."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f563f",
  "node": "Eug2Obj25",
  "text": "Celeste gave me a concerned look,[p/] but I nodded to show her it's okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0070c7d",
  "node": "Eug2Obj25",
  "text": "She moved to sit on the bench and kept a careful watch on Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0980826",
  "node": "Eug2Obj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Okay.[p/] Lead the way."
}

{
  "id": "line:010c3f6",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Miriam: ...Laefe.[p/] Are you there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:066961b",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Miriam found Laefe sitting in Beatrice's dusty old room."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c88bc",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "She was staring at nothing.[p/] Her mind was elsewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fefaf7",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "She barely acknowledged Miriam as she entered the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf8bb8",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Miriam: ...How are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cab31f",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...I'm okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3e438",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Miriam: T-[p/][s/]This trial has really been something, hasn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d7c33",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Miriam: M-[p/][s/]Maybe we could take a break from all of this.[p/] We could have that tea you wanted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c06e69",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...I don't think that would be a good idea, right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ae715",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Her voice was empty.[p/] She was practically muttering her words."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a2292",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Miriam: Right.[p/] Of course..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d785ae",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...Miriam,[p/] why do you hate me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a53a8",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Miriam: What?[p/][s/] I-[p/][s/]I don't—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0348e19",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Laefe: You never want to visit,[p/] and you always avoid talking to me when you do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a30d0a",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Laefe: This is the first time I've even seen you in years,[p/] and you want nothing to do with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d5896",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Miriam: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c1c9c",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Laefe: I know I'm annoying,[p/] and I know I'm not as smart as you,[p/] but I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:025b619",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2",
  "text": "Miriam: That's not—![p/][s/] Ugh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cce00b",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: ...I don't hate you, Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b3d4a",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Nobody likes me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c37068",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: Anyone who spends time with me is just trying to get something from our family or just trying to get [i]with[/i] me."
}

{
  "id": "line:037d52f",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: Then I see you,[p/] tripping over yourself trying to please Father and everyone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaee2e",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: You're so desperate.[p/] It infuriates me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2612d",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: I thought I was better than you.[p/] I thought I was stronger than you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fc437",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: I had risen above what had happened,[p/] while you were still living in the past."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9f4e8",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: But then Beatrice suddenly came back,[p/] and—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e72c4a",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Laefe: Miriam..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0637bff",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Laefe: I like you."
}

{
  "id": "line:04886a3",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "That just made Miriam burst out laughing."
}

{
  "id": "line:061e911",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: Really,[p/] [i]you[/i] like me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6280a",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: Is it my [i]welcoming[/i] personality,[p/] or my amazing people skills?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0037a10",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Laefe: No![p/][s/] I really [i]do[/i] like you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e657e7",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Laefe: I've always admired you![p/] You're intelligent and confident!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3a968",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Laefe: You're even working with the Crown Prince![p/][s/] I wish I could be more like you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdd688",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Laefe: [i]I[/i] definitely didn't have a perfect average at the Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cff544",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: ...I hate that average.[p/] It just means I'm never allowed to make a mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0e3f7",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Laefe: You're the only person who could understand what living under Father was like."
}

{
  "id": "line:0816009",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: ...What about Beatrice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbc31b",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Laefe: I was talking to her earlier...[p/] She admitted to me that she really did kill Father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcb850",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: What?![p/][s/] Why would she—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe00b3",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: ...Why [i]would[/i] she tell you that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2b0fa",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Laefe: I don't know,[p/] but she even told me she was behind the attack on Lady Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc4935",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Laefe: I've been thinking of telling Tyrion Cuthbert about this,[p/] but I don't know what to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9b3e6",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: Hm...[p/] Knowing him,[p/] he probably already knows."
}

{
  "id": "line:01beb8a",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: It's not as if we have any proof anyway,[p/] and if we testify,[p/] people will just think we're trying to steal her share of the inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c00032",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Laefe: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I don't know what to do anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:099b610",
  "node": "LaefNMiriam2a",
  "text": "Miriam: ...You can start by telling me more about what exactly Beatrice said to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:083bdad",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is the defendant prepared to take the stand?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc1b50",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tymora.[p/] I asked you a question."
}

{
  "id": "line:092ddef",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is the defendant prepped or not?"
}

{
  "id": "line:048f60a",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "RubyC: ...She is.[p/] If the prosecution still wants to move forward with—."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a28889",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Tyrion: The prosecution [i]will[/i] be moving forward with this.[p/] Please bring in the witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:060aa31",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you still see it, Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:030f22d",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] It's still there.[p/] Should I reveal it now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:016b3fc",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] Let's really make a point of it.[p/] Wait for my signal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9921f",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thank you for agreeing to take the stand, Ms. Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:07409af",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:021cd04",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's my understanding that you were with the two princes for most of the night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2a507",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Yes, I was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cce500",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Which is why I'm [i]still[/i] quite confused as to why I'm being charged for this crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:009de86",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Out of everyone there that night,[p/] I'd have thought my alibi was the most apparent."
}

{
  "id": "line:095c4b4",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That remains to be seen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0720cb1",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Clearly."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c60c6",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways...[p/] Since you still maintain your innocence,[p/] you'll have no problem going into detail about your supposed alibi."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d13b7f",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Beatrice: As you know,[p/] I was with Crown Prince Aster and Prince Alaric for most of the Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9dd41",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Beatrice: I went there after my meeting with my father,[p/] and I remained with them until I was arrested for his murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb1de5",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Lord Steelwind and the Kingsguard kept watch over me for the entire night as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7ad4c",
  "node": "Courtroom2B2",
  "text": "Beatrice: I neither had the means nor the opportunity to steal the Sword of Spell Eating [i]and[/i] break into my father's study to murder him."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b1cde",
  "node": "Courtroom2B3",
  "text": "Tyrion: And [i]that[/i],[p/] Ms. Frega,[p/] is where you're mistaken."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aced7b",
  "node": "Courtroom2B3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You definitely had the [i]means[/i] to commit both crimes while under the eye of everyone there that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:01617f8",
  "node": "Courtroom2B3",
  "text": "The most effective tool an attorney had was revealing a contradiction in a witness's testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0661050",
  "node": "Courtroom2B3",
  "text": "It not only completely shattered their argument,[p/] it also made the court doubt whether the witness was acting in good faith."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be095e",
  "node": "Courtroom2B3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Now, Celeste!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a36e62",
  "node": "Courtroom2B3",
  "text": "Celeste: [b]Aburio[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0209fa3",
  "node": "Courtroom2B3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Wait...[p/] What are you doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9c5ee",
  "node": "Courtroom2B3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] The witness's testimony is clearly—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e1d5e",
  "node": "Courtroom2B4",
  "text": "RubyC: Oh my god![p/][s/] What the hell [i]is[/i] that thing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06eb4f9",
  "node": "Courtroom2B4",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion![p/][s/] Get behind me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0075ebf",
  "node": "Courtroom2B4",
  "text": "Gallery: A-[p/][s/]A monster![p/][s/] It's a monster!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05379f7",
  "node": "Courtroom2B4",
  "text": "Gallery: Someone call the Inquisition,[p/][s/] t-[p/][s/]the Kingsguard,[p/][s/] a-[p/][s/]anyone!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ab35d",
  "node": "Courtroom2B4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] Can you [i]please[/i] restore order?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b4dff",
  "node": "Courtroom2B4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Your Honor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:034da3f",
  "node": "Courtroom2B4",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...The old man fled out the back door the moment he saw me."
}

{
  "id": "line:07039c5",
  "node": "Courtroom2B4",
  "text": "RubyC: I-[p/][s/]It can talk?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0506ddb",
  "node": "Courtroom2B4",
  "text": "Gallery: I-[p/][s/]It's a demon![p/][s/] It must be!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08078f0",
  "node": "Courtroom2B4",
  "text": "Gallery: It's just like the legends say!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00230fb",
  "node": "Courtroom2B5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can we [i]all[/i] just calm down?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:068aea1",
  "node": "Courtroom2B5",
  "text": "It took a while before we could get everyone in the room to settle down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc33ae",
  "node": "Courtroom2B5",
  "text": "Eventually,[p/] it became clear that the \"demon\" wasn't intent on harming anyone...[p/] At least not yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0100bf2",
  "node": "Courtroom2B5",
  "text": "The court ordered in extra guards just in case,[p/] and we were eventually able to bring everyone back to the courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef6434",
  "node": "Courtroom2B5",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert![p/][s/] What is the meaning of this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0efd560",
  "node": "Courtroom2B5",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry...[p/] I didn't know it was a—"
}

{
  "id": "line:08626d5",
  "node": "Courtroom2B5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Actually...[p/] What [i]are[/i] you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04df381",
  "node": "Courtroom2B5",
  "text": "Judge: Are you a d-[p/][s/]d-[p/][s/]d-[p/][s/]demon?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a2be0",
  "node": "Courtroom2B5",
  "text": "Marrunath: Why, yes.[p/] [i]*laugh*[/i][p/] I [i]am[/i] a d-[p/]d-[p/]d-[p/]demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ccb49",
  "node": "Courtroom2B5",
  "text": "Gallery: Demons actually exist?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0092dc5",
  "node": "Courtroom2B5",
  "text": "Gallery: I thought they were only a legend...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:089e06c",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/] Not only [i]do[/i] demons exist,[p/] the defendant has made one into her familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c552b",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's only blind in the legal sense![p/][s/] She's constantly looking through the eyes of her familiar to see!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0146e03",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "RubyC: ...And?"
}

{
  "id": "line:037c110",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you mean \"and\"?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c088f",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's obvious that making a pact with a [i]demon[/i] is incriminating by itself."
}

{
  "id": "line:04525c7",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "RubyC: Tell me, Your Honor.[p/] Do the laws of Wyverngarde prohibit entering an accord with a demon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:085030c",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Judge: T-[p/][s/]They don't,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa99e1",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "RubyC: Then my client has committed no crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:072e8cf",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Beatrice: Even so,[p/] I really would have preferred [i]not[/i] revealing Marrunath like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:073459a",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Marrunath\".[p/] Is [i]that[/i] your name?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8f27c",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...It is what most people call me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa43c0",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose the defense has a point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3afa6",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Having a demon as a familiar isn't technically illegal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f479a3",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Tyrion: However,[p/] this [i]does[/i] prove that the defendant had a way to commit the murder,[p/] all while under the eye of everyone in the Ballroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e3007",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Tyrion: She could have sent Marrunath upstairs to the Gallery and then had him steal the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0027fc6",
  "node": "Courtroom2B6",
  "text": "Tyrion: After that,[p/] they would just need to traverse the vents into William's Study,[p/] just like Eugene did that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0424abd",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "RubyC: The fact that her familiar is a demon [i]proves[/i] that she couldn't have done that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0075953",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f112c6",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "RubyC: You saw how everyone reacted when they saw Marrunath's form."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c81087",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "RubyC: A monkey may have raised some eyebrows,[p/] but someone [i]surely[/i] would have reported Marrunath if they saw him."
}

{
  "id": "line:06101ba",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tymora.[p/] Your client is a master of [b]illusion[/b] magic.[p/] Can I assume that we'll find [b]Invisibility[/b] in her [b]Spell Compendium[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a96f65",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "RubyC: ...You might."
}

{
  "id": "line:07aa4f4",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "Tyrion: And with the connection granted by [b]Familial Bond[/b],[p/] she could have cast this spell on him [i]regardless[/i] of where each of them was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e57c51",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "RubyC: But [i]could[/i] my client have continued casting it unnoticed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26e3d",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"[i]Continue[/i] casting it\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0b9cc",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "RubyC: I'd like to remind the courts of the order of events that occurred that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d56ce",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "RubyC: At an unknown time,[p/] someone stole the Sword of Spell Eating from the Haroldson Gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:026b3c3",
  "node": "Courtroom2B7",
  "text": "RubyC: Due to the timing of this,[p/] I'll admit that it [i]would[/i] be logically consistent [i]if[/i] my client were the thief."
}

{
  "id": "line:0763af0",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: However,[p/] sometime later,[p/] my client met with the Crown Prince and was watched closely by the Kingsguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:037e288",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: From witness accounts,[p/] [i]including[/i] yours,[p/] we know that this happened at 12:45 AM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0557ae1",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: And since this time,[p/] my client hadn't left the Kingsguard's sight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a673c2",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: It was around this time that William Frega retreated into his study and locked the door."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cfaa5",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: He made a point of telling everyone that he didn't want to be disturbed."
}

{
  "id": "line:064ef98",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: Then at 1:03 AM,[p/] Lord Haroldson finally discovered that the Sword was stolen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0544af7",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: He reported the theft to the Inquisition and they activated the lockdown system."
}

{
  "id": "line:0025fce",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: Shortly after the report,[p/] Laefe Frega tried to speak with her father about the theft."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2f0bb",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: William Frega reiterated that he did not want to be disturbed."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bb8e6",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: Laefe saw his face,[p/] and there weren't any traces of [b]illusion[/b] or [b]necromancy[/b] directly on his body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ceaacd",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: This means that William Frega was still alive at this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0162837",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: Unbeknownst to everyone at the time,[p/] William Frega was attacked by the murderer at 3:12 AM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afd732",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: This was confirmed not only by Jan Hughes's testimony,[p/] but also by the Autopsy Report."
}

{
  "id": "line:0759fe4",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: Then at 3:26 AM,[p/] the Kingsguard found the Sword of Spell Eating in my client's old room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd850c",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: The Kingsguard tried to arrest my client for this.[p/] But the Crown Prince told them to stand down."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d3356",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: Finally at 3:36 AM,[p/] the lockdown was lifted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0493e7e",
  "node": "Courtroom2B8",
  "text": "RubyC: Jan Hughes reported what he heard,[p/] and that's when the Inquisition and the Kingsguard discovered the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be6ae0",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "RubyC: The theft must have happened before 1:23 AM:[p/] when it was actually reported."
}

{
  "id": "line:0288407",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "RubyC: In order to keep Marrunath concealed at every step,[p/] my client would have needed to keep him invisible from 1:03 AM to 3:12 AM."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b924f",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "RubyC: Not only that,[p/] she needed Marrunath to wield the Sword of Spell Eating to ignore the effects of the [b]Anti-Magic Fields[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:091342d",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "RubyC: This means he would need to be invisible for more than an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed559a",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "Tyrion: What's your point?"
}

{
  "id": "line:043dc18",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "RubyC: My point is that [b]Invisibility[/b] has a duration of one hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:0469a2d",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "RubyC: I'll admit that my client [i]could[/i] have cast [b]Invisibility[/b] before she met with the Crown Prince."
}

{
  "id": "line:0891919",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "RubyC: But if she wanted to [i]keep[/i] Marrunath invisible,[p/] she would have needed to recast the spell at some point that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4bac2",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "RubyC: And as you know,[p/] my client couldn't have done so during that night without the Kingsguard noticing it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a82c0b",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your logic makes sense..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e07107",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "Tyrion: But that can only mean that the defendant refreshed the [b]Invisibility[/b] [i]right[/i] in front of everyone watching."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1b036",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "Judge: In front of the entire Kingsguard,[p/] the two princes,[p/] [i]and[/i] Lucio Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ef1b2",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "Tyrion: As unlikely as it is,[p/] it's the only conclusion I can come to."
}

{
  "id": "line:04552d3",
  "node": "Courtroom2B9",
  "text": "RubyC: I had a feeling you'd say that,[p/] which is why we have a witness who can confirm that Beatrice didn't perform any magic that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb4ec2",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...A witness?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7cef9",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "RubyC: Your Honor.[p/] The defense would like to call Prince Alaric to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e4f49",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Judge: I-[p/][s/]I...[p/] see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0845ef0",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Judge: ...He would have certainly been close enough to notice the defendant casting magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b0647",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Judge: But wouldn't the [i]Crown[/i] Prince's testimony be more suitable?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01dcab9",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "RubyC: Are you trying to say that Prince Alaric is unqualified to give proper testimony, Your Honor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0127eb9",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Of course he was saying that![p/][s/] The kid is seven years old!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d491a",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Judge: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] Of course not!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ec00e",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Judge: I-[p/][s/]Is the prince ready to testify?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a02eab",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Grow a spine, for Lord's sake!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05bd038",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thank you for coming in, Prince Alaric.[p/] Could you please—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f8f0a",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Alaric: Hold your tongue, knave!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02691d6",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Alaric: You will speak when you are spoken to."
}

{
  "id": "line:038ae85",
  "node": "Courtroom2B10",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] He sounds exactly like Miriam when we first met her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0daea8f",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Honestly...[p/] he behaved exactly how I'd expect a prince of this kingdom to act."
}

{
  "id": "line:0183955",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Aster was the odd one out.[p/] I wondered what made [i]him[/i] so down to earth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb61d5",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Judge: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] Your Highness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbea58",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert believes that the defendant used her magic while she was with you and the Crown Prince."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d719e",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Alaric: I already gave my statement to the instigators."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c3dd2",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Alaric: This man [i]dares[/i] to question my testimony?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:034035c",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Judge: Yes.[p/] He said it.[p/] Not me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a835c5",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Alaric: If my testimony is required to strike down these redundant accusations,[p/] I will bestow it upon you."
}

{
  "id": "line:031c47f",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Redundant\"...?[p/] Don't you mean \"ridiculous\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0957f96",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Do [i]not[/i] dare to suppose what His Highness really meant!"
}

{
  "id": "line:088e556",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...His boots must be shining from all that licking you're doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4066f",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Judge: What was that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ee0b3",
  "node": "Courtroom2B11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d5aa9",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "Alaric: You think Lady Frega cast magic right in front of me?[p/] Don't be a serf!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0583fe3",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "Alaric: She was under the careful watch of the Kingsguard,[p/] my brother,[p/] [i]and[/i] Lord Steelwind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcc38c",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "Alaric: We conversed for the whole night and I didn't see her cast [i]any[/i] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:073d9f0",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "Alaric: She's been through so much over the last few years...[p/] All because of her horrid father..."
}

{
  "id": "line:010af98",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "Alaric: She'd never do something like this![p/][s/] You [i]and[/i] Lady Steelwind are just jealous!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3ff09",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "He seemed really convinced that he didn't see anything.[p/] I doubted that he was [i]intentionally[/i] lying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d66613",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste.[p/] Usually when you cast [b]Detect Magic[/b],[p/] I can see magical energies overlaying your eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0035c0b",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] there's always a visible magical effect on the target when I cast a spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e593e",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "Tyrion: But Marrunath was probably in another room.[p/] The Kingsguard wouldn't see the initial magical effect of [b]Invisibility[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:05187e8",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "Celeste: Even if there wasn't a visible effect in that room,[p/] she would've still needed to say the incantation and perform the gesture with her hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f140f3",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] Like how you shout [b]Reperio Arcanum[/b] every time you scan a crime scene..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a27ec5",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't [i]shout[/i] it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef689d",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "She must have performed the incantation and gesture at [i]some[/i] point during the night."
}

{
  "id": "line:036bfc4",
  "node": "Courtroom2B12",
  "text": "With so many people watching her,[p/] did she somehow do that without anyone noticing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9c3f8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: You may think the idea is absurd, Your Highness,[p/] but the defendant is clearly an expert at deception."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b63a4",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: She could have easily concealed her actions at some point during the night."
}

{
  "id": "line:03563f4",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: A brief moment to say the incantation and perform the gesture would have been all she needed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddc68f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: But I wasn't the only one watching her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00deba8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: But would they have really noticed her casting one spell?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae2e8a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: The Kingsguard are the most vigilant knights in the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc816c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: They are [i]trained[/i] to watch and counter a mage's spell,[p/] but the defendant needed to target someone who was in another area."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcca36",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: There would be no visual indication that she was using magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:01486ae",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: But she would have still needed to perform the incantation and complete the gesture with her hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0843e98",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "He was pretty knowledgeable about the Arcane Arts,[p/] but as a prince of Wyverngarde,[p/] that was to be expected."
}

{
  "id": "line:0114f76",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: If I recall correctly,[p/] you and your brother were with her until she was arrested for the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:02318fc",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did you speak about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c60a7a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: She told us stories about what she did while she was away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8cfb2",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: She was researching something...[p/] I forgot what she said.[p/] Something about \"the old cult\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb799a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you mean \"the occult\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:046ffd7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: Yes.[p/] That's it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00eea05",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: She was researching ghosts and demons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f52410",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Considering who her familiar was,[p/] that research must have paid off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0250937",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] Your Highness,[p/] could you please add this to your testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:091fc81",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: If I must."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c54ba",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: She told my brother and me how \"the occult are a fascinating phenomena\".[p/] I didn't see her cast [i]any[/i] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b20a0",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wouldn't saying \"the occult [i]is[/i] a fascinating phenomenon\" be more grammatically correct?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b9001",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on, Tyrion...[p/] Don't be one of those guys who corrects other people's grammar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0502bc3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: Yeah...[p/] We all say things incongruently sometimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:035527a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "I felt like he [i]might've[/i] been projecting a little."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6b16c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're clearly sympathetic to her situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa20e1",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you must have only been a toddler when she left five years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0296b92",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: My brother spoke of her a lot.[p/] He told me all about her."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e0900",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: I could tell from his face.[p/] He was really sad that she ran away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0657e0d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Even if it wasn't romantic,[p/] Aster clearly cared about her a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2e196",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Steelwind must have had complicated feelings about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b660db",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Well, I can't speak for Steelwind,[p/] but [i]I'm[/i] just trying to get to the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0601ba1",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: Liar![p/][s/] You just hate her because she's a noble, don't you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab1ec6",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Alaric: Lord von Sanctus told me all about you![p/][s/] You just want to lock nobles up because you're jealous of our power!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6bc2d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "So he spoke with von Sanctus frequently."
}

{
  "id": "line:000f50b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "That actually explained a lot about his personality..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bbe76",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste.[p/] What do you usually need to do to cast a spell?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fff956",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Celeste: Honestly,[p/] there are a lot of things that I need to account for...[p/] Stamina and focus are a big part of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f5342",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Tyrion: Assuming that she's in perfect condition,[p/] what's the bare minimum that she would need to do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c7100",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, she would have to focus her magic,[p/] say the incantation,[p/] and perform the gesture with her hands.[p/] All at the same time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0314b28",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Alaric",
  "text": "That [i]did[/i] sound pretty conspicuous,[p/] but she must have hidden it somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b7eee",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "To cast a spell,[p/] a mage needed to speak an incantation,[p/] but there was nothing that said they couldn't say anything before or after it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e07e98",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Highness.[p/] According to your testimony,[p/] the defendant told you that \"The occult are a fascinating phenomena\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0419bb4",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is that exactly what she said?[p/] Word for word?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c188e",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Alaric: Yes.[p/] Those stories of ghosts and demons she told us were quite interesting."
}

{
  "id": "line:047c776",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Alaric: They really stuck a court with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f0ee9",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I see..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea4354",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, even [i]if[/i] they were interesting,[p/] your testimony proves that she [i]did[/i] cast the [b]Invisibility[/b] spell that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:092368e",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Alaric: Are you deaf?![p/][s/] I already told you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd1e7f",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Alaric: No one heard her say any incantations![p/][s/] Nor did they see her perform any gestures!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8992d",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Unfortunately,[p/] your testimony proves the contrary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f19d3a",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Beatrice Frega said an incantation and performed a gesture right in front of you,[p/] all without anyone even knowing it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5d000",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Alaric: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2a954",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Highness.[p/] There are two components required to cast [b]Invisibility[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb1b1b",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: First,[p/] the caster must speak the incantation \"[b]O-kult-arr-ae[/b]\" and clap both of their hands together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0063597",
  "node": "AlaricObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: As I'm sure you noticed,[p/] the defendant has a habit of clapping both of her hands to calm herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d35d3",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Now that I think about it,[p/] that habit must have come from constantly casting the spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e6ddf",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: The defendant requires Marrunath to see.[p/] So she must constantly cast [b]Invisibility[/b] to keep him invisible."
}

{
  "id": "line:054a72f",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "RubyC: Cuthbert.[p/] You may have an explanation for how she hid the gesture."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fa99f",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "RubyC: But she would've still needed to speak the incantation."
}

{
  "id": "line:068b411",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: However,[p/] she [i]did[/i] speak the incantation.[p/] The witness's testimony proves it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0505ad4",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Alaric: What are you talking about?![p/][s/] I never said that she spoke [i]any[/i] incantation!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07043aa",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Highness.[p/] The incantation for [b]Invisibility[/b] is \"[b]O-kult-arr-ae[/b]\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:00df4fa",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Now,[p/] recall what you said in your testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:085f7f2",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "RubyC: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0894ac1",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: She said,[p/] \"The [b]occult are a[/b] fascinating phenomena\".[p/] The pronunciation of that one phrase is identical to the incantation!"
}

{
  "id": "line:092032b",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Judge: I see...[p/] So she could have hidden the incantation within the conversation itself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd0178",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And because her target was a creature that was [i]outside[/i] of the Ballroom,[p/][s/] no one saw the magical effects."
}

{
  "id": "line:0beafa0",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: This meant that Marrunath had the means to murder William Frega,[p/][s/] just as Eugene did!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a44d8",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "RubyC: Having the means is completely different from actually having done it, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b1525",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Very few people had the ability to shatter the display case to steal the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0550f6c",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And even fewer people had a familiar small enough to traverse the vents."
}

{
  "id": "line:064428c",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "RubyC: Which also makes Haroldson's familiar an equally likely suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:03df936",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "RubyC: And unlike my [i]client's[/i] familiar,[p/] he admitted to breaking into William's Study that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0045988",
  "node": "AlaricObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: If your client's familiar is truly innocent,[p/] then why not have him testify before the court?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdeca4",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "Judge: I see...[p/][s/] Well, it's not as if he's the [i]first[/i] unprecedented witness we've had today."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d8a68",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "Judge: Is...[p/] Marrunath willing to testify, Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:023e259",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "Tymora deliberated with Beatrice and Marrunath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6c908",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "I couldn't hear what they were saying,[p/] but they were clearly in disagreement with each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:086aa56",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "Marrunath,[p/] in particular,[p/] seemed to be the most vocal about his displeasure."
}

{
  "id": "line:075d84d",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "RubyC: Your Honor.[p/] Unfortunately,[p/] Marrunath is unwilling to testify."
}

{
  "id": "line:018e837",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why the change of heart?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0099dad",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "RubyC: My client's familiar may be a demon,[p/] but he's afforded the same rights as any other person."
}

{
  "id": "line:0285bdd",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "RubyC: He is not obligated to testify."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d8ee4",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "Marrunath was staring daggers at me,[p/] grinding his noticably sharp teeth together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5ee76",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "It felt oddly personal for some reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d5002",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "Why were they being so secretive all of a sudden, anyway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0743826",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "A witness could refuse to testify to avoid incriminating themselves,[p/] but a refusal to testify was suspicious in and of itself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0863b68",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "Tymora had no issues with Beatrice taking the stand earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0041555",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "Not to mention that Marrunath seemed to disagree with their decision the most..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6a8bd",
  "node": "AlaricObj3",
  "text": "Harold: Demons supposedly take great pride in their ability to deceive and corrupt people."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b9bde",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I see..[p/] Marrunath is well within his rights to refuse,[p/] if [i]that's[/i] what he truly wants."
}

{
  "id": "line:048a525",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "RubyC: It is..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0200424",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well...[p/] I suppose it's for the best.[p/] I doubt he'd be able to corroborate your story at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a56c85",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "Marrunath ground his teeth together more violently.[p/] It sounded like metal screeching against metal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb3b43",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Considering his diminutive figure,[p/] I don't blame him for being a coward."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2899d",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "Judge: M-[p/][s/]Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] could you please refrain from provoking the [i]literal[/i] demon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bba3c1",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, it's fine, Your Honor.[p/] He can't actually do anything without his master's word."
}

{
  "id": "line:092cdcd",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's clear that [i]Beatrice[/i] is the brains between them.[p/] He's basically just her servant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5c44b",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "Marrunath: Shut your [i]disgusting[/i] mouth, heavensborn!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0820d71",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "RubyC: ...Marrunath?[p/] What are you doing...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b93b3",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "Marrunath: I will not stand here and be insulted by a bloody [i]heavensborn[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:077f1b5",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "...\"Heavensborn\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0420959",
  "node": "AlaricObj4",
  "text": "Marrunath: I am still within my contract,[p/][s/] and I will not flee from the likes of [i]him[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08389c1",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: You want my testimony?![p/][s/] I'll give you my god-damned testimony!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d5aae",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: Y-[p/][s/]Your Honor![p/] My client does [i]not[/i] consent to having her familiar testify."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7d6c9",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tymora.[p/] Didn't you say earlier that Marrunath is \"afforded the same rights as any other person\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0be4fcb",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: He's his own...[p/] demon. He has a right to refuse to testify."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d2e77",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]He's[/i] the only one who can decide if he wants to exercise that right."
}

{
  "id": "line:009537a",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Marrunath,[p/] please testify about what [i]you[/i] were doing on the night of the murder?"
}

{
  "id": "line:047a4d6",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...Gladly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdfcd9",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: I provided sight to my keeper while she spoke with the princes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a857ad",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...[p/][p/]I'll admit that she [i]did[/i] cast [b]Invisibility[/b] on me during their conversation.[p/] She needed to keep me hidden after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2dbc4",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...[p/][p/]But I never left the room where my master was."
}

{
  "id": "line:037729c",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...[p/][p/]Nor did I steal the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:066a5fc",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: You have nothing on me, heavensborn![p/][s/] ...[p/][p/]You don't even have proof that I entered William Frega's Study!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5991d",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you honestly expect us to take your word for it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:008690e",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Or do you have any evidence to support your alibi?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e35c4a",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: I only speak the truth, heavensborn."
}

{
  "id": "line:054b328",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...[p/][p/]There were mages other than my keeper that could have stolen the Sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:058c952",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: And by your own admission,[p/] none of your witnesses [i]saw[/i] me on the night of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0387438",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: The one lacking evidence is you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0162f83",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "He had a point...[p/] I still needed definitive proof that tied him to the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e46c67",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "PRESENTING contradicting evidence might not be possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9738d",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "However,[p/] he was clearly lying in his testimony,[p/] and there was something...[p/] strange about the way he was speaking."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b9d66",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "Why was he pausing so much?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01df511",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "I wasn't seeing any thoughts through the Eye.[p/] My Eye of Horus might not even work on demons."
}

{
  "id": "line:05eed03",
  "node": "AlaricObj5",
  "text": "But maybe I could try to INTERPRET the meaning of his words."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb00ca",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is this something that you frequently do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0683e97",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Marrunath: Yes.[p/] My keeper's accident left her completely blind."
}

{
  "id": "line:043fb3b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Marrunath: She looks through my eyes to see her surroundings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0e60a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Tyrion: And did she look through your eyes while she was with the princes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e54480",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...[p/][p/]Yes, she did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0f682",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Does that mean she [i]normally[/i] casts [b]Invisibility[/b] every hour?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c79454",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Marrunath: My keeper is a powerful mage,[p/] and my pact with her has only made her stronger."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4d21b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Celeste: Wow...[p/] That's actually really impressive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f03435",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Tyrion: Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee17ac",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Celeste: Casting spells may look effortless,[p/] but continuously casting spells takes a lot of stamina out of the caster."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f0036",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Celeste: She would really have to worry about Mageblight when she did that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05709ae",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Celeste: She must have built a lot of stamina if she can cast a high-level [b]illusion[/b] every hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fac1db",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Tyrion: And did your master leave the room while she was with the princes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f03e7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Marrunath: No.[p/] ...[p/][p/]I'm sure you remember.[p/] My keeper was under the careful watch of the Kingsguard [i]and[/i] Lucio Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd9f04",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Tyrion: And you're maintaining that [i]you[/i] never left the Ballroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a04d77",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...[p/][p/]As I said,[p/] I never left the room where my master was."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d2860",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "He had a habit of pausing before he responded to you...[p/] But it only happens sometimes..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06df9e9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Was that just the way he articulated his words?[p/] ...Or was it something else?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecf080",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Tyrion: Beatrice was one of the few mages present who could shatter the glass."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b33ab3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Marrunath: Yes,[p/] but being able to do something and [i]actually[/i] doing it are two different things."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af7182",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Ugh...[p/] He was right.[p/] I wouldn't be able to convict Beatrice until I could connect Marrunath to the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0611123",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "But I had a feeling that [i]he[/i] was the one who'd give me that connection."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f31f7b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why do you keep calling me that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:061c232",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Marrunath: Oh...[p/] Does the heavensborn not know the nature of his blood?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba1633",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "My \"blood\"?[p/] Was he referring to my abilities?"
}

{
  "id": "line:071bd47",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Marrunath: Oh,[p/] how marvelous![p/][s/] You [i]don't[/i] know, do you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:099e1b7",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...If you make a pact with me child,[p/] I can tell you the nature of your blood,[p/] and much,[p/] [i]much[/i] more."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f62c8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Judge: M-[p/][s/]Mr. Cuthbert![p/][s/] Please don't make deals with demons in [i]my[/i] courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a7d16",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I wasn't planning to, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:09daa64",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "He clearly knew more about my lineage than I did,[p/] but making a deal with a demon was just asking for trouble."
}

{
  "id": "line:003a99a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Celeste: He's definitely more direct than most witnesses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd16cf",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah,[p/] but he's still clearly lying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3132c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "Tyrion: And there's something [i]off[/i] about the way he's speaking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8972a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "He would often pause before saying certain statements..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0967c19",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Marrunath",
  "text": "I needed to INTERPRET the statement that seems the most suspicious."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5b2f2",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "He would take pauses before certain statements,[p/] but not all of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:001bfa3",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "And more importantly,[p/] his word choice was different.[p/] Did he slip up?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ae3ff",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Marrunath.[p/] It looks like you misspoke and used the wrong word."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b6da7",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0856880",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Through most of your testimony,[p/] you referred to Beatrice Frega as your \"keeper\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bd489",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you referred to her as your \"master\" during one statement.[p/] Why is that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b4fee",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "Marrunath: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0ccb1",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "For the first time,[p/] he didn't have a retort."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0f31a",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: So I'll ask you again.[p/] Did you leave the Ballroom that night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e1c1a",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...[p/][p/]I...[p/][s/] [i]didn't[/i] leave the room where my master was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de104a",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "Even though I pointed it out,[p/] he was using the word \"master\" again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b503e4",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "Why wasn't he correcting it...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09489b9",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "Did that mean he was intentionally using that term?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06fd4e7",
  "node": "MarrunathObj",
  "text": "There [i]had[/i] to be a reason why..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc0061",
  "node": "MarrunathObj2",
  "text": "0000|0200"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f344f",
  "node": "MarrunathObj2",
  "text": "No...[p/] Throughout his entire testimony,[p/] he referred to Beatrice as his \"keeper\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:069f763",
  "node": "MarrunathObj2",
  "text": "He only referred to his \"master\" in that one statement.[p/] Why would he do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eabbe8",
  "node": "MarrunathObj3",
  "text": "If I took his words at face value,[p/] the \"master\" he was referring to [i]wasn't[/i] Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e76ee",
  "node": "MarrunathObj3",
  "text": "And if Beatrice wasn't his \"master\",[p/] then he really didn't leave the room where his master was."
}

{
  "id": "line:05435f4",
  "node": "MarrunathObj3",
  "text": "But why even bother making that distinction?[p/] He clearly had no moral hangups about committing murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f9d6d",
  "node": "MarrunathObj3",
  "text": "He could have just lied."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c8c98",
  "node": "MarrunathObj3",
  "text": "Demons apparently prided themselves on tricking and corrupting humans."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fe5d3",
  "node": "MarrunathObj3",
  "text": "So why wouldn't he just lie in his testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c08835",
  "node": "MarrunathObj4",
  "text": "No...[p/] He clearly had every incentive to lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd3a4a",
  "node": "MarrunathObj4",
  "text": "It would protect Beatrice [i]and[/i] let him win over the so-called \"heavensborn\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0849135",
  "node": "MarrunathObj4",
  "text": "So wouldn't he just do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d77dcf",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Demons were clearly different from humans,[p/] but would they seriously have a limitation like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5839e",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "It [i]would[/i] explain why Tymora and Beatrice were so opposed to having him testify..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac297e",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "There was only one way to know for sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b05db",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Witness.[p/] Can you repeat the following statement for me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba2ce4",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Tyrion Cuthbert's hair is green.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:027847b",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...[p/][p/]What kind of ridiculous request is that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d83b7b",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "[i]Another[/i] pause..."
}

{
  "id": "line:046548a",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Judge: I'm afraid I must agree, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d83470",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm just conducting a little experiment, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae41aa",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: So I'll ask you again, Marrunath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f66d58",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Say the following phrase:[p/] \"Tyrion Cuthbert's hair is green.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:06e6fae",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: ...Your Honor.[p/] Cuthbert is clearly making trivial requests to stall for time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc60fb",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "RubyC: His request is not worth a response from the witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf9a1a",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's not what I'm doing, Tymora,[p/] and I think you [i]know[/i] that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f1fe1",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Marrunath,[p/] we truly don't know much about demons aside from the stories told in myths."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d41e8",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: So is it possible..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00712cb",
  "node": "MarrunathObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...that demons are physically unable to lie?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:051720b",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05747ca",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: Damn it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0351a44",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "Judge: I'm sorry, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] but that seems quite ridiculous."
}

{
  "id": "line:0560b18",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "Judge: Why [i]wouldn't[/i] the witness be capable of lying?"
}

{
  "id": "line:099bde9",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I genuinely don't know, Your Honor,[p/] but his testimony speaks for itself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a10ea9",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: And he can [i]easily[/i] refute my claim by granting my request."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b61584",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Say \"Tyrion Cuthbert's hair is green\", witness!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09afe2b",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "Marrunath: You said it yourself.[p/] \"Tyrion Cuthbert's hair is green\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1c0ae",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's [i]not[/i] what I asked for, witness!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a0e33",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Repeat the statement I told you,[p/] word for word![p/][s/] Nothing after [i]or[/i] before it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b4c54",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: Your Honor![p/][s/] The prosecution's argument is absurd!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e15a4",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "RubyC: The witness is not obligated to fulfill such an outrageous request."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c3b7b",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "Judge: I might be compelled to agree with you, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:019754a",
  "node": "MarrunathObj6",
  "text": "Judge: ...If the witness wasn't [i]clearly[/i] avoiding that request."
}

{
  "id": "line:078987b",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well?[p/][s/] We're all waiting, Marrunath!"
}

{
  "id": "line:019fe08",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can easily prove me wrong by repeating my statement plainly!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da5cd4",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...You filthy heavensborn!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e476b6",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Say it, Marrunath!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0947be5",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Marrunath: \"Tyrion...[p/] Cuthbert's\""
}

{
  "id": "line:07ee9a3",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Marrunath: \"Tyrion Cuthbert's hair is...\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8dfc5",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Marrunath: \"TYRION[p/][s/] CUTHBERT'S[p/][s/] HAIR[p/][s/] IS\""
}

{
  "id": "line:091c2f2",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...blond."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c7a3d",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Technically[/i], it's a dirty blond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0880996",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Marrunath: Oh, [i]shut[/i] up!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab20ee",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Judge: ...Is Mr. Cuthbert correct, Marrunath?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b12dbe",
  "node": "MarrunatObj7",
  "text": "Judge: Are you [i]actually[/i] unable to lie?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c04bb9",
  "node": "MarrunatObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think his silence speaks for itself, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d9bfa",
  "node": "MarrunatObj8",
  "text": "Judge: Remarkable...[p/] I would have never imagined."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec3a6b",
  "node": "MarrunatObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: And with [i]that[/i],[p/] proving my case becomes a [i]much[/i] simpler matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6277f",
  "node": "MarrunatObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Marrunath.[p/] Did you murder William Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0803604",
  "node": "MarrunatObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure you understand, witness.[p/] Under [i]these[/i] circumstances,[p/] staying silent is basically an admission of guilt."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b06959",
  "node": "MarrunatObj8",
  "text": "Beatrice: You have no reason to stay quiet, Marrunath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0561e65",
  "node": "MarrunatObj8",
  "text": "Beatrice: Tell him the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:00147f1",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Marrunath: Lady Beatrice,[p/] what are you—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0191e3b",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Beatrice: I believe it's time to come clean,[p/] don't you, Marrunath?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0425171",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Marrunath: I see...[p/] So [i]that's[/i] your play."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d3d4f",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't think you can just stall for time, Ms. Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:08493db",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Marrunath has no choice but to answer the question."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae263d",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Beatrice: Do it, Marrunath.[p/] Tell the court the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:062f556",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...To answer your question,[p/] yes."
}

{
  "id": "line:05857b4",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Marrunath: I [i]did[/i] murder William Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cd98a",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "RubyC: W-[p/][s/]What are you doing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:054fa63",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Judge: Ms. Frega...[p/] Does this mean you are confessing to the murder?"
}

{
  "id": "line:063c87f",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh, Your Honor.[p/] [i]I'm[/i] not admitting to anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:08db34e",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Beatrice: Marrunath was the one who confessed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d212f5",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Tyrion: But your [i]own[/i] familiar just—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:094c30c",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Beatrice: Let me ask you a question, Marrunath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8cb32",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Beatrice: Did I directly [i]order[/i] you to murder my father?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07296e5",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...[p/][p/]No.[p/] You did not, Lady Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e6805",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What are you talking about?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a35752",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're lying, aren't you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01990db",
  "node": "MarrunatObj9",
  "text": "Beatrice: You said it yourself, heavensborn.[p/] Demons are [i]physically[/i] unable to lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:011b453",
  "node": "MarrunatObj11",
  "text": "Damn it...[p/] She was right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5edba",
  "node": "MarrunatObj11",
  "text": "Did she plan for this?[p/] She must have arranged things so that statement would be technically true."
}

{
  "id": "line:004e7c5",
  "node": "MarrunatObj11",
  "text": "She could have asked [i]someone else[/i] to give the order,[p/] or she could have simply implied it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5076d",
  "node": "MarrunatObj11",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] she could just plead ignorance and blame everything on Marrunath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dab272",
  "node": "MarrunatObj11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Still...[p/][s/] This isn't over."
}

{
  "id": "line:05424b4",
  "node": "MarrunatObj11",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh?[p/] Is that so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03dd3c8",
  "node": "MarrunatObj11",
  "text": "Beatrice: Let me tell you.[p/] This trial was over the moment Aria turned her blade against me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0180607",
  "node": "MarrunatObj11",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't care [i]who[/i] you are.[p/] Man,[p/] king,[p/] or demon,[p/][s/] you're [i]not[/i] going to get away with this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7ee24",
  "node": "MarrunatObj11",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh,[p/] I do love the gravitas behind that,[p/] but I wonder how long it will last."
}

{
  "id": "line:0391c51",
  "node": "MarrunatObj11",
  "text": "Beatrice: Take your best shot, heavensborn."
}

{
  "id": "line:0993f46",
  "node": "BeatCornered",
  "text": "Tyrion: Beatrice Frega![p/][s/] You may not have [i]technically[/i] ordered your father's murder,[p/][s/] but you were clearly acting with malice!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c82f21",
  "node": "BeatCornered",
  "text": "Tyrion: You brought something dangerous into the manor.[p/][s/] Something that you [i]knew[/i] would harm your father!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbc865",
  "node": "BeatCornered",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh, really?[p/] And what would that be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:018b617",
  "node": "BeatCornered",
  "text": "Beatrice: What was [i]so[/i] dangerous that it implies lethal intent?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c13e99",
  "node": "BeatCornered2",
  "text": "Marrunath|Familial Bond"
}

{
  "id": "line:0522a74",
  "node": "BeatCornered2",
  "text": "No...[p/] That wasn't right."
}

{
  "id": "line:041ac53",
  "node": "BeatCornered2",
  "text": "She clearly entered that manor assuming that she might have to murder her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0744be9",
  "node": "BeatCornered2",
  "text": "And she brought something into the manor to make sure that she could do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e39cb5",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You brought Marrunath into Frega Manor that night!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d984e7",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were clearly planning to murder your father from the start!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02fb1e1",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Ha![p/] I require Marrunath to [i]see[/i].[p/] That does [i]not[/i] imply lethal intent."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e4763",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you brought a [i]demon[/i] into that house![p/][s/] And as a result your father was killed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c335b",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: That was hardly an innocent mistake!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc631c",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "RubyC: My client specifically asked her father if familiars were allowed.[p/] We even received a written legal confirmation beforehand."
}

{
  "id": "line:032986b",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: But he couldn't have possibly expected her to bring in a [i]demon[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b8904",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "RubyC: He didn't specify [i]not[/i] to do this.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:057775e",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "RubyC: The presence of Marrunath did not break [i]any[/i] of his rules,[p/] nor [i]any[/i] laws made by the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a7b1a",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Right you are, Tymora.[p/] I can hardly be blamed if my familiar acts without my knowledge."
}

{
  "id": "line:0639099",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: How can you be blameless in Marrunath's actions?![p/][s/] He's [i]your[/i] familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:06096c2",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Beatrice: By that same logic,[p/] shouldn't we also blame Lord Haroldson for the actions of his pet monkey?"
}

{
  "id": "line:021cdff",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Beatrice: If I recall,[p/] he broke into the study,[p/] tampered with the crime scene,[p/] and then left my father's body without reporting it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d1207",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c8d8a",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Marrunath and Eugene are intelligent and sentient creatures.[p/] They have their own autonomy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef939d",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Their keepers aren't legally responsible for their actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0233080",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Damn it...[p/] She was playing Devil's Advocate,[p/] but I suppose that was fitting for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d060e7",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you still cast [b]Invisibility[/b] to keep Marrunath hidden that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d4a03",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] I [i]always[/i] cast [b]Invisibility[/b] on Marrunath.[p/] I can't very well let people see him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0306f27",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Face it, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] You have nothing on me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0705274",
  "node": "BeatCornered3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Every crime related to the murder was committed by Marrunath."
}

{
  "id": "line:04aef4e",
  "node": "BeatCornered4",
  "text": "Sword of Spell Eating 3|Sword of Spell Eating|Sword of Spell Eating 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:003bd39",
  "node": "BeatCornered4",
  "text": "No...[p/] She said that she \"didn't commit any crimes that night\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbbb1d",
  "node": "BeatCornered4",
  "text": "More specifically,[p/] she meant that there was nothing Marrunath did that was her fault."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b995e",
  "node": "BeatCornered4",
  "text": "But wasn't there something else that required her magic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1eae8",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Beatrice.[p/] Marrunath [i]required[/i] your magic to break the wards guarding the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b95cde",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: You may be able to explain why you cast [b]Invisibility[/b] that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d38472",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you [s/][i]can't[/i] explain why you cast an [b]evocation[/b] spell powerful enough to shatter that display case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0999d28",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh, that.[p/] I'd almost forgotten."
}

{
  "id": "line:0206c71",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "Beatrice: I plead guilty."
}

{
  "id": "line:090dc14",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea1c1b",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "Beatrice: To the charge of Grand Theft,[p/] I mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfba9d",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "Beatrice: I ordered Marrunath to help me steal that artifact so I could sell it on the black market."
}

{
  "id": "line:0400bf3",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "Beatrice: I would have never [i]imagined[/i] that he'd use it to murder my father..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e20271",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "Right...[p/] It didn't matter if she was found guilty of stealing the Sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:087a657",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "The Slayer Rule only took effect if she was found to be responsible for her father's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8b46a",
  "node": "BeatCornered5",
  "text": "Was there seriously nothing I could do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8a450",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Threaten [c=\"Marrunath. The sentence for first-degree murder is death! Are you really willing to [i]die[/i] for your keeper's crimes?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a81a07",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Appeal [c=\"Marrunath! It's not too late! You can still do the right thing and tell the truth!\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b89baf",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: M-[p/][s/]Marrunath![p/][s/] It's not too late!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e65c69",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can still do the right thing and tell the truth!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d8aec",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh my god![p/] Are you serious?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0645d8a",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Beatrice: Are you [i]that[/i] desperate?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8858f",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Beatrice: What on earth made you think you could appeal to the morals of a bloody [i]demon[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0777146",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] That was a long shot.[p/] Even for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb1d1a",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Deflect [c=\"That still doesn't absolve you of bringing a [i]demon[/i] into the Lords' Ball.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f3adb",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: That still doesn't absolve you of bringing a [i]demon[/i] into the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0292279",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Beatrice: Do you think we'll just accept your flawed claim if you say it over and over again?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e0e19",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "RubyC: Cuthbert.[p/] If you recall,[p/] we have a written notice allowing her familiar into the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ecd22",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "RubyC: The law is on our side.[p/] There was nothing illegal about Marrunath's presence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4e070",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "Damn it...[p/] They were prepared for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df2176",
  "node": "BeatCornered6",
  "text": "That document put the burden of proof on me."
}

{
  "id": "line:043dcc2",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Marrunath.[p/] The sentence for first-degree murder is death!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0734a40",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you really willing to [i]die[/i] for your keeper's crimes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e9598",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Marrunath: Heavensborn, I think you'll find death to be somewhat less permanent for a being such as I."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f4852",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...Even if I [i]could[/i] truly die,[p/] a fate much worse than death awaits me if I fail..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a8a29",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:040c9be",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Agh...[p/][s/] Those three are a pain to argue against when they're together."
}

{
  "id": "line:080ad82",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "I couldn't break their confidence at all!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e22c26",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Beatrice: So...[p/] Do you have anything else, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:083f2eb",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0ddf1",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Beatrice: I didn't think so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0432428",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Beatrice: Your Honor.[p/] It appears we found the true culprit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfbaad",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Beatrice: I can't [i]believe[/i] you killed my father, Marrunath.[p/] I'm so cross with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:037b1e3",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...Death will actually be very inconvenient for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d576a",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Marrunath: It's going to take me a whole weekend to sort this all out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc8197",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Beatrice: Don't worry,[p/] I forgive you."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b8a28",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Beatrice: Now then.[p/] Is there any reason why this trial hasn't ended already, Your Honor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4a5b3",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on![p/][s/] Don't you have anything else?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba70d6",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "There [i]was[/i] one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:089f60a",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "RubyC: Damn it...[p/] Not again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd6461",
  "node": "BeatCornered7",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh?[p/] Is that all you can do now?[p/] Glare at me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b37aa",
  "node": "BeatCornered8",
  "text": "W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04449d7",
  "node": "BeatCornered8",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Marrunath.[p/] What did you just do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e07c43",
  "node": "BeatCornered8",
  "text": "Marrunath: I've been watching him.[p/] He's been using a trick from the Domain of Radiance."
}

{
  "id": "line:012b00d",
  "node": "BeatCornered8",
  "text": "Marrunath: But it's weak.[p/] Horus's blessing won't work here, heavensborn."
}

{
  "id": "line:0903a64",
  "node": "BeatCornered8",
  "text": "Tyrion: You...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0357659",
  "node": "BeatCornered8",
  "text": "RubyC : ...It looks like [i]that[/i] was your last piece, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ad006",
  "node": "BeatCornered8",
  "text": "No...[p/][s/] This [i]can't[/i] be how it ends.[p/][s/] Not after I'd come this far!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b8c00",
  "node": "BeatCornered8",
  "text": "RubyC: What is it that you like to say in these situations...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1ba9d",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "RubyC: ...Checkmate, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a63f59",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Judge: Well...[p/] I have to say this was one of the more eventful trials I've overseen."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c705c",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Judge: It was many things,[p/] if not enlightening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1765a",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Judge: But I suppose it all ended the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d1c2d",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Come on...[p/] I needed to think of something—[p/][i]anything[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0083c2d",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Judge: While I find the defendant's actions extremely suspect,[p/] I must agree with their argument."
}

{
  "id": "line:087da91",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Judge: Aside from the theft of Lord Haroldson's exhibit,[p/] none of Ms. Frega's actions that night were illegal under Wyverngarde law."
}

{
  "id": "line:0276c84",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Judge: And there's no proof that the [i]defendant[/i] is responsible for her familiar's actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d66f89",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Judge: With these revelations,[p/] I see no room for debate."
}

{
  "id": "line:062697d",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Judge: We will be taking a brief recess.[p/] I will announce my verdict once we resume."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cacfb",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Damn it...[p/][s/] Was this seriously how it's going to end?![p/][s/] After [i]everything[/i] I'd gone through to get here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0213962",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Frey: This world is bleak,[p/] merciless,[p/] and unforgiving."
}

{
  "id": "line:008cae1",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Frey: But don't let it extinguish the flickering flame I can see within you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fbf62",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Frey: Use my eyes.[p/] Peer beyond the Divine Gate just as I once did."
}

{
  "id": "line:06dc5af",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Frey: Use it to build your own path to happiness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2b943",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "Marrunath called me a \"heavensborn\",[p/] and my mother told me that there was a \"light\" within me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b914d",
  "node": "BeatCornered9",
  "text": "I had no idea what that even meant...[p/][s/] What even [i]was[/i] the Divine Gate?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00283f1",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Why do I have the Eye of Horus?[p/][s/] Why was I blessed by a god that I didn't know about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01720a5",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "I'd been so lost lately.[p/] I thought I was finally figuring out who I was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e03abd",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "But all of this,[p/] everything I'd been working towards.[p/] It was all a lie..."
}

{
  "id": "line:024b0a0",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "I'd spent my whole life trying to be like Ms. Tymora...[p/] But [i]she[/i] wasn't even like her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc094a",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "No...[p/] She just wanted to raise me into a tool for the Eyetaker..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e95435",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "She was never my guardian...[p/] She was never my mother..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d13137",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "My [i]real[/i] mother died years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0733c4d",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "...Was Eris right?[p/] Was I just a pawn?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f527f",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Looking back on it,[p/] I had no idea what to do with myself the moment my mother died."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c2e66",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "I just made mistake after mistake—[p/]leaving Aurinax,[p/] trusting Tymora..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0604d7b",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "I'd always just done as I was told...[p/] I never once made a path for myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:06dfd75",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Frey: But you saved Celeste,[p/] Wallace,[p/] and Dracogen.[p/] All when no one else would stand against the tide."
}

{
  "id": "line:051f1c1",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Frey: Was saving them a mistake?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0960deb",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Frey: You fought for a dream that didn't exist,[p/] but that doesn't mean that you can't make it real."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d79828",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Frey: It's true that you followed Tymora's lead,[p/] but you've [i]always[/i] done what you thought was right above anything else."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e000f",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Frey: You wouldn't have stood up to that criminal if you truly didn't know right from wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:0917289",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Frey: And you wouldn't be standing here if you'd just done as you were told."
}

{
  "id": "line:000e70e",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What do I do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b0b3c",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Frey: I'm not going to tell you that.[p/] You already know the answer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cad70c",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Frey: You've [i]always[/i] known the answer."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e6dfa",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "Frey: The light within you will show you the way."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ccb21",
  "node": "BeatCornered13",
  "text": "This was [i]not[/i] how this story would end."
}

{
  "id": "line:0930451",
  "node": "BeatCornered14",
  "text": "I took a deep breath and relaxed my thoughts."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a163ed",
  "node": "BeatCornered14",
  "text": "Situations could seem hopeless sometimes,[p/] but there was [i]always[/i] a way to win in the end."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ad2a2",
  "node": "BeatCornered14a",
  "text": "No...[p/] No matter what I did,[p/] it wouldn't mean anything unless I proved one fact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0226cc9",
  "node": "BeatCornered14a",
  "text": "I needed to prove that Beatrice [i]ordered[/i] Marrunath to kill her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0048a74",
  "node": "BeatCornered14a",
  "text": "I would need something concreteto prove that.[p/] Testimony wouldn't be enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:072b694",
  "node": "BeatCornered14b",
  "text": "In order to convict Beatrice,[p/] I needed to prove that she was responsible for Marrunath's actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ff6c9",
  "node": "BeatCornered14b",
  "text": "People always leave trails...[p/] Actions [i]always[/i] left evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:074a917",
  "node": "BeatCornered14b",
  "text": "There [i]had[/i] to be something that proved Beatrice gave Marrunath the order, even indirectly."
}

{
  "id": "line:032f267",
  "node": "BeatCornered14b",
  "text": "Beatrice's relationship with Marrunath was clearly different than a relationship between two humans."
}

{
  "id": "line:043af60",
  "node": "BeatCornered14b",
  "text": "There was a specific way their relationship worked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da360e",
  "node": "BeatCornered14c",
  "text": "No...[p/] Beatrice's relationship with Marrunath wasn't the same as one between humans."
}

{
  "id": "line:0631c26",
  "node": "BeatCornered14c",
  "text": "It wasn't even the same as the one between a mage and their familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e04523",
  "node": "BeatCornered14c",
  "text": "There was something special about a human's relationship with a demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf7dd1",
  "node": "BeatCornered14d",
  "text": "There's a specific way their relationship works...[p/] Or their \"pact\",[p/] as Marrunath calls it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddc9ae",
  "node": "BeatCornered14d",
  "text": "...Wasn't there something that someone said?[p/] But what was it...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b96f0e",
  "node": "BeatCornered15",
  "text": "No...[p/] This wasn't the first time I'd heard about demons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0847dc7",
  "node": "BeatCornered15",
  "text": "Someone said something to me earlier—[p/]something about the history and legends of demons."
}

{
  "id": "line:013eceb",
  "node": "BeatCornered16",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, right.[p/] The Sword of Spell Eating is said to have been forged from a pact between a demon and a mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0069f0f",
  "node": "BeatCornered16",
  "text": "Celeste: Isn't making a deal with a demon just [i]asking[/i] for trouble?"
}

{
  "id": "line:049a13a",
  "node": "BeatCornered16",
  "text": "Celeste: They'd definitely betray you the first chance they got."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eacad1",
  "node": "BeatCornered16",
  "text": "Harold: Legends say that demons often drafted Blood Contracts for this reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae4cd8",
  "node": "BeatCornered16",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Do you mean like a [i]legally binding[/i] contract?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cdea1",
  "node": "BeatCornered16",
  "text": "Harold: The concept is similar,[p/] but once you sign a Blood Contract,[p/] both you and the demon are magically compelled to fulfill its terms."
}

{
  "id": "line:057ae07",
  "node": "BeatCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's right![p/][s/] Beatrice must have signed a \"Blood Contract\" with him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:050ba41",
  "node": "BeatCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: A soul-binding document like that [i]must[/i] describe how their relationship works."
}

{
  "id": "line:08415f6",
  "node": "BeatCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: Someone as meticulous as Beatrice would have those terms clearly laid out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7b056",
  "node": "BeatCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But it's not as if they'd ever show it to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0936f9b",
  "node": "BeatCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: It would be a tall order to even [i]prove[/i] that Blood Contracts even exist..."
}

{
  "id": "line:091ac4e",
  "node": "BeatCornered17a",
  "text": "Divine Edict"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b079d0",
  "node": "BeatCornered17a",
  "text": "There had to be some kind of clue as to how I could obtain Beatrice's Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:06869ab",
  "node": "BeatCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: Marrunath![p/][s/] Dweller of Avernus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ce5b5",
  "node": "BeatCornered18",
  "text": "Marrunath: Wait...[p/][s/] What are you doing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:057a3f1",
  "node": "BeatCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: By the Radiance of Horus,[p/][s/] I issue upon you a [b]Divine Edict[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed96e6",
  "node": "BeatCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: Release thy guards and manifest your Blood Contract with Beatrice Frega!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe06ab",
  "node": "BeatCornered18",
  "text": "In a surge of radiant light,[p/] a stack of papers appeared on the table in front of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd48aa",
  "node": "BeatCornered18",
  "text": "It was several pages long,[p/] and the writing was a sharp crimson red."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b8a2a",
  "node": "BeatCornered18",
  "text": "It would've been impossible to read through this in time,[p/] but somehow,[p/] I knew every detail of Beatrice's Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0525e8b",
  "node": "BeatCornered18",
  "text": "Horus: Well done, my heavensborn.[p/] You may yet survive the encroaching shadows."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c46e4",
  "node": "BeatCornered18",
  "text": "Beatrice: What in the nine hells was [i]that[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:090f612",
  "node": "BeatCornered18",
  "text": "Marrunath: Y-[p/][s/]You![p/][s/] When did you learn how to—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b73c7b",
  "node": "BeatCornered18",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert...?[p/] What just happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09dcae7",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] I just manifested the witness's Blood Contract with Marrunath!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ac619",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Beatrice: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb593a",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Judge: ...Blood Contract?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0a44b",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can think of it as a legally binding document.[p/] It lays out the terms of the pact between Beatrice Frega and her familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0253e0a",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Judge: I don't understand, Mr Cuthbert..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d99543",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Judge: How were you able to do such a thing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ce626",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "There was no legal precedent for this.[p/] I would need compelling evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0139fa1",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "...Doing this could very well change everything about my life."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a1857",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "But with House Frega's resources,[p/] William had caused nearly thousands of innocent deaths—[p/]all just so he could get ahead of House Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c13167",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "I couldn't let Beatrice or the Eyetaker get hold of that kind of power."
}

{
  "id": "line:037a1f7",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "...There was only one path forward."
}

{
  "id": "line:0563d9b",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor.[p/] My family doesn't hail from Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:005d7f2",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Tyrion: My ancestry originates from the Theocracy of Lumina."
}

{
  "id": "line:01848c2",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "RubyC: C-[p/][s/]Cuthbert![p/][s/] What are you doing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:023eed6",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion,[p/] what—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aedc71",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm a magic user known as a cleric of Horus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04bff0a",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Tyrion: And I used my divine magic to manifest the Blood Contract between Beatrice and Marrunath!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7e1a7",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Judge: T-[p/][s/]The Theocracy?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb5dae",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Gallery: A cleric of the Theocracy is practicing law in Wyverngarde?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af90b1",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Gallery: He's a traitor![p/][s/] He's an agent of our greatest enemy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1547e",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] The defense's argument is such:"
}

{
  "id": "line:02fcb53",
  "node": "BeatCornered19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Marrunath was acting alone.[p/] Therefore, the defendant was not to blame for his actions that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0671425",
  "node": "BeatCornered19a",
  "text": "Tyrion: However,[p/] take a look at page 7 of this Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0e3f8",
  "node": "BeatCornered19a",
  "text": "Tyrion: It specifies that Marrunath is prohibited from killing any and all humans."
}

{
  "id": "line:05469d5",
  "node": "BeatCornered19a",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's only one scenario where he can do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:039f62f",
  "node": "BeatCornered19a",
  "text": "Tyrion: And that's when Beatrice Frega designates someone to be exempt from this rule!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb6862",
  "node": "BeatCornered19a",
  "text": "Beatrice: You..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7351d",
  "node": "BeatCornered19a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Beatrice Frega![p/] You didn't [i]directly[/i] order Marrunath to kill your father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f862c0",
  "node": "BeatCornered19a",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you implied it by telling Marrunath by permitting the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b44084",
  "node": "BeatCornered19a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not only [i]that[/i],[p/][s/] you did so within the twenty-four hours of the Lords' Ball!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd5a55",
  "node": "BeatCornered19a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your intent was clear![p/][s/] You brought Marrunath into Frega Manor with full knowledge that he could and [i]would[/i] kill William Frega!"
}

{
  "id": "line:059d4be",
  "node": "BeatCornered19a",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And [i]that[/i][p/] is Checkmate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7105d",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] After [i]everything[/i] you've just said,[p/] I don't understand how you can expect any in this room to trust your words..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf13ba",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't need you to trust my words, Your Honor.[p/] I only need you to do what you've always done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ece7ee",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: And that's to acknowledge the evidence I've presented."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e371aa",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor,[p/] you know the implications of what I just revealed.[p/] You know what it could mean for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0844dcd",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why else would I do something like that if I weren't telling the truth?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e3190",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "The judge cursed under his breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8170b",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Judge: ...Despite the lack of [i]any[/i] legal precedent,[p/] I have no choice but to acknowledge the prosecutor's divine magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dbf36",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Judge: Do you have anything to say in your defense, Lady Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae2806",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Beatrice: Do [i]not[/i] call me that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a73843",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's almost funny that you hate your name that much."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e543be",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your entire plan depended on your claim to the Frega Estate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0016656",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Do you have any inkling of what you've just cost me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7bef4",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Beatrice: [i]Everything[/i] has been ruined because of you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5bde9",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're just another noble.[p/] Trying to steal power for yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b959d3",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Beatrice: Don't you [i]dare[/i] lump me together with those tyrants!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cadb9",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Beatrice: We wouldn't have just liberated House Frega![p/][s/] We would have liberated everyone!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0065f81",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Beatrice: Miriam,[p/] Laefe,[p/] Aria,[p/] even Aster."
}

{
  "id": "line:054653c",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Beatrice: Our system is [i]broken[/i]![p/][s/] The only way we can fix it is by burning it down from the inside!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0959864",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Beatrice: As long as the Four Pillars grip our kindgom[p/]—as long as King Olivier sits idly on his throne—[p/][s/]this suffering will only continue!"
}

{
  "id": "line:007abc9",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Judge: L-[p/][s/]Lady Frega!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc7669",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...As the prosecutor,[p/] I should warn you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03afac5",
  "node": "BeatCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: You don't want to add treason to your list of crimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0944514",
  "node": "BeatCornered21",
  "text": "Beatrice: Hmph...[p/] It doesn't matter.[p/] I'm done either way."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ef8b3",
  "node": "BeatCornered21",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Heavensborn,[p/] look at page 46 of the Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e2ce0",
  "node": "BeatCornered21",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"By accepting this pact,[p/] Beatrice Frega forever binds her soul to the Abyssal Hells.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:075b108",
  "node": "BeatCornered21",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"If Beatrice Frega fails to pay her debt by claiming House Frega and all of its assets...\""
}

{
  "id": "line:01b3ce1",
  "node": "BeatCornered21",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Her soul,[p/] her mind,[p/] and her life will be claimed by the Empress of Discord.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:065d7d3",
  "node": "BeatCornered21",
  "text": "The contract went on to name several parts of House Frega's holdings.[p/] There was very little room for ambiguity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3d712",
  "node": "BeatCornered21",
  "text": "Beatrice: Aria was [i]almost[/i] right.[p/] She just jumped to the wrong conclusion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddcd39",
  "node": "BeatCornered21",
  "text": "Beatrice: My debts were never to the Eyetaker...[p/] They were to the Abyssal Hells themselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f2d3d",
  "node": "BeatCornered21",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why would you agree to something like this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:036c438",
  "node": "BeatCornered21",
  "text": "Beatrice: Because I miscalculated..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b60d4",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...I know it was you.[p/] It has your name written all over it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce8dd0",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "Beatrice: You paid civilians to put in false reports of insurrections to the Crown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb6ac6",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "Beatrice: You paid off representatives in the House of Lords to vote in favor of sending Steelwind's soldiers to those regions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7b13c",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "Beatrice: And you paid mercenaries to assassinate beloved figures to enrage the commonfolk and incite those riots."
}

{
  "id": "line:089b017",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "William: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04346a2",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "Beatrice: It took me a while,[p/] but I've got proof that indisputably connects it all to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1d17a",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...It would be a shame if this information fell into Lucio's hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f32c77",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "William: You think this feeble attempt at blackmail will frighten me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09969d9",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "William: I've dealt with far more formidable adversaries than you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfdbe2",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "William: There's [i]nothing[/i] I can't solve with House Frega's resources."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dba03a",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "Beatrice: What are you talking about...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:053037e",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "Beatrice: Do you seriously think Lucio will stand idly by while you steal the Crown from him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:052373b",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "William: It's clear your time away from the manor has taught you nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5aa79",
  "node": "BeatCornered22",
  "text": "William: [i]Everyone[/i] can be bought.[p/] With my money,[p/] I'm practically a god."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eddb4a",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Beatrice: My father was clever.[p/] He knew how to manipulate people.[p/] He knew how to turn them against each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bb506",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Beatrice: No one knew this better than my sisters and I."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ade102",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Beatrice: I saw him as this unstoppable, tyrannical force,[p/] but I never even [i]considered[/i] one possibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8f518",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...That William Frega was an arrogant moron,[p/] so drunk off of his own power that he wouldn't acknowledge [i]anyone[/i] as a threat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c43c59",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Tyrion: He honestly thought he could buy his way out of his conspiracy being revealed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef6493",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Beatrice: I could've sent this information to House Steelwind and the King.[p/] He would've surely been executed for treason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d29d50",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Beatrice: But I was running out of time.[p/] I [i]needed[/i] to inherit House Frega soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1ed28",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Beatrice: I felt trapped...[p/] I felt angry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c11bf1",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Beatrice: I just needed [i]something[/i] to change."
}

{
  "id": "line:003b157",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...A Blood Contract is still a legal contract, isn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:065551a",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:082e9b5",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Tyrion: If it's a contract,[p/][s/] we can dispute it."
}

{
  "id": "line:099ea2a",
  "node": "BeatCornered23",
  "text": "Tyrion: We can find [i]some[/i] kind of loophole to get you out of it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0980e2e",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Marrunath: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:092eb24",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Trying to [i]redeem[/i] the enemy you [i]just[/i] defeated?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03089a6",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Beatrice: You really [i]are[/i] a heavensborn."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e36131",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Beatrice: I'm sorry, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] but I won't accept your help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0077685",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?![p/][s/] Why?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a23918",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Tyrion: We can at least try, can't we?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0fabc",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you seriously come this far just so you could die?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba5d15",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...To dispute a Blood Contract is to bet your own soul."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eacc03",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Marrunath: If you fail to render it null,[p/] [i]your[/i] soul will be dragged to Hell alongside hers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a142f2",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Marrunath: Even your divine blood won't save you from that fate."
}

{
  "id": "line:03eae44",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]But, still![p/][s/] I can't just—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cab525",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Beatrice: You've beaten me, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:05251c2",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Beatrice: I won't drag anyone else down with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:065da4e",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Beatrice: Not you.[p/] Not Laefe.[p/] Not Miriam."
}

{
  "id": "line:00949f2",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Beatrice: Despite everything,[p/] I still have my pride."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d46932",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Judge: ...I believe there's no further need to prolong this trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0042018",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Judge: Bailiff.[p/] Please escort Lady Frega and her familiar to a holding cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbf534",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Judge: I'll be passing my verdict shortly."
}

{
  "id": "line:09910a0",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey...[p/] Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0488267",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] As okay as I [i]can[/i] be."
}

{
  "id": "line:087d5be",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "I still felt uneasy about how things turned out.[p/] It didn't feel quite like the victory I was hoping for."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f87db",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Honestly,[p/] every case I've defended felt that way.[p/] Maybe that's just how the world was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7f6d0",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "I fought against the demons,[p/] but I still felt like I'd lost."
}

{
  "id": "line:01990df",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Ruby: We need to talk."
}

{
  "id": "line:06426e7",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...What's done is done,[p/] but the Eyetaker isn't going to take this lying down."
}

{
  "id": "line:07973ac",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Ruby: I know it's a long shot,[p/] but maybe if you talk to him,[p/] he'll—"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d71de",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Tyrion: No."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7b96f",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert![p/][s/] This is serious!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0625c22",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Ruby: He's [i]going[/i] to send people after you—[p/][i]dangerous[/i] people![p/][s/] You can't just [i]ignore[/i] this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a95c77",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Eris: How old were you when your [i]real[/i] mother was executed?[p/] Ten years old?"
}

{
  "id": "line:009c34c",
  "node": "End3",
  "text": "Eris: Back then,[p/] you barely [i]knew[/i] Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0604152",
  "node": "End3",
  "text": "Eris: She was the adult in that situation,[p/] and what did she do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:068e033",
  "node": "End3",
  "text": "Eris: Instead of allowing you to process your grief and move on,[p/] she fed your anger and hatred for the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc7ab0",
  "node": "End3",
  "text": "Eris: Tymora took you away from your only friends and isolated you from society."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d429b1",
  "node": "End3",
  "text": "Eris: Do you really think she loves you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0ca66",
  "node": "End3",
  "text": "Ruby: Please just listen to me and—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a13c7e",
  "node": "End3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Shut.[p/][p/][s/] Up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0030f46",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: How could you do this...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea7213",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: How could you work with [i]criminals[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f32be",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert...[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de3ff3",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Everything[/i] you told me![p/][s/] All those ideals about protecting the weak!"
}

{
  "id": "line:071ea97",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was all a lie!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0898a44",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Everything Commander White said about you was true, wasn't it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9535e",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Ruby: I'm just trying to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0105c3c",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "All of the confusion—[p/]all of the frustration over not knowing anything—[p/]it all boiled over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecb2be",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't [i]want[/i] your help!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff913f",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "As I yelled at her,[p/] my voice echoed throughout the lobby.[p/] Everyone turned silent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0995fe5",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I gave up [s/][i]everything[/i] for you![p/][s/] My childhood![p/][s/] My home![p/][s/] My happiness!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9d915",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I left it all behind to chase the ideal that [i]you[/i] told me you were fighting for!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05167c3",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But it was never real, was it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0103870",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You made me throw away [i]everything[/i]![p/][s/] [i]All[/i] for a god-damned lie!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07892d5",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I'll make it real."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c87f37",
  "node": "End4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And I'll do it without you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ede5a5",
  "node": "End5",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion...[p/][s/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:032706e",
  "node": "End5",
  "text": "Her voice was breaking.[p/] It was the first time I'd ever seen her like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cd3d5",
  "node": "End5",
  "text": "She reached out to me.[p/] I just stepped away."
}

{
  "id": "line:040e969",
  "node": "End5",
  "text": "Tyrion: You never cared about me, did you...?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd5a24",
  "node": "End5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...All you cared about was using the Eye of Horus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d98983",
  "node": "End5",
  "text": "Ruby: That's not—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc5222",
  "node": "End5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Shut up![p/][s/] I don't want to hear [i]any[/i] more of your damn lies!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3eec3",
  "node": "End5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Go away![p/][s/] Get the [i]hell[/i] away from me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8f54a",
  "node": "End5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]never[/i] want to see you again!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c1702",
  "node": "End5",
  "text": "Without a word,[p/] she walked out of the courthouse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7ee81",
  "node": "End5",
  "text": "She reached out her hand to mine,[p/] but she hesitated."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ff662",
  "node": "End6",
  "text": "Eris: Do you think [i]Celeste[/i] will ever love you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b2ace",
  "node": "End6",
  "text": "Eris: Do you think she has the luxury of playing hero with you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7d421",
  "node": "End6",
  "text": "Eris: Or did you actually think that she [i]enjoyed[/i] spending time with you that much?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d3502",
  "node": "End6",
  "text": "Eris: Tyrion.[p/] You have to look at this rationally."
}

{
  "id": "line:084c677",
  "node": "End6",
  "text": "Eris: The support and affection she's given you have been to keep you as an employer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7a647",
  "node": "End6",
  "text": "Eris: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ad388",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Celeste: Is everything really going to be okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:069176f",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Tyrion: It will be.[p/] I'll get you that acquittal no matter what."
}

{
  "id": "line:020bf1f",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Man, king, or god?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8282f",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]*chuckle*[/i][p/] Yes.[p/] Man,[p/] king,[p/] or god."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ced4c",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Celeste: There![p/][s/] What about that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:057f4b3",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "I immediately moved my queen to respond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f98adb",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Checkmate."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cde08",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Celeste: Damn it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f04d5e",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion, are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:013fb78",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Celeste: I know you're not,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6440f",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e59f7",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Celeste: It's [i]not[/i] fine!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da63fb",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Does it have something to do with what happened to your mom?"
}

{
  "id": "line:025b521",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Celeste: For the last two nights,[p/] you've been calling out for her in your sleep."
}

{
  "id": "line:092e09b",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Celeste: Please.[p/] Just talk to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a5130",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "My hands were trembling.[p/] Why was I so scared right now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d7342",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "I felt Celeste gently hold my shaking hand from behind me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0204abf",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "It was warm and comforting...[p/] It was that same sensation that I'd felt back then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4c43c",
  "node": "End7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm not going to do that, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf9adc",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "As she hesitated to take my hand,[p/] I softly grasped hers."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e3516",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "She smiled as I took hold of it.[p/] She seemed glad I didn't pull away this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f204f3",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "...My arms moved without thinking.[p/] I pulled her into a hug."
}

{
  "id": "line:02432c1",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Celeste: T-[p/][s/]Tyrion?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b71f8",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sorry.[p/] I just really need this right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e4d81",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Should I stop?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02fcec3",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Celeste: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] It's just..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bdd31",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Celeste: People are staring at us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0463f5d",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Who cares?[p/] They're nobles."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c3209",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're going to hate us no matter what we do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7d1f9",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "I still wasn't sure what was going to happen next."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc9b05",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "But maybe I didn't need to—[p/]even [i]if[/i] Tymora's ideal was a lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:01355e5",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hey, Celeste.[p/] There's been something I've been wanting to tell you about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a70176",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Oh?![p/][s/] U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] What is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0510096",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's hard to explain, really...[p/] I don't even know where to begin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0628c26",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Tyrion: But it's about where I came from and what I can do."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c2a97",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have this ability called the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0486359",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Even if that ideal was a lie,[p/] I wasn't going to give up on making it real."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3f309",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "I couldn't trust Tymora anymore,[p/] but I didn't have to do this alone."
}

{
  "id": "line:049b252",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "Celeste was by my side,[p/] and Aria had more than proved she was worthy of my trust."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cd0d6",
  "node": "End8",
  "text": "And I'm sure I would find more allies in the future."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a36b77",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: What a [i]fine[/i] mess this is..."
}

{
  "id": "line:052d107",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: That kid has completely and [i]utterly[/i] ruined everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f1156",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: ...As much as Tymora hates it,[p/] we're going to need to put him in the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0942d37",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eris: I don't think that will be necessary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5e376",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Sorry, Love.[p/] I know you're fond of him,[p/] but he crossed me."
}

{
  "id": "line:02250d6",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: He's going to have to pay the price."
}

{
  "id": "line:0deb0fa",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eris: I think you've misunderstood me, \"father\".[p/] I meant that this facade has run its course."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8cb22",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a88c9",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0916beb",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: What...?[p/][s/] What the hell?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02bfae2",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eris: Is something wrong, \"father\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f88d52",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Who...[p/][s/] Who the hell are you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ac726",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: You look [i]nothing[/i] like my daughter![p/] So, why—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ae859",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eris: It happened centuries ago,[p/] I believe."
}

{
  "id": "line:033c1f2",
  "node": "End9",
  "text": "Eris: Your great-ancestor wanted the Crown for himself.[p/] He entered an accord with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e18e3",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eyetaker: W-[p/][s/]What are you talking about?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe9086",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: But fate seldom bends to mortal desire, I’m afraid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c07e9a",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: Poor Lord Leiran's scheme was laid bare.[p/] The banners of his house were torn down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a004b1",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: His very name was stricken from the annals of history."
}

{
  "id": "line:03227ee",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: ...He was [i]supposed[/i] to give me Wyverngarde,[p/] but I had to settle for his bloodline."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2685c",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eyetaker: \"Leiran...\"?[p/] H-[p/][s/]How do you know about my name?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0029201",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eyetaker: [i]No one[/i] knew about that name![p/][s/] Not even my [i]real[/i] daughter!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0691a1c",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: It's been centuries,[p/] but I haven't forgotten, Jon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff873c",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: Every soul in your bloodline belongs to me,[p/][s/] [i]including[/i] your daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f8ab6",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eyetaker: You bastard![p/][s/] What did you do to her?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0734fb9",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: What I do to all my prey.[p/] I made her suffer."
}

{
  "id": "line:077f4b6",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eyetaker: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cae71b",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: Did you know that she was crying out for you for months?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d42027",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: I made her watch, you know.[p/] I made her watch as I took her place."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f482a",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: All while the \"father\" that she so desperately called out for forgot who she was."
}

{
  "id": "line:010d133",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: All while my minions slowly and painfully tore her soul apart—[p/]piece by agonizing piece."
}

{
  "id": "line:085e88a",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eyetaker: You...[p/][s/] You monster!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1643f",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: I enjoyed her torment while it lasted,[p/] but even [i]that[/i] couldn't satisfy me."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e997b",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: What I [i]really[/i] crave is the blood of the divine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d161b9",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eyetaker: [i]That's[/i] what this is about?![p/][s/] That stupid kid?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c60a2",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: But I can't have you kill my dear Tyrion just yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca204a",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eris: At least not until [i]I'm[/i] done with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:079eb4c",
  "node": "End10",
  "text": "Eyetaker: You goddamned demon![p/] I'll kill you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0698c5b",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Eris: This man is your enemy.[p/] Your life's goal is[p/] and always has been to exact revenge on him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0678e63",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Eyetaker: W-[p/][s/]What the [i]hell[/i] are you talking about?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09366e6",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Knight: You![p/][s/] I lost [i]everything[/i] because of you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0377783",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Knight: They kicked me out of the Inquisition because of your false testimony!"
}

{
  "id": "line:046660e",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Eyetaker: W-[p/][s/]What...?[p/] L-[p/][s/]Let go of me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:090a022",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Peasant: Y-[p/][s/]You...[p/] You killed my entire family!"
}

{
  "id": "line:018d401",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Peasant: I won't let you get away with this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c88ebe",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Eyetaker: W-[p/][s/]What are you talking about?![p/][s/] I didn't do anything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c191d",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Townsfolk: Hey...[p/] Isn't that the noble who killed all those children?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d3ea3",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Townsfolk: I heard he got released by paying off the judge!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f47343",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Eyetaker: What are you all talking about?![p/][s/] Get away from me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d9a10",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Townsfolk: Don't lie to us![p/][s/] We know what you did!"
}

{
  "id": "line:087e4bf",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Eyetaker: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/][s/] Stay away!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05bd4c1",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Eyetaker: AGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGH!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9ada0",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Eris: We've finally entered the final act,[p/] my dearest Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:06aa8e8",
  "node": "End11",
  "text": "Eris: And from what I've seen,[p/] I think I know [i]exactly[/i] how I'm going to break you."
}

{
  "id": "line:001031b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "Ms. Tymora led me out of the courthouse and into the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0503f05",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "Every time I asked her where she was taking me,[p/] she avoided answering."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5f739",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "Ruby: Alright...[p/] We're here."
}

{
  "id": "line:094a5fb",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "We arrived at an empty alley in the frankly seedier part of the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:03658c0",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "As Ms. Tymora approached one of the derelict buildings,[p/] she was met with a large, burly man who was guarding the back door."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af011c",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "The man silently acknowledges her and steps aside to let her in."
}

{
  "id": "line:066bc43",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Ms. Tymora?[p/] Where are we going?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ede407",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "Ruby: I'm sorry about this...[p/] I'm sure you're confused."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a668a1",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "Ruby: But you need to trust me.[p/] I'll explain everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:00223c0",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "Before I had a chance to ask for more,[p/] she moved into the building."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b29af",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "The man guarding the door looked at me expectantly."
}

{
  "id": "line:072a4c8",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "The entire situation didn't sit right with me,[p/] but I still followed after her."
}

{
  "id": "line:06962e7",
  "node": "EyetakerScene",
  "text": "Despite our recent disagreements,[p/] I knew that I could still trust her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc4edd",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "As we went further into the building,[p/] I found myself in a surprisingly well-furnished room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0626039",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "From how it looked outside,[p/] I would have never guessed that it would look like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:041b841",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "It almost looked like a room that I'd encounter in the Frega Manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:034703c",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "As I entered,[p/] I spotted several armed men standing at various points in the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:046934d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "...And most surprisingly,[p/] I saw Eris standing near the window."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e91eb",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "I shot her a confused look,[p/] but she simply smiled and waved at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:038764e",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "Sitting at a desk next to her,[p/] was a man with an eyepatch."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ec107",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "He looked friendly and welcoming,[p/] but my Eye of Horus couldn't read anything from him."
}

{
  "id": "line:06af0d9",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "It was like trying to read thoughts from a stone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc2bf3",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "He felt reminiscent of those charlatans trying to sell me suspicious \"miracle\" potions on the street."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d879fa",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Ah, Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6b33a",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "Upon seeing the two of us,[p/] he cordially welcomed my mentor before turning his attention to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6fbf8",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "Eyetaker: And [i]you[/i] must be Tyrion.[p/] Tymora has told me a lot about you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7369c",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Who are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05ab613",
  "node": "EyetakerScene2",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Hm...[p/] I've been called many names over the years,[p/] but my favorite has always been \"The Eyetaker\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d673d7",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Eyetaker..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0868617",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: From the sounds of it,[p/] you've already heard of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:007636b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Ms. Tymora.[p/] What is this...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4fc71",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Ruby: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc3ae9",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: My daughter Eris has told me all about your work prosecuting this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:076bb57",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eris was his [i]daughter[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d9660",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: But I have to say,[p/] I'm quite impressed."
}

{
  "id": "line:08122b3",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Getting a [i]monkey[/i] to testify?[p/][s/] I don't think [i]I[/i] could even pull off a grift like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0366968",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: You've pretty much blown past my expectations.[p/] Why I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0357a4e",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Get to the point."
}

{
  "id": "line:043928c",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "As soon as I interrupted him,[p/] I felt every person in the room tense up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba8b3e",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: ...Relax, everyone.[p/] Kids will be kids."
}

{
  "id": "line:000d220",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: I'm a father myself, you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a582de",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eris: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0910ee2",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: I'll get straight to the point."
}

{
  "id": "line:044424d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: I have a certain interest in the outcome of this trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a62f38",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Little Lady Frega has been a client of ours for a long time."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f2bd7",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: I've done quite a lot of favors for her.[p/] It's been quite an investment, you see?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09fca3f",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Those debts that Steelwind mentioned..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bade6a",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: They all belong to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2bb01",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: But there's no need to worry.[p/] I know she's good for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01929d3",
  "node": "EyetakerScene3",
  "text": "Eyetaker: That is...[p/] [i]if[/i] she can inherit House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0415171",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Tyrion: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d42d6",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Tymora's a good attorney,[p/] even [i]without[/i] my help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0713752",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: If she were convicted,[p/] we could've easily reduced her sentence by rubbing the right hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbe7e0",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: But, you see...[p/][s/] There's that pesky Slayer Rule."
}

{
  "id": "line:0961242",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: The thing is, Cuthbert,[p/] I [i]need[/i] Beatrice Frega to be acquitted in the current trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0941311",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "I narrowed my eyes at him,[p/] then to Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d7d3f",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So [i]that's[/i] what this is about?[p/][s/] House Frega's gold?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0adf2c0",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's why you helped her [i]murder[/i] William Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f5cc7",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Please.[p/] My goals aren't nearly so short-sighted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7ca80",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: I have big plans—[p/]not just for Beatrice but for this entire kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c062f",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: And I need House Frega for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:017702f",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Just like you \"needed\" Justin Waye?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01fe289",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fac055",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Ah, Justin.[p/] It's really a shame what happened to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0662d3d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't act so innocent...[p/][s/] He would have never gotten involved with von Sanctus if it weren't for his debts to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:09669df",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Is that so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2a78f",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Do you think I just randomly showed up on his doorstep one day,[p/] demanding gold?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08eb87c",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: [i]He[/i] was the one who came to [i]my[/i] people for help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e13d85",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: I just told him to pay back what he owed."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b4ed9",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: If he hadn't come to me,[p/] it would have been some other criminal locked up with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:00300c1",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: But that's beside the point.[p/] Enough about what I wanted from Justin."
}

{
  "id": "line:06406ac",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Let's talk about what I want from you."
}

{
  "id": "line:037a42d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You want me to throw the case?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f93e28",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Ah, I love this kid![p/][s/] I don't have to beat around the bush with this one!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9e1f6",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: No one will doubt you.[p/] Especially considering the amount of work you put into this already."
}

{
  "id": "line:077e9a5",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: You don't [i]need[/i] to do anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0630387",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: ...Just stumble a little near the end.[p/] Take a dive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0408402",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Tyrion: And let someone [i]else[/i] take the fall?"
}

{
  "id": "line:057d020",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Tyrion: No matter [i]what[/i] happens,[p/] the courts [i]will[/i] blame someone for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0576c5c",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: If it makes you feel better,[p/] I can assign Tymora to defend the old man [i]and[/i] his monkey."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fd7a8",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: That way,[p/] everyone can come out of this unharmed."
}

{
  "id": "line:023b8d6",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Everyone wins."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d5c43",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Except for the fact that a [i]murderer[/i] will be put in charge of House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c611f9",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Kid,[p/] there was [i]always[/i] a murderer in charge of House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:077b99b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: You've been hearing about it in the news, haven't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b0397",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: ...About all those \"insurrections\" in the countryside?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aad376",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Tyrion: What does [i]that[/i] have to do with House Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7841e",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Didn't you ever stop to think how little sense it made?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed0fa1",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Why would Lucio Steelwind [i]keep[/i] massacring all those people?[p/] What did he gain from that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:018ec28",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: It doesn't matter how bloodthirsty he is.[p/] He wouldn't last very long in this kingdom if he had that little self-control."
}

{
  "id": "line:087878e",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: His reputation's in the hole now.[p/] It's even mucking up his daughter's arranged marriage to the future king."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c435c4",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: ...Who do you think gained the most from that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4cbf0",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Scaled Lord..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e12af",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: The man with the money decides the rules."
}

{
  "id": "line:0712c58",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: House Frega secretly owns every printing press in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:04981f8",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Buy a few false reports here,[p/] pay for a few assassinations there,[p/] you get the gist."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f4935",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: For a man with William's resources,[p/] public opinion can be whatever he wants it to be."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fc559",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: We should all thank little Ms. Frega for digging all this up."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c8447",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "I looked at Ms. Tymora.[p/] Had she been hiding this from me the whole time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01111c3",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Was Lucio Steelwind even as bloodthirsty as I'd always thought he was?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9a0e5",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "I never actually [i]saw[/i] him do anything that criminal during my case in Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a76c28",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...If you all knew about this,[p/] why didn't you release it to the public?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a33e6",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Damn...[p/] Are you really that naïve?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e50b0",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5a",
  "text": "Eyetaker: The public will do zilch.[p/] Everyone's out for themselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d93c29",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5a",
  "text": "Eyetaker: People will get angry for a week or two,[p/] but no one really gives a damn."
}

{
  "id": "line:0399324",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5a",
  "text": "Eyetaker: You saw it yourself.[p/] You caught von Sanctus red-handed,[p/] and he didn't even get hit with community service."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc304b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5a",
  "text": "Eyetaker: We're all just pawns in the nobility's game."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c296b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5a",
  "text": "Eyetaker: But I've got a pawn myself,[p/] and she's going to become a beautiful queen by the end of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba79b8",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5a",
  "text": "Eyetaker: We'll finally have a level playing field with those bastards."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d6ebe",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5a",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion,[p/] please.[p/] Just listen to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0278ca6",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5a",
  "text": "Tyrion: How can you just go along with this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0605e23",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5a",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I told you a long time ago that there were certain parts of my job that I couldn't tell you about."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c2e87",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5a",
  "text": "Ruby: Well?[p/][s/] [i]This[/i] is it.[p/][s/] [i]This[/i] is what we need to do to beat them!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b28645",
  "node": "EyetakerScene5a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Those rumors about you.[p/] They're all true, aren't they...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee73a1",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Forgery,[p/] bribery,[p/] blackmail—[p/]you're guilty of each and every one of them..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b6648",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Tyrion: And you used [i]him[/i] to do it![p/][s/] All so you could keep winning!"
}

{
  "id": "line:047d419",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]blackmailed[/i] Miriam, Ms. Tymora!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7345e",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Ruby: Oh, as if we should show [i]any[/i] pity for that spoiled princess!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f42de3",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "A dreadful thought came to mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f262b0",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind...[p/] She was attacked the day that Beatrice was arrested..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0776e5f",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was that—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ecafc",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Ruby: I-[p/][s/]I didn't [i]know[/i] that's what they were planning!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06145ed",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Eyetaker: I have no doubt in Tymora's skills,[p/] but I'm afraid there was too much riding on this to leave to chance."
}

{
  "id": "line:042d83d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Eyetaker: You've got to make your own luck if you want to beat the system."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b2b79",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Tyrion: How could you?![p/][s/] She almost died!"
}

{
  "id": "line:068b59e",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Eyetaker: We never expected her to strain her injuries like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e67ad",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Eyetaker: And we definitely didn't expect [i]you[/i] to take her place."
}

{
  "id": "line:053ba51",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Eyetaker: So believe me when I say,[p/] that I'm being [i]uncharacteristically[/i] reasonable right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:030bea9",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Tyrion: How...[p/][s/] How could you even [i]consider[/i] working with someone like him?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb4bd9",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Don't you think it's a little arrogant to judge her, Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c636c3",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Eyetaker: You talk about defending people as if you two are even close to being equals."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c4cad",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Eyetaker: But [i]she[/i] doesn't have the luxury of looking into people's minds,[p/] now does she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:053285d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene6",
  "text": "Tyrion: You...[p/][s/] You [i]told[/i] him about the Eye of Horus?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:087c149",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e7d71",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Eyetaker: The future of magic is changing, kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0317072",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Like I said before.[p/] I have big plans for this kingdom,[p/] and I also have big plans for [i]you[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d829be",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you think I would ever—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb53d2",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion![p/][s/] Stop!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0e635",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: I hate this as much as you do..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e726f",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: But whether you like it or not,[p/][s/] we [i]need[/i] help from people like them!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a18d0",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: It's the only way we can ensure we win!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ca91d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Tyrion: But this is—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2629b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: Think about every client you defended![p/][s/] Think of Celeste!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0889d69",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: If you didn't have the Eye of Horus,[p/][s/] what would have happened to her?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a5b55",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: If even [i]one[/i] thing had gone differently,[p/][s/] Pierce would have gotten away,[p/] and Celeste would have been executed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bea612",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: You've taken chances and followed your instincts,[p/] and that's worked for you so far."
}

{
  "id": "line:014d39d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: But one day,[p/] it's not going to be enough.[p/][s/] Who's going to die because of that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:020d593",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: With his help,[p/] you'll never have to worry about that again."
}

{
  "id": "line:024b02d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Eyetaker: So what's it going to be, kid?"
}

{
  "id": "line:039dd65",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Eyetaker: You already know about what happened to Steelwind's brat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e57301",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Eyetaker: So I don't need to tell [i]you[/i] what'll happen if you don't play ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b50977",
  "node": "EyetakerScene7",
  "text": "Ruby: W-[p/][s/]Wait!"
}

{
  "id": "line:077f63b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Eyetaker: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6bae7",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Maybe you're right.[p/] Maybe I [i]can't[/i] always win against the nobility unless I operate as they do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0677e3e",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Tyrion: But [i]this[/i]?![p/][s/] This won't change anything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0537aad",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'd just be trading one set of criminals for another!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0edc1be",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Ruby: T-[p/][s/]Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:066bf67",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm [i]not[/i] going to become everything I hate about this kingdom.[p/] Not even for you, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cb014",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Eyetaker: ...I'm sorry to hear you say that, kid.[p/] I really am."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c40cd",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "With one motion of his hand,[p/] every mercenary in the room drew their weapons."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a038a",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Ruby: W-[p/][s/]Wait![p/][s/] Stop!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5f7c3",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Whatever conviction I had before was slowly fading."
}

{
  "id": "line:0776aab",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "I should have never entered this place...[p/] I [i]knew[/i] something was off."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f5de8",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "There were about a dozen mercenaries here,[p/] and there were even [i]more[/i] guarding the exit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aced11",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "I was nowhere near as physically strong as Celeste,[p/] but maybe I could make a break for it if I get lucky."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ff630",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Celeste: ...No."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9f5d5",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Tyrion: C-[p/][s/]Celeste?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06faa5b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene8",
  "text": "Eyetaker: What the—?![p/][s/] How'd you get in here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbe08b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you honestly think I'd just let you take him to some suspicious shack?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093f040",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Hmph...[p/][s/] It doesn't matter.[p/][s/] As if one girl will make a difference."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d558e",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Well?[p/] What are you all waiting for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a221de",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Mercenaries: ...Is that really her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bee352",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Upon seeing Celeste,[p/] the mercenaries cautiously stepped back.[p/] No one wanted to make the first move."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba3ad3",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Mercenaries: This monstrous aura...[p/] It [i]has[/i] to be her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0d023",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: What the hell are you doing?![p/] You have her surrounded!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa0f8b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Despite his command,[p/] no one took a step forward."
}

{
  "id": "line:019940f",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Ruby: L-[p/][s/]Look...[p/] Let's all just sit down and talk about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:032e4bd",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Eris: Perhaps a different approach is warranted here, Father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c69bab",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Eris: Could I have the opportunity to speak with Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c7d34",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Eris: I believe [i]I[/i] can make him see things our way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0c3c2",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: I'm sorry, sweetie. But I can't just[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b062d6",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: Well...[p/] You've never been wrong before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0883b95",
  "node": "EyetakerScene9",
  "text": "Eyetaker: I'll leave them to you, love."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ab58b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Eris: Shall we go, you two?"
}

{
  "id": "line:070ab7f",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Celeste silently watched Eris with her sword drawn,[p/] but unlike the mercenaries,[p/] Eris seemed unfazed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7d925",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "She simply walked past her and out the exit.[p/] Celeste and I exchanged glances and followed after her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7b308",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I don't think I could have fought that whole room while protecting you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd68bb",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Eris: You two are really courageous to a fault, aren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0885f11",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eris.[p/] I appreciate you stepping in,[p/] but I'm not changing my mind about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2a5a6",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Eris: Oh, I'm well aware of that.[p/] Why do you think I intervened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:022f0a9",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh.[p/] Well...[p/] thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f482a",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is this really okay?[p/] Won't your dad be mad?"
}

{
  "id": "line:067e68b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Eris: I should be asking [i]Tyrion[/i] that same question."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0df63",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Eris: You've seen your adoptive mother's true colors and rejected them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea693b",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Eris: How are the two of you going to move forward?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b505d2",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]She's not my—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05dfcd9",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Eris: Isn't she, though?[p/] She lost any right to deny it the moment she took it upon herself to raise you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c22b54",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Tyrion: She only did that because I asked her to...[p/] It wasn't her choice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0211936",
  "node": "EyetakerScene10",
  "text": "Eris: Oh, but it was."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d63d6",
  "node": "EyetakerScene11",
  "text": "Celeste: Eris!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d42dae",
  "node": "EyetakerScene11",
  "text": "Eris: She even homeschooled you, didn't she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:033daa9",
  "node": "EyetakerScene11",
  "text": "Tyrion: T-[p/][s/]That's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0507c",
  "node": "EyetakerScene11",
  "text": "Eris: As a result,[p/] you never formed any other relationships."
}

{
  "id": "line:075a521",
  "node": "EyetakerScene11",
  "text": "Eris: You made your first close friend at the age of twenty,[p/] and she was your [i]client[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d8656",
  "node": "EyetakerScene11",
  "text": "Eris: Don't you think that's a bit sad?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b02776",
  "node": "EyetakerScene11",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That's not true![p/][s/] That's not why she—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aefb11",
  "node": "EyetakerScene11",
  "text": "Eris: From what I've seen today,[p/] you clearly have no idea who [i]Tymora[/i] is."
}

{
  "id": "line:024b17c",
  "node": "EyetakerScene11",
  "text": "Eris: Even with the Eye of Horus,[p/] you're clearly a terrible judge of character."
}

{
  "id": "line:0296ef9",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Eris leaned in really close to me and whispered something into my ear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf404a",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Eris: Do you really think Tymora loves you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fefedb",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Eris: ...Do you think [i]Celeste[/i] will ever love you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0340765",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...W-[p/][s/]What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0402336",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Eris: I'm sure you understand now.[p/] Tymora can only afford to pay her exorbitant salary because of my father."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c3d37",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Eris: You've already burned that bridge.[p/] So, where do you think the Crimson Demon will go when you can't afford her services anymore?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07fecd3",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] She's not—"
}

{
  "id": "line:041b98d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Eris: With Flinhart dead,[p/] she has to worry about her mother."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7952d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Eris: Or did you actually think that she [i]enjoys[/i] spending time with you that much?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1ad84",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Eris: The affection she's given you has been to keep you as an employer."
}

{
  "id": "line:061f65d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Celeste: I had to do a lot of networking when I was a mercenary."
}

{
  "id": "line:01195d8",
  "node": "EyetakerScene12",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you know how many times I had to charm a merchant into hiring me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae805a",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Why...[p/] are you telling me this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e986d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Eris: Because I want to break you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a629fe",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Eris: I'm just trying to keep you from getting hurt."
}

{
  "id": "line:06af2dd",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Eris: It may seem cruel,[p/] but you have to be realistic about these things."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ad7bf",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Eris: ...You trusted Tymora,[p/] and she betrayed you."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d744d",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Eris: You'd do well not to make the same mistake twice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe3577",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Celeste didn't hear anything she said,[p/] but she could see how rattled I was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9fd64",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Celeste: Eris![p/][s/] That's enough!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe6e03",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Eris: Ah.[p/] My apologies."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ef6c8",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Eris: I've been told that I've been too blunt sometimes,[p/] but I do hope you'll think about what I said."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed183f",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Eris: ...Anyways,[p/] the trial should be starting soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eac32e",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Eris: We should make our way back to the courthouse."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ad8ba",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Eris: I'm genuinely curious to see how this trial ends."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d71a5",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Celeste: H-[p/][s/]Hey, Tyrion?[p/] Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:072c933",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Celeste: What did she say to you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b04d19",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "She took my hand,[p/] but I instinctively yanked it away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7706a",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...S-[p/][s/]Sorry.[p/] I didn't mean to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b28f0",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm okay, really."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b606f7",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "Celeste: Um...[p/] Okay... [h=\"...Is he mad that I followed him?\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:029f574",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "...I could think about everything else later."
}

{
  "id": "line:082081e",
  "node": "EyetakerScene13",
  "text": "I knew what I needed to do at that moment.[p/] I needed to convict Beatrice Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:084dbff",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Sword"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c58325",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The display case is completely shattered..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01baa48",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The thief was able to do this despite there being several [b]abjuration[/b] spells protecting it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0828ea7",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Earrings"
}

{
  "id": "line:064eae5",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The display case holding the Earrings of Vitality is completely untouched."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8cea0",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Whoever stole the artifacts ignored it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ea3c1",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Armbands"
}

{
  "id": "line:022802a",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The display case that held the Armbands of Intellect is empty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1d54e",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: According to Harold,[p/] the Armbands were stolen discreetly..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e5a1e",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Painting 1"
}

{
  "id": "line:0640f49",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of some sort of scientist."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a69b93",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: That man is Dr. Luke Kuepfer.[p/] He was an alchemist and inventor from the nation of Arcarus."
}

{
  "id": "line:009fd77",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: He is well-known for his studies into imbuing intelligence into automatons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0440833",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Intelligent automatons...[p/] Would that make them similar to Arcane Constructs?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9d9bd",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Yes, actually.[p/] I wouldn't be surprised if Lord von Sanctus used Dr. Kuepfer's research to create those Constructs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbfaac",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "I doubted he even created them.[p/] He seemed to be importing all of them from Arcarus and taking credit for their work."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c10ad2",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Supposedly[p/], his name is Dr. Luke Kuepfer.[p/] He was an alchemist and inventor from the nation of Arcarus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0250176",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: He was well-known for his studies into imbuing intelligence into automatons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0359961",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: Intelligent automatons...[p/] Like Arcane Constructs?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0312c6d",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Von Sanctus was importing a bunch of them from Arcarus for his plans in Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d864d8",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The technology for those Constructs was probably invented there."
}

{
  "id": "line:092d493",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Painting 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:056f65f",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of a researcher."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbab86",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: That is Professor Matt Ferland.[p/] He was a professor of some renown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba2388",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: He was a researcher of Combinatorial Magic Theory."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b1646",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What's that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a7a47",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: It's the study of how different types of magic interact with each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e7874",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: He famously ran an experiment on what would happen if two [b]Anti-magic Fields[/b] overlapped each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba94f0",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That's actually pretty interesting.[p/] What were the results of the experiment?"
}

{
  "id": "line:036cd6d",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Well, they had mages enter the space where the two fields overlapped."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b8ee1",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: It turns out that those mages [i]were[/i] able to use their magic in that space."
}

{
  "id": "line:0848ae6",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait,[p/] how would that be possible?[p/] They would have had two [b]Anti-magic Fields[/b] affecting them."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c904f",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: When the two fields overlap,[p/] they cancel each other out.[p/] I've heard that it's akin to multiplying two negative numbers together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0214dff",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Supposedly, his name is Professor Matt Ferland.[p/] He was a professor of Combinatorial Magic Theory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a56fb8",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: What is that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f2d76",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have no idea."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eae5a5",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Detect Glass"
}

{
  "id": "line:0994a92",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: There are traces of [b]evocation[/b] magic on the shattered glass."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f12ec4",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: [b]Evocation[/b] is the school of magic that creates and unleashes raw energy."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fca42",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's the most primal of the seven schools of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec769d",
  "node": "Examine_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Someone must have used a powerful spell to blast the display case apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ebe20",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: The Artifacts"
}

{
  "id": "line:086b3e5",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't believe a [i]museum[/i] owns a magic item like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bd2bf",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: I would have expected the noble houses to take them for themselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:076d612",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: The nobility of today doesn't have much use for items such as these."
}

{
  "id": "line:068cbbc",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: The power of a lord is based on politics rather than magical strength nowadays."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c44e5",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: And a noble wouldn't want to wield the sword of a demon,[p/] even [i]if[/i] the legends are just stories."
}

{
  "id": "line:0495b51",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: A demon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:050dbb0",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Would that be similar to a [i]legally binding[/i] contract?"
}

{
  "id": "line:032ae91",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: It's said that violating its terms will result in instant death for the offender...[p/] No matter who they are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4b3e8",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: So I guess there's [i]some[/i] protection..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6e321",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Well...[p/] As an attorney,[p/] I'm sure you understand that it's possible to exploit and use loopholes in [i]any[/i] contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aac75d",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: And according to the legends,[p/] demons take great pride in their ability to deceive and corrupt people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adb85a",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: ...Although,[p/] I'm sure you know that already, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4297a",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Wait,[p/] what did he mean by that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b407b5",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: The Theft"
}

{
  "id": "line:017405e",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: According to the prosecution,[p/] the theft took place during the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0578cb1",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Shouldn't there have been plenty of witnesses in the gallery at that time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0088067",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: That's the strangest thing...[p/] Supposedly,[p/] the gallery room was completely empty when it happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da7b15",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?[p/] That can't be right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a0b43",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: And honestly,[p/] I have no idea how [i]anyone[/i] could produce enough magic to [i]shatter[/i] the display case anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8af77",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: Were the wards protecting the case [i]that[/i] powerful?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e987b",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: They [i]were[/i] powerful,[p/] but that's not the issue here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eaac46",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: It would be one thing to dispel the wards and remove the glass protecting it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d11506",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: But it's another thing to [i]shatter[/i] the glass while the wards were active."
}

{
  "id": "line:027c040",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Doing something like that would require an extremely powerful spell.[p/] Far more powerful than simply dispelling it."
}

{
  "id": "line:033d2b2",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: But something about the readings on the lock console were strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:095cf1f",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: It's as if the protective magic had been completely nullified,[p/] but that shouldn't have been possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:044b5cf",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: The locks are designed to be immune to [b]Anti-Magic Fields[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e661c6",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: The only thing that could bypass it was the Sword of Spell Eating itself,[p/] and it only works when being held by someone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0341673",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But if they had access to the Sword already,[p/] they wouldn't have needed to break the display case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d04279",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think it's more likely that someone used an extremely powerful spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fd8c7",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Probably..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0434d76",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: But the Sword of Spell Eating wasn't the only item that was stolen, either."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d24a89",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "What?[p/] Was another artifact stolen that night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e3562",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Other Stolen Items"
}

{
  "id": "line:0251d22",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You mentioned that [i]another[/i] item was stolen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf1f32",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Yes.[p/] It's extremely concerning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee8334",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "What was going on here?[p/] The two thefts were completely different from one another."
}

{
  "id": "line:0437669",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: The Thief"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dba0c8",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You mentioned that someone would have needed a powerful spell to shatter the display case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0386ee8",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wouldn't that narrow down the list of suspects for the theft?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dac2b2",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not everyone attending the Ball could cast spells that powerful."
}

{
  "id": "line:007316e",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Well, according to the Inquisition,[p/] Beatrice Frega's magic was powerful enough to have done this."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e337e",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Discounting the fact that she's completely blind."
}

{
  "id": "line:04157a9",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Yes.[p/] I'm well aware of that,[p/] and it doesn't sit quite right with me either."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ccace",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was there anyone else at the Lords' Ball capable of matching Beatrice's power?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0801c45",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Only the heads of the Four Pillars could have invoked magic this powerful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdac6a",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: But apparently,[p/] Beatrice is an exception to that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05eaf0b",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Was Beatrice really that powerful?[p/] Or was she being framed by one of the House leaders?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a60b7",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: But the cases [i]can[/i] be opened normally, can't they?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0425ddc",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Ah, yes.[p/] The magical locks on the case [i]can[/i] be disabled. [h=\"\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d32ce",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "I detected some fear.[p/] Was he hiding something?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4716f",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "So Harold [i]could[/i] have \"stolen\" the Sword that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0270a59",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Could he have staged the robbery to cover his tracks?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06779e6",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Defunding the Hall of History"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db6dd0",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Harold...[p/] A witness told us that you got into an argument with William Frega on the night of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:095f417",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was William Frega planning on defunding the Haroldson Hall of History?"
}

{
  "id": "line:048212b",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Yes,[p/] he was,[p/] but that doesn't mean that I had anything to do with his murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:08add61",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did your argument that night turn hostile?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03df706",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: I'll admit that our discussion turned heated,[p/] but it never escalated to threats or violence. [h=\"With how insulting he was,|it should have...\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a4c41",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: William was being unreasonable,[p/] and I was frustrated.[p/] But that's all there was to it. [h=\"He deserved|what happened to him...\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0be56a4",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Did you have any conflicts with him prior to that night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:073d89e",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: We [i]have[/i] had disagreements in the past."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bd753",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: He was receiving pressure from the Crown about what I was displaying in my museum."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a032b8",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: The King believed that some of my exhibits were too \"controversial\" for the public eye."
}

{
  "id": "line:0393d0b",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: I'm sure you've noticed the rising tensions between the commonfolk and the nobility as of late."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f05c48",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: I've never been one to shy away from the bloodier parts of Wyverngarde's history."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba2e57",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: The citizens [i]must[/i] know about these parts of history.[p/] Otherwise,[p/] we're liable to repeat them."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c46e7",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: ...We're already seeing that happen with Grand General Steelwind and these insurrections in the countryside. [h=\"Nothing but brutish simpletons,|the lot of them...\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b9f14",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "It was clear that Harold was passionate about his work."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ce504",
  "node": "Talk_Gallery1",
  "text": "Would that passion have driven him far enough to commit murder, though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d682a7",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Ah, what is this—[p/]a rare artifact?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0522e44",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's an Attorney's Runestone.[p/] It proves that I'm a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:06088f8",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Bah,[p/] all of my colleagues have similar devices."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c66e17",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: They're so enamoured with all these newfangled functions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4be7b",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Well, you won't catch [i]me[/i] chasing passing fads like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a5173",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice's Inheritance 0|Beatrice's Inheritance 1|Beatrice's Inheritance|Beatrice's Blindness"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d5692",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: It's truly a shame how that young woman's life turned out."
}

{
  "id": "line:031a1e0",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: William was always cold and calculating...[p/] But to treat his own [i]daughter[/i] like that...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f8ebe",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: I can't begin to imagine the hardship that she must have gone through."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aec178",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Autopsy Report: William Frega|William Frega"
}

{
  "id": "line:0742909",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: I've had my disagreements with William.[p/] But it's regretful that [i]this[/i] is how his story ended."
}

{
  "id": "line:056081e",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "He seems sincere when he says that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcf82a",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "But you should still be wary.[p/] You never know who you can truly trust."
}

{
  "id": "line:0680898",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: So...[p/] [i]Harold Haroldson[/i] is your real name?"
}

{
  "id": "line:045acb0",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Of course.[p/] My name has been passed down for generations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a98455",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "So, this wasn't a one-time occurrence."
}

{
  "id": "line:092a186",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is this a cultural thing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c540c",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: I know I haven't been back in Wyverngarde for a while.[p/] But I don't remember redundant names like this being normal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0403c77",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] It's [i]definitely[/i] unique to him..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f70b67",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Sword of Spell Eating|Sword of Spell Eating 2|Sword of Spell Eating 3|Armbands of Intellect|Haroldson's Security"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae742a",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: These thefts are extremely concerning."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c43a6",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: I had these exhibits abjured with the strongest spells gold could buy.[p/] But perhaps it wasn't enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1d516",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: ...But to think that one of my artifacts would be used for [i]murder[/i] of all things."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be7c52",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Earrings of Vitality"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d4e35",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: ...If there's any silver lining to this,[p/] it's that the Earrings of Vitality were left untouched."
}

{
  "id": "line:00920d0",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: I was almost worried that I wouldn't be able to use them anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cd685",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: That was a joke...[p/] Right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a45e9c",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Player: Armbands of Intellect 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffdef9",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's clear why the Sword of Spell Eating was stolen.[p/] But I'm still not sure how the Armbands of Intellect fit into everything..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba764b",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: ...While unlikely,[p/] it's possible that the thefts are coincidental."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1b319",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "But there's no way that can be true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a26273",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "...Although,[p/] it [i]might[/i] explain why the thefts were so different from each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:0893f8c",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Mr. Haroldson?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c87c7b",
  "node": "Present_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Sorry.[p/] I'm not really sure what to make of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:09362b0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "We returned to the gallery and saw a legion of knights inspecting the crime scene of the theft."
}

{
  "id": "line:0008bee",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "I didn't see Mr. Haroldson anywhere.[p/] The Inquisition must've still been questioning him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0a073",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: ... [h=\"This is a|complete mess...\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:018aa61",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "As we entered the gallery,[p/] we spotted Lord Haroldson.[p/] He was inspecting the shattered remnants of the display case."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ec7e6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: Oh, Mr. Cuthbert. [h=\"He's working for the Crown Prince.|Can he be trusted?\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c51726",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "...It seemed that word had spread about my deal with Aster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7ae49",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: I'm glad you seem to be doing better."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a2a9a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b01a56",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a long story...[p/] I'll tell you later."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b233bd",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Not that I could explain exactly what had happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:08853b0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways, Mr. Haroldson,[p/] could we—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:062c292",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right...[p/] Harold.[p/] I'm sure you already know that I'm investigating the murder of William Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:078fd8d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The prosecution suspects that someone used the Sword of Spell Eating to break into the Duke's room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b090f7",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was wondering if I could ask you some questions about the theft last night."
}

{
  "id": "line:011d284",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Harold: I'll tell you what I can.[p/] But I'm not sure how much help I'll be."
}

{
  "id": "line:06775b6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "Tyrion: So many people had a motive to murder William Frega...[p/] But who actually did it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0280e7c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Gallery1",
  "text": "I took some time to review everything that I'd already learned."
}

{
  "id": "line:045ea9e",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: Motives aside,[p/] let's go over the events that happened that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0beb3e1",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: It all started when the Sword of Spell Eating was stolen."
}

{
  "id": "line:007f1c5",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: We don't have a specific suspect,[p/] but we do know something about them."
}

{
  "id": "line:000800d",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce2",
  "text": "No...[p/] I still didn't know who stole the sword that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d4344",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce2",
  "text": "But I [i]did[/i] know some traits about them due to what we found in the gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3a5ab",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: The thief has powerful magic.[p/] Magic strong enough to bypass the abjurative wards entirely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0346eef",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce3",
  "text": "Celeste: But what about Harold?[p/] He could have just unlocked it using his password."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6120f",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: He could have stolen the Sword and staged a robbery,[p/] but he couldn't have shattered the glass."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dec90c",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Only a powerful mage could have done that.[p/] And I doubt Harold would lie about that when we could easily confirm it with Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0104190",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce3",
  "text": "Celeste: Right.[p/] But then what happened next?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e107da",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: They brazenly stole the Sword of Spell Eating.[p/] This caused Harold to report the theft to the Kingsguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff3ed6",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce4",
  "text": "Aria: After Lord Haroldson reported what had happened,[p/] the Inquisition discreetly placed the manor on lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bc81e",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce4",
  "text": "Aria: They searched every room in the manor to try to find it."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f9c03",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce4",
  "text": "Aria: But it was eventually found in Beatrice's bedroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de6106",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And that led them to believe that [i]she[/i] had stolen it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fac44",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce4",
  "text": "Aria: That's correct.[p/] The Kingsguard moved to arrest her,[p/] but Prince Aster ordered them to step down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0472c7f",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: And then there's Laefe's statement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea26cc",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce5",
  "text": "Laefe: My father was extremely upset.[p/] I think Beatrice may have offended him during their meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:056ed12",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce5",
  "text": "Laefe: He told me to leave him alone and let the Kingsguard investigate the Sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d1c67",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Laefe's account gives us a clear fact about [i]when[/i] William died."
}

{
  "id": "line:0908fee",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce6",
  "text": "No...[p/] Laefe spoke with the Duke before he went into his study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0611385",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce6",
  "text": "And unlike the Nightgrave case,[p/] the time of death was [i]after[/i] this encounter."
}

{
  "id": "line:068e8c2",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce6",
  "text": "It's unlikely that Laefe saw someone else disguised as her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:04354ed",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce6",
  "text": "It [i]had[/i] to have been him."
}

{
  "id": "line:076b73e",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: William Frega was murdered [i]after[/i] the lockdown was activated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c08ab5",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "Celeste: This means that whoever killed him bypassed the lockdown and broke into the magically locked room."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bf26a",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "Celeste: They [i]had[/i] to have used the Sword, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f5b4c",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] Most magical locks are immune to [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b], otherwise the lockdown would've just disabled the locks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d02066",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Sword of Spell Eating must function differently if it produced that effect."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b671c",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "Celeste: That's still not concrete evidence, though..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f1821",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "Celeste: And we haven't even spoken to all of the suspects yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0cbf9",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "Right...[p/] I never got a chance to speak with Lucio Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0153859",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "But given his status,[p/] I wondered if that would even be possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:09684ee",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Either way,[p/] it's a good start.[p/] And it's not as if we're defending this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bab67",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: The trial is getting close anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc21ae",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "I didn't doubt Ms. Tymora's abilities,[p/] but I could still compare notes with her before the trial began."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a98aa3",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "It was a little strange that I hadn't seen her since the investigation started."
}

{
  "id": "line:0644015",
  "node": "Inves1Deduce7",
  "text": "Maybe she was meeting with Beatrice at the dungeons."
}

{
  "id": "line:079beb7",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a crimson-red short sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:034c8d9",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: That's the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a23680",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Legends say that it has the power to nullify [i]any[/i] kind of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:08914b0",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: So it's like an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f86238",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: In a way,[p/] but it has less-than-heroic origins."
}

{
  "id": "line:0febe1e",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: It's said that this sword was created through a blood pact between a mage and a demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d48d14",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: A demon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093a00d",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Demons are terrible and powerful creatures.[p/] They exist solely to sow chaos and oppose the gods."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a3c67",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: They supposedly took great pride in their ability to deceive and corrupt people."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a438f",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Legends say that most demons had the power to absorb and nullify magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bfd37",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Many have theorized that a demon imbued some of that power into this sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d664e",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is it safe to put something like this on display?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2935d",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Don't worry.[p/] These displays are fortified with several [b]abjuration[/b] spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2d26e",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: I'd bet even Lord Steelwind would have trouble getting into this."
}

{
  "id": "line:02315bc",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a pair of golden earrings.[p/] There are small jewels embedded in each of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d35b6a",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: I call them the Earrings of Vitality."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d294c",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: They're an artifact I found in the ruins of a large Luminite temple."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b741e",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Whoever wears these would have their lifespan increased tenfold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0998a52",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure it's just a legend, though.[p/] Did you read that from some ancient texts?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0207d24",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: ...Not exactly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b34c6b",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I didn't even know that there were Luminite temples in Wyverngarde?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc6cd1",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Almost all of them have been completely demolished by the Kingdom over the years."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f7b9c",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: A lot of Wyverngarde's territory once belonged to the Theocracy,[p/] the Kingdom would rather have everyone forget that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f09423",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a pair of metallic armbands.[p/] There are several magical runes carved onto them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0766086",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Those are the Armbands of Intellect."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4ee73",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: They were actually created by a member of House Frega many centuries ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddccc9",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Centuries\"?[p/] That would mean these Armbands predate the invention of artificery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0418877",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: That's correct.[p/] Legends say that whoever wore these armbands would be granted unparalleled levels of intellect."
}

{
  "id": "line:09acb64",
  "node": "Examine_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Many believed that House Frega created these to help them unlock the secrets of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ef861",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Player: Harold Haroldson"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e1684",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: So what's a historian doing at the Lords' Ball, Lord Haroldson?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0613d93",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh—[p/] Uh—[p/] Okay...[p/] Mr. Harold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6724c",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: [i]Harold[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0385c07",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "He was being really stubborn about this.[p/] It'd be best to just go with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:002bae4",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: My apologies,[p/] Harold."
}

{
  "id": "line:007ce15",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: It's the Haroldson Hall of History,[p/] located in the city of Homherith."
}

{
  "id": "line:0885d98",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Unfortunately,[p/] I don't think his guests appreciate the historical significance of these items."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff9ea1",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Honestly,[p/] I think [i]you're[/i] the only person in years who's taken a meaningful interest in them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5d343",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Player: Small Monkey"
}

{
  "id": "line:048b3f0",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sorry,[p/] but I really have to ask...[p/] Is that a monkey riding on your back?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f782b",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "I looked at the animal,[p/] but he quickly avoided eye contact with me and hid behind Harold's shoulder."
}

{
  "id": "line:094fa86",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Eugene helps me with my day-to-day."
}

{
  "id": "line:034bc4f",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: These old bones aren't as spry as they used to be, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb5c95",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Player: The Celestial Gods"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ca2c3",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Harold,[p/] what do you know about the celestial gods?"
}

{
  "id": "line:056dd4f",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I haven't been able to find anything about them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f76029",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: That makes sense.[p/] They're primarily worshipped by the people of the Theocracy of Lumina."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3927c",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "That might explain why worship of them was outlawed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f19667",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Lumina was the kingdom west of us,[p/] but I knew very little about them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a75515",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "All I knew was that we fought them during the first war of Wyverngarde,[p/] and then later during the Great Luminite War."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb586d",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "They'd been Wyverngarde's longstanding enemy for a while.[p/] Simply asking about them could raise suspicions of treason."
}

{
  "id": "line:024f91b",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: There are nine celestial gods,[p/] each representing a divine domain in heaven."
}

{
  "id": "line:0540f5e",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Deus,[p/] Odin,[p/] Machina,[p/] Horus—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05866fa",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry...[p/][s/] One of them is named \"[i]Horus[/i]\"?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04109e8",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Yes,[p/] Horus the Lightbringer.[p/] He's the God of Radiance and ruler of the Sixth Domain in heaven."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a5d98",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "I thought I just made that name up when I was younger.[p/][s/] Horus was [i]real[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0993879",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: ...Is something wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bd302",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] I was just thinking about what you said..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ce1ac",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Player: Horus the Lightbringer"
}

{
  "id": "line:000e71c",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Could you tell me more about Horus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba241b",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: As I said,[p/] he's the God of Radiance.[p/] The sun and the concept of light lie within his domain."
}

{
  "id": "line:00147ba",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: He's also said to embody the virtues of truth,[p/] justice,[p/] and life itself.[p/] He is the enemy of lies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3fd40",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "It was a little unnerving how much of a chord that struck with me.[p/] It also reminded me of something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb9e89",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Did that mean that naught could remain concealed from him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1e40e",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Some legends claim so."
}

{
  "id": "line:068b874",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: I'll be honest.[p/] I only have so many texts available to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc3936",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: My knowledge of Lumina is limited to their myths,[p/] and my requests to travel to Lumina have been denied for decades."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a28b87",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: But there are many stories of his followers being blessed with the ability to see through lies and deception."
}

{
  "id": "line:0771764",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Almost as if they had his eyes..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0790213",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "But that didn't make any sense.[p/] I didn't worship Horus.[p/] I didn't even know who he was until tonight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c59f90",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Why would he give me this ability?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c375e",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "No.[p/] I needed to think of this more rationally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0155316",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "The mages of Wyverngarde supposedly descended from people blessed by the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:032e123",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Using that logic,[p/] could I have descended from people who were blessed by Horus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0feea04",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are any of his followers established in Wyverngarde?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03eb2e2",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Heavens, no.[p/] The Luminites are viewed as enemies of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acf367",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: ...I'd imagine any known followers would've had unfortunate accidents befall them."
}

{
  "id": "line:012559e",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "That might explain why my mother never talked about him with me,[p/] but I'd really wished she'd left me [i]something[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b73934",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: ...You're being awfully inquisitive about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3559a",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Why are you so interested in Horus and his followers?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06dab17",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's purely academic curiosity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4dbe4",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09106f2",
  "node": "Talk_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "He clearly wasn't convinced,[p/] but he didn't push the matter further."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b42359",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: So what is a historian doing at the Lords' Ball, Mr. Haroldson?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd0d91",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Um...[p/] right,[p/] Harold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9d0ac",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Anyways,[p/] the Duke invites my museum to set up some displays here every year. [h=\"He must think it adds|a semblance of culture, the fool.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0fd45",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: You own a museum?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0491dc5",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Yes.[p/] It's the Haroldson Hall of History, located in Homherith."
}

{
  "id": "line:0597887",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "...That's a mouthful."
}

{
  "id": "line:09aa419",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Honestly,[p/] I think [i]you're[/i] the only person in years who's taken an interest in their histories."
}

{
  "id": "line:054d4a1",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Player: Sword of Spell Eating|Earrings of Vitality|Armbands of Intellect"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c7b17",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did you obtain such powerful items anyway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0789454",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'd have thought that the kingdom would still have a use for these."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1b584",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Unfortunately,[p/] the members of the kingdom's upper class only care about political power."
}

{
  "id": "line:0183a44",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: These items are tools of a bygone era."
}

{
  "id": "line:088c1bc",
  "node": "Present_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: I'm afraid many nobles don't see the value in them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0597d63",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "I continued exploring the manor and found myself in a room with several displays."
}

{
  "id": "line:075a877",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "It looked like a gallery of some kind,[p/] but it was slightly out of place here."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d9181",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "There were a few nobles in the room,[p/] and they were all silently appreciating the exhibits."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c7904",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "William Frega must have paid a museum to display some historical exhibits for the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c6bd6",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: There's a face I haven't seen before..."
}

{
  "id": "line:022f64e",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "He wore the vestments of an archaeologist,[p/] carrying two large satchels crammed with tools,[p/] maps,[p/] and other instruments."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d43c12",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "His hair was white and his skin was wrinkled,[p/] but he walked with the youth and spirit of someone who had a much longer life ahead of him."
}

{
  "id": "line:090c262",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Although,[p/] all of these features were far less notable than the monkey hanging off of his back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4f9be",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "The small orangutan tilted his head as he looked at me curiously."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c4298",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "When I looked directly at him,[p/] he hid himself behind the old man's shoulder,[p/] peeking at me from behind it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3f6cf",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: I'm Harold Haroldson.[p/] I'm the curator of this collection."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ba1ba",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is that name a pseudonym or something?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9869c",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: No."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1fa67",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:01efacf",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Wait...[p/] As the curator of this museum,[p/] he must have known a lot of myths and history."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b550b",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "I wondered..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0484584",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How much do you know about the myths and cultures of nations other than Wyverngarde?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0491076",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "His eyes narrowed.[p/] Even his monkey eyed me suspiciously."
}

{
  "id": "line:01decbf",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: ...I know you.[p/] Your name is Cuthbert, isn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5951c",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/][s/]Ah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0537ae0",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "It was never a [i]good[/i] sign whenever someone recognized me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e6b50",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: You're not exactly a friend of the nobility.[p/] I have to ask why you're here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c951b",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm accompanying my mentor.[p/] She has business with someone here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f12fff",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "He eyed me warily,[p/] but his stare didn't carry the usual disdain I received from other nobles."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c478f",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I swear on the Scaled Lord.[p/] I'm telling the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af516d",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: The Scaled Lord is not someone whose name you should invoke so lightly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff2832",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: ...But it sounds like you're telling the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0885fee",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: I just can't help but wonder why you're interested in the other nations, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:075026e",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "I needed to tread carefully.[p/] He seemed nice,[p/] but he was still a noble."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a70c7",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "The kingdom scoured any available knowledge on the other nations.[p/] It was difficult to find anything on the celestial gods."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c74d4",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "...But I didn't get many opportunities like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fcaf4",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm trying to learn more about the celestial gods."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c33664",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: ...That's not something I'd make a habit of telling people,[p/] especially someone in your position."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca27c5",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know,[p/] but it's been impossible to find any information about them."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e7ae2",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I really need to find out more.[p/] Can you help me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:080948d",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I can't exactly say no to such a curious mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd64d6",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: I'll help you the best I can,[p/] but don't let anyone know about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be06f7",
  "node": "Check_Events_GalleryIntro",
  "text": "Harold: Sharing this information is technically outlawed by the kingdom. [h=\"...This boy could put|all of us in danger.\" e=\"fa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:074e1b3",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "My attention was drawn to the Earrings of Vitality."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8b624",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "They were supposedly an artifact from the ancient days of the Theocracy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fef08f",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "Tyrion: Harold,[p/] would it be okay if I took a closer look at these earrings?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e6181",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "Harold: ... [h=\"How presumptious...\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:070ddd2",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I promise I'll be careful with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:050d95d",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "Harold: ...I suppose I can make an exception this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af0db7",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "Lord Haroldson walked up to the display case and whispered something into the runic console attached to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fbb1c",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "I heard several magical locks disengage before he opened the display case and carefully pulled out the artifact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f93f75",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "I laid my hands out so he could delicately place them in my hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d6cb1",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "I carefully inspected the earrings.[p/] Each of them had a golden frame with a red luminous stone embedded at its center."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f676c3",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "They gleamed brightly under the artificial lights of the gallery,[p/] almost abnormally so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc755f",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] There's something engraved in these earrings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0361599",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "I could barely make out the text engraved on the golden frame.[p/] It was nearly microscopic."
}

{
  "id": "line:098ca31",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"I lie at the beginning of illumination.[p/] I lie within eternity,[p/] and I cannot be found in shadows.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb1213",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"What am I?\""
}

{
  "id": "line:059135c",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd",
  "text": "Harold: ...A riddle?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b4904",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd2",
  "text": "00"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d02446",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd2",
  "text": "Fail"
}

{
  "id": "line:073a4e0",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd2",
  "text": ":No...[p/] The riddle was as such:"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d513e0",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd2",
  "text": "\"I lie at the beginning of illumination.[p/] I lie within eternity,[p/] and I cannot be found in shadows.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0086274",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd2",
  "text": "There's always a trick to riddles like this.[p/] It wasn't speaking literally."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ff750",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's the letter \"i\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:081d1d0",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Illumination\" starts with \"i\",[p/] \"eternity\" contains \"i\",[p/] and there's no \"i\" in \"shadows\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:06781fa",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "The Earrings suddenly lit up,[p/] blinding light washing over the gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bd6c5",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "I felt the ground disappear from under me.[p/] It felt like I was floating in water."
}

{
  "id": "line:0065038",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "I should have been shocked and surprised,[p/] but this sensation somehow felt familiar and nostalgic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7d2a2",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Horus: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e07fed",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Horus: You've strayed very far from home,[p/] young one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8043a",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "A voice rang out from all around me.[p/] It felt like bells ringing and reverberating inside my head."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7b0f7",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Horus: You're not much of a warrior,[p/] but maybe a warrior isn't what's needed to dispel the encroaching shadows."
}

{
  "id": "line:08baba0",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Horus: ...That light within you,[p/] why is it so reminiscent of my fallen friend?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05fe5c7",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What are you talking about?[p/] Who are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:080b369",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Horus: I suppose it doesn't matter from which spark that flame came."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ac4bc",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Horus: It burns bright within you like that of a burning star."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f7ac0",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Horus: Go forth and walk the Path of Radiance, my heavensborn."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e3399",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Harold: ...Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00da326",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...W-[p/][s/]What?[p/] What just happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a056a2",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd3",
  "text": "All I did was blink.[p/] I suddenly found myself back in the gallery,[p/] as if awoken from a dream."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad39d8",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Harold: You were just standing there, staring at nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f9651",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Didn't you see that blinding light?[p/] There was that loud voice, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:005e8bd",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Harold: I didn't see anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:00af33c",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Harold: ...May I see those earrings?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e8baa",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right, of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:05841b0",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Harold: I don't see the engraving you were talking about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9b55b",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know it's small,[p/] but it's right—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a6c32",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "As I took another look at the earrings,[p/] I realized that the riddle had disappeared."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf15b1",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "The golden frame was smooth and unblemished.[p/] It was as if the text had never been there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b44048",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was I just seeing things?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0254b88",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Harold: I doubt you hallucinated such a specific riddle."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed4090",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Harold: ...Am I being pranked?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a6216",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Harold: Did someone from the historical society put you up to this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09fcdd2",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] It was—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c053af",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "...What was going on?[p/] Did that riddle have something to do with the Eye of Horus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bef93f",
  "node": "HaroldIntroEnd4",
  "text": "I hoped Celeste's investigation was going better than mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c8fb0",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Player: Vent"
}

{
  "id": "line:0095bd7",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's an air vent over here.[p/] It looks like it goes from the ceiling to the ground floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0450297",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is this where that \"rat\" escaped to, Tracker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8bd7f",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tracker: That's where the jumping rat went."
}

{
  "id": "line:067e87a",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I thought you said it was a \"flying rat\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:018bf88",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker see that too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d56877",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "...It would probably be better to just move on."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ec5cc",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] where did this rat come from?"
}

{
  "id": "line:050c9bf",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tracker: Rat come out the other wall."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c44d5c",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you mean the vent on the opposite side?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5622f",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tracker: Yes.[p/] Tracker saw flying rat escape that way."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e0575",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] What was this \"rat\" doing here in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b9753",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Player: Crystal"
}

{
  "id": "line:04adfc2",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: These crystals supposedly generated an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b] during the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a16d61",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: However,[p/] the Sword of Spell Eating would make its wielder immune to these fields."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baf262",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Player: Detect Vent"
}

{
  "id": "line:0040e8f",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you see?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf2b23",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm seeing small traces of [b]illusion[/b] magic inside them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd6f37",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Celeste: They're in the shape of droplets,[p/] and some of them are shaped like footprints."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c16ba5",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Footprints?[p/][s/] What kind of footprints?"
}

{
  "id": "line:053d669",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...They look like they came from some kind of animal.[p/] It's hard to tell what kind, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f4049",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Celeste: I also see some small handprints, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:022216a",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbe406",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...The traces also go [i]deep[/i] inside these vents."
}

{
  "id": "line:008bcf0",
  "node": "Examine_Hallway2",
  "text": "Celeste: It's the same for the vents on the other side too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3c3f2",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Player: Eris"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2656f",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What are you doing here, Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e6b0f",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: I should be asking [i]you[/i] the same thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:01583b1",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: I recall you telling me that you were a [i]defense[/i] attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0e596",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: Yet here you are,[p/] prosecuting a defendant.[p/] You're even leading the Inquisition that you supposedly hated so much."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a08180",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: But to answer your question,[p/] I'm here on behalf of Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:081a3e9",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Laefe: My sister?"
}

{
  "id": "line:004474f",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: Yes.[p/] Tymora is occupied handling other aspects of the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b540b",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: So she sent me here to investigate on her behalf."
}

{
  "id": "line:0047c58",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?[p/] I'm surprised she trusted you to handle something so important."
}

{
  "id": "line:007add6",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: How do you two even know each other?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed2934",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You said she was acquainted with your father,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0358ac5",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: Ah.[p/] [i]We[/i] met during her days at the Imperial Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fc5de",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: We both studied [b]illusion[/b] magic together."
}

{
  "id": "line:093f453",
  "node": "Talk_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: I've always been a patron of hers.[p/] One in my position would be saddened to see her in this dreadful situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0337e5e",
  "node": "Present_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: Ah, of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a87c3",
  "node": "Present_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: I see that old habits die hard."
}

{
  "id": "line:012d2e6",
  "node": "Present_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry,[p/] am I being obnoxious with this thing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a5925",
  "node": "Present_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: Not at all.[p/] I'd be more disappointed if you didn't try to show me the badge."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca5621",
  "node": "Present_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's a Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0465387",
  "node": "Present_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd8d9a",
  "node": "Present_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this, Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:038b947",
  "node": "Present_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: Hm...[p/] No."
}

{
  "id": "line:022e12d",
  "node": "Present_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: I don't seem to have any dialogue for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccd978",
  "node": "Present_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I...[p/] see."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f2b89",
  "node": "Present_Hallway2",
  "text": "[i]That[/i] was a strange way to say that she doesn't know anything about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01da720",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "I allowed Tracker to lead me to the location where he found the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1a485",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Surprisingly,[p/] it was fairly close to Beatrice's Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c605c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "He apparently didn't travel very far before he met those \"rats\" he mentioned."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aec9ab",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "As we continued towards our destination,[p/] Tracker suddenly became extremely tense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d47c98",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Tracker?[p/] What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0439469",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tracker: Enemy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb15d3",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "He was growling toward the end of the hallway.[p/] Aster was there.[p/] So was Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c93bd9",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "How did she even get access to Frega Manor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d2612",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: Oh?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f9e57",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Before we even had a chance to react,[p/] Tracker jumped between Eris and me.[p/] He began barking at her angrily."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e6e15",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: Oh, dear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc60b8",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Laefe: Tracker?![p/][s/] Stop that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e201ee",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Laefe tried to calm Tracker down,[p/] but he was undeterred."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7e472",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "He continued to bark at Eris,[p/] and it looked like it was taking all of Laefe's strength to hold him back."
}

{
  "id": "line:071a5c6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aster,[p/][s/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:076a4c1",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Aster: M-[p/][s/]My apologies, Mr. Cuthbert![p/] I am deathly afraid of dogs..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b4bf6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Aster: I understand why you're—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0edce3e",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Tracker: [i]*bark*[p/][s/] *bark*[p/][s/] *bark*[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf7d49",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Aster: I-[p/][s/]I have to go..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d53e92",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Before I could get a word in,[p/] Aster quickly excused himself and ran down the hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:06090a4",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Laefe: I-[p/][s/]I'm terribly sorry![p/][s/] He's not usually like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0f10b",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "Eris: Ah, it's to be expected."
}

{
  "id": "line:0380c49",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "ERIS: I'm not sure why,[p/] but animals have always been able to see me for what I am."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d414ed",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "ERIS: I'm not sure why,[p/] but animals have always disliked me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01042e7",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "What [i]was[/i] Eris doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0078c94",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "She said that her father was friends with Beatrice,[p/] but was she involved in this case somehow?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2f3e5",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "...I guess it didn't matter.[p/] I didn't come here to talk to anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:048eaa1",
  "node": "Check_Events_Hallway2",
  "text": "I needed to EXAMINE this hallway and search for clues."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a2bc1",
  "node": "VentSeen",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why would there be traces of [b]illusion[/b] magic [i]inside[/i] the vents..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03872dd",
  "node": "VentSeen",
  "text": "Tyrion: What spell could have possibly left those traces?"
}

{
  "id": "line:037a2e0",
  "node": "VentSeen",
  "text": "Eris: As I told you many months ago,[p/] [b]illusion[/b] spells tend to do one of two things."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8824d",
  "node": "VentSeen",
  "text": "Eris: They either create free-standing illusions,[p/] or they can disguise an existing creature."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf8214",
  "node": "VentSeen",
  "text": "Tyrion: Spells only leave traces on the objects they are cast on.[p/] A free-standing illusion wouldn't have left traces like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:053e640",
  "node": "VentSeen",
  "text": "Tyrion: A disguised creature must have been [i]inside[/i] these vents at some point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c36581",
  "node": "VentSeen",
  "text": "Tyrion: These small red droplets have to be blood—[p/]most likely from a creature affected by an illusion."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ad2f8",
  "node": "VentSeen",
  "text": "Celeste: But these vents are tiny.[p/] [i]No one[/i] would be able to fit inside them."
}

{
  "id": "line:038688b",
  "node": "VentSeen2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But a [i]rat[/i] would be able to fit in these vents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d14bea",
  "node": "VentSeen2",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, yeah.[p/] I guess that'd be true."
}

{
  "id": "line:075acd3",
  "node": "VentSeen2",
  "text": "Celeste: But that would mean a rat had an [b]illusion[/b] spell active on it at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:00abace",
  "node": "VentSeen2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's not only that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abe80c",
  "node": "VentSeen2",
  "text": "He said that the \"queen finally answered\" him,[p/] and this happened after he picked up a \"stick\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:049f2ce",
  "node": "VentSeen2",
  "text": "But that contradicted something else that we knew was active at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:08be7d4",
  "node": "VentSeen2a",
  "text": "No...[p/] I don't know exactly when he found that \"stick\",[p/] but it's very likely that it happened during the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c21486",
  "node": "VentSeen2a",
  "text": "Laefe's ability to communicate with Tracker was facilitated by [b]Familial Bond[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ecf97",
  "node": "VentSeen2a",
  "text": "But would she have been able to do that during this time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03512ee",
  "node": "VentSeen2b",
  "text": "But that shouldn't have been possible because of the [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d5c2f",
  "node": "VentSeen2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tracker saw this \"rat\" [i]during[/i] the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:089ecf6",
  "node": "VentSeen2b",
  "text": "Celeste: ...They would have been inside the [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b] created by the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd167c",
  "node": "VentSeen2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: There can only be one way that \"rat\" could have an [b]illusion[/b] spell active on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:000b379",
  "node": "VentSeen2b",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/][s/] You can't mean—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df9981",
  "node": "VentSeen2c",
  "text": "No...[p/] If this all took place during the lockdown,[p/] there would've been [b]Anti-Magic Fields[b/] active at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c439b1",
  "node": "VentSeen2c",
  "text": "There's only one way this \"rat\" could have been invisible during this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c07d4",
  "node": "VentSeen3",
  "text": "Tyrion: That \"rat\" was holding the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:05821ed",
  "node": "VentSeen3",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/][s/] That can't be right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0805137",
  "node": "VentSeen3",
  "text": "Celeste: A rat wouldn't have the strength or hands to carry a sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae4044",
  "node": "VentSeen4",
  "text": "Celeste: No...[p/][s/] Are you serious?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04bd1c8",
  "node": "VentSeen4",
  "text": "Tyrion: We know that Harold had a motive to kill William Frega.[p/] He was planning to defund the Haroldson Hall of History."
}

{
  "id": "line:096214e",
  "node": "VentSeen4",
  "text": "Tyrion: They had an argument that night,[p/] and [i]that's[/i] when William Frega decided that he was going to defund Harold's museums."
}

{
  "id": "line:08df7ab",
  "node": "VentSeen4",
  "text": "Tyrion: He must have struck a deal with Beatrice,[p/] and with Beatrice's portion of House Frega,[p/] she could have easily kept his museums funded."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6aaf5",
  "node": "VentSeen4",
  "text": "Tyrion: He could've faked the robbery and sent his familiar to murder William."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f44b9",
  "node": "VentSeen4",
  "text": "Tyrion: And there's something else that Tracker said."
}

{
  "id": "line:0853d5b",
  "node": "VentSeen4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tracker.[p/] You said you had to [i]smell[/i] to \"see\" where the rat was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0170c11",
  "node": "VentSeen4",
  "text": "Tracker: Yep.[p/] Tracker couldn't see the rat with his eyes.[p/] So Tracker used his nose to see it."
}

{
  "id": "line:086d61b",
  "node": "VentSeen4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...The monkey was invisible!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b5c29",
  "node": "VentSeen5",
  "text": "Tyrion: No one would have noticed a small invisible animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0035fee",
  "node": "VentSeen5",
  "text": "Tyrion: In addition to that,[p/] he could move through the air vents..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a46b0",
  "node": "VentSeen5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eugene would've been nearly undetectable that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e9557",
  "node": "VentSeen5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Beatrice is a master of [b]illusion[/b] magic.[p/] It's possible that she cast [b]invisibility[/b] on Eugene."
}

{
  "id": "line:05332c6",
  "node": "VentSeen5",
  "text": "Tyrion: And then there's the position of this air vent."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f116e",
  "node": "VentSeen5",
  "text": "Tyrion: We're currently in the hallway just north of Beatrice's room."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c8936",
  "node": "VentSeen5",
  "text": "Tyrion: And this air vent connects to the ground floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0059126",
  "node": "VentSeen5",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we align the two floor maps together,[p/] this vent must lead to the storage room."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b9ce2",
  "node": "VentSeen5",
  "text": "Celeste: Right.[p/] The air vent there curved upwards.[p/] This must be where it leads."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cca7f",
  "node": "VentSeen5",
  "text": "Tyrion: And according to Jan,[p/] that air vent led directly to William's Study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0469d",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "Tyrion: It would have been the perfect route to enter William's Study and leave undetected."
}

{
  "id": "line:050fab2",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "Celeste: But he wouldn't have needed to nullify the lock to enter that room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2b281",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "Celeste: Why would he need to use the Sword of Spell Eating at all?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e38f55",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because of [b]Familial Bond[/b],[p/] they can telepathically communicate with each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c51cd6",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Harold probably needed Eugene to hold the Sword so he could tell him exactly where to go."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f61463",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Sword's magic affects anyone magically connected to the wielder.[p/] And [b]Familial Bond[/b] connects them magically."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc20e6",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "Tyrion: It makes sense now...[p/] Harold could have easily faked the robbery to take suspicion off of him."
}

{
  "id": "line:08701d3",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's even possible that he was lying about how the display glass was shattered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dda78f",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "Laefe: But I've known Lord Haroldson for many years,[p/] I just can't believe that he'd be involved in this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07642bd",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "She may have known Harold for a long time,[p/] but she's never read his thoughts."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8ae48",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "His thoughts could be very hostile and rude despite his kind expression.[p/] He was very good at hiding what he was truly feeling."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a71b43",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "Laefe: And Beatrice...[p/] There's no way she'd participate in a plan like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:026b13a",
  "node": "VentSeen6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Look, Laefe...[p/] I know you don't want to suspect your sister,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b61ce0",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "She couldn't have been working alone in her condition."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a5c25",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "And I couldn't think of any other way she'd be involved in this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2978b",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Laefe: Anyways,[p/] we're finished here, aren't we?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f7b45",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes.[p/] Thank you for lending Tracker to us, Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:04115db",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Laefe: ...I only want to help you find out what really happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f97b1b",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Laefe: I know my sister is innocent.[p/] I hope once you find out the truth,[p/] you'll see that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0079e27",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I guess we'll have to see."
}

{
  "id": "line:023cb8a",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Laefe: Now if you'll excuse me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc8485",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Celeste: So that's it, right?[p/] We finally know who really committed the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0354913",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "And if we could get Harold to confess on the stand,[p/] he might reveal Beatrice's involvement as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0001442",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "If he did that,[p/] I might be able to convince her and Ms. Tymora to take a plea deal."
}

{
  "id": "line:020cb6b",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "...Although,[p/] knowing Ms. Tymora,[p/] that would be easier said than done."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f2ed6",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] this is definitely the lead that we've been looking for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff4891",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Celeste: But is it really enough?[p/] We still don't have any physical evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0909028",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Tyrion: It'll have to do for now.[p/] We're running out of time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f25ac8",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'll just have to call Harold to the stand to testify about what he did that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:049e075",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Tyrion: If I can push him far enough,[p/] I might be able to catch him lying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc8f6a",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "But I doubted it would be that easy.[p/] He clearly had a good poker face."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e4a07",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Just how much would he be able to hide his true thoughts?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08891b6",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Harold: I already gave my statement to the Inquisition.[p/] Is my testimony really necessary?"
}

{
  "id": "line:049c225",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Orym: Sorry, old-timer.[p/] My orders come [i]straight[/i] from the prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:063100a",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Orym: We're going to need you on the stand today."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f28f7",
  "node": "VentSeen7",
  "text": "Harold: ...I see.[p/] I'll do what I can to help."
}

{
  "id": "line:045813f",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm glad we can talk like this again.[p/] I'd forgotten how much I missed speaking with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0858abc",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat",
  "text": "Beatrice: Yes,[p/] I only hope our next conversation isn't within a cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:010935d",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat",
  "text": "Laefe: Beatrice, on that night,[p/] what were you talking to Father about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c44ab",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat",
  "text": "Beatrice: I'm sorry, Laefe,[p/] but I can't tell you that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0317e68",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat",
  "text": "Laefe: Beatrice,[p/] I just want you to know that I believe in your innocence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e499d4",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...How are you so sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdc385",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat",
  "text": "Laefe: Because you're my sister.[p/] I know you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0966c56",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat",
  "text": "Beatrice: Laefe,[p/] do you know the things I've done over the last five years?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab3500",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat",
  "text": "Laefe: N-[p/][s/]No,[p/] I can only imagine how difficult it was to survive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f90556",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Survival would never be enough.[p/] I've had too much stolen from me."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d4f3a",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: I've been denied what was rightfully mine,[p/] and it's taken me years to finally wrench it back."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f30c1",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Laefe: W-[p/][s/]What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0577f97",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: I know you suffered under him,[p/] and I understand your pain."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db1459",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Once this trial is over,[p/] we can finally heal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfc3ca",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: I've already taken care of Steelwind.[p/] I simply need that boy to have an unfortunate accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0089851",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: You still have that dog, don't you?[p/] And you're on good terms with Tyrion, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0cb50",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: It should be easy for you to facilitate another unfortunate accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0663667",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Hm...[p/] I can tell from the sound of your voice that you don't have the stomach for such things."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e78b8",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: No matter.[p/] I can take care of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:076fa2b",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: But I suggest you keep quiet about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0581e20",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Or you might end up meeting the same fate as Father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4c07b",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Laefe trembled,[p/] her hand going to her mouth in realization of what her sister was saying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcd0c4",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "She said nothing in response.[p/] She just ran from the dungeons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef87bb",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Eris: ...Must you flaunt that ability so recklessly?[p/] You're making me envious."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cdd8a",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Nine hells, Eris...[p/][s/] What do you want?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd4073",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Eris: Why wouldn't I want to see my favorite little mole-rat?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0530cd5",
  "node": "LaefeAndBeat2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Ugh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d164c",
  "node": "Examine_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "They even had gold-tinted chandeliers in the hallways..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9f089",
  "node": "Examine_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "It was ridiculous when I really thought about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8e7be",
  "node": "Examine_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "There were several jewels mounted on the walls,[p/] and they were all equidistant from each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:064f046",
  "node": "Examine_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "I already knew that House Frega was wealthy,[p/] but embedding jewels into the walls made the manor look a little tacky."
}

{
  "id": "line:06307e5",
  "node": "Check_Events_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm...[p/] This place looks pretty quiet,[p/] but there aren't any tables anywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f72001",
  "node": "Check_Events_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I [i]could[/i] play on the floor..."
}

{
  "id": "line:068dc3b",
  "node": "Check_Events_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What the-?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e55b27",
  "node": "Check_Events_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "As I was walking through the hallways of the manor,[p/] I suddenly came face to face with a large animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f95571",
  "node": "Check_Events_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "Before I could even realize what I was looking at,[p/] the creature quickly scampered away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc913b",
  "node": "Check_Events_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Did someone leave a door open?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d5ea8",
  "node": "Check_Events_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "I thought about telling someone,[p/] but the manor was full of nobles."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6ca6f",
  "node": "Check_Events_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "I was sure that a servant would spot it eventually,[p/] and it wasn't as if anyone would believe me anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad7d5c",
  "node": "Check_Events_HallwayIntro",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] it would be best to look for somewhere else to play."
}

{
  "id": "line:089fe5a",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "In the kingdom of Wyverngarde,[p/] there was a gulf between what was lawful and what was just."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a77b9",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Here,[p/] ideals were just fairy tales.[p/] They were pleasant to think about,[p/] but they distracted from how the world really was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce5da7",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "You're naïve,[p/] but I've been starting to think that if everyone else was like you,[p/] the world wouldn't be the way it was."
}

{
  "id": "line:069749a",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "But the world [i]was[/i] the way it was.[p/] Not even you—[p/]with all of your special, divine powers—[p/]could change that."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f5454",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Ruby: I can't believe Cuthbert used the Eye of Horus on the client."
}

{
  "id": "line:09aebc9",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Ruby: He's becoming more and more reckless,[p/] and I think McCoy is just making him worse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0999931",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Ruby: I wonder what he was like with his real mother..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a8fc1",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Ruby: He's definitely nothing like Ryan was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7842f",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Adopting him was a mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:026c4b0",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Is something wrong, Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:000f6e4",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Ruby: No...[p/] It's nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f51219",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Well,[p/] the trial is about to begin,[p/] and [i]all[/i] of our futures are at stake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0e5fb",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Ruby: Of course, Ms—"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ace61",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Ruby: Actually,[p/] what [i]do[/i] you go by now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0435f80",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: I prefer just \"Beatrice\",[p/] but they'll be using my legal name anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e001d2",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice muttered some kind of mantra before clapping her hands together."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bef0a",
  "node": "LobbyIntro",
  "text": "She'd been doing that a lot since we'd met.[p/] It must've been some kind of meditative ritual for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c35eb0",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "I couldn't help but side-eye Eris.[p/] I was a little annoyed with how careless she was being."
}

{
  "id": "line:0977f67",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Eris: ...Is something wrong, Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e97d8",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Ruby: I'd just like to know what you think you're doing here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0762413",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Eris: My father sent me to accompany Beatrice to the courthouse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f83ceb",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Eris: It's a new environment for her.[p/] We do need to keep her condition in mind, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fa941",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "I wasn't so convinced.[p/] Her father had a lot more sense than that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd00a5",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Not to mention that Eris always liked stirring up trouble."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c09236",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "She took a lot of pleasure in complicating my jobs.[p/] It was apparently her favorite pastime."
}

{
  "id": "line:0032e82",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "...And the boss—[p/]doting father that he was—[p/]just let her do as she pleased."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a758b6",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Ruby: I hope you understand how much you're risking by being seen with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e1df0",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Ruby: You were already pushing it when you approached us at the Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:072c2f8",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Eris: Don't you think you're worrying too much?[p/] You've been preparing for this, haven't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb6b09",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Ruby: Just keep your head low and make sure no one connects you to your father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0003f89",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Ruby: You know how important this trial is."
}

{
  "id": "line:01328db",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Eris: Why?[p/] Would knowing my true identity cause friction with your son?"
}

{
  "id": "line:008bd4b",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Ruby: He's not my—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f602d",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Eris: Oh...[p/] Speak of the devil."
}

{
  "id": "line:0534219",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "I spotted Cuthbert and McCoy walking into the courtroom with the other members of the gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8951c",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "I guess after our little argument,[p/] he wanted to see how this trial would turn out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcd586",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "McCoy spotted me and give me a friendly,[p/] yet uncomfortable smile."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3a1b1",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Cuthbert froze for a moment before looking away and walking silently into the courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a9c34",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Eris: ...Parental troubles?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cc590",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...We had a disagreement earlier.[p/] It's nothing to worry about."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f4e8c",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_2",
  "text": "Eris: If you say so."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a6085",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "I [i]was[/i] wary about what he saw in Beatrice's mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:02002af",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "He'd always been a good kid,[p/] but he was also really stubborn.[p/] It clouded his judgment sometimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0922a5f",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "He hadn't been practicing law for very long."
}

{
  "id": "line:002d3c6",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "It didn't help that his string of victories was getting to his head."
}

{
  "id": "line:0266854",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "But I was sure that once he'd seen enough of what the courts were really like,[p/] he'd understand why I needed to do this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b221ea",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "Aria: The trial is about to begin.[p/] Do you really have the time to be making small talk here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c51a0",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "Prosecutor Steelwind approached the three of us,[p/] tailed by a familiar face."
}

{
  "id": "line:0257cba",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Wallace Nightgrave?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0055955",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "Wallace: U-[p/][s/]Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d6667",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "Aria: ...He's accompanying me as my aide for this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:019328a",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "Ruby: So,[p/] can I assume you'll be prosecuting?"
}

{
  "id": "line:085df40",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "Aria: Of course.[p/] I would never pass up the opportunity to face the \"infamous\" Ruby Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0783297",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "Ruby: Really?[p/] If I remember correctly,[p/] you haven't even beaten [i]Tyrion[/i] once so far."
}

{
  "id": "line:0375949",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "Aria: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:091c16f",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "Oh, it seemed [i]that[/i] struck a nerve.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ace77",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_3",
  "text": "I might be able to use that later."
}

{
  "id": "line:0115d02",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "Wallace: La—[p/][s/] [i]Ms.[/i] Steelwind,[p/] don't strain yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c25d2",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "Aria: What's that look for, Beatrice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f39312",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "Aria: You seem almost [i]surprised[/i] to see me here..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b7b41",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Considering the circumstances,[p/] I thought you might recuse yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7ccc8",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "Aria: I am more than capable of remaining objective."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec1926",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "Aria: ...Especially for a case of this much importance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0268527",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "Beatrice: Well,[p/] I hope your mind is as strong as you think it is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec54cd",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "Wallace: Ms. Steelwind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05185cd",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "Nightgrave looked unusually reprimanding and concerned for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0178c48",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "He was really averse to confrontation, wasn't he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04aca64",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "Eris: Oh,[p/] I [i]love[/i] a good reunion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e32c4b",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "Ruby: [i]*sigh*[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a84d59",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "The deck was already stacked in our favor."
}

{
  "id": "line:038c27c",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "I just needed to follow through and get this over and done with."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ab9d7",
  "node": "LobbyIntro_4",
  "text": "After that,[p/] we'd finally have everything we needed to topple the Four Pillars."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b0716",
  "node": "Examine_Storage",
  "text": "Player: Air Vent"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8a135",
  "node": "Examine_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's an air vent that leads into the Duke's Study."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d69a3",
  "node": "Examine_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Supposedly,[p/] Jan heard the altercation between the Duke and his assailant through this."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e04a2",
  "node": "Examine_Storage",
  "text": "Player: Ladder"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e70cfe",
  "node": "Examine_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a step ladder."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d499a",
  "node": "Examine_Storage",
  "text": "Celeste: I agree."
}

{
  "id": "line:0908ab4",
  "node": "Examine_Storage",
  "text": "Player: Boxes"
}

{
  "id": "line:02806e4",
  "node": "Examine_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are several boxes in this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c180a9",
  "node": "Examine_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: They appear to contain various cleaning supplies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb7884",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Player: Jan Hughes"
}

{
  "id": "line:04abf4c",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Celeste: So you're working as a servant now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e7662",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Not exactly,[p/] but I was a part of the catering staff."
}

{
  "id": "line:079327d",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: The twins started their own food business after Frega threw us out of the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3d34b",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right...[p/] Sorry about that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04293bd",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Eh...[p/] Things happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:033e988",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: I'm honestly glad I'm out of that place."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ba538",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait,[p/] are Valentina and Valerie here too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01505bd",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Nah.[p/] They just contracted some staff to the Duke for the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a1386",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: I think a bunch of other businesses did the same thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0609c1c",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "I wondered how they felt about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:074c558",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "They lent their services to the very man who got them fired in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dab256",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "William must've offered them a lot of gold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0222d09",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Player: The Murder"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5190d",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Man,[p/] I can't believe I got myself pulled into [i]another[/i] murder investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0700e",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Do I have bad luck or what?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b2569",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: The prosecutor told us that you heard the altercation through the air vents."
}

{
  "id": "line:058e94b",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you tell us exactly what you heard?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db95bb",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Well,[p/] I didn't hear everything.[p/] I was taking a nap in this room when it happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b98733",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Celeste: Why [i]were[/i] you napping here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d4f95",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: I had nothing else to do.[p/] I accidentally closed the door when the lock was engaged."
}

{
  "id": "line:0573023",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Before I knew it,[p/] I was trapped here."
}

{
  "id": "line:00eb883",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: After a while,[p/] the sounds of some kind of scuffle were coming through the vents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb193a",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: I couldn't hear everything but I heard the Duke shout,[p/][s/] \"Who are you?![p/][s/] What do you want?!\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0d88bfc",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: That went on for a few seconds.[p/] Then I heard the sound of someone getting stabbed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2da0b",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you hear the voice of the assailant?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a6324",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: They didn't say anything,[p/] but I [i]did[/i] hear them."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e1484",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Their voice was really raspy.[p/] I think they had a sore throat or something."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f7828",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Or they were trying to mask their voice..."
}

{
  "id": "line:060846e",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Player: The Storage Room"
}

{
  "id": "line:05bca19",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why did you enter the storage room anyway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0560b9e",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: I heard one of them running in the vents upstairs,[p/] and I followed it here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7b3c7",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: After I was done,[p/] I tried to leave,[p/] but the door was locked."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d8e0d",
  "node": "Talk_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: So...[p/] I took a nap."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b75ff",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: ...I feel like we've done this before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0192fd0",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sorry,[p/] did I already show you my Runestone at the Academy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a450b2",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: I don't know.[p/] Probably."
}

{
  "id": "line:051d9a9",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: You know what they really need to make?[p/] A Runestone that can instantly clean any surface."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a52721",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why would an attorney need a function like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0707a",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Man...[p/] I never thought I'd see [i]you[/i] two again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a641be",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Trouble seems to follow you wherever you go."
}

{
  "id": "line:00deedf",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Celeste: I think it's more that [i]we[/i] tend to follow trouble wherever [i]it[/i] appears."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8eb94",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Celeste: So you're working as a caterer now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0069cef",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Not exactly.[p/] But I was a part of the catering staff."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c7128",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Nah...[p/] It's not your fault."
}

{
  "id": "line:007f975",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Even if Redmond was still headmaster,[p/] I'm sure the board would've found some other way to get rid of us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0944861",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: No.[p/] They just contracted some staff to the Duke for the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d83098",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Player: Rats in the Vents"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5d504",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's strange that they had you chasing rats in the vents."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c2d0f",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'd expect the manor servants to take care of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4814f",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: They've tried,[p/] but they haven't had much luck."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de496d",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: I don't know what's up with them.[p/] These rats have avoided all of the traps they've set."
}

{
  "id": "line:07dae97",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Mr. Hughes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a7942",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0578b00",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Mr. Hughes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a99e0f",
  "node": "Present_Storage",
  "text": "...That didn't evoke much of a response from him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd734b",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "We entered the storage room,[p/] hoping to investigate the air vent that connected to the Duke's Study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c265ea",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "...When we come across a person lying on the floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0153680",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb75ec",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] Jan?[p/][s/] Is that you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b20901",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Aw, man...[p/] What's with all the noise?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aea229",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: I was having such a good nap too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0daa8bf",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Mr. Hughes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0324a3e",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Oh...[p/] It's you two."
}

{
  "id": "line:094eb2b",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Celeste: Why are you taking a nap in the storage room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f268a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: The Kingsguard won't let us leave until they finish investigating the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e528ef",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: And I spotted Lucio Steelwind in that room with the nice couches."
}

{
  "id": "line:038db38",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: No way am I sleeping anywhere near that guy."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e603c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Lucio Steelwind was here?[p/] I'm surprised someone like him would attend the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:02428b0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] the prosecutor told us that you heard the murder from here during the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd0dc0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you think you could tell us what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e1229",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: Sure.[p/] Why not?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc8caf",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Jan: My nap's ruined anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0636b65",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "He only heard a few words before the murderer struck the final blow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0218744",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "It was a small piece,[p/] but a piece nonetheless."
}

{
  "id": "line:026eef2",
  "node": "Check_Events_Storage",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] it was time to MOVE somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0878804",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Another chandelier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0904048",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: This room probably costs more than my family's tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:020c357",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Fireplace"
}

{
  "id": "line:0516094",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a fireplace...[p/] Could the murderer have entered through here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f078fb",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: That wouldn't be possible.[p/] The chimney is far too narrow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0888622",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Even a small child wouldn't be thin enough to fit through it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a2e1d",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Painting"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a0b3d",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of some sort of scholar.[p/] There's some text on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2c2f4",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Rook Resingar:[p/] economic scholar and aristocratic accountant.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0a50123",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"He was known in some circles as \"Rook the cook\",[p/] due to his ability to \"cook the books\" of the Four Pillar Houses.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0e23f5f",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: \"Rook the cook\"..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d649f",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: Sometimes I wish I could have a nickname like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8b467",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What about \"Crimson Demon\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e5c43",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] Not that one."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c0e15",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Bookshelf"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b90a0d",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a bookshelf filled with books."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0ac14",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: I wonder what kind of books the Duke owned."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f351d6",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait a minute...[p/][s/] They're all blank!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0862112",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: All of his real books seem to be on the floor and his desk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba20bc",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Window"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a0f72",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a window that leads into this room..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0a790",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could the murderer have escaped through here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c121e7",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: No.[p/] The window didn't open and the glass was magically reinforced."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c70ddd",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Books"
}

{
  "id": "line:03603bb",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are several books about economics and politics."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef3501",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It doesn't look like there's anything of note."
}

{
  "id": "line:098bd37",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Body"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2f68c",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a pool of blood and a chalk outline where the body must have been."
}

{
  "id": "line:016bad2",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a large mahogany table at the end of the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5c952",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Duke must have done his work here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1632f",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Detect Body"
}

{
  "id": "line:02cd53b",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: There are small traces of [b]illusion[/b] magic over here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0215578",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "I leaned down and inspected the floor where she was pointing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aac239",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "There were small flecks of some kind of dried liquid."
}

{
  "id": "line:004aae3",
  "node": "Examine_Study1",
  "text": "Was this blood or something else?"
}

{
  "id": "line:048623d",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about the murder?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5da1a",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: William Frega was found dead in this room after the lockdown was lifted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9fa93",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Wait...[p/] \"lockdown\"?[p/] What lockdown?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0530283",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: From what we can tell,[p/] his throat had been slashed open with a letter opener."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b4f34",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Wallace: The cause of death was blood loss.[p/] Both of his carotid arteries were severed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0178b8c",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: It was expertly done.[p/] Whoever did this knew what they were doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0812c05",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Here's the Autopsy Report if you want a detailed description."
}

{
  "id": "line:09422a4",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Were you able to find the murder weapon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e3a8b",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Yes.[p/] It was a letter opener owned by the victim."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a28494",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm...[p/] The murderer must have found it in this room and used it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae6eaa",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: There [i]was[/i] one strange detail about the weapon."
}

{
  "id": "line:087f52a",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: The handle was completely shattered."
}

{
  "id": "line:03dcf9a",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: We're not sure what to make of that detail,[p/] but it's as if something crushed the handle using tremendous force."
}

{
  "id": "line:0325ac2",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "What could have caused the handle to shatter like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a84bf",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Lockdown"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7ac30",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You mentioned that there was a lockdown.[p/] When did this happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f43d4",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: You didn't notice?[p/] The Inquisition [i]did[/i] try to be discreet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6e073",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: But everyone noticed the commotion Beatrice and the two princes made over it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf1e60",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: ...I suppose you two must have been lost in your own little world, weren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:059b57a",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "...Oh."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b5cd8",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/][s/]Anyways,[p/] you said that the Duke's body was found [i]after[/i] the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:00143f9",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was the lockdown triggered when the Sword of Spell Eating went missing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0efc8ea",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: It didn't just go missing.[p/] There was clear evidence that someone had broken into one of the Haroldson exhibits."
}

{
  "id": "line:0773790",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: So there was also a theft last night..."
}

{
  "id": "line:008a48b",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Does the manor's lockdown system behave like the one at the Imperial Academy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc0822",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: The systems are somewhat different."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf37d0",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Unlike the Imperial Academy,[p/] the lockdown only prevented people from leaving or entering the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:020dc30",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: So not [i]all[/i] of the rooms were locked,[p/] but what about this specific room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0608f63",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: [i]This[/i] room does have abjurative wards that lock the door and prevent teleportation in and out of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a75eee",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: In addition to that,[p/] the system placed an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b] over the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c39a09",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And the system somehow covered the entire manor in this effect..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0876331",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sure you noticed the several purple crystals embedded in the walls of the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baa6d9",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Each of those crystals produced an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b] during the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ce3b8",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: So no one could cast magic during the entirety of the lockdown?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaef99",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Not exactly...[p/] Someone could have used the stolen artifact to circumvent it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e046f8",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Stolen Artifact"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d02629",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you tell me more about the theft?[p/] Who reported it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1e116",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: That's correct.[p/] The Kingsguard moved to arrest her,[p/] but His Highness ordered them to step down."
}

{
  "id": "line:090fa76",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: It didn't look like she was planning on fleeing.[p/] So they planned to wait until after the party had ended."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f638a2",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But then they found the Duke's body."
}

{
  "id": "line:01487e2",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Correct.[p/] We believe that she used the stolen sword to nullify the magical locks and break into the Duke's study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f97187",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: But if she had the Sword,[p/] why wouldn't she use [i]that[/i] to commit the murder?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8eb37",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: We're not entirely sure.[p/] We have a few working theories."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a36e8f",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: She might have wanted to prevent the theft from being tied to the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:056de6f",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Or perhaps she had more confidence wielding a knife instead of a sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:065290b",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Regardless of her reasons,[p/] it's clear that the Sword wasn't the murder weapon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c211a3",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "So she's not just being implicated in the Duke's murder.[p/] She's also being charged with stealing the Sword of Spell Eating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3e1c5",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "But what possible reason would she have to do either of those crimes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0358c83",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "And how could she possibly carry out all these crimes if she were blind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4adb9",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Player: The Duke in the Study"
}

{
  "id": "line:0786b82",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Since the body was found here,[p/] was the Duke locked in this room during the lockdown?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0471e44",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Yes.[p/] William Frega knew that this room [i]should[/i] have been secured."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6112f",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: He was supposedly in a bad mood.[p/] He locked himself in this room for most of the night."
}

{
  "id": "line:072c302",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: He refused to let anyone into the room.[p/] The only person he spoke to after that was Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a5df7",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: She tried to tell her father about the theft,[p/] but he was apparently preoccupied with something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f4711",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: He said that he wanted to stay in his Study for the rest of the night."
}

{
  "id": "line:04853bb",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: When did this happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0604fd4",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: It was shortly before the lockdown was activated.[p/] A little after 1:00 AM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6db9c",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Laefe must've been the last person to see William Frega alive then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0deea8a",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "I was already acquainted with her.[p/] She might be able to tell me more about the Duke's actions that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0270b78",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: By the way, Steelwind.[p/] Do you have a map of the manor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd4e50",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I do.[p/] Would you like a copy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:010ebe1",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Please and thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0876b29",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Witnesses"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a3dc7",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Were there any other witnesses aside from Laefe who saw the Duke that night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f78607",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: There [i]was[/i] someone who heard the altercation,[p/] but it's not much to go off of."
}

{
  "id": "line:05836e5",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: A servant was trapped in a storage room nearby."
}

{
  "id": "line:0418817",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: The air vent that connects to this room runs through that storage room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0258804",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: He supposedly heard sounds of a struggle through that vent."
}

{
  "id": "line:013d3a2",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did this witness hear?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0797bc1",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: There were sounds of a struggle before he heard the Duke choking,[p/] presumably on his own blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:0704982",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: When the lockdown was lifted,[p/] he informed the Kingsguard of what he'd heard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f99048",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: That's when they discovered the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:062afae",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I see.[p/] Who was this servant?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f3303",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I believe you actually know him.[p/] His name is Jan Hughes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0031cea",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Wallace: What is Jan doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02bc940",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "I never expected to see [i]him[/i] again.[p/] Much less [i]here[/i] of all places."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9fdc0",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Did William Frega hire him after he was let go from the Academy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e54d4b",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Player: The Meeting"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfb844",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Would you happen to know why Beatrice was meeting with her father after all these years?"
}

{
  "id": "line:051d6ae",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I have some ideas,[p/] but nothing concrete."
}

{
  "id": "line:015f920",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I was hoping [i]you[/i] could tell me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b47836",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Tymora and Beatrice have both refused to disclose anything about their meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:063d154",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "What could that meeting have been about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a35c8",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Speaking of which,[p/] I haven't seen Tymora anywhere in the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d6326",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: As the defendant's attorney,[p/] I would have thought that she'd be here to investigate the murder alongside you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcaef7",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "That [i]was[/i] strange...[p/] But Ms. Tymora has always had her own way of doing her job."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6114a",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Perhaps she was using a different strategy."
}

{
  "id": "line:06142a0",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Anyways,[p/] I imagine that she met with her father to request financial aid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e59202",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What makes you say that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e4dd5",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: ...I have it on good authority that she was deeply in debt. [h=\"But that seems so unlike her.|Was she truly that desperate?\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da1eda",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: That's the only reason why she would speak with her father after all these years."
}

{
  "id": "line:0174e18",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: It's also why I believe she was the one who murdered him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed7c69",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You think she murdered him for his inheritance?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c2337",
  "node": "Talk_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: It's the only motive that makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c0366",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Steelwind,[p/] I really need to understand why you think Beatrice did this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cca0a8",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's completely blind, isn't she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06da304",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: ...You don't know her as I do."
}

{
  "id": "line:069dabe",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: It just seems really difficult to believe."
}

{
  "id": "line:010047e",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: House Frega has always thrived by politically maneuvering around the other Pillar Families."
}

{
  "id": "line:090da16",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: And no one has embodied that more than Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0feefc0",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: In her years studying at the Imperial Academy,[p/] she didn’t just excel—[p/]she dominated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6d4c1",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: She has an uncanny talent for understanding what people wanted,[p/] and she knew exactly how to use that to her advantage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc80e7",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: During her first year,[p/] she had the ear of the student council president."
}

{
  "id": "line:0101354",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: By her second year,[p/] she had stolen his position from him,[p/] and she only gained more influence after that."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b2af4",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: It wasn't long before professors were deferring to her.[p/] Students would seek her favor.[p/] She even had her hands in the school board."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c2a26",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: In four short years,[p/] she had turned the Imperial Academy into her own personal empire."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c8a7a",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: She's always calculating,[p/] and she knows exactly how to get what she wants."
}

{
  "id": "line:0965213",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: ...She was even arranged to marry the Crown Prince. [h=\"Even now,|I'm living in her shadow...\" e=\"sa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d18e51",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Did something happen to change that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f3246",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: I won't speak much more of it,[p/] but there was an accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d534c9",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: She was horribly injured,[p/] and she lost her sight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b75530",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: I'm not sure what happened after that,[p/] but she later fled Frega Manor and went into hiding."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c73ab",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: No one knew where she'd gone,[p/] and she ignored any attempts we made to contact her."
}

{
  "id": "line:02399d4",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Aria: Last night's ball was the first time in years that Aster and I had seen her."
}

{
  "id": "line:06007fe",
  "node": "BeatConv",
  "text": "Then how did Ms. Tymora meet her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b87ed",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Your Runestone is still in good shape, I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b76cc",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Only because Celeste is really good at repairing it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c44564",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: ...You never told me you could work with artificery."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e41a0",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: I just started learning about it a month ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b2dec",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Really..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0962aa7",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2422f",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: ...It's nothing. [h=\"How does she have|so much raw natural talent...?\" e=\"sa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e30fcc",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I was quite surprised to see you two at the Lords' Ball yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b1d94",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] It's a long story."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fc5da",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Clearly.[p/] You came accompanied by Beatrice Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd5d18",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: She was the last person I expected to see that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:08dc354",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "I sensed some disdain in her voice."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d5e95",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I apologize that your investigation didn't lead anywhere, Ms. McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:041d230",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: No, it's fine.[p/] My expectations weren't that high coming into this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0851f0a",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: But I still wanted to try, you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b58875",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: If only I could have that much optimism."
}

{
  "id": "line:06db4e1",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: Steelwind,[p/] did the Inquisition happen to find my sword anywhere?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d4fd1",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: [i]Your[/i] sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0818402",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I can't say I've heard anything about it,[p/] and I'm sure the Inquisition would have recognized it."
}

{
  "id": "line:044b825",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't worry.[p/] I'm sure we'll find it somewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f3fee",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0089089",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We somehow always end up meeting each other, don't we?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0081bd2",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Well, it can't be helped.[p/] We work on opposite sides of the same profession, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:018479f",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Although,[p/] I am remiss that I still don't know much about you,[p/] despite our many meetings."
}

{
  "id": "line:074ce07",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Would you like to go somewhere together in the future?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c98a9",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I'm only joking.[p/] I would never think of asking you out in front of your lover."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d38023",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Wha-?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce52d0",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: C-[p/][s/]Celeste is—"
}

{
  "id": "line:066e2e1",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "I found myself stammering over my words."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3c1d4",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait a minute...[p/][s/] Is this payback for last night?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:040aa19",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: ...I have no idea what you're speaking of."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da3eb7",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Orym"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ae010",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I haven't seen Commander White since last night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0581b28",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: He's currently collecting statements from the witnesses at the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0410c92",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I hope he's competent enough to do [i]that[/i] correctly."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cc49f",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Right...[p/] He hasn't had the best record as of late."
}

{
  "id": "line:098f4fb",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Ruby"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa6994",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is this the first time you've faced off against Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0561bc4",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: No...[p/] I've prosecuted her defendants before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1d3b0",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I've actually had more luck convicting her defendants over yours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0936299",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait,[p/][s/] really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0323625",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I wouldn't let that inflate your ego.[p/] You're clearly more picky about who you defend."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6eb35",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What's [i]that[/i] supposed to mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0969d41",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: You tend to pick defendants that you're sure are innocent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2531d",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure Ms. Tymora does that too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d18fa9",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wonder how Miriam is taking all of this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f8d3f",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I'm surprised that you're worried about her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df01b1",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Last I remember,[p/] she was quite furious with you two for tricking her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d50cfe",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: She may be a pompous jerk,[p/] but she still lost her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d9a1e",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And now her long-lost sister is being charged with murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da265d",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] She must be going through a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf91e9",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not that I doubt his skills, but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0175c49",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why choose Wallace as an aide?"
}

{
  "id": "line:090c46f",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Wallace: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] W-[p/][s/]Well—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba4331",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I have my own reasons for choosing him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad1fbb",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "She seemed pretty tight-lipped about Wallace,[p/] but I didn't see any reason to pry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f61316",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure you have mixed feelings about Aster hiring us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0228694",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I don't.[p/] He is free to put his trust in whoever he wishes. [h=\"He does admire you,|after all.\" e=\"af\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1c6a1",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "The Eye of Horus begged to differ."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c5279",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: He [i]clearly[/i] trusts your judgment more than mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0937629",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: He didn't even [i]think[/i] to ask me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b26fc1",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion.[p/] Change the subject, please."
}

{
  "id": "line:02968da",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice|Beatrice's Inheritance 0|Beatrice's Inheritance"
}

{
  "id": "line:037f385",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: If it's not too much trouble,[p/] do you know how Beatrice became blind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b64af3",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sorry.[p/] But I'm not going to discuss that. [h=\"It would just|dig up old wounds...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:08bb758",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b274c4",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "So she [i]does[/i] know what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:084e506",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why would Harold keep such a dangerous weapon on display?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04297e1",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: There's value in remembering and honoring our kingdom's history.[p/] Especially the unsavory parts."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4a075",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Anyways,[p/] the exhibits were heavily protected."
}

{
  "id": "line:061cc50",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: Only a powerful mage like Beatrice could have broken into them."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a458c",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "So,[p/] even someone like Steelwind considered Beatrice to be a powerful mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:086ad13",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Haroldson's Security"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b44ee5",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I still fail to understand how you think Beatrice broke into Haroldson's secure exhibits."
}

{
  "id": "line:0955338",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: She's...[p/] creative.[p/] I'm sure she found a way."
}

{
  "id": "line:08396c3",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about William Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01eb4d5",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: He was probably the most powerful nobleman in Wyverngarde aside from my father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b30ffb",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: My family has been at odds with the Fregas for as long as we can remember."
}

{
  "id": "line:000185a",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: My father is probably salivating at the thought of House Frega losing its head."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9d963",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What's your impression of Laefe Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0717aa8",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: She tends to keep to herself.[p/] So I don't know her very well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f56856",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: After Beatrice left,[p/] every one assumed that she would be the one to inherit House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:008308c",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sure that was a difficult burden for her to bear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f02663",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Player: Lockdown System|Method of Entry"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8fc08",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The crime scene was a locked room with no method of entry."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b57fd",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: But the Duke still died.[p/] That means that the murderer used something to nullify the lockdown in some way."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d4f83",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "But did they really use the Sword of Spell Eating to do so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a4ac8",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05edcf3",
  "node": "Present_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sorry.[p/] But I'm not the person to ask about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a634e",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "I arrived at the crime scene and saw the usual swarm of Inquisition knights."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f09b10",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "However,[p/] there were also some members of the Kingsguard alongside them."
}

{
  "id": "line:098b517",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "They must've been working together since the victim was the head of a Pillar Family."
}

{
  "id": "line:04799b9",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I wasn't expecting to see you here, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:028b6be",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I thought Ruby Tymora was defending this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:04955a6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Prosecutor Steelwind approached us as we entered the study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db2559",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "And she was followed by an unexpected yet familiar face."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3de3c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: Wallace?[p/] What are [i]you[/i] doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8069e",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Wallace: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ba9e3",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: He's here as my aide for the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:00af174",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "I didn't doubt Wallace's abilities,[p/] but why would Steelwind need his help?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b58ff9",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] we're here on behalf of the Crown Prince."
}

{
  "id": "line:0167ee2",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Tyrion: He hired us to investigate this case independently."
}

{
  "id": "line:033961d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: I...[p/] see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8d0d5",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]I'm sure he just wants to make sure the investigation goes smoothly."
}

{
  "id": "line:021287b",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Aria: ...Well,[p/] if you're here on behalf of His Highness,[p/] I'll do whatever I can to help you."
}

{
  "id": "line:029e13c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "This whole situation was strange,[p/] but our goal remained the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:09eefd0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study1",
  "text": "Steelwind should be able to tell us more about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a311cb",
  "node": "StudyDeduce",
  "text": "There was a lot to work through here."
}

{
  "id": "line:099427d",
  "node": "StudyDeduce",
  "text": "The prosecution was trying to assert that Beatrice committed the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0935dcf",
  "node": "StudyDeduce",
  "text": "But what would she have needed to do to carry out all of the actions described?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0747b55",
  "node": "StudyDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: We need to narrow down the time that the murder occurred."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f8f76",
  "node": "StudyDeduce",
  "text": "Celeste: The body was discovered [i]after[/i] the lockdown was lifted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c75fe9",
  "node": "StudyDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: And Laefe Frega saw her father alive before it was activated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0428b2f",
  "node": "StudyDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: He entered his study,[p/] and she watched as the lock engaged."
}

{
  "id": "line:00978bc",
  "node": "StudyDeduce2",
  "text": "No...[p/] If I assumed that Laefe's testimony was correct,[p/] William Frega [i]was[/i] alive before the lockdown was triggered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0daf023",
  "node": "StudyDeduce2",
  "text": "Not only that,[p/] he said that he would stay in the Study for the rest of the night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e79583",
  "node": "StudyDeduce2",
  "text": "Which meant that he probably never left his study."
}

{
  "id": "line:032e850",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right.[p/] The murder must have occurred during the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df7be1",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Celeste: But that means that the murderer somehow got past the abjuration wards that protected this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0178187",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind and the Inquisition believe that Beatrice used the Sword of Spell Eating to get past them."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b6898",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Regardless of what they think,[p/] we need to assume that the murderer used some kind of magic nullification to get into William's study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec49c5",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Celeste: But that's not necessarily true, is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3b3d5",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Celeste: What if the murderer entered the room [i]before[/i] William locked it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc9e21",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm...[p/] If they were in the room when William locked it,[p/] they would have been trapped here until he decided to leave."
}

{
  "id": "line:0849821",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not only that.[p/] They would have been discovered the moment the guards entered his study."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ae005",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Celeste: Maybe they used some kind of invisibility?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d55f2f",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Celeste: Or they could have teleported away the moment the Kingsguard unlocked the door."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7eaa1",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Aria: This room is enchanted to block teleportation.[p/] A spell like that wouldn't have worked."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c3a1d",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Right...[p/] I remember Miriam did something similar to her dorm room at the Imperial Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:065edcd",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: What about Celeste's theory of an invisible assailant?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0be2f80",
  "node": "StudyDeduce3",
  "text": "Aria: I'll admit that we [i]did[/i] find small traces of [b]illusion[/b] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0736e47",
  "node": "StudyDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So we know for sure that they weren't here before or after the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:070bfc0",
  "node": "StudyDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: This means that whoever committed the murder used some way to bypass the abjurative wards that protect this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:04212c8",
  "node": "StudyDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: The next thing to consider is the murder weapon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1084a",
  "node": "StudyDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was a letter opener that was presumably owned by William Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb7f24",
  "node": "StudyDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: The murderer probably used it to avoid leaving evidence that incriminated them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1552d",
  "node": "StudyDeduce5",
  "text": "No...[p/] The letter opener was clearly owned by William Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0050e89",
  "node": "StudyDeduce5",
  "text": "So where would the murderer have taken it from?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a9c57",
  "node": "StudyDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right.[p/] The letter opener came from this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adc4b1",
  "node": "StudyDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: The murderer probably wanted to avoid using a weapon that would've implicated them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1ac9d",
  "node": "StudyDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: So they decided to use it and leave it here afterward."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8ee18",
  "node": "StudyDeduce6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But that leaves a glaring hole in the prosecution's case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0711b",
  "node": "StudyDeduce6",
  "text": "Aria: And what would that be, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e0e71",
  "node": "StudyDeduce7",
  "text": "No...[p/] The prosecution's allegations are definitely possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb164a",
  "node": "StudyDeduce7",
  "text": "However,[p/] the flaw with Steelwind's case lies in [i]who[/i] she's targeting it with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0474c58",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Beatrice Frega is completely blind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0351d00",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even [i]if[/i] she were somehow able to break into a highly guarded exhibit,[p/] how did she slip past the guards and enter the Duke's study?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5491a",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Furthermore,[p/] how did she locate the letter opener if she couldn't see it in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0440fcb",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: None of it makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdb29c",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Committing this murder unseen would've been a tall order for anyone.[p/] I can hardly believe a blind person did all of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c157dc",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Aria: ...You'd do well not to underestimate her, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:05723b1",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Look,[p/] I understand that she's probably really intelligent,[p/] but it just seems impossible."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e8d87",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Aria: If there's anything I know about Beatrice Frega,[p/] she can turn impossibility into inevitability if she wants to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0815ff5",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well,[p/] I guess we'll see."
}

{
  "id": "line:002b2d1",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Aria: Can I ask you a question, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0c0a1",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I tend to have an insight into these sorts of things."
}

{
  "id": "line:074273c",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've never been in that position."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c22890",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Aria: I've already seen your uncanny ability to read people,[p/] but why don't you humor me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d6919",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Aria: ...What would you do if they were guilty?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f8997",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why do you ask?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e043ad",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Aria: Hm...[p/] No reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0279a7d",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0063e04",
  "node": "StudyDeduce8",
  "text": "...Anyways,[p/] she'd made her stance clear.[p/] I still had a lot of leads to follow up on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f69b5e",
  "node": "Examine_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: It looks pretty small.[p/] The chimney is probably narrow too."
}

{
  "id": "line:07543ed",
  "node": "Examine_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: Even a kid wouldn't be thin enough to fit through it."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c49df",
  "node": "Examine_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Supposedly,[p/] it's magically reinforced."
}

{
  "id": "line:025c314",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Player: What were you looking for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:060e8e5",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What could be so important that you'd disturb an [i]active[/i] crime scene?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5cd5f",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I-[p/][s/]It's none of your concern.[p/] I'm merely trying to find something that belongs to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:069bcc1",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Really?[p/] Because I have a feeling that we might be looking for the same thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de3f57",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're looking for the will that your father was drafting, aren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb1b79",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: T-[p/][s/]that's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6020f",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: Were you trying to destroy it before we could get to it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:095789b",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] Of course, not!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02908ed",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:076c8cf",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: ...I just needed to see it for myself. [h=\"Did she really do this?\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db8e00",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Player: The Modified Will"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af075a",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why are you so determined to see the drafted will, Miriam?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2fc96",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I just wanted to see what my father's final wishes were."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baca7b",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: But your father already had a will filed previously.[p/] Wouldn't [i]that[/i] be enough?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0221013",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You also suspect something, don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:058d67a",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: Of course, not![p/][s/] Beatrice would never do something like this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ddeef",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Frega,[p/] I never even mentioned Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b1e8d",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f932d3",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know we're not on the best terms,[p/] but please understand that we're just trying to get to the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ed4ea",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't think your sister did this,[p/] but she may have been involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad0727",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: She may have worked with someone else to orchestrate her father's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b6e86",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Unlike Laefe,[p/] she didn't immediately deny it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f45960",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Player: Where is the will?"
}

{
  "id": "line:058996c",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Where is the will, Miriam?[p/] I need to see it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc63c1",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I...[p/] don't know.[p/] I haven't been able to find it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a865a9",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "I recall that she was frantically searching William's desk earlier.[p/] She was probably telling the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8e3d6",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: ...It [i]should[/i] have been here,[p/] but I can't find it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce480c",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He locked the door when he began drafting it.[p/] In addition to that,[p/] the Inquisition closed the area off after the body was discovered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0349695",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That means that someone took it [i]during[/i] the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:07083c6",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: It was probably stolen by whoever murdered him, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e499c",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah.[p/] That would make the most sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:073b99b",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Which means that whoever did this [i]wanted[/i] to nullify whatever was written on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:04abb64",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "It was looking more and more like the motive behind this was William's inheritance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a172d3",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice's Guilt"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f86639",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Miriam,[p/] it almost sounds like [i]you[/i] suspect Beatrice as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0650741",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: That's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a1fbc",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Am I incorrect?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d11fd",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I...[p/] don't know what to think anymore. [h=\"Why else|would she threaten me?\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d647cf",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Wait...[p/][s/] She was threatened?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a12067",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Miriam...[p/] Did Beatrice threaten you in some way?"
}

{
  "id": "line:065038c",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: W-[p/][s/]What?![p/][s/] Of course, not!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0cc64",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Your testimony yesterday was quite convenient for the defense.[p/] It almost got the whole case thrown out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf9ed7",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And Laefe didn't seem to understand what was going on either."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1e332",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: With the way she gave her testimony yesterday,[p/] it was almost like she was covering for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f782f",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I... [h=\"Does he seriously|not know?\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a891a4",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: ...Please.[p/] Promise me that you won't tell anyone about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:041bc0a",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I won't tell anyone.[p/] What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d41a4",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: About an hour after the murder,[p/] I was approached by Ruby Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d3ae8",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: She gave me a list of statements to give in my testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8b91e",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: ...The statements weren't true,[p/] but she assured me that my status would protect me from any scrutiny."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d1d1d",
  "node": "Talk_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: She had information that I had tried to keep secret,[p/] and she threatened to make it public unless I cooperated with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a5ed8",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: ...I should have known you were an attorney when you showed it to me back at the Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0756360",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] you almost blew our cover, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:085a5eb",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's a habit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ceb7b7",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: To think you'd be so enamoured with such a mundane piece of artficery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc94c4",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: Of all the places,[p/] I never expected to see you here."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ac0e0",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've been getting that a lot today."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b0a39",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I definitely didn't expect to see you again, McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:030bdbd",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah.[p/] Well, don't get used to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f42fa",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: I still remember how you treated Tyrion back at the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbbb0c",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I still have that tea from the Eastern Kingdoms if you'd like some more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3cf39",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright,[p/] I'm listening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3bf32",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Is [i]that[/i] all it took to win her over?"
}

{
  "id": "line:022eb03",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I can't believe someone attacked Aria.[p/] I hope she's okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edb483",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I never expected you to care that much about her."
}

{
  "id": "line:048039b",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: Of course I care about her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a96853",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: E-[p/][s/]Er...[p/] I-[p/][s/]I mean..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bcfaf",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: How can I prove I'm better than her if she falls at the hand of some common brute?"
}

{
  "id": "line:022762e",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Player: Laefe|Liafal's Testimony|Liafal's Testimony 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:019213c",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What's your relationship like with Laefe?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffd404",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I don't want to talk about that. [h=\"I regret saying|those things to her...\" e=\"s\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:08727cc",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice|Beatrice's Inheritance 0|Beatrice's Inheritance 1|Beatrice's Inheritance"
}

{
  "id": "line:0810667",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: Beatrice...[p/] She's changed so much since I last saw her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0075bad",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What was she like before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:097caa7",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: She was far quicker to anger before,[p/] and she never cared much about decorum."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de6b9a",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: She looks so composed and calm now...[p/] It's like she's a totally different person."
}

{
  "id": "line:0469c7e",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: She was terrifying before,[p/] but now it's impossible to read what she's thinking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aabea6",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about your father, Miriam?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e0761",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I'm sure you know a lot about him already.[p/] This trial has made his character [i]very[/i] apparent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efa3e0",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And you don't want to refute any of the statements made against him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e5a46",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "That seemed like a sore spot for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8ab68",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Player: William's Modified Will"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d48ba2",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You really have no idea where the draft of the will is?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a42ab",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: No.[p/] It [i]should[/i] have been here."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e9a2a",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Considering the circumstances...[p/] The murderer probably took it."
}

{
  "id": "line:064949e",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Player: Frega Manor Floor 1|Frega Manor Floor 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a12574",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You have quite a large house, Miriam."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d03535",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Many people could only dream of living in this kind of luxury."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce67d4",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: Really?[p/] I find it to be very quiet and empty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccd698",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I much prefer my dorm at the academy.[p/] At least, there are people around there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0397bb5",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Miriam?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00aac8f",
  "node": "Present_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I'm not sure what you're expecting me to say..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cf2fd",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: Come on...[p/] Where is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f6899",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "As we entered William Frega's study,[p/] we spotted a small figure rifling through the drawers of his desk."
}

{
  "id": "line:030b851",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: Why isn't it here...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d4bd9",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: Where else would he put it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe8f29",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Miriam?"
}

{
  "id": "line:052ed32",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c84ae",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "She banged her head before she quickly stood.[p/] She tried to subtly slide the drawers closed,[p/] but I'd seen it clearly."
}

{
  "id": "line:010cae1",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...This is a crime scene.[p/] What are you doing here, Miriam?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdc861",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: A-[p/][s/]As if that's [i]any[/i] of your business."
}

{
  "id": "line:0456cf8",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Considering that [i]I'm[/i] the prosecutor,[p/] it's very much my business."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9ba79",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "I glanced at the knights stationed outside the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ad68c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "They [i]should[/i] have stopped her from entering,[p/] but they were probably intimidated by her status."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d33f91",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "However,[p/] this [i]could[/i] be a blessing in disguise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0525222",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "She was clearly looking for [i]something[/i] in this room,[p/] and I had a feeling that I knew what it was."
}

{
  "id": "line:028a67c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] it looks like we won't be able to find the will."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e0f9f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But the fact that it was taken [i]must[/i] imply something."
}

{
  "id": "line:030fc65",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: For now,[p/] we should follow our other leads."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aba278",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: We still don't know [i]who[/i] committed the murder and how."
}

{
  "id": "line:0042b59",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't we already know the \"how\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df4561",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: The murderer stole the Sword of Spell Eating and used it to break into the study."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fb249",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's true,[p/] but think about how they would have needed to move around the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a3f9a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: The murder took place on the first floor,[p/] within William Frega's study."
}

{
  "id": "line:01928e1",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But the gallery was on the second floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:03dc0ef",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: They would have needed to go upstairs,[p/] steal the sword from the gallery,[p/] and then use it to nullify the lock on the study."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ace28",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not only that,[p/] they would have needed to go back upstairs and plant the sword in Beatrice's room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0173b11",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: About that...[p/] If someone conspired with Beatrice to do this,[p/] why would they plant the sword in her room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08150ba",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's a good point..."
}

{
  "id": "line:048ec07",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe they had a falling out.[p/] Her partner might've tried to betray her by pinning the blame on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef8502",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: But if that was true,[p/] why wouldn't she just sell them out and make a deal with Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:032fd6c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: It would be because of the Slayer Rule."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f159b",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: \"Slayer Rule\".[p/] I remember the guy at the will reading also mentioned that.[p/] What does that mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02793fc",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: It was a law passed by the Crown centuries ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cddff7",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: If someone is involved in another person's death,[p/] even accidentally,[p/] they will not be allowed to inherit the deceased's property."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d1e18",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So even [i]if[/i] Beatrice wasn't directly responsible,[p/] she'd lose her cut of the inheritance if she took a plea deal."
}

{
  "id": "line:061789d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "...More importantly,[p/] it didn't sound like [i]Miriam[/i] believed in Beatrice's innocence either."
}

{
  "id": "line:00733e4",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "If [i]that[/i] was true,[p/] what else could she tell us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a14726",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d72cc",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: No![p/][s/] She would never do that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f7837",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: I-[p/][s/]I'm telling the truth!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09cb6ae",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Miriam: P-[p/][s/]Please![p/][s/] You can't tell Tymora that I told you![p/][s/] She'll ruin me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7f523",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "The Eye showed that her fear is genuine...[p/] She wasn't lying."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d8f64",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Orym: ...I’ve seen how she defends her clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dae307",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Orym: Forgery,[p/] bribery,[p/] blackmail—[p/]she’ll do whatever it takes to win."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f1ea9",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Orym: It doesn’t matter what you say.[p/] I know you’re just like her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0308832",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Those rumors...[p/][s/] Were they really true this whole time?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:043c39e",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "No![p/][s/] Absolutely not!"
}

{
  "id": "line:091550c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey,[p/] Tyrion?[p/] Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a78eb9",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "...Now wasn't the time to doubt myself.[p/] There was too much at stake right now,[p/] and I wasn't done yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0305834",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...We should check on Commander White.[p/] He might have found something."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bda32",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: Um...[p/] Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c6fb7",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Celeste: Just don't push yourself, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0554711",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a3654",
  "node": "Check_Events_Study2",
  "text": "...I'd have plenty of time to think about this later."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cafa45",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Laefe: Miriam, you're back!"
}

{
  "id": "line:032b362",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Miriam: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] Hello, Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0263fb8",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Laefe: How have you been faring?[p/] I heard about what happened to Professor Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2f761",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm terribly sorry.[p/] That must have been an awful ordeal for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0227db0",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Miriam: Yes...[p/][s/] Um—[p/][p/] Thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e75418",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Laefe: But I've heard about your independent studies with the Crown Prince![p/][s/] Father is extremely proud of you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d19c77",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Miriam just scoffed at the obvious lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:02398a7",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Laefe: It's been so long since you've been back at the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:02145de",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Laefe: I was thinking we could have some tea together in the garden before the guests arrive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cacaf4",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Miriam: I-[p/][s/]I am terribly sorry,[p/] but I'm already exhausted from the trip here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6575c",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Miriam: I think I'd like to rest in my room and prepare for the Lords' Ball tonight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2267c",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Laefe: O-[p/][s/]Okay...[p/][s/] But let me know if you change your—"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cf694",
  "node": "TrueStart",
  "text": "Laefe wasn't even finished before her sister walked past her and entered her room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0d985",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ugh...[p/] I feel so out of place here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0217297",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "Despite my [i]clear[/i] issues with Wyverngarde's upper class,[p/] I'd somehow found myself at a party filled with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcc879",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "I hardly recognized anyone,[p/] but from all the looks I was getting,[p/] they clearly recognized me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d38999",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "CDress: Why are you in the corner by yourself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c2a41",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't believe I let you talk me into coming here..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06774aa",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "Tyrion: Everyone is—"
}

{
  "id": "line:037503d",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "...I lost my train of thought."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c222e4",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "CDress: I've been wanting to wear this dress for a while now.[p/] What do you think?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f5c93",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I...[p/] Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a0a37",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "CDress: ...Oh, it's that bad, huh? [h=\"...What am I supposed to do|when he looks at me like that?\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d38bd",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-No...[p/] Um...[p/] You look—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e70a8a",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "Stunning?[p/] Beautiful?[p/] Breathtaking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0327d69",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "Several words came to mind—[p/]all of which would be mortifying if I said them out loud."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a15d4e",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Good.[p/] You look good."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf2cce",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "CDress: Oh,[p/] I look \"good\"? [h=\"That's a start.\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:097233a",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "It's almost as if [i]she[/i] had the ability to read my thoughts."
}

{
  "id": "line:002a5e4",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "...She couldn't actually do that, could she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d24cea",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "I mean [i]I[/i] had the ability to read people's minds,[p/] so logic would dictate that I'm not the only one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c223d3",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "...What if she [i]could[/i] read my mind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ec53a",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "What if she was reading it [i]right now[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae4fc4",
  "node": "TrueStartA",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Am I interrupting something?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03af51c",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: M-[p/][s/]Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:098241f",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "Celeste and I quietly stepped away from each other when my mentor suddenly appeared."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb1a36",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I wanted to check in on you two before we went to meet with the Duke."
}

{
  "id": "line:0845c7c",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "I spotted Ms. Tymora's client following behind her."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c4986",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "It was hard to read her.[p/] The Eye of Horus couldn't glean anything from her mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0101812",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "Her poise barely shifted.[p/] She carried herself with the grace of someone who didn't seem easily rattled."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8c74d",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "Her expression was calm yet distant.[p/] Even when we made eye-contact,[p/] it felt like she was just staring through me."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e61b5",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "This was my first time meeting her,[p/] but she still looked familiar for some reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b3393",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "I extended my hand to shake hers."
}

{
  "id": "line:05df9cb",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "She seemed a little unapproachable.[p/] I hoped that I wasn't being too forward."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c356cf",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "I wasn't sure about the details,[p/] but my mentor was brokering a deal between Beatrice and William Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c3580",
  "node": "TrueStart_1",
  "text": "There were [i]many[/i] elements of that which I found puzzling,[p/] but my mentor was tight-lipped as always."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5bea3",
  "node": "TrueStart_2",
  "text": "Ruby: We're going to head to Frega's study."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b7326",
  "node": "TrueStart_2",
  "text": "Ruby: Can you two stay out of trouble while we're gone?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0616e12",
  "node": "TrueStart_2",
  "text": "CDress: Oh, come on![p/][s/] It's not like we always go [i]looking[/i] for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f1f0e",
  "node": "TrueStart_2",
  "text": "Ruby: ..Yet you two always seem to find trouble anyways."
}

{
  "id": "line:0823b59",
  "node": "TrueStart_2",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert,[p/] we're in a manor filled with the highest members of the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0621910",
  "node": "TrueStart_2",
  "text": "Ruby: You're going to meet some familiar and unfriendly faces."
}

{
  "id": "line:033a7b9",
  "node": "TrueStart_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't worry.[p/] We'll keep it low-profile, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3b178",
  "node": "TrueStart_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So...[p/] Why [i]were[/i] you so insistent on accompanying Ms. Tymora to the Lords' Ball?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfd991",
  "node": "TrueStart_2",
  "text": "CDress: Ah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f94cf1",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You know you can tell me anything, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2144a",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "CDress: Everything that happened in Aurinax made me think about things..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0407e6b",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "CDress: Every noble in the Kingdom attends this ball.[p/] I thought maybe whoever left me at my family's tavern would be here."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e78b5",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "CDress: ...But being here is starting to make me feel weird."
}

{
  "id": "line:098947c",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "CDress: The McCoys are my real family.[p/] Looking for the people who abandoned me feels...[p/] wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:0940621",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don't think that's true."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c5a73",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "CDress: Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2f3c1",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wouldn't be the person I am today without Ms. Tymora,[p/] but I still keep the memory of my mother close to me too."
}

{
  "id": "line:065d95e",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't think it's disrespectful to find out more about yourself,[p/] and I'm sure your mother will understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f4480",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "CDress: You think so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d142ea",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ed707",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And I'm [i]also[/i] sure of another thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0103d80",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: If [i]I'm[/i] with you,[p/] I doubt any of the nobles here will want to speak with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ab271",
  "node": "TrueStart_3",
  "text": "CDress: Yeah...[p/] I didn't want to be rude,[p/] but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4839d",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't worry.[p/] I can find something to fill the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b412c",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "CDress: ...You're just going to play chess alone somewhere, aren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b9d13",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Maybe?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ced2a1",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "CDress: You really need to learn to talk to other people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2606d",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "CDress: Make some new friends or something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e47a83",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...In a room full of nobles?"
}

{
  "id": "line:050c38c",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "CDress: I'm sure they're not all bad.[p/] Aria is pretty great, right?[p/] Aster, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b94c73",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "She had a point,[p/] but I was never really one to make small talk with strangers."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b6e6b",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "I looked around the room of nobles.[p/] I recognized some of them from news articles I had read over the years."
}

{
  "id": "line:044beaa",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "There were also some people there who were around my age.[p/] They must've been the children of the noble heads."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c89120",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "I [i]could[/i] approach them.[p/] Chances were that [i]one[/i] of them wouldn't be an arrogant pig."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff81f6",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "...But the thought of everything that could go wrong was paralyzing."
}

{
  "id": "line:036b60c",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ugh...[p/] It's fine.[p/] I don't need more friends."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bfb28",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I spend most of my time with you anyway.[p/] That's enough for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0022122",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "CDress: W-[p/][s/]Well,[p/] [i]I'm[/i] going to try to talk to some people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa3075",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah.[p/] I'll see you later."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc7059",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "Celeste left to mingle with some of the other partygoers.[p/] I was almost envious of how easily she could do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e515d4",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "I really wished I could strike up conversations with random strangers the same way she could."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd8018",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "...It was fine.[p/] She had her strengths,[p/] and so did I."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c735ed",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "But that only made me wish I could be there with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:09be580",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "Stop it.[p/] She was her own person.[p/] She was perfectly capable of handling herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0459db5",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "I would need to find something pass the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e51705",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "...My hand instinctively went to my satchel."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fbc1c",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "I thought about bringing out my chessboard,[p/] but if I did that here,[p/] I'd just stand out even more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac3f54",
  "node": "TrueStart_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I should try to find somewhere where I can be alone."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ff254",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's as if every room in this house needs a chandelier..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2fe01",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What a waste of gold..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0caf296",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of some adventurers in a tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:056e79c",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Supposedly,[p/] one of Frega's ancestors was part of a band of adventurers."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b35a5",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "But I couldn't help but feel that there [i]should[/i] have been someone in the corner."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca9b70",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ah.[p/] This must be Beatrice Frega the First."
}

{
  "id": "line:066fa2c",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The First?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d67bfd",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: According to legend,[p/] she was one of the descendants of the seven heroes of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:064d517",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: She joined a band of adventurers who were traveling across the nation."
}

{
  "id": "line:011510a",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "It was difficult to imagine the Fregas coming from such humble beginnings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb5f0d",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a88964",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: What is it now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cab132",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That muscular man in the corner...[p/][s/] He just vanished!"
}

{
  "id": "line:056a5df",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: What are you on about?[p/] There was never a man there..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbbfc1",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: He's right."
}

{
  "id": "line:085e794",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: No![p/][s/] I'm [i]sure[/i] he was there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0991286",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you feeling okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0705f4b",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Maybe I was just seeing things...[p/] I really needed to sleep."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ba8e9",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a shelf filled with books."
}

{
  "id": "line:082d427",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]Fake[/i] books.[p/] They're completely blank."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec2d15",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Door"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f04ee3",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a door that leads to the Coat Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:032bd67",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Chair"
}

{
  "id": "line:0737c84",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a chair made from mahogany."
}

{
  "id": "line:0389e1c",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Every part of this house just exudes wealth..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5a377",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Wealth that's been siphoned out of the commonfolk."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f1685",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a window with a view of the outside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0930290",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Von Sanctus's Motive"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0d138",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Main Suspect"
}

{
  "id": "line:0164e72",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You mentioned that other people would benefit from Frega's death.[p/] Who specifically?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0075c1c",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: If I had to venture a guess,[p/] I would say Lucio Steelwind benefits the most."
}

{
  "id": "line:079cc14",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you [i]just[/i] said that the Duke's death could have unimaginable consequences for the economy."
}

{
  "id": "line:071a984",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ha![p/] Do you think that brute [i]cares[/i] about Wyverngarde's economy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d44c50",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: No...[p/] All that man cares about is power—[p/]pure and physical power."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ffa6b",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: House Steelwind and House Frega have been fighting for control of Wyverngarde for generations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0615fb8",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: And in this long-lasting era of peace,[p/] the Steelwinds' military has become far less valuable to the Crown."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b26f6",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: The only thing House Steelwind [i]has[/i] done was completely mishandle these recent insurrections."
}

{
  "id": "line:023b477",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: If it weren't for Lady Steelwind's engagement to the Crown Prince,[p/] they might not even be [i]considered[/i] a Pillar family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0779b41",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: The death of William Frega is probably exactly what Lucio Steelwind has been waiting for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3c4ca",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "That was definitely in line with what I'd heard about the Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a32916",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "It wasn't as if he were a stranger to murder either."
}

{
  "id": "line:034f6b3",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Could this have been another one of his assassinations?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc84bb",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Not to mention,[p/] if our economy were to suffer,[p/] it would slowly create civil unrest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0453fa1",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: In a scenario like that,[p/] the Crown would [i]have[/i] to rely on Steelwind's forces to maintain order."
}

{
  "id": "line:049ddf4",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: And I'm sure you can imagine how [i]that[/i] might turn out."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f2f70",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Other Suspects"
}

{
  "id": "line:096a996",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's clear that you think Lucio Steelwind would have much to gain from this,[p/] but can you think of anyone else?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04eef3f",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Well, there [i]is[/i] Harold Haroldson."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e118a7",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...That [i]can't[/i] be his real name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf1fb5",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But what would Mr. Haroldson possibly gain from Frega's death?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0375517",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: From what I've heard,[p/] William was planning to defund the Haroldson Hall of History."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e13e27",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Really...[p/] Why would he do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dec580",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: I'm not sure of the specifics."
}

{
  "id": "line:06698b9",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Supposedly,[p/] Lord Haroldson has refused to...[p/] omit the less flattering parts of Wyverngarde's history from his exhibits."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8783d",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: It's gotten blatant enough that he's drawn the ire of the king himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b33f1d",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: They actually got into a very heated argument during the Lords' Ball about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:091fd53",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: I heard that William declared he would be removing House Haroldson from his estate."
}

{
  "id": "line:09156b5",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "I didn't want to suspect Mr. Haroldson,[p/] but I needed to examine every possibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ff5ef",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "He had the easiest access to the Sword of Spell Eating,[p/] and he could have staged a robbery to cover his tracks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb2ff0",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice's Return"
}

{
  "id": "line:0685c7c",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you find Beatrice's return to be inconvenient for you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7b82c",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...What are you on about now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b462c0",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Please.[p/] Don't insult my intelligence, von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f49c2",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:081f3ac",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Fine.[p/] If you [i]must[/i] know,[p/] my son was arranged to marry William's daughter:[p/] Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0143e10",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Laefe?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4c635",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Since Beatrice showed no signs of returning,[p/] it was apparent that [i]Laefe[/i] would inherit House Frega instead of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d55a9",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: I know when my days are numbered.[p/] So I took pre-emptive action."
}

{
  "id": "line:00eff92",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: William wanted a male heir,[p/] and [i]I[/i] needed to preserve my House.[p/] So we both came to an accord."
}

{
  "id": "line:015aba8",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: My son and Laefe were arranged to be wed."
}

{
  "id": "line:047f471",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: House von Sanctus would have been absorbed,[p/] but at least my Jaiden would stand at the helm."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b38e6",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You nobles are absolutely awful. [h=\"I should probably consider myself|lucky I was abandoned...\" e=\"s\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:018684b",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Think what you will.[p/] I wouldn't expect a commoner to understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdc6b4",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: That's the problem with your generation.[p/] You have no sense of duty or obligation."
}

{
  "id": "line:076f7c8",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Laefe has already expressed resistance to this marriage.[p/] Even though she was well aware of the details."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f35e7b",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Now I worry she'll hide behind her sister to end the engagement altogether."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bc582",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Laefe never mentioned [i]any[/i] of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:047569c",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "As much as I hated to think it,[p/] William's death could have gotten her out of the arranged marriage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0086cef",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "I needed to talk to her about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1e9e9",
  "node": "LloydBeatConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about the defendant in this case?"
}

{
  "id": "line:021b182",
  "node": "LloydBeatConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: What?[p/] She's [i]your[/i] client.[p/] Surely, you would know her better than I."
}

{
  "id": "line:0def95a",
  "node": "LloydBeatConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Humor me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0261df5",
  "node": "LloydBeatConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: Well, I'm sure you're aware that she fled the Frega estate five years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b0693",
  "node": "LloydBeatConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: In doing so,[p/] she dealt a blow to House Frega's reputation [i]and[/i] directly insulted the Crown Prince by breaking her engagement to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b10ca",
  "node": "LloydBeatConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: It was quite the scandal at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbd412",
  "node": "LloydBeatConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: And Lucio wasted no time in pushing his daughter into taking Beatrice's place."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cbb4e",
  "node": "LloydBeatConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: Honestly,[p/] this situation is just an absolute mess. [h=\"And that woman's return|will complicate things.\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf6265",
  "node": "LloydBeatConv",
  "text": "Beatrice's return would \"complicate things\"?[p/] What did he mean by that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:009d041",
  "node": "LloydLloydConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: Honestly,[p/] it's just one mess after another with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3be88",
  "node": "LloydLloydConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Mess\"?[p/] Wouldn't [i]you[/i] have a lot to gain from William Frega's death?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1dcae",
  "node": "LloydLloydConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: If one only viewed things superficially,[p/] you might be right,[p/] but it's far more complicated than that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d894d9",
  "node": "LloydLloydConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: House Frega controls the banking houses.[p/] They are the main pillar of support for Wyverngarde's economy."
}

{
  "id": "line:03acc9a",
  "node": "LloydLloydConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: William's death could have unimaginable economic consequences,[p/] [i]regardless[/i] of who inherits his house."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d3e87",
  "node": "LloydLloydConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: I wouldn't be foolish enough to do something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5f5de",
  "node": "LloydLloydConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] Think what you will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7ea47",
  "node": "LloydLloydConv",
  "text": "Lloyd: There are others who would benefit from William Frega's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1e360",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Why do you always show this thing to me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0019995",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: To let you know that there will always be people willing to stand up to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d21915",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...You know Von Sanctus Industries manufactures those Runestones, don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef60a6",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: The kingdom distributes those to practicing attorneys."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d60541",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Where did you [i]think[/i] they came from?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c65d35",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "...My world had just been shattered."
}

{
  "id": "line:01972ec",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't let him get to you, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fab189",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]But,[p/] my Runestone—"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c4754",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: —Proves that you're a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e9ed7",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: It doesn't matter where it comes from.[p/] It matters how you use it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e89f52",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd51a3",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b67293",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ugh...[p/] I really hoped that I'd seen the last of you in Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a606aa",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And [i]I[/i] really hope you're not involved in what happened to William Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d56966",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Please.[p/] As if I'd even humor such a preposterous accusation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6ed18",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] As usual,[p/] the Steelwind brat is sticking her nose where it doesn't belong."
}

{
  "id": "line:0092d45",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I take it you're not a fan of House Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8f223",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Fan?[p/] Hardly.[p/] Those brutes have no place in our civilized kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f09a5b",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Have you heard about what Lucio's been doing in the countryside?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f9d2d",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And yet,[p/] I can't help but feel like you'd never say that to her face."
}

{
  "id": "line:05435e9",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ugh...[p/] You [i]and[/i] that woman..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0595c37",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: You two do nothing but weave chaos into the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fd372",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: With how you aristocrats abuse your power,[p/] I'll gladly create as much chaos as I need to."
}

{
  "id": "line:090882c",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: William Frega...[p/] Even in death,[p/] he still remains a thorn in my side."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ed5cd",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: At least now,[p/] he won't meddle in my affairs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd689c",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3db3b",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Laefe|Liafal's Engagement"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc653c",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Laefe...[p/] I'm sure she'll use William's death as yet [i]another[/i] excuse to further avoid her obligations."
}

{
  "id": "line:036898e",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: She just lost her father![p/][s/] What is [i]wrong[/i] with you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c59844",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: William Frega may be dead,[p/] but his daughters must carry out their roles—[p/]lest their House's reputation suffers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfd0d3",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is that all you care about?[p/] The reputation of the noble houses?[p/] What about justice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0783d75",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Justice?[p/] Justice is an illusion that you commoners fruitlessly cling to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef98b3",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: The Frega family has always been influential,[p/] but with William's death,[p/] their power will be diminished."
}

{
  "id": "line:05018b4",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: And with Laefe's reluctance to fulfill her duties,[p/] the Frega name will continue to suffer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4a95e",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: You people are horrible..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e12289",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ah...[p/] Aster do Wyverngarde,[p/] the Crown Prince himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:02073f9",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: I can't say I care much for his childish ideals of justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:030c38d",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Those \"childish ideals\" are the only justice that matters."
}

{
  "id": "line:0043f0f",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's not something the likes of [i]you[/i] would understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f48b0a",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Harold Haroldson...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a496c2",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: I couldn't care less about that quack's personal affairs.[p/] He can find financial aid elsewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0845a06",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Lloyd"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c737dd",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice's Inheritance 0"
}

{
  "id": "line:072b895",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] Beatrice's rebellious nature is only a result of William's terrible parenting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccca11",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: You'd never catch my Jaiden acting like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8f13d",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this, von Sanctus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:010ff3a",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph...[p/] I doubt I can say anything meaningful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0927be7",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Ask someone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d98a6",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "I explored the manor further and found one of its many sitting rooms."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b2abd",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "...And there,[p/] I spotted a [i]very[/i] familiar face."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ca909",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "He was sipping on a glass of wine,[p/] and his indifferent expression turned into a sneer the moment I entered the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:08689c2",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Oh...[p/] wonderful.[p/] As if my day couldn't have gotten [i]any[/i] worse."
}

{
  "id": "line:00719bb",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Von Sanctus.[p/] What are [i]you[/i] doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a295c",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: The head of a noble house has just been murdered.[p/] I can't very well return to Aurinax when my affairs are in such disarray."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d7187",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I hear that you've been busy since we last met.[p/] It must be difficult losing your empire to House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:041b5f7",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] We [i]do[/i] need his testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec3a16",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: Is that so?[p/] And what makes you think I'd [i]ever[/i] help the likes of you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:086c814",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because it would take suspicion off of you,[p/] and with your reputation,[p/] you could probably use all the help you can get."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e65d2",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: How dare you![p/][s/] I'll have you know that I am still a respected member of the nobility!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6a1bf",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Respected\"?[p/] Is [i]that[/i] why the papers keep talking about your plot to blow up Aurinax?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02dc935",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because the way I see it,[p/] being involved in [i]another[/i] scandal would destroy what's left of your reputation,[p/] but it makes no difference to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5d0b2",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: To be perfectly honest,[p/] I'd like nothing more than to drag you onto the stand and embarrass you a [i]third[/i] time."
}

{
  "id": "line:01243b9",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "All he could do was grumble under his breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0178f67",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Very well."
}

{
  "id": "line:007cf99",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Lloyd: If it means I won't have to suffer your presence any longer,[p/] I'll oblige and answer your questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d02661",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "Von Sanctus gave us a decent list of suspects."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ed9a0",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "I probably learned everything I could from him for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0079c58",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom1",
  "text": "It'd be best to MOVE and follow up on those leads."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b3caf",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What a waste of the kingdom's gold..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e1f9b",
  "node": "Examine_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "And that wealth was probably siphoned right out of the commonfolk..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f8d52",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion and Celeste"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ee51f",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "...If looks could kill."
}

{
  "id": "line:06dc2f6",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: McCoy...[p/] One might misinterpret that look of yours as murderous intent."
}

{
  "id": "line:03630ef",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: Aw...[p/] Guess you [i]do[/i] have some battle instincts, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adb847",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: I honestly wasn't sure.[p/] Since you so [i]obviously[/i] have a silver spoon stuck up your—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0996ea7",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: C-[p/][s/]Celeste..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ce7e3",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Such lack of respect and discipline..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3b6f8",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: If you were one of my soldiers,[p/] I'd have you hung."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ceb975",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: If I were one of your soldiers,[p/] I'd hang myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a34b3",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Anyways[/i],[p/] Grand General.[p/] You were here at the Lords' Ball when the murder occurred."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e121a3",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...I was."
}

{
  "id": "line:040d8d9",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you mind if I ask you some questions about what you saw that night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:083a247",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:095fc4e",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]If that's okay with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0521409",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: You don't need to be scared of this guy, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:017d7dc",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "That was easy for [i]her[/i] to say."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb4d12",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: I suppose I must oblige...[p/] Considering that my daughter has so unceremoniously thrust her responsibilities onto you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0791a90",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Player: Aria Steelwind"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0d90d",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry about what happened to your daughter.[p/] I'm sure that you're very worried."
}

{
  "id": "line:051544f",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Hmph...[p/] It's her own fault for exerting herself despite her injuries."
}

{
  "id": "line:07097af",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: There's a clear line between bravery and foolishness."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ed7eb",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: How can you say that?![p/][s/] Your daughter did everything she could to see justice done!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03198f5",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: By prosecuting the heiress of House Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0392fc3",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: She had very little evidence to substantiate a conviction."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9ccc9",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: If she wanted to strike a blow to a rival house,[p/] she should have made sure her first attack would be her last."
}

{
  "id": "line:0894cd3",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: But now...[p/] If Beatrice Frega is found innocent,[p/] any hopes of an alliance between House Frega and House Steelwind will be completely annihilated."
}

{
  "id": "line:005a36e",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Where were you throughout the night, Grand General?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4241d",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: I so loathe gatherings like that,[p/] and I couldn't do with all the badgering about the recent news."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d0b44",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: I was in this room,[p/] but then I received word that the Duke's lost heiress made an unexpected appearance."
}

{
  "id": "line:090d66d",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: She was supposedly speaking with the Crown Prince.[p/] So I made my way to the Ballroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd23ef",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you speak with them at any point?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f4c4d",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: No.[p/] I kept my distance and stayed near the Kingsguard. [h=\"I needed to make sure she wouldn't try anything.\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0451340",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Was this because you were wary of Beatrice Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a3194",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...Anyone who knew Beatrice Frega would be wary of her,[p/] and her allegiance with Ruby Tymora is only more concerning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f70e36",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: The Crown Prince has always been a bleeding heart,[p/] and the Fregas are taught to sharpen their tongues from birth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0650bc0",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: I needed to make sure that she wouldn't try to interfere with his engagement to my daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e046e3",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were worried that she was going to try to take Aster back."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fe1a7",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: I was,[p/] but it was clear that wasn't her intention."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f3554",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you [i]did[/i] overhear their conversation?[p/] What were they talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ce793",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Their conversation was completely inane.[p/] It was all just small talk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0142497",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Lady Frega spent most of her time entertaining Prince Alaric."
}

{
  "id": "line:0906c6d",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Right...[p/] The younger prince was there too."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c76ad",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice's Alibi"
}

{
  "id": "line:073c030",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "I knew that Beatrice had [i]some[/i] role in the murder,[p/] even if she wasn't directly responsible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9b2a4",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Did she have some goal when speaking to the two princes?[p/] Was she trying to establish an alibi?"
}

{
  "id": "line:044a880",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You went to the Ballroom when you heard that Beatrice had returned."
}

{
  "id": "line:00259ec",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was this before or after the lockdown?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb97cd",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: It was before the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:062d289",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "That sounded about right.[p/] That meant that she was present before the theft was reported."
}

{
  "id": "line:0716992",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And did you see her leave at any point?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6201f",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: No.[p/] She spoke with the two princes for quite a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1ae22",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: She didn't leave their side until she was arrested for the Duke's murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ef5a3",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "So she was accounted for the [i]entire[/i] night."
}

{
  "id": "line:063b12c",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "But her thoughts said that she was an accomplice in William's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed4c29",
  "node": "Talk_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "How did she participate if she was with the princes the whole time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0464a41",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's an Attorney's Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee1389",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It proves that I'm a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd296f",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...I don't understand what you want from me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0504b35",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion|Ruby"
}

{
  "id": "line:083b4ea",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'd have thought that someone of your standing would barely notice someone like me."
}

{
  "id": "line:00455f9",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: I knew of you well before Aurinax—[p/]the infamous Ruby Tymora as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:050e90e",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:027e275",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: I also know that my daughter has failed to defeat you even a single time."
}

{
  "id": "line:020c9a6",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: I await the day when she tears you down from your throne."
}

{
  "id": "line:0864152",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:098d3ac",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "...I thought he disapproved of her becoming a prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0221efb",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Celeste McCoy:[p/] the Crimson Demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:033b01b",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: How do people keep learning about that name?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ab354",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Please.[p/] House Steelwind secures the borders of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a12c88",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Don't think I'm unaware of your illegal travels to the Eastern Kingdoms."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccb915",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah.[p/] You want to arrest me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0460c99",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: Try it.[p/] See how that goes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf9a2e",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Can you stop antagonizing him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f08cf",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've heard you don't approve of Aria becoming a prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a0ba0",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Of course I don't."
}

{
  "id": "line:0615194",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: A member of House Steelwind shouldn't debase themselves by doing the work of a civil servant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bba1b1",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But she clearly has her own motivations for doing so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bab64e",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Hmph...[p/] Is [i]that[/i] how you see it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb75cc",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: She's merely following the misguided path of the Crown Prince. [h=\"I regret bringing|those two together.\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06056aa",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice|Beatrice's Blindness|Beatrice's Alibi"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e16213",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Beatrice Frega is a remarkable mage.[p/] It's truly a shame that [i]this[/i] is how it turned out."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ce56a",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm...[p/] surprised to hear you say that.[p/] I assumed most in the nobility hated her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c27b04",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: If you're correct,[p/] then most of the nobility are imbeciles."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8a79b",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: At the age of thirteen,[p/] she surpassed her father's magical talents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbdb6f",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: If she had been allowed to develop,[p/] she could have revolutionized the study of [b]conjuration[/b] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e99766",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: She would have been a great asset to our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:033b02d",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Ever the pragmatic one, wasn't he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0098f40",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: William Frega...[p/] A fool to the very end."
}

{
  "id": "line:09342fe",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: From what I've heard,[p/] you two weren't on the best of terms."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c2b78",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Hmph...[p/] That fool believed that every problem in our kingdom could be solved with gold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f00b45",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: He failed to see the exterior threats posed to our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c55caa",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: What this kingdom needs is a sharp weapon and an iron fist to wield it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da7776",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What are your thoughts on Crown Prince Aster?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ace27",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: He has misguided ideals of justice,[p/] but I suppose he's still young."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc9136",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: But I do worry for our future under his rule. [h=\"The king's health|is worsening...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d895e6",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Wait...[p/][s/] What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06528b9",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "I'd never heard [i]anything[/i] about King Olivier being ill."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f8f26",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Perhaps it'd be best not to mention it,[p/] he'd demand to know how I found out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb4587",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "He seemed to know about the Eye of Horus,[p/] but he probably wouldn't take kindly to me reading his mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c1fa1",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've been told that House Steelwind controls Wyverngarde's military."
}

{
  "id": "line:067da1c",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Hmph...[p/] We don't [i]control[/i] the military."
}

{
  "id": "line:036578c",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: We control the very foundation that maintains order in our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:064d145",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Those fools in the palace or the House of Lords have no idea what it takes to lead a nation."
}

{
  "id": "line:037ce5b",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: These recent commonfolk uprisings are evidence of that fact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a407e9",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Lord Haroldson...[p/] I can't believe it took this long for William to deal with his defiance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a943c2",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: But if it were up to me,[p/] I'd have the old fool executed for treason."
}

{
  "id": "line:04187bd",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "...He must only see nails with that gigantic hammer of his."
}

{
  "id": "line:09594e7",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice's Inheritance 0|Beatrice's Inheritance 1|Beatrice's Inheritance"
}

{
  "id": "line:0883f1d",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: What a mess this is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3ff4f",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Aria's actions have completely sabotaged our political relations with House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f86fa",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Beatrice Frega would have been a powerful weapon for me to use."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eafd0a",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "It almost sounds like he respects Beatrice.[p/] How powerful a mage is she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d99b7",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Ms. McCoy.[p/] That sword of yours is of Eastern make, isn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0875fff",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: I [i]do[/i] wonder how someone of [i]your[/i] status earned the favor of an Ixian regent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee6ece",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait, what?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4dc12",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I'll tell you that story later."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b08d9d",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this, Lord Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0560153",
  "node": "Present_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...Completely inane.[p/] What else do you expect me to say?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa3d83",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "As we moved around the manor,[p/] I peeked into the Sitting Room to see if von Sanctus was still there."
}

{
  "id": "line:01abc73",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "I didn't see [i]him[/i] there.[p/] but I spotted the Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af3d79",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: This aura... [h=\"An enemy...?|Here?!\" e=\"af\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:084c05d",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: You must be daft if you think I wouldn't notice your presence, Luminite!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e30bcb",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "W-[p/][s/]What?[p/] Did he notice us?[p/] I was barely inside the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0558d94",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Before I had a chance to respond,[p/] Lucio grabbed the handle of his great-axe and charged towards us."
}

{
  "id": "line:05be6a5",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "He swung his weapon,[p/] using it's hefty weight to propel him forward and close the distance between us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0751122",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Wait, I—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8643b",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "I brought up my arms to block his blow,[p/] but in hindsight,[p/] that probably wouldn't have done much against a weapon that large."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0c5c9",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: [b]Protegus[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:05aa0e7",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "I opened my eyes.[p/] Celeste was now standing between the Grand General and me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2500e",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "I'm not sure what happened,[p/] but it looks like she'd knocked him several feet back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0570a29",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1c90a",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Oh, it's you two."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c733d6",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: That's all you have to say?![p/][s/] You could have killed him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aacc1f",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: He shouldn't have snuck up on me like that.[p/] I almost cleaved him in two."
}

{
  "id": "line:0604b7d",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]Tyrion[/i] didn't do anything wrong![p/][s/] Who the hell do you think you are?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:051bb40",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: ... [h=\"What happened?|Why is his aura so much stronger?\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0869690",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] it's fine.[p/] I'm not hurt."
}

{
  "id": "line:0215d5b",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "She looked more than a little irate right now,[p/] but she begrudgingly put away her sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0843877",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "...The Grand General was one of the people with a motive to murder William Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef7a6c",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Not to mention that he was clearly no stranger to violence."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c7f85",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "He might know something.[p/] At the very least,[p/] he might have some knowledge about William and his affairs."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ef77f",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thank you for answering our questions, Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb9da8",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: Hmph...[p/] I'm merely repaying my daughter's debt to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddc8ba",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "He'd been surprisingly cooperative,[p/] but that didn't lift any suspicion off of him just yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b12058",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "I would need to find more evidence if I wanted to know for sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0066974",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] we should probably MOVE somewhere else.[p/] Let's go, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e3617",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e05638",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...Your spell casting is undisciplined,[p/] but your battle stance and reflexes are commendable."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a93c1",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: You have my respect as a warrior."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d11e7",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...As if that means anything coming from you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7eafe",
  "node": "Check_Events_WaitingRoom2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...Hmph.[p/] What an undisciplined and defiant brat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4ca70",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "For the first time since the Lords' Ball,[p/] I was finally able to get some sleep."
}

{
  "id": "line:0248364",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "I woke up this morning refreshed,[p/] but also a little anxious about the results of the will reading."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e7bf1",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "We arrived back at Frega Manor.[p/] Beatrice,[p/] Laefe,[p/] Miriam,[p/] [i]and[/i] von Sanctus had all been gathered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0400752",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": ":...Along with Ms. Tymora:[p/] who was accompanying Beatrice as her attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c5877",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "I wasn't really sure what to say to her after everything that had happened..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02eee2c",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "The air still felt too awkward to approach her and talk about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a722bf",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Nobleman: Thank you all for coming here today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa3740",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Nobleman: As William Frega's close associate,[p/] I must express my deepest condolences for your loss."
}

{
  "id": "line:003adba",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Nobleman: I think I speak for all of Wyverngarde when I say—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb49a8",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Miriam: ...Enough.[p/] Just get on with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:085ee13",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Nobleman: [i]*Ahem*[/i][p/] Very well, then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d596f4",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Nobleman: To get straight to the point,[p/] the Duke's will was magically sealed when it was given to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0273af7",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Nobleman: He asked me:[p/] his executor,[p/] not to submit it to the courts for probate until [i]after[/i] his death."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a0ff2",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Nobleman: Although I imagine none of us expected such a time to come so suddenly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0d896",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "The attorney opened the sealed envelope and quickly scanned over the will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc2e48",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Nobleman: The Duke's assets included sole ownership of several banking houses throughout Wyverngarde,[p/] the equivalent of ten million gold in various investments..."
}

{
  "id": "line:029f70d",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Celeste: Ten million...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee352a",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Ten-million gold...[p/] I couldn't even begin to imagine what [i]anyone[/i] could do with that amount of wealth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8e028",
  "node": "WillReading",
  "text": "Nobleman: And lastly,[p/] sole control and ownership of the Frega Noble House."
}

{
  "id": "line:09683fb",
  "node": "WillReading2",
  "text": "Nobleman: \"I,[p/] William Frega,[p/] being of sound mind and body,[p/] do hereby declare this to be my Last Will and Testament.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0c516ec",
  "node": "WillReading2",
  "text": "Nobleman: \"I hereby give,[p/] devise,[p/] and bequeath all of my assets and property,[p/] both real and personal,[p/] to Jaiden von Sanctus...\""
}

{
  "id": "line:045c8de",
  "node": "WillReading2",
  "text": "Nobleman: \"...provided that he enters into a legal and binding engagement with my daughter,[p/] Laefe Frega:[p/] within six months of the date of my death.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0e76e22",
  "node": "WillReading2",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...What?![p/][s/] That's—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:077c4d9",
  "node": "WillReading2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aac64d",
  "node": "WillReading2",
  "text": "William must have added that addendum to prevent von Sanctus from trying to steal his empire."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ea7ae",
  "node": "WillReading2",
  "text": "But that \"legal and binding engagement\" was predicated on Laefe accepting it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f08a76",
  "node": "WillReading2",
  "text": "She clearly didn't want to go through with it.[p/] So if she simply waited six months,[p/] von Sanctus [i]wouldn't[/i] have any claim to the estate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b28fb2",
  "node": "WillReading2",
  "text": "Nobleman: \"In the event that Jaiden von Sanctus does [i]not[/i] enter into such an engagement within the specified time frame,[p/] my assets and property shall be distributed as such.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0a35468",
  "node": "WillReading2",
  "text": "Nobleman: \"All of House Frega will be divided equally among my children,[p/] as per the laws of our kingdom.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec7667",
  "node": "WillReading2",
  "text": "I was right.[p/] William Frega never disinherited Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:094b723",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "And since Beatrice [i]would[/i] receive a portion of William's inheritance,[p/] she had a motive to commit the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f48d7",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "I glanced at Miriam.[p/] It was hard to read her expression,[p/] but something appeared to be on her mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b601af",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "Without a word,[p/] she walked out of the room,[p/] ignoring both Beatrice and Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:03bc819",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "...Laefe,[p/] on the other hand,[p/] seemed to be in good spirits."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f33f4f",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "Laefe: Isn't this great, Beatrice?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0468f3d",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "Laefe: You can lead House Frega now![p/][s/] Just as it should have been!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b73b0",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "Nobleman: Regarding that.[p/] In light of recent events,[p/] I believe I should clarify one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26f2e",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "Nobleman: As per the \"Slayer Rule\",[p/] if Beatrice Frega is found guilty in the current court case,[p/] her inheritance will be revoked and divided between you and your sister."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5432b",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "Laefe: I-[p/][s/]I see... [h=\"I shouldn't feel|so happy for myself...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:038d1ca",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "Lloyd: That can't be all, can it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:053add7",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "Lloyd: [i]Surely[/i] William added a note of Laefe's obligation to marry my son!"
}

{
  "id": "line:075af95",
  "node": "WillReading3",
  "text": "Nobleman: I'm not sure what you're trying to imply."
}

{
  "id": "line:00831c6",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Nobleman: Laefe Frega is an adult with legal autonomy.[p/] She is free to make whatever decision she wishes about who she legally marries."
}

{
  "id": "line:089e561",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Nobleman: Now if you'll excuse me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc5981",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Lloyd: Wait![p/][s/] We're not finished yet!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7012e",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Lloyd: Come back here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08207ce",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Beatrice: I'd love to catch up with you, Laefe,[p/] but I was only allowed out of my cell to attend the reading."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d5571",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "I noticed an Inquisition Knight outside the door.[p/] He seemed to be watching Beatrice intently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2210d",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Beatrice: But don't worry.[p/] I'm sure once this misunderstanding is resolved,[p/] we can talk all we want about our family's future."
}

{
  "id": "line:091b399",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Laefe: Of course!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0868deb",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "A group of knights led Beatrice out of the manor,[p/] and Laefe followed after them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2d411",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "...Leaving Celeste and me alone with Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c84279",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Tyrion: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] About what happened—"
}

{
  "id": "line:081922a",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Ruby: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Look...[p/] I'm not angry, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b69848",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Ruby: It was an...[p/] extremely unforeseen situation,[p/] and Steelwind clearly put you on the spot."
}

{
  "id": "line:047a78e",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Ruby: You felt pressured to do something,[p/] and you made a rash decision."
}

{
  "id": "line:0605951",
  "node": "WillReading4",
  "text": "Ruby: I'm sure the court will understand if you withdraw."
}

{
  "id": "line:09977ab",
  "node": "WillReading5",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert.[p/] You're [i]not[/i] a prosecutor.[p/] You know that, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:040dfd0",
  "node": "WillReading5",
  "text": "Ruby: Didn't you become an attorney to [i]defend[/i] persecuted mages?"
}

{
  "id": "line:017f21f",
  "node": "WillReading5",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]But Beatrice [i]is[/i] guilty.[p/] I [i]saw[/i] it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0840e43",
  "node": "WillReading5",
  "text": "Ruby: I'm not going to argue about this again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5107c",
  "node": "WillReading5",
  "text": "Ruby: You are [i]going[/i] to withdraw.[p/] This is not up for discussion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8eef9",
  "node": "WillReading5",
  "text": "I'd always regarded and respected Ms. Tymora.[p/] She'd never steered me wrong before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e367cf",
  "node": "WillReading5",
  "text": "Maybe she was right...[p/] Maybe she knows more about what's going on than I did,[p/] and she was still my mentor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e670fa",
  "node": "WillReading5",
  "text": "I [i]wanted[/i] to believe that.[p/] I really did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b96e42",
  "node": "WillReading5",
  "text": "But deep down,[p/] I knew that this was wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfd3c0",
  "node": "WillReading5",
  "text": "Ms. Tymora may believe in Beatrice's innocence,[p/] but I couldn't just abandon this case and let her escape justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:03087e3",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Ruby: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:015fef6",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not going to withdraw.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfd8c7",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you believe in Beatrice's innocence,[p/] and if you truly believe you're on the right side..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ac2ce",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Then prove it by beating me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c74c6",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Fine.[p/] Do whatever you want,[p/] but you're only going to make everything more difficult for everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:033f533",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d0d93",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "As soon as Ms. Tymora stepped out of the room,[p/] my body dropped to the floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c3180",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Whatever bravery I felt before got replaced with an extreme amount of fatigue."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e4cc4",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Scaled Lord...[p/] That's the first time I've ever spoken to her like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9e186",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Celeste: But you still did it.[p/] You stood your ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:03228af",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Figuratively,[p/] I mean...[p/] Right now,[p/] you're kind of just sitting on the floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0267d70",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] I need to take a moment.[p/] Can we go back to the ballroom?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad9b9d",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Orym: Hey, so...[p/] I didn't want to interrupt whatever [i]that[/i] was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d87879",
  "node": "WillReading6",
  "text": "Celeste: Just follow us to the ballroom, Orym!"
}
